engTitle: Praise God, from Whom All Blessings Flow
verse1:
Thupha kheempeuh hong pia Pasian
Phat un, leitung mi khempeuh aw
Phat un vantung mi honpi'n zong
Phat un Pa, Ta le Kha Siangtho

engTitle: The King of Love My Shepherd Is (Dominus Regit Me)
verse1:
Itna Kumpi, ka tuu-cingpa
Ama hoihna sia ngeilo
A mi suak leng sapna om lo
Tawntung Ama mi hi ta
verse2:
Nuntakna tui a luanna ah
Tat khiatsa ka kha tonpih
Lo no naah hong paipih hi
Vantung an tawh hong vaak hi
verse3:
Khuamial sihna kuam sung lau lo
Kei kiang Topa Na om hi
Ka lung nuam sak, Na ciangkhut in
Lam hong hilh singlamteh in
verse4:
Ni sim tawntung kizom suak in
Na hoihna kipelh ngeilo
Tuu-cing siampa, Nang kong phat hi
Tawntung Nangma innpi sung Amen

verse1:
Vantung zahtak huai Kumpipa bia un
A vaanglian leh hong itna la sa un
A hong liah hong keem hong uk tawntung maangpi
A vaanglian hi, ci in phat huai Topa hi
verse2:
Hongit hong hehpihna van pan taang a
A vaang liatna thu la in sa unla
A heh ciangin kekkia tawh kibang ding hi
A thu khenna in haksa mahmah ding hi
verse3:
Na lamdang tawh a dim leitung in ah
Vaanglian tawntung tawh Pasian a hong piang
Pel ngeilo na hanciamna tawh a kip hi
Puan bangin a kiimkot tuipi hi sak hi
verse4:
Naupang bangin thanem leivui tate
Nang sungah muan'na bukna kong mu diam
Nong hehpihna kicing a tawp dong in ah
Hong bawl pa, hong dal pa, hong gumpa i Lawm

zoTitle: Pa Tung Min Than'na Om Hen
verse1:
Pa tung min than'na om hen
Tapa tung leh Kha Siangtho tung ah zong
Piancil lai leh tuhun bangin
A tawntung in hih leitung om den ding hi
Amen Amen

engTitle: Now Thank We All Our God
verse1:
Lungsim khut le kam tawh Pasian tung i lungdam hi
A bawl lamdangte tawh leitung kheempeuh lungdam hi
Nute' ang pan kipan Tuni ciang dong takin
Ki gentheilo itna'n Hong keem thupha takin
verse2:
A cingh, migi Pasian I khan tawntung hong nai hen
Lungdam lung nopna siang Hong ompih sak tawntung hen
A hehpihna sungah Lungman' ciang lamlak hen
Lei pan vantung dongah A sia hong pel sak hen
verse3:
Pa Pasian le Tapa, Amau tawh maang Kha Siangtho
Tu'n phatna lungdamna Van saangbel ah i puak to
Leitung, vantung, tawntung Amah bek biakna pia'n
 Tuma, tulai, tunung Amah khat bek Pasian

zoTitle: Pasian’ Vaang Liatna Ka Phat Nuam Hi!
engTitle: Oh Could I Speak the Matchless Wotth!
verse1:
Hong gum Topa tungah a taang
A lian tawntung mahmah a vaang
Phat ding kahto thei leng,
Vantung leeng to in gawsem tawh
A lamdang la ka sa ding ta
Gabela dem nuam ing
Gabela dem nuam ing
verse2:
Mawhna pan hong tat khiat na’ngin
Zeisu’n A si hongbua zo hi
Pasian lungdam na’ngin
Ama vaanglian a siangtho na
A dem zo om kei, a siamna
La pha sa tawntung ni
La pha sa tawntung ni
verse3:
A saang vantung tokhom tungah
Tu in a om hong uk Topa
Zeisu a hong itna
A ngaih mahmah la awte tawh
A vaanglian phatna la sakna
Keimah ka hilh ding hi
Keimah ka hilh ding hi
verse4:
Lungdam huai Ama maitangpi
Hong mu in ci’n a hong sap ni
A hong tung lai ding hi
Hong it manin zawhna ngah a
Hong gum Zeisu ka u kiangah
Ka om tawntung ding hi

engTitle: How Sweet the Name of Jesus Sounds
verse1:
Zeisu a min bangzah ngaih hiam
A um ta dingin ah
Gimna, natna damask a nuam
Launa a hawlkhia ta
verse2:
A zan gawp lungsim damsak hi
Dahna lungsim nuamsak
Kha Siangtho kial vahna pia hi
A gim mi tawl damsak
verse3:
A to suangpi it huai minpha
Gal panna belhna hi
A tam bel itna hehpihna
A kikholna lian hi
verse4:
Zeisu ka lawmpa, tuu cingpa
Ka siampi, ka Kumpi
Ka Topa hin’na lam a pha na
Phat tawntung ngah pah hi

zoTitle: Hong Pai In, Thupha Nam Kim Nak
engTitle: Come, Thou Fount of Every Blessing
verse1:
Hong pai in, thupha nam kim nak
Ka lungsim hong puahsak in
Kang ngeilo nong hehpihna nak
Nakpi’n hong phat thei sak in
Vantung mite phatna la ngaih
Kei zong hong sa thei nuam ing
Nong itna tung kip ka lungngiah
Tua itna mual ka phat ding
verse2:
Nong huhna tawh hih ciang kong tung
 Huhna mual suang hiah phut ing
Nong deih sakna hangin tu nung
Lung muangin inn hong tung ning
Lam khial a Pasian ka nusia
Ahih hang Zeisu’n hong zong
A si manpha tawh hon tankhia
Gimna lauhuai pan hong hon
verse3:
A nisim in hong hehpihna
A tampi hong ba sak den
Na hehpih na’n hong khih inla
Na kiang pan hong pial sak ke’n
Topa kong vak san dek zeel hi
Ka it Pasian, hong keem in
Hiah! Ka lungsim, Nang sung seel ni
Nang aading na ciamteh in

verse1:
Leitung ah om mihing te aw
Pasian phatna la sa un la
A vaangliatna thu gen un la
A mai pai in sa un nopna
verse2:
Amah bek Pasian takpi hi
Mi kheempeuh bawl Topa hi a
Ka tuu te hong suak un, hong ci
Kong keem, kong cing nuam ci in ah
verse3:
Hong itna in bei thei ngei kei
Hong hehpihna om tawntung hi
A thu ciamna sia sak ngei kei
Amin i phat tawntung ding hi
verse4:
Pasian bang hang migi bel hiam
A hong itna maan taktak hi
A thumaan a cilin in om ta
A thumaan a cilin in om ta

verse1:
Hong gum Topa hong it lamdang
Lungdam sin damla ka sa
Kiciamna hong pel sak nuam hi
Singlamteh tung si zo ta
verse2:
Vantung inn nuampi luah nading
A lamdang thupha gen hi
Hong hehpih hong it luat man in
Ka mawh hong phel sak zo hi
verse3:
Hong gum Topa A minthang hi
Nisim la sa in phat ning
Sih ciang mawh tanna mei kuang sung
Hong tung sak nuam lo ding hi
verse4:
Hong gum Topa hong itna pha
La pha ka sak ding ngai hi
Sihna, hin’ tawntungna lam ah
Amah tawh ka om ding hi
chorus:
Topa phatna sak ding la pha
A sipha tawh hong sawp hi
Singlamteh tung sihna thuak a
Ka mawh hong phel sak zo hi

crossrefs: (Kilakna 4:8), R.Herber, D.D.(1783-1826), SS.22 Dr. J.B. Dykes, (1823-1876)
verse1:
Siangtho, Siangtho, Siangtho! A lianpen To Pasian!
Zingsang tungin phatna la kong sak to ding uh hi
Siangtho, Siangtho, Siangtho! Hehpih thei a vanglian!
Thum kigawmna siangtho thupha Pasian!
verse2:
Siangtho, Siangtho, Siangtho! Na mi siang khempeuh in
Kham lukhu te suah khia in Nangmah hong bia uh hi
Vantung mihing te in Nangma mai ah kun in
Tawntung Pasian Nangmah hong bia uh hi
verse3:
Siangtho, Siangtho, Siangtho! Khuamial hong liah hangin
Mawhna mit in Na vanglian hong mu thei lo hangin
Nangmah bek na siangtho Kua mah’n hong ban zo lo
Na vangliatna, Itna le Sian’ tho na
verse4:
Siangtho, Siangtho, Siangtho! A lian pen To Pasian!
Leitung, tuitung, vantungah Na min kiphat ding hi
Siangtho, Siangtho, Siangtho! Hehpih thei a vaanglian!
Thum kigawmna siangtho thupha Pasian!

verse1:
Ngai in, ka kha aw, vantung mi la sakna
Leitung lungdam tuipi tung zong thang hi
La pha sakna a aw zaknop huai bel hi
Hing kikheel mawh kiphelna thu gen hi
verse2:
La aw zak ciang mailam nawtin i pai hi
Lungkham a gimte aw hong pai un ci
Khuamial sungah Topa Zeisu kiko hi
Vantung inn lam hilhna thupha aw hi
verse3:
Gamlapi ah nitak siklong ging bangin
Leitung, tuitung ah Zeisu aw ging hi
Tul then thamlo a van lel mi tampi in
Tuu cing Topa aw Na kiang kong pai hi
verse4:
Tu laitak I lungkham a sawt hangin ah
Khuamial kheng leeng nuam na’ng khuavaak ding hi
A gimte zuihna lam a bei ciangin ah
Kha Siangtho maang ding kham gam tung ding hi
chorus:
Thu ciamna cing kham vantung mihingte in
A aw zak nop huai in la sa uh hi
Nitak kap a zingsang lungdam sak hi
Sawtvei khuamial itna khuavaak sak in

verse1:
Leitung mihingte aw en un
Dahna thuak Zeisu a hi
A gal kheempeuhte zo gawp zo
Mi kheempeuh in bia uh hi
verse2:
Vantung a mihing kheempeuh in
Topa Zeisu min phat hi
Thukhen tokhom tung tusak a
Vantung mite’n phatsak hi
verse3:
Migilo te’n ling tawh kigan
Lukhu Zeisu khusak hi
Mi siangtho leh vantung mite’n
Tu’n Zeisu a min phat hi
verse4:
A min phatin ah kiko un
Galzo pawikhaamna ngai un
Topa Zeisu in maan ngah hi
Lungdam huai bel hi, en un
chorus:
Kumpi lukhu, kumpi lukhu
Topa Zeisu khusak un
Kumpi lukhu, kumpi lukhu
Topa Zeisu khusak un

verse1:
Pa aw, ka kikhen uh ciang
Ko lungsim Nang deih bang hi ta hen
Thungetna (Prayer)
Eite khat leh khat, i kikhen ciangin,
Topa Pasian in, i omna ciat-ah,
Hong keen tawntung ta hen, Amen!

engTitle: Praise to the Lord, the Almighty
verse1:
Topa phat un, na kheempeuh a piangsak
Kumpipa hi! Aw, ka kha aw
Amah phat in damna gupna hong pia!
Tua thu zate’n a biakkinn sungzuan dingin
Amah va bia khawm ciat ve ni
verse2:
Topa phat un, na kheempeuh a vekpi Ama uk hi
A kha nuai ah tawldam
Lungmuan' nopsakna a hong pia
Na deih nai hiam A hoihna na muh ciangin
Ama hong piak kheempueh thei ni
verse3:
Topa phat un, na sepna bawlna kheempeuh hong huh hi
A maan takin hehpihna leh nopna tawh hong khuh dia
Lung ngaingai in, Amah tha hatna thei in
Amah tawh va kipawl thei ni

zoTitle: Topa Thupha Sang Nuam I Kikhawm Hi
engTitle: We Gather Together to Ask the Lord’s Blessing
verse1:
Topa thupha saang nuam ngen in i kikhawm hi
Ama deihna theih nading manlang hong puak
Dawi net cip thuak nate tu’n bei in lung nuam ta
Amin phatna la sa, A mi mangngilh lo hi
verse2:
Eite lam hong lak ding, Pasian i kiang hong om
A vantung gam puakin a siangtho sak hi
Tua ahih man in, a kipat pan gal i zo
Ko lam aa hong pang Topa, Na min thang ta hen
verse3:
Na min kong phat uh hi, Galzo makai pipa
Kote hong dal hong keem ding kong ngen uh hi
Zeetna tawh mite hong kipelh sak in
Na min kiphat den hen! Topa hong gum in

zoTitle: Pasian Naseemte Aw, Na Topa’n Gen Khia
engTitle: Ye sercants of God, Your Master Proclaim
verse1:
Pa na seemte aw, gamlapi zeel un
Topa’n thangsak hi, lamdang Ama min
Na kheempeuh a zo min Zeisu ahi hi
Ama gam in zai a na kheempeuh uk hi
verse2:
Thahat Pasian in gum ding van pan uk
Amah’n hong zuan hi, A kiang i om hi
Mihon tampi’n zong zawhna la sa uh hi
Ei hong gum Kumpipa Zeisu hi, ci hi
verse3:
Kumpi tokhom tung hong Gumpa Pasian
Vekpi in phat hi, A Tapa phat hi
Vantung mite’n zong Zeisu a phat uh hi
Tuuno mai bok in, Amah a bia uh hi
verse4:
Ei zong phat tek ni, A vaangliatna thu
A min than’na thu, A pilna, hatna
Phatna leh thupha tawh i phat tek ding hi
Van pan vantung mi’n tawntung itna phat hi

verse1:
Zing ni suak sensan ta
Ka lungsim khanglo lo
Zeisu Khazih phat huai!
Na seem ding, thungen ding
Zeisu kiang va zuan ning
Zeisu Khazih phat huai!
verse2:
Lungsung dahna om hiam
Hih-ah ka dahna kiam
Zeisu Khazih phat huai!
Leitung nuamna bei le
Hehnepna om veve
Zeisu Khazih phat huai!
verse3:
Vantung lungdamna ah
La a ngaih pen hih mah!
Zeisu Khazih phat huai!
Khuamial vaangte’n kihta
A zak uh ciang hihla
Zeisu Khazih phat huai!
verse4:
Leitung ka hin’ lai teng
Sa ning ka sih mateng
Zeisu Khazih phat huai!
Sih ciang vantung tung leng
Ka la hih mah hi leng
Zeisu Khazih phat huai!

zoTitle: Zeisu! Na Min Ngaih Ka It Hi
engTitle: Jesus! I Love Thy Charming Name
verse1:
Zeisu! Na min ngaih ka it hi
Bil in tua la ka za
Nakpi pi in ging khia sak in
Vantung leitung thawn in
verse2:
Ka kha aading Nang Na manpha
Ka lampi leh ka muan’
Nangma mai ah suang manphate,
Milim no zep bang hi
verse3:
Ka deih teng leh ka ut kheempeuh
Nang sungah kimtak om
Kei mit in kiman lo sa keng
Lawmtak lo bang sa keng
verse4:
Na hehpihna ka lung sung teeng
A namtuina hong bua
Liamma kheempeuh a damsak thei
Itna tawh hong keem hi

verse1:
Kong phat uh hi, Topa tuzan
Na thupha khuavaak hong pia in
Hong keem in, aw, kei hong keem in
Na vaanglian Kumpi kha nuai ah
verse2:
Zeisu min in hong maisak in
Tuni dong ka mawhna sa te
Hih leitung ah Nang leh kei bek
Nuam takin hong ihmu sak in
verse3:
Nuntakna lam kei hong hilh in
Tua hi kei leh kei ka si ding
Sihna ding thu kei hong hilh in
Thu khenni ciang thawh kikna thu
verse4:
Ka kha Nang kiang hong la in la
Nuam tak kei hong ihmu sak in
Tua in kei hong thahat sak in
Ka thawh kik ciang Topa phat ning

zoTitle: Hong Khihna In A Pha Hi
engTitle: Blest be the Tie That Binds (Tune: Denis)
verse1:
Ei lung hong khih na ding,
Zeisu itna pha hi
Lung kituakna in vantung khua
Kituakna bang om hi
verse2:
Ei Pa tokhom mai ah
Nakpi thu i ngen hi
Ei lawpna upna deihna teng
A kibangin om hi
verse3:
Ei te’n dahna thuak khawm
Van puakna ki pua hi
Khat veivei i lawmte aading
Khitui a luang thei hi
verse4:
Eite kikhen ciangin
Lungsim dahna piang hi
Hih hang i lungsim tawh om khawm
Nung ciang kimu ding hi

engTitle: Lord, Dismiss Us With Thy Blessing (Tune: Sicitian Mariners)
verse1:
Topa aw, Nangma thupha tawh
Dim in hong kikhen sak in
Nangma itna bang neihna tawh
Hehpihna hong phawksak in
Tha hong guan' aw, tha hong guan’ aw
Hih gam mang sung zin lai in
verse2:
Nangma lungdam thu hangin ah
Nang kong phat uh Topa aw
Ko lungsung leh gamtatna ah’
Na hotna gah lang leh maw
Nang thumaan ah, Nang thumaan ah
Hong kip tawhtung le ung maw
verse3:
Leitung pan in Nong sap peuh ciang
Sihna kihta het loin
Vantung mite’n hong lenpih ciang
Hong man ning lungdam takin
Tawntung Na kiang tawntung Na kiang
Nangmah tawh hong maangsak in

zoTitle: Topa Aw It Huai Na Min Phat Na'ng La!
engTitle: Saviour, Again to Thy Dear Name (Tune: Ellers)
verse1:
Topa aw, it huai Na min phat na’ng la
Lungsim kikhat in kong sa lai uh a
Ko kikhen ma in kong phat khawm uh hi
Nangma thupha kun in kong ngak uh hi
verse2:
Nangma thupha tawh hong ciah sak in la
Na min tawh tuni hong khin sak in la
Ka kam ka muk uh leh ko mau lungsim
Khial lo na dingin Nangmah’n hong cing kim
verse3:
Tuzan khuavaak lungnopna hong guan’ in
Khuamial, ko aading, khuavaak suak sak in
Nang aading sun le zan danglo man in
Na tate launa pan hong keem ta in
verse4:
Leitung nun'tak lai lungnop hong pia in
Dah hong neem in, hong kipsak tawntung in
Ko galdona Nong tawlngak sak tak ciang
Hong sam in tawntung nopna Nangma kiang

zoTitle: Topa A Inn Siangtho Sung Om Hi
engTitle: The Lord Is In His Holy Temple
verse1:
Topa A inn siangtho sung om hi
Topa A inn siangtho sung om hi
Dai dide in om ta un
Dai dide in om ta un
Amai ah, Dai dide’n om ta un
Amai ah, Amen...

zoTitle: Nangmah Tawh pasian Om Khawm Ta Hen
verse1:
Nangmah tawh Pasian om khawm ta hen
A hong pi, a hong len dingin
A tuute hong keem bit dingin
Nangmah tawh Pasian om khawm ta hen
verse2:
Nangmah tawh Pasian om khawm ta hen
A kha nuai hong liah hong dal in
Nisim "Manna" hong vaak dingin
Nangmah tawh Pasian om khawm ta hen
verse3:
Nangmah tawh Pasian om khawm ta hen
Launa’n hong lungam sak ciangin
Ang sung hong pom bikbek dingin
Nangmah tawh Pasian om khawm ta hen
verse4:
Nangmah tawh Pasian om khawm ta hen
Itna nuai ah hong cing dingin
Sihna tuihual satpaai dingin
Nangma tawh Pasian om khawm ta hen
chorus:
I kimuh kik mateng
Zeisu kiang kimuh mateng
I kimuh kik mateng
Nangmah tawh Pasian om khawm ta hen

verse1:
Kei tawh om khawm in, ni a tum zo a
Khuamial semsem in, kei kiangah om ta
Hong gum ding a dang om lo laitak in
Hong gum Topa aw kei kiangah om in
verse2:
Leitung nun'takna mengmeng’n bei thei
Leitung ah nuamna om tawntung thei kei
Leitung ah siatna ngentang ka muta
Kei tawh om khawm in sia thei kei Topa
verse3:
Kei tawh om khawm, keima tha a pha kei
Nangmah bek in zeetna na zo thei
Nangmah bangin kua’n hong paipih thei maw?
Lungdam loh laitak kei tawh om khawm aw
verse4:
Thupha na hong piak leh kei ka laulo
Dahna khitui’n zong hong siasak zo lo
Sihna leh han in hong zo thei lopi
Kei tawh na om khawm leh ka zo thei hi
verse5:
Keima ka mitsi ka sih laitak in
Na singlamteh ka mai ah hong lak in
Vantung khuavaak leitung khuamial bei a
Sih laitak kei tawh om khawm in Topa

zoTitle: A Vaanglian Pa Aw, Ko Thum Na Hong Ngai In
verse1:
A vaanglian Pa aw, kong thum hong ngai in
Na ma hong ngak ko thupha hong pia’n
Amen

zoTitle: Tung Sun Ni A Tum Ta A
engTitle: Day is Dying in the West (Tune: Chautauqua)
verse1:
Tung sun ni a tum ta a
Tawl ngakna hun hong tung ta
Zan aksi hong suak lai a
Thangvan paak bang palh lai a Pasian bia ni
verse2:
Nuntakna a uk Topa
Van nuai teng Nangma om na
Nangma mai hong zong ko te
Na ang sungah hong khawm ve
Kinai takin.
verse3:
Khua hong mial semsem hangin
A taang aksi te khengin
Ko lungsim hong kha to tan
Nangma mai mu nuam in ah
Vannuai itpa
verse4:
Aksite le zan le sun
Mu ngei nawn lo ding a hun
Hong tun’ ciang, vantung Topa’n
Tawntung zing khua vaak sak ta’n
Kote’ mai ah.
chorus:
Siangtho, siangtho, siangtho, Topa Pasian'
Leitung, vantung ah Na vaang
Nangmah phatna hong kilang
Saangbel Pasian!

engTitle: God That Madest Earth and Heaven (Tune: Ar, Hyd Y Nos)
verse1:
Leitung, vantung, khuamial, khuavaak piangsak Pasian
Sun nasep hun leh zan tawlngak hong pia Pasian
Na vantung mi hong cingsak in
Ihmut nuam tawh hong hehpih in
Ngaihsut, lamet siangtho hong guan in
Tuzan khuavaak.
verse2:
Nun'tak lam mainawt nading zing khuavaak ciang a
Ko hong mang keeikaai zo nading Nangma deihna
Siatna' vang pan in hong dal in
Lam kawcik ah hong paipih in
Sun niloh hong mu khial sak kei in,
Nangma maipha

zoTitle: Tu In Sun’ Ni Tum Ta
engTitle: Now the Day is Over (Tune: Merial)
verse1:
Tu in sun ni tum ta, Zan hong nai ta hi
Nitak khuamui mialna, Damdam hong tung hi
verse2:
Zeisu aw a gimte, Tawldam hong pia in
Na thupha tawh kote, Hong ihmu sak in
verse3:
Ko Nangma tano te, Nang hong musak in
Tuipi tung khualzin te, Nangmah’n  Na keem in.
verse4:
Tuzan khuavaak in ah, Na vantung mite’n
Ko tung kha zak in ah, Ko hong cing uh hen

engTitle: Saviour, Breather an Evening Blessing (Tune: Evening Prayer)
verse1:
Topa aw, ko ihmut ma in
Nitak thupha hong pia in
Mawhna le kisapna ko nei
Nong hon thei, Nong damsak thei
verse2:
Siatna in hong kiimvel hangin
Thaltang tawh hong kap hangin
Na vantung mite’n hong cing a
Nong nai ciang lau nawn lo ta
verse3:
Zan khua a mial phat hangin
Nang hong liah lo khuamial in
Na mihing te’ om na peuh ah
Nang, gim ngeilo a cing Pa
verse4:
Tuzan ciangin ko lupna tung
Theih kholh loh ka si zongun
A vul ngeilo paakpalh bangin
Vantungah zing khanglo ding

verse1:
Hong gum Topa ni taang bang hi
Ama kiang khuamial ngeilo hi
Topa aw, Na mai kong muh na’ng
Meiilum kaite na thengsak in.
verse2:
Topa, ka lungkham cianag in ah,
Mitgui in a kham luat lai ah
Topa aw, Nangma ang sungah
Ka tawl ka hong damsak nuam ta
verse3:
Topa aw, Nang na om lai ah
Sih ding ka kihta keimah in
Keimah tawh a om khawm dingin
Nisim in Topa hong pai in
verse4:
Tu lai a Na thu hong sel a
Thupha bel hong nialte in ah
Nung ciangin a khialh loh na’ngin
Lam a khialte na hehpih in
verse5:
Nitak a a thum a taute
Cidam lo a a zawngkhalte
Na thupha kong na hon’ in la
A lung na damsak in, Topa

engTitle: Softly Now the Light of Day (Tune: Seymour)
verse1:
Tu in sun ni tum diaidiai
Ka mit khua hong mui hiaihiai
Lungsim, pumpi tawlnga in
Topa, hong om khawm nuam ing
verse2:
Ka sung ka pua Na mu khin
Hong maisak in a vekpi’n
Kilang a ka khialhna le
Simtham a ka mawhnate
verse3:
Kei aading a sawt lo in
Sun khuavaak hong bei ciangin
Mawhna dahna peng in ah
Hong la in Nangma kiangah
verse4:
Nang Na neih loh hang mawhna
Na thei ka gitnat lohna
Tua hi a To Zeisu aw
Hehpihna tawh hong en aw

zoTitle: Topa, Ni Nong Piak Ni, Bei Khin Ta
engTitle: The Day Thou Gavest, Lord, Is Ended (Tune: St. Clement)
verse1:
Topa ni Nong piak ni bei khin ta
Na thupiak bangin khua hong mial
Zing simin phatna la hong sak ung
Tawlnga lo in Nang hong phat nung
verse2:
Hih leitung khuavaak hong taan’ lai in
Na pawlpite ihmu ngeilo
Gam kheempeuh ah Nangbek hong ki en
Sun le zan tawlnga ngei kei nung
verse3:
Leitung tuitung tuikulh mun tengah
A hun sialsial in khua hong vaak
Tawlnga ngeilo in thu hong gen ung
Na min phatna bei ngeilo ding
verse4:
Hih leitung kumpi gamte bangin
Na ukna gam bei ngei kei hen
Na bawlsa leitung na kheempeuh in
Na ukna gam bei ngeilo ding

zoTitle: Ka Kha Aw, Topa Phat In
verse1:
Minthang Kumpi phat un, Amah bek Pasian
Phat un, ei hong lak zo hi, na lamdang lian
Khualzin mi tonpih den ding, hong ciam phat un
Meikhuam leh sun aa meiipi hangin phat un
verse2:
Mi kheempeuh tat khiatna hong pia khong phat un
A siangsak thei tuikhuk hong piak man phat un
Migi hong it, hong kepna hangin phat un
I thunget nate hong dawn’ manin phat un
verse3:
Hong it man hong ze etna hangin phat un
Eite hong kip sak in, hong lak hi, van mun
Galzo muan’na, mit lo lawp’na hang phat un
It teng kituak khawm na’ng mun hangin phat un
chorus:
Phat un, a taang van mi’n
Kham gawsem tum in, A mi kheempeuhin phat
A mai en sa in, A gam lianpi sungah
Kum tawn kha tawn in, A bawlsa te’n phat ding
Ka it kha aw phat in, A bawlsa te’n phat ding
Ka kha aw phat in

zoTitle: Na Kheempeuh A UK Topa’n Kumpi
verse1:
Na kheempeuh Topa, Kumpi suak
Na min than’na Ni, aksi’n taang
Leitung buppi hin’na laizang
Itna lungsim neite kiang nai
verse2:
Nuntak na Ni, eite aading
I lampi ah hong taang suk hi
Lametna aksi na vot sak
Zan sawt vil a om mi nuam sak
verse3:
Zan khuamial in Na nuih mai liah
Sun ni taang Nong hehpihna hi
Sakhi tuihup hehpihna lim
Mawhna meii bang a thengsak ta
verse4:
Suah takna thumaan hong pia in
Nang aading lungsim tawh kuan’ in
A nungta Na biakinn suah dong
Siangtho khuavaak, vantung khuavaak
Amen

zoTitle: Lungdam In Kong Bia Uh Hi
engTitle: Joyful, Joyful We Adore Thee (Tune: Hymn to Joy)
verse1:
Min than’na leh itna Topa
Lungdam in kong bia uh hi
Lungsim paak bang palh Na mai ah
Na vaangtaang sung hong malh hi
Mawhna dahna meiitheng sak in
Hawlkhia in lung muan’lahna
Sun ni taang ko sung hong dim in
Tul lo nuamna hong guan’ Pa
verse2:
Lei leh vann in na vaang lang sak
Hong pahtawina bawlsa te’n
Aksi leh van mite’n hong sak
Tatsat lo in hong phat den
Lo leh tu lak mual leh kuam te’n,
Lo dumna kham leh tuipi
Cik tui phul leh vasa ham te’n
Nang sung nuam din’ hong zawn’ hi
verse3:
Mawh maisak Pa, thupha pia Pa
Cing tawntung thupha Na hi
Tuinak bang nun’na sung nuamna
Tawl ngakna nuam pen Na hi
Itna nei peuh Nang aa hi khin
Kote’ Pa leh Honpa aw
Ko ki-it tek na’ng hong hilh in
Na nuamna sung dom to aw

verse1:
Zeisu’n I thumna hong za
A migi i tuucing Pa’n
Na hehpihna tawh kote
Lungsim bittak hong keem in
Amen
verse2:
Nang sung ka tha hat nangun
Natna kheempeuh nuamsak in
Na deih bang hong hi sak in
Lungdam hiah kimuh kik nang
Amen

engTitle: A Mightly Fortress is Our God (Tune: Ein’ Feste Burg)
verse1:
I Pasian muan’huai kulhpi hi
A sia ngeilo kidalna, Mawhna tui bang a let mite
Puan bang sawp siang Huhpa hi, Tanglai pu le pa gal
Ei tung gal bang hong zong, A siamna vaang a lian
Gitloh muh dahna dim, Leitung leh a gam teh lo
verse2:
Eite’n ei tha bek i suang hiam?
Ei tha bekin zolo ding, Ei lam a pang mi maan omlo
Pasian teel khiat mipa in, Kua pen a hi ding hiam?
Zeisu Khazih a hi, A min Topa Pasian
Tanglai, tulai kibang, Gal a zo tawntung ding hi
verse3:
Dawi tawh kidim hih leitung in
Ei te hong bawlsia dingin, Pasian deih kei, i lam kei ding
Amah’n hong zawhpih ding hi, Khua mialna kumpipa
Aading i liing kei hi, Amah i do zo ding
En un, sia dek ta hi, Kammal khat tawh puk ding hi
verse4:
Leitung vaang liatnate tungah
Lungdamna piak kul lo hi, Kha Siangtho hehpihna ei aa
Ei lam Amah hong pang khawm, Leitung nuntakna leh
Nate sia khin ding a, Pumpi a that ding hi
Pasian thumaan kip in, A gam kip tawntung ding hi

zoTitle: A Hing Tawntung Kha Siangtho Piang Sak Den Hi
verse1:
A hing tawntung Kha Siangtho in piangsak hi
Hih leitung a, nuntakna nei kheempeuh
Nuntakna sih ni tawlnga neilo in pai
Na minthan’na zingsol la in kisa
Hih leitung mite in siatna ngak in om
Mite lungsim siatna bek tawh dim hi
verse2:
Aw, Topa Nang sung sian’thona a dim hi
Nang sungah nuntakna ciktui luang hi
Na Kha Siangtho in manlaang takin khauh sak
Mawhna, sihna te tungah gual zo hi
Ko kha dim sak in la, hong siangtho sakin
Ka gal uh ka zawh nading hong huh in!
verse3:
Lungnop nading pan, haksatna sungah mang
Nat theihna, sih theihna khuamial sungah
Nong itna khuavaak hong taan sak tawntung in
Lungkham gimna a thuak mi hong keem in
Lungsim kha hangte Nang deih bang hi hen
Tho a a dang tawh kibat kik nading!
verse4:
Aw, Nang sung bekah ko hoihna ding kimuang
Tanglai pek a Na mite hong omna
Na hehpihna guah bang a a zu sak den
Zingdai bang nisial a thak a suak
Kote lamet bang lungsim tha hong guan’in
Tha khauhna ngah in lam ka pai nangun! Aman

verse1:
Topa Pasian Nangma khut a na bawlsa
Leitung khempeuh ka ngaihsut ciangin ah
Aksite mu in, vangingte ka za hi
Leitung kheempeuh ah Na vaang kilang hi
verse2:
Sing lakah zong ka vak kawikawi ciangin ah
Singkung tungah vasa ham ngaih ka za
Mual sang dawn pan khuam thuk sung ka et suk ciang
Lui ging za in huih dam hong nung hiauhiau
verse3:
Pasian inah A Tapa haza lo in
Hong puak ka ngaihsut ciang um kei phial ing
Singlamteh tung kei van lungdam tak pua in
Sisan luangin, ka mawhna hong paih sak
verse4:
Kikona tawh, Khazih hong pai kik ciangin
Hong ciahpih ding, Bangzah ka nuam ding hiam?
Tua ciang kiniam khiatna tawh ka bia ding a
"Ka Pasian lian hi," ci’n ka kiko ding
chorus:
Tua ahih ciang, la kong sa hong honpa
Bangzah Na lian, Bangzah Na lian
Tua ahih ciang, kong phat hi, Topa aw
Nang Na lian hi, Nang Na lian hi

zoTitle: Na Thumaanna Lian Hi, Ka Pa Pasian Aw
verse1:
"Na thumaanna lian hi," ka Pa Pasian aw,
Kihei kikheelna liim Na nei kei hi,
Nangma hehpihna kikheel in bei ngeilo,
Tanglai bangmah Na hi tawntung ding hi.
verse2:
Ni, kha le aksite, ngeina bang ciat in,
Khuakhal le tuk hunte, phalbi, nipi,
Ngeina bang zui a hunhun a piangte in,
Na thumaan, hehpih, itna hong lak hi.
verse3:
Mawhna mai sakna le a kip lung nopna,
Nong ompih lung damna, lam Nong hilhna,
A ni sim Nong kepna, mailam lung muan’na,
A pha tampite zong, Nangma thupha.
chorus:
"Na thumaanna lian hi, Na thumaanna lian hi,"
Zingsang simin hehpihna thak ka mu,
Ka sapna teng Na khut in hong guan’ tawntung,
"Na thumaanna lian hi," Topa kei’ tung.

verse1:
A hong kum suk Topa,
Na min phatna ding la ko hong pia in,
Vaanglian minthang Topa Leitung kheempeuh zo a,
Hong pai hong uk in la, Beisa ni tawh.
verse2:
Biakna nuamna hong pia,
Kote’ thu hong ngeina na hong ngai in,
Lam khial nei mite in thumuh kik nading in,
Lam hilh ding hong pai in Kha Siangtho aw.
verse3:
Thuhilh Kha Siangtho aw,
Hilh ding hong pai in la tu’n hong pai aw,
Siamna a om kheempeuh Kha Siangtho om kheempeuh,
Ko tungah hong pia’n la hong uk ta aw.
verse4:
Nam thum pawl khat Pasian,
Topa Nangmah a lian, Na min thang hen,
Vantung gam sung Nangmah, Na vaanglian mi dingin,
Nangmah a tawntung in ka it ding hi.

verse1:
Kiimkot khuamialna a taang Zeisu aw,
Hong masuan in, ka inn panin gamlapi ah ka om,
Lam hong hilh in, Keima khe hong kepsak in,
Gamlapi muh ding ngenlo,
Kal khat bek pha zo ta.
verse2:
Tua bangin thungetna ni dang lai in om ngeilo hi,
Ka teelsa lam ka zuih hangin tu ni,
Nong kha ding hi, kisak theihna dingin ka deih,
Keimah’n ka kiphasak,
Ka mawhna ngaihsun ke’n.
verse3:
Sawtpi Nangmah’n thupha nong piak manin ,
Hong pai lai in, gam kuam, mual kal, tuipi kheng Topa in,
Lam hong hilh ta, khuavaak ciangin sau veipi ka it mi,
Lungdamin ah keimah’n ka um ding hi.

engTitle: A Shelter in the Time of Storm
verse1:
I bukna Suangpi Topa hi,
Huihpi nun’ ciang a kidalna,
A sia nam kim aading bit hi,
Huihpi nun’ ciang a kidalna.
verse2:
Sun in ni lim, zan in kulhpi,
Huihpi nun’ ciang a kidalna,
Galte bangmah patau lo hi,
Huihpi nun’ ciang a kidalna.
verse3:
Huihpi’n i kiimkot nuai hangin,
Huihpi nun’ ciang a kidalna,
Nusia lo ding cikmah hunin,
Huihpi nun’ ciang a kidalna.
verse4:
Pasian, Suangpi, belh ding it huai,
Huihpi nun’ ciang a kidalna,
Tawntung hong nai, hong keem, hong huai,
Huihpi nun’ ciang a kidalna.
chorus:
Gimna gam sungah Zeisu Suangpi a hi,
Belh ding Suangpi, Belh ding Suangpi,
Gimna gam sungah Zeisu Suangpi a hi,
Huihpi nun’ ciang a kidalna.

verse1:
Amah’n  hong kha hih thu mahmah,
Hehnepna dim thupha a hi,
Ka sepna, ka paina tengah,
Pasian' khut in kei hong kha hi.
verse2:
Khatvei leh Eden bang nuamna,
Khatvei leh khuamial na thukpi,
Bang ka tuak hang muan’na launa,
Ama khut in kei hong kha hi.
verse3:
Phun lo, puam lo, lungkim takin,
Topa, Na khut ka len nuam hi,
Bangbang tuak zong bang lung khamna,
Ka Pasian in kei hong kha hi.
verse4:
Na hehpihna tawh galzo a,
Nasep ka khit ciang a vekpi,
Sih ding laulo, Pasian in-ah,
Zawdan gun galah hong kha hi.
chorus:
Amah’n hong kha, Amah’n hong kha,
Ama khut tawh Amah’n hong kha,
A’ nung maantak ka zui ding hi,
Ama khut in kei hong kha hi.

verse1:
Siangtho, siangtho, siangtho,
I Topa, Siangtho, siangtho, siangtho,
Vantung i zin Pa, Amen.

.Kitam a om a kip suangpi,
Hong liah in gimna le tawlna a tampi,
Hong liah in, Topa itna ka lungsim ah,
Mihing khen thei lohna mun ah,
A kip tawntung suangpi pha aw, hong liah in.
verse2:
Mawhna kuam sung tun’loh na’ngin,
Hong liah in Topa ka lungsung ah suangpi,
Hong liah in, hih leitung min than’ liat lai in,
Ka mawh na’ngin hong zol lai in,
A kip tawntung suangpi pha aw, hong liah in.
verse3:
Dahna khua a mial laitakin,
Hong liah in, minthan’ ni zingsang mateng in,
Hong liah in, Zawden gun gei a nai ciangin,
Na ang sungah hong tum sak in,
A kip tawntung suangpi pha aw, hong liah in.

zoTitle: Kei Sang A Saang Zaw Suangpi
engTitle: The Rock That is Higher Than I
verse1:
Khat-veivei ciang i nuntakna,
Haksat mahmah hun hong tun’ ciang,
Lungkham sinkham dah leh kah in,
Huihpi seem bangin hong seem thei.
verse2:
Khat-veivei ni tum thei lo bang,
Khat-veivei i gim diakdiak bang,
Leitung nuntak gimna sung pan,
Thupha Suangpi beel leng nuam ding.
verse3:
Tua Suangpi ke’n ka beel nuam hi,
Dahna nopna ka thuak zongin,
Mual sang guam thuk sung ka pai zong,
A suk a to-ah ka pai zong.
chorus:
A lian Suangpi ka beel nuam hi (beel nuam hi),
Keimah sang-a a saang zaw Suangpi (zaw suang pi),
A lian Suangpi ka beel nuam hi (beel nuam hi),
Keimah sang a sangzaw Suangpi.

engTitle: O God, Our Help in Ages Past (Tune: St. Anne)
verse1:
Tanglai-a a lian bel Topa,
Nungciang a lawpna hi,
Tui kilok cinag na omna sung,
Hehpih in hong liah hi.
verse2:
Topa Pasian tokhom nuai-ah,
Mi siangthote’n nuamsa,
Na khut tawh Na liahna, kepna,
Bitbel ding hi Topa.
verse3:
Lei le vanpi a kip kei zong,
Lei pumpi Nang tang hi,
Topa a kip Pasian na hi,
Na om pello ding hi.
verse4:
Kum tul kum then Topa mai ah,
Nitak om ngeilo hi,
Khuamialna in a leeng mang a,
Zingsang khuavaak bang hi.
verse5:
Tuikhu bang hin’na bei thei hi,
Manlangin top thei hi,
Zan, nitak, zingsang ciang mang hi,
I mang tawh kibang hi.
verse6:
Tanglai-a a lian bel Topa,
Nung ciang a lawpna hi,
Gimna thuak ciang hong keem pha in,
Na innah hong koih in.

verse1:
Lungmang mi aw, nang kihta kei in,
Nangma Topa Pasian na muang ta in,
Thu ngen in, na singlamteh gik hangin,
Amah'n hong huh ding hi.
verse2:
Lungmang mi aw, gal tam hangin ah,
Gal nan'na leh thu upna lian sak ta'n,
Topa vaangliatna tawh na do ding a,
Gal zo na hi ding hi.
verse3:
Lungmang mi aw, lam haksat ciangin,
Topa'n kihtakna a paih khiat sak ding,
Huhna na deih leh,
Amah'n nei lai ding,
A min pha sak ta in.
chorus:
Amah in nang a honggum thei lai hi,
Ama khut in gal liahna hi ding hi,
Amah in nang hong gum thei lai ding hi,
Tua hi a lau kei in.

zoTitle: Topa In Hong Kem Ding Hi
engTitle: God Will Take Care of You
verse1:
Gimna thuak hang lungmang kei in,
Pasian in hong keem hi,
Ama itna nuaiah om in,
Pasian in hong keem hi.
verse2:
Nasep nakpi na bawl laitak,
Pasian in hong keem hi,
Na paina lam launa om leh,
Pasian in hong keem hi.
verse3:
Ama'h na deih teng hong pia ding,
Pasian in hong keem hi,
Piak loh bangmah om kei ding hi.
verse4:
Ze-et gitlohna thuak hangin,
Pasian in hong keem hi,
Ama ang sung na om ding hi,
Pasian in hong keem hi.
chorus:
Pasian in hong keem hi,
Nisim in-ah, tawntung in-ah,
Amah in hong keem hi,
Pasian in hong keem hi.

verse1:
A-men, A-men, A-men, A-men,
A-men, A-men, A-men

Hih ka Pa' leitung hi,
Ke'n ka ngaih ciangin-ah,
Na kheempeuh in, ka bil sungah,
La ngaih sa bang ka za,
Hih ka Pa' leitung hi,
Ka ngaihsut ciang nuam hi,
Singkung, suangtum, vanpi, tuipi,
Ama bawl lamdang pha.
verse2:
Hih ka Pa' leitung hi,
A min phat ding kipaak,
Vasa ham ngaih zingsang khuavaak,
A kilawm unok paak,
Hih ka Pa' leitung hi, A hoih khempeuh sungah,
Amah om a hong pau pih-na,
Ka paina teng ka za.
verse3:
Hih ka Pa' leitung hi,
Ke'n mangngilh ngei kei ning,
A sia lamsang a hat hangin,
Uk lai Pasian mah in,
Hih ka Pa' leitung hi, Gal kizo nailo hi,
Zeisu lungkim nailo ding hi,
Lei le van kikhat ma'n.

zoTitle: Hong Gum Topa Hong Liah In
verse1:
Na siangthona mun ah Topa,
Kei hong liah ta in,
Tawl damna na kiang ka ngah lai,
Na maitang hong lak in.
verse2:
Nun'tak na huihpi a nun lai,
Kei hong liah ta in,
Tuipi tungah vakhu bangin,
Nang kiang hong lutsak in.
verse3:
Dahna tawh ka lung, kitam lai,
Lungdamna hong pia'n,
Khitui tawh nuamna ka zon' lai,
Keimah hong liah ta in.
chorus:
Hong liah ta in,
Hong gum Topa hong liah in,
Lau lohna na kiang,
Keimah hong om sak in.

verse1:
Lam hong lak Gumpa ka kiang hong nai ciang,
Bangbang hong kiimvel hang lau om nawn lo,
Huihpi guahpi te hong daisak ding a,
A khutkuak sung muan'huai hi.
verse2:
Itna tawh a ang sung kei hong pom ciang,
Kilemna thu Kha Siangtho hong hilh a,
Pasian khut in kei hong kip let zawh ciang,
A khutkuak sung muan'huai hi.
verse3:
Ka kha kem kei hong nusia nawn lo ding,
Hong itna khau tatsat zo om nawn lo,
Ka thei hi, Amah in hong kem den ding,
'A khutkuak sung muan'huai hi.
chorus:
A khutkuak sung muan'huai hi,
A khutkuak sung muan'huai hi,
Bangbang hong kiimvel hang lau om nawn lo,
A khutkuak sung muan'huai hi.

zoTitle: Zingsang Mateng Ka Om Ding Hi
engTitle: I'll Stand By Until the Morning
verse1:
A tum dek teembaw kimkot ah,
Huihpi in sem hi,
Huih in len a kisia dek hi,
Tuipi thuk sungah.
verse2:
Lametna bei a teembaw mi,
Lung thaneem ta hi,
Topa sapna aw za uh a,
Lungdam khin uh hi.
verse3:
Tuipi tung huih nun' phat lai ah,
Teembaw tum dek hi,
A gum ding Zeisu va pai a,
Lungman' dam thei hi
verse4:
No hong it manin hong kum a,
Nang tang ding si hi,
Siatna paai in a thu um in,
Inn na tung ding hi.
chorus:
Hong gum Topa ko in,
Hong thupiak ngai in,
Zingsang mateng kong ompih ding,
Lau ke'n hong gum ding kong pai hi,
Hi hi, zingsang mateng ompih ding,
Lau ke'n hong gum ding kong pai hi.

zoTitle: Topa In Hong Liah Ding Hi
verse1:
Leitung tuitung haksa lua a,
Launa huih hong nun' ciangah,
Topa aw, Nangma khaliim ah,
Bu dingah kong tai ding ta.
verse2:
Gimna tawntung hong ze-et hang,
Inn nuam kong tut nop man hi,
Heh het loin hong it man in,
Gimna hong thuaksak thei hi.
verse3:
Dawi mangpa pawl i galte in,
Hong bawlsia nuam semsem hi,
Ahih hangin ah Pasian in,
Lungdam na'ng hong pia ding hi.
verse4:
Leitung singlamteh puak lai-in,
Dahna huih bang nung thei hi,
Ka kha Topa Zeisu cing in,
Ka gal tuaksak lo ding hi.
chorus:
Gal hong tun' zawh loh na'ng in-ah,
Topa in kei hong kem ding ta,
Topa in a kha liim nuaiah,
Tawntung kei hong kem ding hi.

zoTitle: Sung Lawh Taang Bang Pha Lailung
engTitle: How Firm a Foundation (Tune: Portuguese Hymn)
verse1:
Tung Pasian tawldam tang bang a pha bel in,
Lai lung sung khuam bang kipna dingin suan in,
Zeisu mamawh a lumbang belte siangtho,
Sung lawh tangbang pha lai lungah omzo hi,
Sung lawh tangbang pha lai lungah omzo hi.
verse2:
Nangtawh omkhawm-zo lai lung muangmawh nawn ke'n,
Kei in na tung Pasian ka hi nang kongsam,
Pian'dang bel tawh tui bang a dim ka banzal,
Na zaitha leh na lai lungkip sak ding hi'ng,
Na zaitha leh na lai lungkip sak ding hi'ng.
verse3:
Damtui kul thuksung a nang na kum ding pawl,
Tang khuang bang kong kho ham bang vai kong bawllo,
Phamna tawh zingdai bang na kipelh na'ng in,
Damtui bang na sian' na-ding kei ka om hi,
Damtui bang na sian' na-ding kei ka om hi.
verse4:
Tatsa sial bang et nang kammei sung tung ding,
Hehnepna tui bang kicing kong langsak ding,
Kammei thul guah bang thuakloh na'ng hong keem ning,
Vaivut a suaksa kham bang kong piangsak ding.
verse5:
Kum khua sawt a tum bang vuai dong ka mite,
Tui bang kiamlo mu bang ngah kum khua om ding,
Na pa ang leh sum leh sam a kang zongin,
Ka ang lai-ah kip takin vom bang sia ning.

verse1:
Leitung ah launa tampi a om hang,
Bangmah kihtak ka nei kei,
Ki-lang lo Pasian tawh ka om ciang in,
Koimah peuh pai ding ka lau lo.
verse2:
Hak satna namkim a hong tun' hangin,
Bangmah kihtak ka nei kei,
Pasian ka kiang-ah a hong om peuh leh,
Koimah peuh pai ding ka lau lo.
verse3:
Sihna guam thuk sung dong ka tung zongin,
Bangmah kihtak ka nei kei,
Gam nuamah om ding Topa gam sungah,
Koimah peuh pai ding ka lau lo.
verse4:
Mi namkim in kei hong do hangin ah,
Bangmah kihtak ka nei kei,
Pasian vaang liatna a om ka sungah,
Koimah peuh pai ding ka lau lo.
chorus:
Tua bangin u le nau,
Pasian lamah na lung kip hen,
Cik-mah hun lungkia lo in,
Pasian kiang i tun' ciangin,
Lung nopna bangzah takin a om diam.

verse1:
A siangtho tui luan-na mual kuam zui dingin,
Zeisu in lam hong pi leh, lungdam zui ning,
A khut zan in tuipi hual tung hong sawl zong,
A mangte gupna ding A thu va puak ning.
verse2:
Bangmah omlo, mualsang tung a hi zongin,
A lawmte tawh kikhen a mangthang tuuno,
Huih le guahpi a zu zong, va zong ning,
Gumpa hong lah bang mailam nawt va pai ning.
verse3:
Ka zui ding hi, Gumpa hong lah mah bangin,
Dah ta leng, nuam ta leng, lungdam in zui ning,
Gumpa'n thei hi, tha muanhuai thumaan lampi,
A tang kham khuapi sungah hong tunpih ding.
chorus:
Lam hong hilh bang zui ning,
Lungdam takin zui ning,
Gumpa hong hilh bang lam zui ning,
Lungdam tak zui ning.

zoTitle: Keimah Topa Zeisu Lamdang Honpa Hi
verse1:
Kei-ma Topa Zeisu lamdang Honpa hi,
Kei aading lamdang Honpa hi,
Suangpi kitam sungah ka kha hong liah sak,
Nuamna gunpi bang hong musak.
verse2:
Kei-ma Topa Zeisu lamdang Honpa hi,
Amah'n pua khia keima vanpi,
Amah'n hong len a kei ka liing kei ding hi,
Ka ni bangin tha hong pia hi.
verse3:
Kisim zolo thupha hong pia kimat-in,
Ama hoihna tawh kidim-in,
Lungdam in la ka sa Pasian minthang hen,
Hih bang Tanpa ka nei hi ke'n.
verse4:
Ama dikna puanpaak silh a ka thawh ciang,
Amah dawnin ka leen' toh ciang,
Ama hong itna le hong hotna kicing,
Van-ah awn tampi tawh sa ning.
chorus:
Suangpi kitam sung, kei-ma kha hong liah sak,
Tua suangpi'n gam gawtak liap sak,
A itna sungah ka nun'tak na phum ta,
Ama khutin kei hong hum ta,
Ama khut in kei hong hum ta.

verse1:
A' kha nuai-ah lungmuang takin ka om a,
Khuamial pha a huihpi nak nun' hangin,
Ka muang thei hi, hong kem ding hi, ka thei hi,
Hong tan zo hi, Ama ta ka hihi.
verse2:
A' kha nuai-ah dah ciang belh dingin pha hi,
Ama kiang a tawldam nuam lunggulh ing,
Leitung in hong damsak zolo ciangin ah,
Tua lai-ah hehnep, lungdamna ka ngah.
verse3:
A' kha nuai-ah nopna bangzah tak manpha,
Nuntak haksatna bei mateng beel ning,
Hong hah, hong dal, siat na'n hong su thei lo ding,
Zeisu sung khawl leng lungmuang tawntung hi'ng.
chorus:
A' kha nuai-ah hong itna pan,
Kua mah'n hong khen zo lo ding,
A' kha nuai-ah keima kha teeng ding,
Lungmuang tak om tawntung ding.

verse1:
Tuu khumna inn sungah gal muang takin,
Tuu sawm kua le kua te om hi,
Gamlak mual tungah khat mangthang a tua tuu,
Tuubuk tawh kigamla mahmah hi,
Gam sim tham gam daihna tulak mual-lak ah,
Tuucing, migi pa kep lohin om hi,
Tuucing migi pa kep lo in om hi.
verse2:
Topa tuu sawm kua le kua te om lai,
Tua teng pha zo sa lo na maw?,
Tuucing migi pa lungkim dek nai lo hi,
Gam la pi ka man'suah hangin ah,
Lam haksat na mual-lak, ken lak hi ta leh,
Ka man'suah sa ka tuu va zong ding ci,
Ka man'suah sa ka tuu va zong ding ci.
verse3:
Tua thupha kua mahin thei kim nai kei,
A haksatna kithei lo hi,
A muh kik mateng a zon' kawikawi na in,
Khuazin' khuamial a zawtzawt na thu,
Gamlak gam lapi ah, a ham aw za a,
A cimawh a si ding a om mu hi,
A cimawh a si ding a om mu hi.
verse4:
Mual tung khuadam huihpi guah pi lak-ah,
Ken lak kawl lak ahih hangin,
Vantung kongpi pan in hong kiko khia-a,
A mang sa ka tuu mu kik ing ci,
Vantung mite in zong, tokhom kiim vel ah,
Nuam un, Topa'n tuu mang mu zo ci hi.
verse5:
Topa a si lam tawntung ah kia in,
Tua si in mualtung lam hong lak,
A gammang tua tuu-no aading hong luang hi,
Tuu cing pa in hong ciahpih kik ding,
Ka Topa aw, na khutte liam gawp zo a,
Amaute tuzan ling in sun gawp zo.

zoTitle: A Sawt Loin Lung Khamna Bei-in
verse1:
Sawt loin lung khamna bei-in Inn i tung ding,
Sawt loin huih meiipi bei-in, Inn i tung ding,
Tawmvei sung singlamteh pua in,
Zeisu tawh kham lukhu khu ding,
Sawt loin lung khamna bei-in Inn i tung ding.
verse2:
Sawt loin kahna zan bei-in Inn i tung ding,
Sawt loin eite hong cingin, Inn i tung ding,
Sawt loin mawhna te zo in,
Sawt loin i om khawm den ding,
Sawt loin lung khamna bei-in Inn i tung ding.
verse3:
Sawt loin nuntak na bei-in Inn i tung ding,
Sawt loin kamkhum pen gen in Inn i tung ding,
Sawt loin khau bang kihuai in,
Khanan gam lam zui i pai ding,
Sawt loin lung khamna bei-in Inn i tung ding.
chorus:
Hun te manlang in bei-in I tawlnga den ding,
Lung khamna om nawn lo ding,
Inn i tun' ciang

verse1:
Lungsim gal dona le dahna sung panin,
Kei sang a sangzaw suangpi ka delh nuam hi,
Mawh lua, gimlua zo, Nang aa hong hi ta ning,
A kip Suangpi aw, Nangmah kong bel ta hi.
verse2:
Sun in gamdai a, dah in lungleng laitak,
Ze-etna in a vaang tawh hong tuam ciangin,
Nuntak huihpi nung, tuipi kihual laitak,
Thupha Suangpi aw, hong liah in bit takin.
verse3:
Gal do laitak-in gal in hong neh ciangin,
Tai in kong ko zel hi, ka belh Suangpi aw,
Tuihual bang ze-et gimna hong tun' ciangin,
Na sung kong bu hi, keima kha' Suangpi aw.
chorus:
Nang kong bel hi, Nang kong bel hi,
Nangmah kong bel hi, a kip thupha Suangpi.

zoTitle: Ni Khat Ni Ciang Lungdam Ni
verse1:
A zaknop huai langaih ka za,
Tua la ka sathei nai kei hi,
A zaknop huai la aw ngaih pi,
Khatvei ni ciang ka sathei ding.
verse2:
Ni khat ni ciang ka tawldam ding,
Leitung bei ding vantung om ding,
Lam haksa teng ka khinkhin ding,
Ka Topa maitang ka mu ding.
verse3:
Ni khat ni ciang lungnop om ding,
Vantung kongkhakpi kihong ding,
Ni khat ni peuhpeuh lut ning,
A tawntung in ka tawldam ding.
chorus:
Ni khat ni ciang, lungdamna ni,
Tua la ngaihpi kasa thei ding,
Tua la noptak in ka sak ciang,
Zeisu kiang vantung ka tun'ciang.

verse1:
I lungngaih tawntung dingin ah 
Topa Pasian itna,
Mawhna a lian i neih napi "Tate aw," hong ci hi.
verse2:
Topa tawh kinai theih nading 
Zeisu a si luangsak,
"Ka ta itte aw," ci'n hongsam.
A ang sung i khawl ding.
verse3:
Nung ciang i min bangci than' ding 
Tu'n kithei nailo hi,
Topa Zeisu hong kum kik ciang 
Amah i sun ding hi.
verse4:
Tua thu a lawpte kheempeuh in 
I Topa band ding hi.
Sihna a zo minthang Topa
 Mai mu dingin a pha.
chorus:
En un Topa Pasian in 
"Tate aw," hong cihna Pasian tate i tang ding hi,
En un, Topa Pasian in,
Ei hong it thupha phatna.

verse1:
Mawhna thukah tum suk in,
Suahtak nading gamla,
Ka sung mawhna nin dim in,
Tumcip ding ka hi ta,
Ahih hangin Topa in, Ka kikona hong za,
Tuisung pan hong dom to in, Tu'n ka suakta.
verse2:
Amah bek ke'n ka muang ta,
Amah beel tawntung ning,
A mai nuamah ka khawl ta.
Amah phat tawntung ning,
Hi zah ta a hong itna,
Ka siam tawpin phat ning,
Itna tawh Ama deihna, Seem tawntung ning.
verse3:
Kha nuntak na tan' dekte,
Zeisu'n hong hon thei hi,
Tuipi hual sung tum dekte,
A hong dom to ding hi,
Ama uk hi tuihual te,
Ama thu mang uh hi,
Hong hon nuam hi, na ut leh, Tu ni, tu ni.
chorus:
Kei hong phong hi! kei hong phong hi!,
Itna in a ci mawh, Kei hong phong hi.

zoTitle: Lampi Khial Lo Dingin Hong Hilh In
engTitle: Lead Me, Savior, Lest I Stray
verse1:
Lampi khial lo dingin-ah,
Lampi hong hilh in Topa,
Nang kiangah ka om laiah,
Gal hong bawlsia thei lo ta.
verse2:
Tuipi in kilok lai in,
Ka kha gal liahna ding in,
Kei kiangah na om lai in,
Na hehpihna ka muang ding.
verse3:
Nuntakna huih nung ta a,
Khitui kinul, Na khua ah,
Keimah ka tun' mateng in,
Hong gum Topa lam hilh in.
chorus:
Lam hong hilh in, Topa lampi hong hilh in,
Huan gun geiah lampi-ah, 
Hong gum Topa hong hilh in.

zoTitle: Pasian In Leitung Hong It Hi
verse1:
A mawh khinsa leitung mite,
Pasian in hong it hi,
A pha bel a vaang lianpi te,
Man nei lo hong pia hi.
verse2:
I up leh i Topa ding hi,
A hing kik Pasian Ta,
Sihna tawh ei hong gum zo hi,
A si'n hong sawp zo ta.
verse3:
Itna in hong kicing sak a,
Mi siangtho te'n gen hi,
Zeisu thupha bel um leteh,
Nuamna na ngah ding ci.
verse4:
A Umte aw nuam in pai un,
Vantungah nopnapi,
Na upna bang un leitung ah,
No na ngah ding uh hi.
chorus:
A lamdan bel dipkuat huai 
Zeisu hong itna hi,
Eimah hong gup nading amah'n 
Kalvari mual si hi.

verse1: A-men, A-men, A - - - men.

zoTitle: A Tawntung Ang Sungah Om Ning
verse1:
Aw, kipawlna nuamna kei aa hi zo,
Tawntung ang sungah kei khawl ta ing!,
Aw, nopsakna lian, aw, nopna siangtho,
Tawntung ang sungah kei khawl ta ing!
verse2:
Hih khual zinnaah lungmuang taktak ing,
Tawntung ang sungah kei khawl ta ing!,
A ni ni'n ka lam nuamsa semsem ing,
Tawntung ang sungah kei khawl ta ing!
verse3:
Ke'n bang Kihta ding, kei bang lau nawn ding,
Tawntung ang sungah kei khawl ta ing!,
Honpa tawh om khawm nopna lian ngah ing,
Tawntung ang sungah kei khawl ta ing!
chorus:
Khawl ing, khawl ing,
Launa pan lungmuang khin zo ing,
Khawl ing, khawl ing,
Tawntung ang sungah kei khawl ta ing!

zoTitle: Topa Nangmah Ka It Ka Thei
engTitle: I know I Love Thee, Better, Lord
verse1:
Leitung ah sum khempeuh sangin,
Topa kong it zaw hi, 
Kisia ngeilo nopsak na'ngin
Topa in hong pia hi.
verse2:
Leitung ka zawl khempeuh sangin Topa nai nuam zaw ing,
Leitungah la ngaih khempeuh sang,
Thu ngaihna pha zaw hi.
verse3:
Ka lung hong damsak zo ta hi,
Cik mah'n bei lo ding hi,
Hong itna thupha om kei leh,
Lungsim kisia ding hi.
verse4:
Hong om khawmpih kithei lopi,
Hih zah lung damna lian,
Topa maii mu ding takpi,
Bangzah a nuam ding hiam.
chorus:
Hong it hong ngaihna a thupha,
Kimkhat beek gen nai kei,
Hong sawp siangthona a thupha,
Kimkhat beek gen nai kei.

zoTitle: Kote Hong Thumna Hong Ngai In, Topa
verse1:
Kote hong thumna,
Hong ngai in Topa,
Kolam hong nga in la,
Hong pia'n lung nopna.. A - men.

engTitle: O Little Town of Bethlehem (Tune: St. Loiuis)
verse1:
Betlehem khua neu mite aw,
No lah ihsip keei maw,
Aksi te'n zong hong khengkheng veh,
Khua phawk kei si uh teh,
En un, no khua kongzing lak,
Taang hi, tawntung Khuavak!,
Kum khua a kingak no khua ah,
Tuzan hong tung petmah!
verse2:
Bang hiam na hong cih leh, Mazih,
Sung pan suak hi Khazih,
Vantung mite'n na cing 
Amah mi ihmut kal in ah,
No zingsol te'n na vek un nau suahna tangko un,
Pasian Kumpi A min thang hen,
Mitung nopna tung hen.
verse3:
Lamdang lungdam huaina lianpi,
Hong kidai piakkhian hi,
Pasian in thupha hongpiak zia 
tua bang ngeingei a hi,
Bilin kiza lo hangin,
Mawhna a dim hangin,
Lungneem in saang nuamte sungah,
It huai Khazih lut pah.
verse4:
Betlehem Naungek siangtho aw,
Ko kiangah hong kum aw,
Kote mawhna hawl khia in la,
Hong suak in ko sugna,
Nang suah tangko van mite'n,
Lungdamna thu hong gen,
Hong pai in hong om in ko tawh,
Imanuel Topa aw.

verse1:
Hong luang zuazua, zankim laitak,
Vantung la ngaihpi hong gingsuk hi,
A la dawng lah, la ngaih mahmah,
A sate lah, vantung mi honpi.
verse2:
Tuucing mite'n tua thupi mu,
Tua a taang mite' thu pulak za,
Bawngkuang sung a Pa na kibia,
Huih lak kheempeuh thawn in la kisa.
verse3:
Khazih Honpa, Pa' Sathau nilh,
Leibat lauhuai loh ding hong pai zo,
Dahna mite nialsa mite,
I mawhna puakhia Pasian Tuuno.
chorus:
A sang belah minthang hen aw,
Leiah mite tung nopna om hen,
Khangsawm te'n tu bang ciing hen aw,
Lei in pahtawi kikkik hen.

zoTitle: Ong Pai Un Thu Um Teng
engTitle: Oh Come, All Ye Faithful (Tune: Adeste Fideles)
verse1:
Hong pai un, thu um teng,
Lungdam in kipak un,
Hong pai un va en ni,
Betlen khua-ah,
Vantung Kumpipa Bawngkuang sung hong suak, ci.
verse2:
Sa un, kipahna la,
Vantung mi honte aw,
Vantung a sang belna,
Kheempeuh thawn un,
Van sang belna-ah Pasian' minthang ta hen.
verse3:
Hi hi, hong hon ding Pa 
Tu ni'n kong dawn uh hi,
Zeisu Topa, Na min Thang tawntung hen,
Pa Pasian', deih thu Mi bangin hong piang ta.
chorus:
Va bia ni, hong pai ta un,
Va bia ni, hong pai ta un,
Hong pai un, va bia ni,
Khazih Topa.

verse1:
Leitung lungdam Topa hong pai,
Kumpi za ngah ding hi,
Lungsim kheempeuh bawl phat sak hi,
Van leh lei la sak ngai,
Ven leh lei la sak ngai,
Vanleh, vanleh lei la sak ngai.
verse2:
Leitung nuam na'ng Zeisu maang hi,
Mihing te'n la sa hen,
Lo lai, tuipi, suangpi, mualpi'n,
Kidem in ham uh hen,
Kidem in ham uh hen,
Kidem kidem in ham uh hen
verse3:
Nung ciang mawhna a khan loh na'ng,
Ling in bawlsia lo ding,
A pha lo na a pha bel in,
Bawl pha ding hong pai ding,
Bawl pha ding hong pai ding,
Bawl pha, bawl pha ding hong pai ding.
verse4:
Hong hehpihna thupha bel in,
Leitung hong uk ding hi,
A minthang siangtho hong itna,
Mi khempeuh theisak hi, 
Mi khem, mi khempeuh theisak hi.

engTitle: O Come, O Come, Emmanuel (Tune: Veni, Emmanuel)
verse1:
Hong pai hong pai, Immanuaila,
Hon' in sal suak Itazila,
Hi lai lungzuang nilkhiat thuak mi,
Pasian Tapa kilat mateng,
Itazila te aw nuam un,
No kiang Immanuaila hong pai.
verse2:
Hong pai hong pai Zise suan aw,
Satan khut sung pan hong hon in,
Hong hon in hell khua sung pan in,
Sihna han pan zawhna hong pia'n,
Itazila te aw nuam un,
No kiang Immanuaila hong pai.
verse3:
Hong pai Davuih Tapa hong pai,
Ka vantung kong hong za hon'in,
Muangtak vantung tun' na'ng bawl in,
Siatna lampi bingsak ta in,
Itazila te aw nuam un,
No kiang Immanuaila hong pai.
verse4:
Hong tung Topa lungdamna ni,
I lungsim a hong lawpsak ding,
Zan khuamialna hong bei sak in,
Meiite khengin khuavaak hong pia!
Itazilla te aw nuam un,
No kiang Immanuaila hong pai.

verse1:
Eite aading Khazih Topa,
Hong suak tu nitak in,
Leitung mite vantung mi in,
A thu ngai ding uhhh,
Leitung mi le vantung mi in,
A thu ngai ding uh hi.
verse2:
A min ding "Kilemna Kumpi"
A tawntung kiphat ding,
Amah in a lamdang a lian,
A vaang lian Topa hi,
Amah in a lamdang a lian,
A vaang lian Topa hi.
verse3:
A mong nei lo ukna kicing,
A khang semsem ding hi,
Van a tokhom tung thu manna,
A nuaiah kilemna,
Van a tokhom tung thumaanna,
A nuaiah kilemna.

engTitle: The First Noel, the Angels Did Say
verse1:
Noel masa vantung mite sak,
Tuucing zawng pawlkhat tuu cin' lai,
Gampa lakah tuu vilom laitak,
Phalbi khuadam lai, zan khuamial laitak.
verse2:
A khuadak ciang ni suahna lamah,
Gamla pi pan, aksi taang khat kilak,
Leitung tengah nakpi in taang hi,
A sun, a zan ci loin taang tawntung hi.
verse3:
Tua aksi taang zui kawm in ah,
Gamla pi pan mipil thumte in ah,
Kumpi zong ding in hong pai uh hi,
Aksi paina kheempeuh hong zui uh hi.
verse4:
Mipil thumte zong buk sung lut a,
Zahtakna tawh khuk din' uh hi,
Kham, paaknamtui, paaknamtui kha,
A khe kiang ah sua'n a pia uh hi.
chorus:
Noel, Noel, Noel, Noel,
Itazi la Kumpipa suak.

engTitle: If Coine Upon the Midnight Clear (Tune: Carol)
verse1:
Zankim gamdaih kim laitak-in,
Hong ging vaanglian la pi,
Vantung mite hong kum sukin,
Kham gawsem tawh sa hi,
"Vantung Kumpipa kiang pauin,
Nopna leitung dim hen",
Ci'n hong sak laitak leitung mi'n,
Dai khipkhep in ngai hi.
verse2:
Van kong pan hong pai lailai mah,
Kilemna kha zak in,
Gimna dimna hih leitung ah,
Van la ngaih kiza lai,
Dahna lung khamna kuam tung ah,
Hong leeng diaidiai uh a,
Pau nam tampi gamlum lakah,
Vantung la pha hong sa.
verse3:
Leitung nun'tak vangik nuaiah,
Vangik lel a om te,
Nun'tak haksa lamto a kah,
Pheiphung suan kha mi aw,
En un, lungdam nuamna ding hun,
Manlang va bang hong leeng,
Gimna lamgei ah na khawl un,
Vantung la ngai dih un.
verse4:
Thei un, hong tung petmah ding ta,
Tang kamsangte gensa,
A kum a kha hong veei ding a,
Hong tung ding kham hun pha,
Leitung-ah nopna lemna pha,
A vaang hong taang ding ta,
Vantung mite hong sak la pha,
Leitung mi'n dawng ding ta.

zoTitle: Vantung Mite'n La Sa, Ngai Un
engTitle: Hark, the Herold Angels Sing (Tune: Mendelssohn)
verse1:
Ngai un, vantung mi'n la sa,
A suak Topa min than' na,
Leitung nuamna hong khang sak hi,
Mawhna kheempeuh phel ding ci,
Leitung mi kheempeuhte in,
Lungdamna tawh tho un la,
Zeisu Betlen-ah suak hi,
Vanpi dongah min thang hi,
Vantung mite'n la sa hi,
"A suak Topa minthang," ci.
verse2:
Zeisu Topa Pasian Ta,
A om tawntung Kumpipa,
Nungak sung pan hong suak hi,
Mi bangin-ah hong piang hi,
Pasian in mi bang piang a,
Pasian itna mi sungah,
Ka hong khawlkhawm sak nuam ci,
Emanuela Zeisu hi,
Vantung mite'n la sa hi,
"A suak Topa minthang," ci.
verse3:
Zeisu lungdamna pia hi,
Mi siangtho a min kici,
Natna gimna a om lo,
A taang vantung a mial lo,
Vaangliatna a paai Maangpa,
Sih kikna a pelsak Pa,
Misi hing kik sak ding a,
Zeisu in leitung hong suak,
Vantung mite'n la sa hi,
"A suak Topa minthang," ci.

zoTitle: Zeisu In A Omna A Nusia Hi
verse1:
Zeisu in van ah tokhom nusia a,
Mi aading leitung hong pai zo,
A hong suak dingin Betlen khua sungah,
A hong suah nading inn om lo.
verse2:
Zeisu in a hong kum suk laitakin,
Vantung mite'n pengkul tum hi,
Hih hang gina lo bek tawh hong suak a,
Leitung hong kiniam sak ta hi.
verse3:
Ngia in zong kua nei a vasa in zong,
Sing dawnah bu a nei uh hi,
Hih hang Galile gam Zeisu om lai,
A lupna leitung bek a hi.
verse4:
Zeisu in zawhna tawh hong pai suk ciang,
Peengkul aw tawh hong pai ding hi,
Amah'n a aw tawh keimah hong sam ding,
"Ka kiang om in" hong ci ding hi.
chorus:
Keima lungsim sung hong om in!
Nang aading omna a om hi,
Keima lungsim sung hong om ta in!
Nang aading omna a om hi.

engTitle: There's A Song In the Air (Tune: Christmas Song)
verse1:
Huih lakah la kisa, aksipi hong kilang,
Nu migi'n thu ngen a, naungek khat a kap bang,
Bang hang aksi hong kilang,
bang hang la kisa,
Betlen khua sungah hong suah hang hi, Kumpipa.
verse2:
Lungdamna gamlum pha,
Naungek lamdang suah hang,
Naungek siangtho Tapa,
leitung kheempeuh te maang,
Aksipi hong taang suk hi, Vantung mi'n la sa,
Betlen khua sungah hong suah hang hi, Kumpipa.
verse3:
Khang tawntung lamet na, tua aksi'n tangko hi,
Van pan gamla kiza, leitung teng kizeel hi,
Bang hang hiam hih innkuan sungah om lungdamna,
Zeisu hong suak zo hi, Innkuan sung Kumpipa.
verse4:
I khuavaak hong tung ta, eite i lungdam hi,
Vantung mite' sak la, eite'n i sasawn hi,
Sa un vantung mite'n hong puak lungdamna thu,
Ei hong honpa Kumpipa hi, Zeisu.

verse1:
Tapidawte nuam un, lungdam in kipak un,
Kong thu gen teng na ngai un,
Ngai un tu ni'n Zeisu hong suak hi,
Bawngte sakol te'n bia hi,
Tu in bawngkuang sungah om hi,
Khazih hong suak hi, Khazih hong suak hi.
verse2:
Tapidawte nuam un, lungdam in kipak un,
Ngai un bei ngeilo nuamna,
Nuamna nuam nading Zeisu suak hi,
Vantung kongpi hong zo hi,
Mihing nuamsa tawntung ding hi,
A hong suah manin, A hong suah manin.
verse3:
Tapidawte nuam un, lungdam in kipak un,
Sih ding tu in lau nawn lo,
Lau lo hong hon ding Zeisu suak zo,
Eite sap loh hong nei lo,
Ama innpi sung kua ut lo,
Hong hon ding suak zo, Hong hon ding suak zo.

verse1:
Lupna luai om lo a Bawng ankuang sungah,
I Topa ngek Zeisu hong kisial ciuciau,
Van pan aksite in hong en suk kiukiau,
I Topa ngeek Zeisu lopa tung ihmu.
verse2:
Bawngte ham papa a Naungek khanglo ta,
I Topa ngek Zeisu lah kap se lo hi,
Topa ngek Zeisu aw, ke'n nang kong ngai hi,
Ka luai kiangah hong cingin zingsang mateng.
verse3:
Ka kiangah nai takin Hong ompih in la,
Ka Topa Zeisu aw kei hong ngai in la,
Naupangno-te kheempeuh hong kem ciat in la,
Nang kiang om thei na ngin a pha'n hong bawl in.

verse1:
Dai dide, Zan siangtho!,
Mial khikhe tawm simloh,
Gal a Naungek lupna kiim,
Nu siangtho le a ma kiim,
Naungek limtak ihmu,
Naungek limtak ihmu.
verse2:
Dai dide, Zan siangtho!,
Thakhatin theihkholh loh,
Tuucingte' kiim taang pempam!
Vantung pan phatna puakkham!,
Khazih hong suak zo hi,
Khazih hong suak zo hi.
verse3:
Dai dide, Zan siangtho!,
Mipil te'n van en to,
Lamhilh Aksi taang zui-in,
Lut uh hi biakna luui-in,
I Kumpi hong suak zo,
I Kumpi hong suak zo.
verse4:
Dai dide, Zan siangpen!,
Aksi pi'n hong taan hen,
Vantungmite bangin ah,
Sa un Kumpi phatna la,
Hong Honpa hong suak hi,
Hong Honpa hong suak hi.

zoTitle: Tuu Cingte'n Tuute A Cin Laitak'
engTitle: While Shepards Watched Their Flock (Tune: Winchester Old)
verse1:
Tuucing te'n zan lai gam lakah,
Tuu vil a om laitak,
Vantung mite hong pai suk a,
A vaang lianpi hong lak.
verse2:
Tuucing te'n lau man vantung mi'n,
"Lau kei un, thuphapi,
Note le leitung mi aading,
Tu in kong paipih hi."
verse3:
Davuih khua Betlen khuapi sung,
Hong gum dingin Khazih,
Davuih suan mihing pawl sung pan,
Tuni in hong suak hi.
verse4:
Bawngkuang sung puan tawh kitun a,
Naupang in a om hi,
No tu in pai un zong un la,
No na mu ding uh hi.
verse5:
Vantung mi'n a cih laitakin,
Van maangte hong pai a,
Pasian vaang lian mahmah ci,
Sa uh hih phatna la.
verse6:
Vanah Pasian min lian hen la,
Leitung nuamna om hen,
Hong hehpihna le hong itna,
Mi tung om tawntung hen.

engTitle: Angels We Have Hourd on High
verse1:
Vantung mite la sakna,
Zang leitung ah kiza hi,
Mualsang te'n zong sang sawn a,
Lumgdam la kithawn hi.
verse2:
Tuucingte no lungdamna,
Nuamna late bang thu hiam?,
Vantung la ngaih no sakna,
Lungdamna thu bang hang hiam?
verse3:
Betlen khua-ah hong pai in,
Note'n zong hong en ve vua,
Khazih Kumpi khuk din'in,
Note'n zong hong phat pih un.
chorus:
Thang....... ta hen,
Pasian minthang ta hen,
Thang....... ta hen,
Van a sang bel Pasian.

verse1:
Ni dang lai in, Davuih khua-ah,
Bawngbuk neu khat a om hi,
Tua bawngbuk sung, bawngkuang sungah,
Nu khat in ta a sial hi,
Tua nu min Mazih hi a,
A ta min Zeisu Khazih.
verse2:
Zeisu pen Pasian le Topa,
Van pan hong kum suk a hi,
Bawngbuk sungah hong giak suk a,
Bawngkuang sungah hong lum hi,
Mizawngte tawh leitung-ah, 
Amah hong kikhawl suk hi.
verse3:
A neulai lamdang mahmah a,
A nu zahtak in mang hi,
A nu in phatak in kem a,
A nu a it mahmah hi,
Tapidaw naupangte zong,
Tua bang mah ding i hihi.
verse4:
Amah'n hong it, hong tat manin,
 Nun ciang a meel mu ding hi,
Vantung-ah Pasian taklam ah,
Tokhom tungah tu ding hi,
A ta te'n puanpaak silh in,
A kiimah a uum ding hi.

engTitle: We Three Kings of Orient Are
verse1:
Ko teng thum ni suahna pan in,
Mual le guam gamlapi kan in,
Letsong pua in kong pai uh hi,
Hih aksipi zui in.
verse2:
Kumpi khat suak zo ngel hi a,
A kumpi lukhu dingin ah,
Ei tung hong maang den ta hen ci'n,
Kong puak hi, Kham manpha.
verse3:
Ke'n zong paaknamtui kong keng hi,
Pasian tawh kinai-na lim hi,
Thu ngetna leh phatna, biakna,
Van a Pasian puak ni.
verse4:
Kei aa pawh paaknamtui kha hi,
Lung khamna leh thuakna lim hi,
Dah in, kap in, sisan luangin,
Han vot sung lum ding hi.
chorus:
Aw, lamdang mahmah zan aksi,
Kumpi vaang a taang aksi,
Hong masuan in, lam hong hilh in,
Khuavaak tak phual hong tun in.

engTitle: Angels From the Realms of Glory (Regent Square)
verse1:
Vantung gam pan vantung mite, 
Vannuai piancil la sate,
Leitung khempeuh-ah hong leeng un,
Tu'n Mesia' suah thangsak un,
Hong pai ta un, Hong bia ta un,
Suak thak Khazih hong bia un.
verse2:
Gampa lakah tuu honte tawh,
Zan giak, no, tuu cingte' aw,
Pasian le mi om khawm zo hi,
En un khuavaak ngek taang hi,
Hong pai ta un, Hong bia ta un,
Suak thak Khazih hong bia un.
verse3:
Mipilte aw, lunggeel nawn ke'n,
A taang zaw khuavaak en ven,
Mi namkim deih lian pen zong un,
A aksi no mu zo tu'n,
Hong pai ta un, Hong bia ta un,
Suak thak Khazih hong bia un.
verse4:
Topa thakhat Ama innah,
Hong kilang ding, ci in-ah,
Ngak a, lawp a, lametna tawh,
Bia-a om mi siangte aw,
Hong pai ta un, Hong bia ta un,
Suak thak Khazih hong bia un.

verse1:
Zeiss hoihna keima sung kilang sakin,
A lamdang hong itna leh A siangthona,
Aw Pasian Kha Siangtho,
kei pumpi hong sawpsiang,
Zeisu hoihna keima sung kilang sakin.

Topa tung lungdam ngah nuamte,
Kisak theihna paii in,
Um in Ama thu a phate,
Hong piak ding ngaihsun in.
verse2:
A thule hong itna pha a 
A si tawh hong sawp hi,
I mawhna khempeuh hong sawp a,
Nopna pha kingah hi.
verse3:
Mawhna vaanglian sugawpna ding,
Siamna pha hong pia hi,
Lungsim sunga sian'thona ding,
Kha pha hong bawlsak hi.
verse4:
A dang lungsim zawhna dingin,
Kha Siangtho hong pia hi,
A pha bel Khazih Topa in,
I lung sungah om hi.
chorus:
Mawh phelna nuam vaanglianpi,
Lungdam sak ning, A min phatna,
Sian'thona pha, Vantung om hi,
Kei tang si hi, Zeisu Khazih Topa.

verse1:
Topa Zeisu aw, kei ka siangtho nuam hi,
Keima lungsim sungah hong om tawntung in,
Gal khempeuh nawtkhia in, hoih lote paai in,
Nong sawp leh ka ngo zaw ding hi, vuk sangin.
verse2:
Topa Zeisu aw, A siang lo bei sak in.
Na sipha tawh Nong sawp ciang mawhna bei hi,
Mawhna khempeuh paisan siangtho ngah nading 
Nong sawp leh ka ngo zaw ding hi, vuk sangin.
verse3:
Topa Zeisu aw, Na kiang kong thum nuam hi,
Nakhut nuai panin ka na ngakngak ding hi,
Upna tawh na si buakna ka mu zo hi,
Nong sawp leh ka ngo zaw ding hi, vuk sangin.
verse4:
Ngak a thuaknate Topa in na mu hi,
Lungsim thak ka sungah nong guansak zo hi,
Topa kiang hong pai khempeuh na nial kei hi,
Nong sawp leh ka ngo zaw ding hi, vuk sangin.
chorus:
Vuk sang ka ngo zaw tham nading in,
Topa aw Nangma sipha tawh hong sawp in.

zoTitle: A Lamdang Tangthu La Sa Ning
engTitle: I Am Sing the Wondrous Story
verse1:
A lamdang tangthu la sa ning,
Zeisu kei taang ding si hi,
Vantung min than'na nusia a,
Singlamteh sihna thuak hi.
verse2:
A gammangte Zeisu'n zong hi,
Lam a khial tuu-te zong hi,
A khut tawh keimah hong pom hi,
Lampi-ah hong kha kik hi.
verse3:
Cina te Zeisu'n damsak a,
A kipuk te zong phong hi,
Mittaw in a launa tam a,
Ahih hang hong gum ding hi.
verse4:
Khuamial kei tungah hong tung ta,
Dahna lampi ka zui ta,
Kei hong ompih in Topa aw,
Hong keem in lam hong hilh ta.
verse5:
Sihna gun gal kah mateng-in,
Topa in hong cing ding hi,
I itte tawh kimu ding in,
Gun gal-ah hong kha ding hi.
chorus:
A lamdang tangthu la sa ning,
Zeisu si hi kei tang ding,
Lim lang tui thuk gei kikhop ciang,
Mi siangtho te tawh sa ning.

verse1:
Topa Pasian longal vanah,
Muan' ding dang om lo hi,
Nun'tak laiteng ka sak ding la,
Zeisu kei aading hi,
Topa'n kei tang gimna thuak hi,
A sipha tawh hong sawp zo hi,
Lungsim siangtho hong guan' zo hi,
Zeisu kei aading hi.
verse2:
Mi a haute ka eng kei hi,
Zeisu kei aading hi,
Leitung sum ke'n ka deih kei hi,
Zeisu kei aading hi,
Leitung hauhna kip lo ding hi,
Na khempeuh kisia gawp ding hi,
Kei nuamna bei thei lo ding hi,
Zeisu kei aading hi.
verse3:
Zawng a gimna ka thuak hangin,
Zeisu kei aading hi,
Ka thum nop loh Topa'n thei hi,
Zeisu kei aading hi,
Ka sum khempeuh ka zang zongin,
Leitung sum a sia khin zongin,
Ganhing teng a si khin zongin,
Zeisu kei aading hi.
verse4:
Galte khutsung ka tung zong in,
Zeisu kei aading hi,
Kisiatna in hong umm hangin,
Zeisu kei aading hi,
Leitung gal a kido hangin
Ka kha in a kap hangin ah,
Topa min tawh ka zo ding hi,
Zeisu kei aading hi.

engTitle: Jesus Is All the World To Me
verse1:
Zeisu-ah deihna teng cing hi,
Hin'na nuamna vannuai,
Nisim in Ama tha loin,
Ka puk ding a lauhuai,
Ka dah ciang Ama kiang ka pai,
Mun dang bang lo ka mai a taii,
Ka dah ciang hong nuamsak, Amah keima lawm.
verse2:
Zeisu-ah deihna teng cing hi,
Lungkham laitak ka Lawm,
Thupha deihin Amah zuan leng,
Aman'n hong pia nawnnawn,
Ni taang le guahtui hong pia hi,
Tuk ciangin an hong la sak hi,
Ni taang, guahtui, le an hong pia keima lawm.
verse3:
Zeisu-ah deihna teng cing hi,
A tung ka thumaan ding,
Kei tungah hong thumaan ka Lawm,
Bang ci ka nial zo ding,
Amah zui leng ka khial ngei kei,
Sun le zan hong cing khial ngei kei,
Sun le zan in zui ning Amah, keima lawm.
verse4:
Zeisu-ah deihna teng cing hi,
Lawmpha zaw deih tuan keng,
Amah tu in ke'n ka muang a,
Muang lai ding sih mateng,
Hihbang Lawm tawh nuntak a nuam,
Bei ngeilo ding hin'na a nuam,
Bei ngeilo nuntakna, nuamna keima lawm.

engTitle: Jesus, the Very Thought of Thee (Tune: St. Agnes)
verse1:
Zeisu thu ngaihsut lai takin,
Lungdam huai mahmah hi.
Hih sang a mai ka muh ciangin,
Lungdam zawlai ding hi.
verse2:
Zeisu a kici min sangin,
Min ngaih zaw om lopi.
Vantung leitung a hi zongin,
Kimu zo ngeilo hi.
verse3:
Dahna a thuakte a muan'na,
Lungniam khiatte nuamna
Thu ngen a zong mite aading,
Itna lian bel hi ta.
verse4:
Na muh mite kilak thei kei,
Thupha a ngah uh hi.
A kisim khin zo lo itna,
Topa Zeisu thu hi.
verse5:
Topa Zeisu Nangmah sim lo,
Nuamna dang om nawn lo.
Tu leh nung ciang a tawntungin,
Komau phat ding om in.

verse1:
Mual tung khua sam lakah,
Migi tuucing in
A tuu mang a zong hi,
Ciahpih dingin.
verse2:
Citak in a zong hi,
Sum man’suah nu in,
Leivui lak khuamial lak,
Lungkia lo in.
verse3:
It tawntung a pa in,
Nuamna tangko hi
"A mang thang sa ka ta, Hong tung zo hi."
chorus:
Hon ding zong hi, Hon ding zon hi,
A mangte Zeisu’n, Hon ding zong hi.
Hon ding zong hi, Hon ding zong hi,
A mangte Zeisu’n, Hon ding zong hi.

engTitle: Once I Was Dead in Sin
verse1:
Si ngei ing mawhna ah,
Lawpna ding om lo hi.
Topa kei tang si a,
Ka nungta kik zo hi.
verse2:
Bat zawh loh ding sang hi,
Lamdang hi, hong itna
Hong gum Topa bekin,
Tua bang itna nei hi.
verse3:
Thupha thei lo ka kha,
Zeisu in nial ding hiam?
Ki-itna bek pha sa,
Biakna sang deih zaw hi.
verse4:
Zeisu hang keimah in,
Hin’na ka ngah kik hi.
Mawhna sung sihna pan,
Kei hong la khia zo hi.
chorus:
Hi zo ding hiam, Topa Zeisu
Kei hong it man’n si hi.

verse1:
Nungta kik Na thupha,
Mi siangte kiang tung ta.
Mi dangte kiang min than’na tawh
Na gen ciang ngai nuam sak.
verse2:
Nungta kik Na thupha,
Na minpha thang sak ni
Mihing khempeuh lungsim sungah
Na itna guang sak in.
verse3:
Nungta kik Na thupha,
Thu hilh a pha pia a
A siangthona thupha zak ciang
Upna na piangsak ta’n.
verse4:
Nungta kik Na thupha,
Kha Siangtho hong guang in
Na min than’na kilang sakin
Ko aadingin a pha.
chorus:
Nungta kik Na thupha,
Na mai khukdin’ ciangin
Topa aw, hong kum suk in la,
Thupha bel hong pia in.

verse1:
Topa Zeisu hong hehpihna,
Lungdam in la sa un.
Leitung kheempeuh a zelh na’ngin,
Lungdam nading kum hi.
verse2:
Mittawte Zeisu en un,
A dahte lungdam un,
Zeisu in hong suahtak zo hi,
Thong sung omte’n sa un.
verse3:
Hong it manin Zeisu si a,
Phat huai lamdang bel hi.
Topa min thang leitung mawhna,
Mi teng hong itna hi.
chorus:
Hong gupna, hong gupna,
Thupha bel hong tung hi.
Hong gum ta, hong gum ta,
Topa Zeisu Kumpi.

zoTitle: Zeisu’ Min Manpha Na La in
engTitle: Take the Name of Jesus With You
verse1:
Zeisu' min manpha na la in,
Dahna gimna' tate aw;
Hehnep nuamna hong pia dingin,
Na paina peuhah keng aw.
verse2:
Zeisu' min na kem tawntung in,
Gal nam kim kidalna lum;
Zeet-na’n hong kimkot ciangin,
A’ min siangtho suangin thum.
verse3:
Zeisu' min a manpha mahmah,
Bangzah i lung hong damsak,
Hong saan’ ciang Ama ang sungah,
Ama la i sak laitak.
verse4:
Lam tawp vantung i tun’ ciangin,
Zeisu’ khe-ah i bok ding;
Kumpi kheempeuh tung Kumpi, ci’n,
Ama maiah i bia ding.
chorus:
Min manpha, Ngaih mahmah!
Leitung mite' lametna;
Min manpha, Ngaih mahmah
Vantungah lungdam nuamna

zoTitle: Mawh Neite Aw Hong Pai Un
verse1:
Zeisu in vantung om napi, Leitung ah hong pai suk hi.
Mihingte taang ding hong om a, Cinate ci damsak hi.
Lai Siangtho sungah kithei ta, A hoih a lian pha bel hi.
verse2:
Khua khempeuh ah a kawi vak a, Mi khempeuh a hehpih hi.
Mihing zawngkhal khempeuhte le, Mittaw, khelbai, misite
A thu in hong dam kiksak a, Lamdang kisa mahmah hi.
verse3:
Zeisu in leitung om lai in, Thupha vive a gen hi.
Keimah zong Zeisu ka um hi, Ka lungdamna piang ding hi.
Ka up lohna Pa Pasian in, Phatak in hong bawl pha in.
verse4:
Pasian in thupha hong piakna, Zeisu’n mi kiangah gen hi.
Mihing kim khat in a um a, Kim khat in a um lo hi.
A um lote in lung khamna, Zeisu cih bang piang ding hi.
verse5:
Ka sih taang ding Topa Zeisu, Singlamteh tungah si hi.
Ama lawmte in a vui a, Ni thum ciang a tho kik hi.
Tu’n vantung khua-ah a om a, Mi kheempeuh a hehpih hi.

verse1:
Zeisu in mawhna hong phel zo.
Hong gum Topa lamdang hi.
Hong tatsa a man a pia zo.
Hong gum Topa lamdang hi.
verse2:
Pasian tawh hong kilem sak hi.
Hong gum Topa lamdang hi.
Hong silsiang si ka phat ding hi.
Hong gum Topa lamdang hi.
verse3:
Lungsim sung mawhna a phel hi.
Hong gum Topa lamdang hi.
I lungsung ah om a uk hi.
Hong gum Topa lamdang hi.
verse4:
Keimah tawh lampi a pai hi.
Hong gum Topa lamdang hi.
Nism in hong keemsak ding hi.
Hong gum Topa lamdang hi.
chorus:
Zeisu in hong Gumpa hi. A lamdang ka sa hi.
Keima Topa Zeisu in, Hong Gumpa a hi.

verse1:
Aw! Ngai un, A lamdang bel tangthu
Mangthang mi lak a simsa;
Vantung pan a hong tuaksuk Zeisu
Haksa-pi’n hong hon'khia hi.
verse2:
Van a a sang mahmah vantung mi
Hong gum zo ding om lo a,
Singlamteh tung a thuakpa bek hi,
Pasian thum lak a khat Pa
verse3:
Hih lamdang tangthu in zui lai a,
Lungsim le kam lawpsak hi;
Van ah hong thumsak Siampi Lianpa
A min Zeisu Khazih hi.
chorus:
Kua’n a si ding hon’khia a hiam?
Amah’n bang hih? Koiah om tu’n?
Vantung-ah hong thumsak hi.

verse1:
A siam bel hong damsak thei Pa,
Hong it Topa Zeisu hi.
Dahna hong nopsak na’ng in-ah,
A hong sapna aw ngai in.
verse2:
Na mawhna a hong phel Topa,
A hong sapna aw ngai in.
Vantung lam nuam tak zui in la,
Zeisu tawh kham lu khu in.
verse3:
A hing kik Tuuno vaanglian,
Pa Zeisu ke’n ka hong um hi.
Hong gum Topa Na min a pha,
A lian bel ka ci ding hi.
verse4:
Zeisu maitang mu ding in-ah,
Vantung ka pai toh ciangin
A hong itna tokhom kiangah,
Phatna la sa tawntung ning.
chorus:
Vantung mi a la sakna,
Leitung mi ha bel cihna
Sa ni a ngaih mahmah la,
Zeisu pha bel min hi.

verse1:
A mangte hong zong in hong zol ngeungeu,
Mual sang tung-a lam a khial mite;
"Keimah hong zuan un," hong ci kik leuleu,
Topa’n tuni in hong sam eite.
verse2:
A mangte zong in, Zeisu lam lak in
Tha hat lo kha leh a na lungsim.
Hot khiatna lampi sungah makaih in,
Nuntak tawntung na lampi lak in.
verse3:
Tua bangin pai ni thupha na seem mi.
Khazih zui den ni a ni sial in
A bah mi lawp sak in, puk mi phong ni,
A mang mi, lampi Zeisu lak ni.
chorus:
Mual sang tung a gamla ah pai ni
A vak mite la kik in,
Mawhnei mi ta’ng ding a si Tuuno
I honpa' tuubuk-ah khum in.

verse1:
Hong gum Topa Betlen khua hong suak a
Bawng nekna ankuang sung kisial zo ta.
Aw a lamdang nuam a min pha mahmah
Keimah a hong zong hi.
verse2:
Topa Zeisu in singlamteh tungah
Kei mawhna tang dingin hong si zo ta.
Maw a lamdang keima lung a dam ta.
Keitang ding hong si hi.
verse3:
Topa Zeisu nidang bangmah in-ah
Huan sung pan lam khial tuu-te a zong ta
Sau veipi dam takin a hong sam hi.
Keimah a hong sam hi.
verse4:
Zeisu vantung pan hong pai kik ding hi.
Kum tampi kheng zo, hi thu ka um hi.
Vantung hong kum suk lai ka mu ding hi.
Kei aading hong kum hi.
chorus:
Keimah a hong zong hi, zong hi
Keimah a hong zong hi
Maw lamdang nuamna a minpha mahmah,
Keimah a hong zong hi.

verse1:
Gup khiatna thu thang sak nuam sing!
Tuuno si tawh gup khiat ka hih;
A it bei lo tawh gup khiat hi’ng,
A tawntung Ama ta ka hi.
verse2:
Gup khiat hi a, zeisu nuamsa
Ka lawpna gen zo kam om kei;
Ama ompihna khuavaak pha,
Kei sung hong tung den ding ka thei.
verse3:
Thupha Gumpa ka ngaihsun a,
Ngaih sunsun ing sun ni lohin;
Om mawk thei lo-in la ka sa
Hong itna sa ing, la pi in.
chorus:
Gup khiat, gup khiat,
Gup khiat, gup khiat,
Tuuno si tawh gup khiat ka hi,
Gup khiat, gup khiat,
Gup khiat, gup khiat,
A tawntung Ama ta ka hi.

verse1:
Leitung nopna te lunggulh nawn kei ing,
Sisan hangin launa pan suakta ta’ng,
Singlamteh phungah ka lungsim nga ing,
Zeisu si in vuk bangin hong ngo sak zo hi.
verse2:
Mawhna sungah khatvei ka mangthang hi,
Khatvei mawhna sila ka hi zo hi,
Pasian ka hehsak ding ka lau ngei hi,
Ahih hang Khazih si in nitna teng sil hi.
verse3:
Kol bulhna thuak ngei hang tu’n suakta ing,
Khuamial sung om ngei hang tu’n khuavaak mu’ng;
Si ngei zo hih hang tu’n Khazih sung hing,
Hong piak khiat kilemna leitung teng ka gen ding.
chorus:
Ka it hi, ka it hi. Amah’n hong it masa,
Kalani khuam tung gupna hong lei sak hi.

zoTitle: Zeisu Tangthu Kei Hong Gen In
engTitle: Tell Me the Story of Jesus
verse1:
Zeisu tangthu kei hong hilh in, A thu ka lungsung gelh in,
A manpha tangthu hong gen in, Zak ngei nai loh thu khum pen;
A suah lai vantung mite sak, La ngaihte hong sak dih in,
Sang bel na ah Pasian thang hen, Leitung kilemna om hen.
verse2:
Sehnel gam an ngawl in om-a, A hih teng hong gengen in,
Ei mawhna hang ze-etna a thuak Thuak hang a zawh teitei-na
A thuak kum sung hong gen dih in, Dahna gimna a puak teng,
Bawlsiat, cilphih a thuakna te, Simmawh nilkhiat a thuakna.
verse3:
Singlamteh in kilh a thuakna, Na sa’n lunggim a om-na,
Han sung guang a, a kicin' na Sihna pan a hin' kikna
Hong gengen in a tangthute, Ka muh ngei loh a siang zaw’n,
Khitui luangin hong kap sak hi, Kei hong tan tua itna in.
chorus:
Zeisu tangthu kei hong hilh in, A thu ka lungsung gelh in.
A manpha pen Zeisu tangthu, Kei hong ciamteh thei sak in.

verse1:
Zeisu min bangzah in ngaih hiam,
Ama' late sasa nuam ing;
Ka lung hong kim sak mahmah hi,
Tua a min manpha Zeisu!
verse2:
Ka lungsim le ka dahna teng,
A thei khin pa’ min ngaih ka sa;
Launa lung mannate beisak,
Tua Zeisu min ka it hi.
verse3:
Tua min ngaih ka zaza nuam hi, Ka lungsim hong nop sak khial kei;
Ama late’n khitui nul sak; Tua Zeisu min thangsak un!
verse4:
Kua mah’n gen thei ngei  het lo hi. Aw, tua min phat na bek ging hi,
Tua ka it min, baangzah’n ngaih hiam; Aw, Zeisu min phat ve un.
chorus:
"Zeisu" Aw, bangzah a ngaih min! "Zeisu" Ni sim in tua mah;
"Zeisu" kici tua min manpha Phat tek ni, a a tawntung.

verse1:
Hong hehpihna thupha, Lungsim khauh zo thei hi.
Leitung a it man a, A Tapa hong pia hi.
verse2:
Gamlakah gul ki-khai, A noptuam mah bangin
Topa Zeisu ki-khai, Nun'tak tawntung na’ng hi.
verse3:
Mawh neite sih kik ding, Thu khenna i thei hi,
Na thu bang zui lo leng, Kisia takpi ding hi.
verse4:
Leitung mawhsak ding a, Zeisu hong pai lo hi.
A min than' mah bangah, Leitung hong gum ding hi.
verse5:
A um lote hehpih, Um na’ng lungsim guan’ hi.
Thupha bel hong tun' ve’n, Hong um phasak ta hen.
chorus:
Kuamah peuhmah in thu um leh
Hin' tawntungna pha ngah ding hi.
Hin' tawntungna pha ngah ding hi.

zoTitle: Kei Hong Honpa A Si Luangin
engTitle: Alas! and Did My Saviour Bleed? (Tune: Martyrdom)
verse1:
Kei hong Honpa A' si luangin,
Ka Kumpi hong si maw.
Tangtel bang bek keimah aading.
A lu tang hong zang maw.
verse2:
Keima gitloh nate hangin,
Singlamteh tung tau maw.
Lamdang hehpihna le itna,
Bang tawh teh thei ding maw.
verse3:
Kei zong singlamteh ka muh ciang,
Zum in ka kiseel diam
Lungdamna tawh lung nehno in,
Ka khi ka luangsak diam
verse4:
Ahih hang khitui takna in,
Itna loh khin zo kei.
Topa, ka pumpi kong pia hi,
Hih kan ka hih thei kei.

verse1:
Hong hon Topa Zeisu talah,
Mi gitna nuam pha tuang;
A lu tung vaangliatna khu a,
A muk pan itna luang,
A muk pan itna luang.
verse2:
Leitung mi tehpih ding om lo,
Amah a pha bel hi
Vaantung mi lakah zong om lo,
Amah kilawm bel hi,
Amah kilawm bel hi.
verse3:
Gimna sung ka kia hong mu-a,
Hon ding hong delh pah hi;
Kei aa ding singlamteh pua a,
Kei dahna kisuan hi,
Kei dahna kisuan hi.
verse4:
Ama hangin kei ka nungta,
Nuamna zong a hong pia;
Hong gualzo sak sihna tungah, Han sung pan hong hon khia,
Hansung pan hong hon khia.
verse5:
Ama omna vantung khua-ah,
Kei hong tun' pih ding hi;
Pasian phatna hong lak ding a,
Ka nuamna kim ding hi,
Ka nuamna kim ding hi.
verse6:
Pasian citna leh hong itna,
Hi bang ka theih nung sang,
Lungsim tul nei leng zong, Topa,
Kong pia khin ding hi Nang,
Kong pia khin ding hi Nang.

verse1:
Singlamteh kiangah omna, Kalani mual tungah
Nuamna hong pia ciktui in,
Mi teng aa ding luang ta.
verse2:
Singlamteh kiang ka ding a. hehpihna’n hong mu a,
A taang zingsol aksi in, Ka kiimkot a taang ta.
verse3:
Zeisu singlamteh kiangah, Ngak-a kong om ciangah
Singlamteh a liim nuaiah, Hong gum hong om sak in.
verse4:
Singlamteh kiangah ka om, A thu um tawntung ning
Gun gal khat a kham khua in, Ka tun’ mateng ngak ning
chorus:
Singlamteh, singlamteh, Ka kisak theihna hi.
Vantung khua ka tun’ ciangin, A nuam ka ngah na’ng hi.

engTitle: Beneath the Cross of Jesus (1st Tune)
verse1:
Zeisu singlamteh nuai-ah, Kei mah’n ka beel nuam hi.
Ni sat phatna gam sung panin, Suangpi liim bang a hi.
Gampa lakah om laitakin, Ni sa liahna a hi.
Van gik mite’n van khia ding a.
A gimte khawl na’ng hi.
verse2:
Zeisu’n singlamteh tungah, kei tang gimna thuak hi.
A pumpi a siat laitakin, Keimah’n ka mu thei hi.
Ka et lai ka khitui luang a, Dah inah ka liing hi.
Tua itna bang dang om lo a,
Gilo mihi'ng ka ci.
verse3:
Zeisu singlamteh liim sung keima omna a hi./nZeisu maitang vaang simlohin 
Ni taang dang omlo hi.
Leitungah sum bangin tuate a met zang thei lopi.
Ka mawhna zumhuaina a hi 
Singlamteh thahna hi.

engTitle: Beneath the Cross of Jesus (2nd Tune)
verse1:
Zeisu singlamteh nuai-ah, Kei mah’n ka beel nuam hi.
Ni sat phatna gam sung panin, Suangpi liim bang a hi.
Gampa lakah om laitakin, Ni sa liahna a hi.
Van gik mite’n van khia ding a.
A gimte khawl na’ng hi.
verse2:
Zeisu’n singlamteh tungah, kei tang gimna thuak hi.
A pumpi a siat laitakin, Keimah’n ka mu thei hi.
Ka et lai ka khitui luang a, Dah inah ka liing hi.
Tua itna bang dang om lo a,
Gilo mihi'ng ka ci.
verse3:
Zeisu singlamteh liim sung keima omna a hi./nZeisu maitang vaang simlohin 
Ni taang dang omlo hi.
Leitungah sum bangin tuate a met zang thei lopi.
Ka mawhna zumhuaina a hi 
Singlamteh thahna hi.

engTitle: There is a Green Hill Far Away
verse1:
Keima aading sihna a thuak Khuapi pualam om a
Zeisu singlamteh na om hi.
Gamla mualpi tungah.
verse2:
Amah in gimna a thuakna I theizo kei ding hi.
Ahih hang komau tang ding in,
Amah in a thuak hi.
verse3:
Eite kiphel na ngah ding in amah in a si hi.
A sipha tawh sawp siang man in 
Vantung i tung ding hi.
verse4:
Khialhna man piak nading in-ah, Mi dang siangtho kei hi.
Amah bek in vantung khua-ah,
A hong lusak thei hi.
chorus:
Amah’n pha takpi hong it hi. Amah i it kik hi.
A hong gum thei a si um in, Ama na i seem ding

verse1:
Sihkhuk a dimin kihong a, Sisan tuibang luang hi,
Tua si tawh kiphum mawh neite, Mawhna tawh kipelh hi.
Mawhna tawh kipelh hi. Mawhna tawh kipelh hi.
Tua si tawh kiphum mawh neite, Mawhna tawh kipelh hi.
verse2:
A si mi mawh pa’n tua sihkhuk a muh ciang a nuam a
Hih mi bang ka gitloh hangin, Mawhna kiphel thei ta.
Mawhna kiphel thei ta. Mawhna kiphel thei ta.
Hih mi bang ka gitloh hangin, Mawhna kiphel thei ta.
verse3:
A liamma-ah hong luang sipha Upna ka muh manin
Hong phelna ding itna a pha Ka sih mateng sa ning.
Ka sih mateng sa ning. Ka sih mateng sa ning.
Hong phelna ding itna la pha, Ka sih mateng sa ning.
verse4:
Nung ciang hih a gik i pum teng, Sih han sung om lai in.
Topa hong phel lung damna teng Vantungah la sa ning.
Vantungah la sa ning. Vantungah la sa ning.
Topa hong phel lung damna teng, Vantungah la sa ning.
verse5:
It huai Tuuno Na si manpha. Bei hun nei ngeilo ding
Gupna ngah mi teng kikhawm ding, Mawh ngei nawn lo ding hi.
Mawh ngei nawn lo ding hi. Mawh ngei nawn lo ding hi.
Gupna ngah mi teng kikhawm ding, Mawh ngei nawn lo ding hi.

engTitle: When I Survey the Wondrous Cross (1st & 2nd Tune: Rockingham)
verse1:
Vaanglian kumpipa hong sihna,
A singlamteh ke’n velvel leng,
Kei hauhna kei kiphatsak-na,
Ke’n tu’n bangmah in sim nawn keng.
verse2:
Khazih ka Pasian sihna lo 
Kisialhpih ding bangmah om kei;
Ka deih bel teng khat zong siit lo,
Ama' si khekna in ka nei.
verse3:
En ven, A' lu, A' khut, A' khe!
Dahna, itna, hong luang suk khawm;
Na mu ngei maw ling lukhu leh 
Itna, dahna gawm kilawm khawn,
verse4:
Leitung kheempeuh pia thei hi leng,
Tam lua kaci ngei kei ding hi;
A hong itna ke’n ngaihsun leng,
Kaa pum ka tak ka pia nuam hi.

zoTitle: Ka Kumpi Na Hi Ta, Tu’n, Nang
verse1:
Ka kumpi Na hi ta tu’n, Nang; Vaangliatna teng tang in
Ling Na khu ka mangngilh loh na’ng 
Kalvari'a hong paipih in.
verse2:
Na kisialna han hong lak in, Nangmah hong kikahna,
Vantung mite’n puan paak silh in,
Nangmah a hong cin' na.
verse3:
Mazih bangin khuamui sungah, Nangmah hong dawnsak in,
Hong paipih in Kalvari ah,
Na han hawm hong lak in.
verse4:
Nangma aading ke’n pua nuam ing, Singlamteh ni simin;
Dahna na hai hong dawnpih ning, Kei aading Nang thuak khin.
chorus:
Getsemani mangngih loh na’ng,
Na thuakna ka mangnglih loh na’ng,
Nong itna ka mangngilh loh na’ng, Kalvari’n hong paipih’n.

verse1:
Leitung mawhna pulak dingin, A sipha min thang mahmah hi.
Pasian Tapa pha bel Zeisu, A liam manin i dam ta hi.
Tuu khum tawh i gamlat hangin, lam khial a gimna thuak hangin.
Vuk sang ka ngo zawk nading in, Tuuno si tawh hong sawpsiang in.
verse2:
Ling tawh kigan lukhu khu a, Singlamteh gik Topa’n pua hi.
Gimna dahnate thuak zo ta. Ahih hang mawkna hilo hi.
Leitung i mawh hong sawpsak ding, A si phualah ei hong la in.
Vuk sang ka ngo zawk nading in, Tuuno si tawh hong sawpsiang in.
verse3:
Pa aw, ke’n lam ka khial zo hi. Ka lungsim tamvei mawh zo hi.
Ka mawhna in si bang san a, Tui in kisawp siang zolo hi.
Keimah in na thuciam um leng, Na si buakna munah pai ning.
