Vuk sang ka ngo zawk nading in, Tuuno si tawh hong sawpsiang in.
chorus:
Vuk sang ngo zaw hi, Vuk sang ngo zaw hi
Vuk sang ngo zaw hi, tuuno si tawh hong sawpsiang leh(sawpsiang leh)
Vuk sangin ka ngo zawk nading hi (ding hi.)

verse1:
A lian a neu kua ci lo, Mawh, Mawhlo ci lo;
Zeisu’n vekpi aading khin, Sawtpi pek in.
verse2:
Saang pen A tokhom tung pan, kum in hong sih ciang,
Na khempeuh a vek in zo, A aw ngai dih un.
verse3:
Lunggim van pua na seem te’n, Koiah seem na hiam?
Khawl dih in Amah’n zo zo, Sawtpi pek in.
verse4:
Na vangik pi teng khia in ,Zeisu khe kiang khia’n
Amah bekbek kiang dingin, Na kheempeuh cin' khin.
verse5:
Zeisu nasep-sa muangin, Na up theih mateng
Han ciamna in kimang lo, Sihna hong tun’ zaw
chorus:
A zo zo hi! Takpi hi, vekpi’n zo khin hi.
Hih hi, mawh neite i sap mawhna pulak ding.

verse1:
Kalani ah Zeisu a si.
Hong gum Topa tua kithat hi.
Tua khuam tungah a si bua hi.
Mawh phel na’ngin a hong lei hi.
verse2:
Suangpi kitam khua hong mial hi. Hong gum Topa lusu, si hi.
A kiliahna puan kikeek a. Hon’sak lam sung nuam tawntung ta.
verse3:
Topa Zeisu aw, bangci hiam. Topa nangin hin’na hong pia.
Singlamteh pua haksa thuak hi. Launa sungah Kalani ah.
chorus:
Aw Kalani, aw Kalani.
Topa Zeisu sihna thuak hi.
Aw Kalani, aw Kalani.
Hong gum Topa, kei aading si.

zoTitle: Muh Khopna Ah Hin’na Om Hi
engTitle: There is A Life for a Look
verse1:
Singlamteh tung kikhai mi na muh ciangin
Thakhatthu’n hinna ngah ta un, ci.
Tua ahih ciang mawhnei te’n en un zong un,
Singlamteh a kithatpa en ni.
verse2:
Mawhna phel ding hi kei leh Amah in-ah,
Bang ding singlamteh thuak nuam ding hiam.
Mawhna pan sihna tawh hong tan nuam ding hiam
A pang pan si bang ding a luang diam.
verse3:
Kisikna bekin mawhna kiphel zo lo.
A si bek in a hong phel zo hi.
A si a hong bua Topa Zeisu kiangah,
Na khialhna khempeuh hong puak in ci.
verse4:
Hong sapna lung hian’ nading om lo ding hi.
Kicing zo hi, ci in hong sam hi.
Lei a bei ciang khatvei hong pai lai ding a
Thu ka hong khen ding hi, a ci hi.
chorus:
En un, hing ta un. 
A kikhai mipa en in hin na ngah ta un.
Thakhat in hin'na pha ngah ta un.

verse1:
Itna siangtho, Itna kicing,
Vantung nuamna, hong tuak suk
Nong hehpihna tung khup nading,
Ko sung hong lam in Na buk,
Zeisu aw, hehpihna Na dim, Itna Siang kicing Na hi;
Lawp-a liing ko kheempeuh lungsim,
Hotna tawh Nong veh ding hi.
verse2:
Lunghimawh mi lungsim sungah,
Itna Nangma Kha guan'in
Note khempeuh Nangma sungah,
Tawldamna hong luahsak in.
Ko mawh nopna lungsim pai khia’n Alpha le Omega in
Upna pan a cingsak Pasian,
Ko lungsim hong khah khia in.
verse3:
Hong pai in, a hon zo pen Pa,
Nang' nuntakna hong guan'in,
Na inn-ah hong tam meng in la,
Pai khia nawn peuhmah kei in.
Thupha kong piapia ding uh a,
Na’na ka seem ding uh hi;
Na itna sungah kipak ta,
Tawlnga lo kong phat ding hi.

verse1:
Zeisu in keimah hong itna,
Keimah hong tatnading inah
Singlamteh gilo hong thuakna,
Kam-a gen zawh hi-lo.
verse2:
Ka nuntak tawntung na’ng in-ah,
Nakpi dahna a hong thuakna,
Ling kiphan lukhu hong khukna,
Kam-a gen zawh hi-lo.
verse3:
Pasian kiang hong thumsak Topa,
Ama sung ka ngah lung nopna
Ama si hang hong piang thupha,
Kam-a gen zawh hi-lo.
verse4:
Hong nai ciang ka ngah lungdamna,
Launa kihei lo tawldamnna,
Ama hang lametna a pha, Kam-a gen zawh hilo.
chorus:
Hong itna kam' gen zawh hi-lo,
Hong itna kam' gen zawh hilo,
Zeisu in keimah hong itna,
Kam-a gen zawh hi-lo.

engTitle: In the Cross of Christ of I Glory (Tune: Rargbun)
verse1:
Singlamteh ka kipakna hi,
Ahun tawh kisia lo hi
Siangtho tangthu kheempeuhte' vaang,
Zeisu' singlamteh kiim taang.
verse2:
Nuntak dahna’n hong phak ciangin,
Lawm pa’n hong khem, lau ciangin
Singlamteh’n hong khem ngeilo hi,
Lungnop, nuamna hong pia hi.
verse3:
Lungdamna ni hong taan’ ciangin,
Itna khuavaak taan' ciangin,
Singlamteh vaang taang in ka ni
Hong taang phasak tuan lai hi.
verse4:
Lungdamna thupha na zak ciang,
Hong pai in, ci’n hong sam.
Upna tawh A si sung bual leeng,
Vuk bang hong ngo sak ding.

zoTitle: Ganhing Khempeuh In Gum Zo Kei
engTitle: Not All the Blood of Beasts (Tune: Boylston)
verse1:
Zudah mite biakna,
Ganhing pawlpawl a hi
Mawhna hong phel i lungdamna 
Neu kha beek piangsak kei
verse2:
Tuuno Khazih in-ah,
Tua biakna sang pha zaw
A si a manpha a hi a,
Mawhna phel thei ta hi.
verse3:
Keimah'n ka um zo hi.
Ka lu, ka khut, ka ngah
Mawhna khempeuh ka kisik hi.
Ka hong thum hi Topa.
verse4:
Singlamteh na tungah 
Nangmah'n na thuak gimna
Kei in ka lungngaih cianginah,
Na hong it ka thei ta.
verse5:
Biakna vantung Tuuno a umte nopsakna
Ke’n um a ka biak ka nuam zo,
Ka phat ding a itna.

verse1:
En in, thuk in a zai tuikhuk,
A luang tawntung tuikhuk;
Vang nih panin hong luang khia a,
Vuk bang hong ngosak ding,
Vuk bang hong ngo sak ding.
verse2:
Kalani khuam tungah,
Lungkham, Natna Thuakin hong si;
Lamdang sisan gun tui, hong luang,
Vuk bang hong ngo sak ding,
Vuk bang hong ngo sak ding.
verse3:
Mi khempeuh dam nading hong luang,
Tua thupha tuikhuk pan!
Upna tawh A si sung bual leeng,
Vuk bang hong ngo sak ding,
Vuk bang hoong ngo sak ding.
verse4:
Lung damna thupha na zaak ciang,/nHong pai in, ci’n hong sam
Upna tawh a si sung bual leeng,
Vuk bang hong ngo sak ding.
Vuk bang hong ngo sak ding.
chorus:
Hong pai hih tuikhuk 
Hong luang hi, tu ni’n
Hong pai khempeuh man ngen lo-in,
Na mawh hong sawp sak ding

verse1:
Manpha si, tawntung manpha si,
Tu’n kei aading manpha,
Tua si ha’ng bek ka kha tawldam,
Dahna teng beisak hi.
verse2:
Mangngilh ngei nawn peuhmah kei ni,
Zuau lo Pasian in ci
"Note mawhna khialhna tangin,
Ka Ta sisan ka bua."
verse3:
Mawhna ka bawl tampi ka thei;
Mai zo diam tuazah pi,
Ahih hang manpha si’n sawp hi,
Mawhna teng puakhia hi.
verse4:
A cimawh lungsim le pumpi,
Si ding a lum zong in,
Lungnuam takin kei ka si ding,
Tua manpha sisan hang.
chorus:
Aw! lamdang hi tua sisan luang,
Gumpa’ pang pan phul khia
Vantung dongah la in sa ning,
"A manpha bel sisan."

engTitle: There is Power in the Blood
verse1:
Na mawh vangik pan na suakta ding hiam?
Si sung, si sung vaangliatna om hi.
Siatna tungah nang na gual zo ding hiam?
Si sung vaanglian lamdang om hi.
verse2:
Na kiphatsak pan na suakta ding hiam?
Si sung, si sung vaangliatna om hi.
Siangtho ngah ding, Kalani tui zuanin
Si sung vaanglian lamdang om hi.
verse3:
Vuksangin na paak zaw mahmah ding hiam?
Si sung, si sung vaangliatna om hi.
Nuntakna tui sung mawhna nin siangta
Sisung vaanglian lamdang om hi.
verse4:
Na kumpi Zeisu' na naseem ding hiam?
Si sung, si sung vaangliatna om hi.
Nisim Amah phatna na sa ding hiam?
Si sung vaanglian lamdang om hi.
chorus:
Si sung vaanglian, vaanglian lamdang om
Tuuno si-san sungah
Si sung vaanglian, vaanglian lamdang om
A manpha Tuuno si sungah.

verse1:
Gamlapi mual tungah singlamteh tul gemgam,
Gentheihna, maizumna lim a hi.
Tua khuampi ka it hi, leitung buppi tan ding; 
A it huai-peen-Pa hong sih na hi.
verse2:
Mi in tua singlamteh a thusim loh hangin,
Ke’n ka phawk tawntung-na a thu in.
Pasian' Tuuno in vantung nopna nusia hi,
Kalani mualah tua pua ding in.
verse3:
Ka mawhna hong maisak, hong siangthosak dingin,
Sisan luangin Zeisu hong si hi.
Pasian Tapa' sisan siangtho a hong baanna;
Tua singlamteh ka veelveel nuam hi.
verse4:
Tua singlamteh khuampi ke’n nusia ngei kei ning,
Taina, zumna ka thuakpih hangin;
Tua hi leh khatvei ciang hong sam ding A innah,
Amah tawh a min thang khawm dingin.
chorus:
Tua singlamteh ke’n ngilh ngei kei ning,
Zawhna minpha ka tut zawh mateng;
Tua singlamteh khah lo lenlen ning,
Kham lukhu ka khekna ni mateng.

verse1:
En un, mawhna khempeuh a pua khia Pa,
Sihna Kalvary mual tungah
Singlamteh tung gimna sihna thuakin,
Kei aading in a sisan hong luang.
verse2:
Mawh sawp siang nang tui, a hong luang zo hi,
Hong Gum Topa sihna mun pan,
A tawntung in tua tui-ah kisilni,
Hong Gum Topa kiang zuan in pai ni.
verse3:
Tua si sunga a kisil khempeuhte,
A mawhna teng vuk bang ngo ding,
"Na mawhna khempeuh uh hong maisak ding,
Ka kiang hong pai un," Topa’n hong ci.
verse4:
Mawhna sungah ka paikik nawn kei ding,
Zeisu'n kei hong suakta sak ding.
A Kha Siangtho in kei hong pi dinga,
A gam sungah hong lutpih ding hi.
chorus:
Hong Gumpa Topa naak sungah,
Sisan leh tui hong luang khia hi.
Ka lung sungah om tawntung hi,
Mawhna kisawp siang zo.

engTitle: The Son of God Goes Forth To War
verse1:
Kumpipa lukhu ngah nading, Pasian Ta-pan’n do ding.
A dial khaina kilak ding hi. A nung kua in zui hiam?
Dahna a thuak hang thum lo-in, Gimna a zo thei mi.
Leitung singlamteh puate in, A nung a zui uh hi.
verse2:
Bawlsiat thuak pen nungzui khat in, Han gal khat mu thei hi.
Topa vantung khua-ah mu a "Hong gum in" ci’n ngen hi
Topa sih laitak a galte, A mawhna a phel bang
A thatte' aading thu ngen ta, Ama nung kua’n zui hiam?
verse3:
A teelsa sawmlehnih tungah, Kha Siangtho hong tum hi.
Amau upna a liat manin Pasian in a gum hi.
Bawl siatna tampi thuak ta leh, Sahang kihta lo hi.
Sihna thuak ding lu a su hi, Amau nung kua’n zui hiam?
verse4:
Mi siangthote tampi, tangval, nungak le nu le pa
Puanpaak silhin Zeisu mai ah, Lung damna la hong sa.
Launa, nasepna gimna in, Vantung lam kahto hi.
Topa amau nung zuih nading, Komau Nong huh ding hi.

engTitle: Lift up, Lift up, Your Voices now
verse1:
Awngun, Awngun la kiko un,
Leitung khempeuh lungdam khin uh;
Topa’n vaanglianpi tawh zozo,
Zawhna tawh naang ding hi, i To.
verse2:
Hankhuk suang tawh kikhak zo lo,
Galkapte in zong cing zo lo;
Vanglianpi tawh han phukham a
Zawhna vaanglian tawh hong tho ta
verse3:
Ama zawhsa, a thuaksa teng, Ei hong pia a,
Hawm sawn thei leeng,
Lawpna, nuamna, lungnop nading;
Ama zawh bang ei zong zo ding.
verse4:
Gal zopa aw, hong do pih in
Sihna pan khuavaak hong tun in;
Nang nung tawn leeng lung himawh lo,
Nang sung si leeng Pasian kiang tho.

verse3:
Nuam un, nuam un, Zeisu mi, lungdam in la sa un,
Hin' tawntung Haleluiah Zeisu Khazih Kumpi!
Muan’na tawh a zong mite’n, Amah mu thei ding uh,
Tua bang itna a nei mi dang om ngei kei.
chorus:
Hing e, hing e, hong hon Khazih Topa,
Hong tonpih a, hong hopih hi, Ka paina kheempeuh ah;
Hing e, hing e, mihing hon khia Topa
Bang ka ci theih hiam, nong cih leh, Ka lung sungah hing hi.

verse1:
Ih Topa hong thawh kik ni! Mun kheempeuh ah gen un
A lungdam huai Paisanna, Topa hong Paisanna,
Sihna pan tawntung nopna, Leitung pan vantung dong,
Khazih in hong suakta sak, gual zawhna la sa un.
verse2:
Lungsim khempeuh sian’ tho ni, Thumaan i muh thei ni
Tawntung Topa mel phat ni, Thawh kik khua hong vaak ni
Topa kam sung zak kik ni, Ama aw neem zakna,
Mite aw phatna la sa, gual zo Topa phat un.
verse3:
Vantung kheempeuh zong nuam ni, Leitung in zong phat hen;
Leitung kheempeuh gualzawh ni, na keempeuh a kim ni
Muhtheih muhmawh kheempeuh in, Lung damna la sa un,
A bei ngeilo lung damna, ih Topa hong thawh ni.

engTitle: Christ the Lord Risen Today (Tune: Worgan)
verse1:
Zeisu hing kik hi tuni, Hallelujah
Nuamna pua hi lungdam un, Hallelujah
Singlamteh tung si zo hi, Hallelujah
A..mite hong teel zo hi, Hallelujah
verse2:
Vanah i Topa Kumpi, Hallelujah
A min phat in la sa ni, Hallelujah
Mawh neite a phel na’ngin, Hallelujah
Si in hanah kivui hi, Hallelujah
verse3:
Gimna a na thuak manin, Hallelujah
Eimah hong gum khin zo hi, Hallelujah
Van pan hong uk tawntung hi, Hallelujah
La sa tawntung vantung mi’n, Hallelujah
verse4:
Mintang Kumpi hing kik zo, Hallelujah
Sihna gu koiah om? Hallelujah
Khatvei si in hong gum zo, Hallelujah
Hankhuk na zawhna koi om? Hallelujah.

verse1:
Han thuk sungah lum hi, Kei Honpa Zeisu
A ni tun' ding ngak hi, Kei To Zeisu’n
verse2:
Cin’ hangin mawkna hi, Hong Hon Zeisu’ han
Ciamteh hang mawkna hi, Kei To Zeisu’n
verse3:
Sihna’n len zolo hi, Hong Honpa Zeisu;
Dalnate sugawp hi, Kei To Zeisu’n

zoTitle: Ka Thei Hi, Kei Hong Tanpa Hing Hi
engTitle: I Know That My Redeemer Liveth
verse1:
Ka thei hi, kei hong Tanpa hinghi
Leitungah hong paikik ding hi
Ka thei hi, nuntakna thak hong pia,
Hehpihna Vaang A khut sung om.
verse2:
Ka thei hi, hong thuciam pel ngei kei
A gensa thu bei ngeilo ding;
A gilo sihna pan ka suakta,
Amah mu ding nung ciangin ah
verse3:
Ka thei hi, ka om na’ng mun bawl khawl,
A omna peuh keizong om ning,
A lamdang a mah’n kei hong keem hi,
Kei aadingin hong paikik ding.
chorus:
Ka thei, ka thei, To Zeisu hing hi.
Leitungah hong paikik ding hi,
Ka thei, ka thei, nuntakna hong pia
Hehpihna Vaang A khut sung om.

verse1:
Minthan' na Nang aa, A thokik Topa,
Bei ngeilo zawhna tawh, Sihna Na zo zo.
Vantung mi siangthote’n, Suangpi lem khia a,
A kituunna puan zong, Hoih takin khep uh.
verse2:
Zeisu tawh kimu, Han sung pan tho zo,
Itna tawh hong dawn in, Launa teng bei zo
A pawlpite lungdam, Nuam na la sa uh,
Topa tu in hing kik, Sihna’n zo zo lo.
verse3:
Um khial nawn kei in, Minthang Kumpipa,
Amah lo-ngal om kei, Hong huh zo ding dang.
Gal zote bek hilo, Sihna zo zo lai,
Zawdan gun kantan in, Vantung inn tung tu’n.
chorus:
A hing kik Topa, Min thanna Nang aa
Bei ngeilo zawhna tawh, Sihna Na zo zo

zoTitle: Ka Thei Hi Keimah Hong Tanpa
engTitle: I Know That My Redeemer Lives
verse1:
Ka thei hi keimah hong Tanpa
A nungta tawntung hi
Thu hong ngetsak itna lahna
Suahtakna hong khaam hi.
verse2:
A mah’n keima lu hong phong to,
Hotkhiatna hong puak hi,
Amah’n kei hong suakta sak zo
A hong lang baih ding hi.
verse3:
Ka sian'tho ding hong deih Amah’n
Ama deih kua’n nang zo.
Kei sungah tua thupha
Amah’n cingsak ding hi pello
verse4:
Zeisu aw, Na thu kiptakin,
Ka um, ka muang zo hi.
Nangma kiangah hong la dingin,
Nong pai takpi ding hi.

engTitle: All Hail the Power of Jesus’ Name (2nd Tune: Disden)
verse1:
Dawn un, Zeisu' min vaanglianna
Vantung mite bok un, Vantung mite bok un
Kumpi lukhu hong la un la,
Kumpi...lian kumpi, Kumpi, Kumpi,
Kumpi, Kumpi, lian bel pia un.
verse2:
Pasian biak man thahna thuakte’n
Amah Kumpi pia un, Amah Kumpi pia un.
Zise' suan in phatna ngah hen;
Kumpi...lian kumpi, Kumpi, Kumpi,
Kumpi, Kumpi, lian bel pia un.
verse3:
Teel tuam Itazila te aw,
Tawm kha na hih hangun, Tawm kha na hih hangun
Hongtan zo hi, hehpih na tawh;
Kumpi...lian kumpi, Kumpi, Kumpi,
Kumpi, Kumpi, lian bel pia un.

verse1:
Vakhu khawl na’ng(Vakhu khawl na'ng) singhiang bawl hi(singhiang bawl hi),
Nitak khuadam(nitak khuadam) a lungnuam hi.(a lungnuam hi)
Tua Pasian thu(Tua Pasian thu) mailam hi, ci(mailam hi, ci),
Lung ngaihna teng(lung ngaihna teng), Galile ah.
verse2:
Paak pawl om hi(Vakhu khawl na'ng), guam tui in nawt(singhiang bawl hi),
A nuam vasa(nitak khuadam) a ham lamdang,(a lungnuam hi)
Nitak zingsang(Tua Pasian thu) i phatna la(mailam hi, ci)
Mai mu ging za(lung ngaihna teng), Galile ah.
verse3:
Ih lungngaih ciang(Vakhu khawl na'ng) khuasikmul tho(singhiang bawl hi),
Tui tungah pai(nitak khuadam) gunpi tungah.(a lungnuam hi)
Kei ka ngaih ni(Tua Pasian thu), khatvei ngah kik(mailam hi, ci),
A nung ka zui(lung ngaihna teng) Galile ah.
chorus:
(Aw Galile)Aw Galile (a nuam gampi)a nuam gampi
(Zeisu deihna)Zeisu deihna (tampi om hi)tampi om hi.
Aw Galile(Aw Galile) a nuam gampi(a nuam gampi),
La sa in la(la sa in la), khatvei sa kik(khatvei sa kik)

verse1:
Ngai un bei thei lo la ngaih, Van pan hong kisa
"Minthang, minthang hen, Pasian," A sang bel ah;
A taang Pasian zumpi ah, Mi siangte le van mi’n sa hi
Minthang minthang hen Pasian, A sang bel ah
verse2:
Ngai un zawhna la ngaih ging, Leitung teng thawn khin,
Tuipi kilok ging bangin, Nuam aw gingin,
"Topa pahtawi in awng un!" A zawhna gam cin in phat hi
Minthang minthang hen Pasian, A sang bel ah
verse3:
Thum kigawm Pasian phat un, Van mi honte aw,
Phat un Pa le a Topa, le Kha Siangtho;
A beisa hun-a bangin, A tawntung in gingging den hi
Minthang minthang hen Pasian, A sang bel ah

zoTitle: Aw Mi Sang Tampi’n Zai Sa Ding
engTitle: Oh for a Thousand Tongues (1st. Tune: Lyngham & 2nd Tune: Azmon)
verse1:
Aw mi sang tampi’n zai sa ding,
Hong taang vaanglian phat ni, Hong taang vanglian phat ni,
Ka Pasian vaang lian belna leh
(Hong hehpihna phat ni)x5
verse2:
Aw ka lim bel keimah hong kha’n
Tang bang damna hong piang, Tang bang damna hong piang,
Hih leitung mi khempeuh tungah
(Na thupha dim ta hen)x3
(Hong heh-pihna phat ni)x2
verse3:
Aw Zeisu aw Nangmah siang bel
Dam na’ng leh lung damna, Dam na’ng leh lung damna,
Mawh neite’n zong hong theih zawh na’ng
(Ka muan lian bel na hi)x3
(Hong heh-pihna phat ni)x2
verse4:
Mawhna khempeuh hong phel zo hi
Mi vai tham zong gum khia, Mi vai tham zong gum khia,
A sipha bel hong luang sak hi
(Eite hong itna hi)x3
(Hong hehpihna phat ni)x2

zoTitle: Gup Khiat Ka Hih Nung Sang
verse1:
Ke’n nei khin tang, ka saknop la
Gup khiat ka hih nung sang
Ka Kumpi, Honpa phatna la
Gup khiat ka hih nung sang
verse2:
Ke’n nei hong lungkimsak Khazih
Gup khiat ka hih nung sang
Ama deih bek ka bawl ding hi
Gup khiat ka hih nung sang
verse3:
Ke’n nei kitel teci pan’na
Gup khiat ka hih nung sang
Bei sak, launa le up lahna
Gup khiat ka hih nung sang
verse4:
Ke’n nei kei aading inn muan’pi
Gup khiat ka hih nung sang
Tua’h a tawntung ka om ding hi
Gup khiat ka hih nung sang
chorus:
Gup khiat ka hih nung sang,
Gup khiat ka hih nung sang
A ma min tawh vaanglian ning
Gup khiat ka hih nung sang,
Ka Honpa’ min in ka vaanglian ding

zoTitle: Zeisu Ka Lungsim In Ka Deih
verse1:
Zeisu ka lungsim in ka deih
Hong hehpihna nakpi’n ka ngen
Hong hehpihna itna hong lang
Amah ke’n ka it phasem ta.
verse2:
Leitung itna sung a nuam pen,
Kiteh thei lo Hong itna tawh
Kong ento lam etna pi tawh
Na mai muh ciang lamdang ka sa.
verse3:
Vantung gam sung nopna kidim
Paakte hoihna mu ding tua lai;
Za nawn lo ding vantung mi aw
Ka kha in lamdang sa ding ta.
verse4:
Nang loin nopna om thei kei
Ka lungsim hong damsak thei ding
Nang Na om ciang dahna nuam sak
Vantung nopna kei sung hong taang.
chorus:
Lungsim pha bel, hong guan’suk in,
Tua Kham khuapi ka muh nading
Lungsim sung hong taang sak in
Tua khuapi nuam kei aading hi.

verse1:
A manpha pen suang ken mu ing
Lungdamin la ka sa.
Zeisu kei aa ci’n la sa ning
Khazih la in sa ning
verse2:
Zeisu siampi ka Kumpi hi
Khuavaak kamsang pa hi
Tokhom mai-ah kamsang lianpa
Ka van Kumpipa hi
verse3:
Amah topate’ Topa hi
Kumpite’ Kumpi hi
Amah in thumaanna Ni hi
A kha nuai ci damna
verse4:
Kilem nading kei tang hong si
Kei tang a si hong bua
A lamdang kei hong gumPa hi,
Amah mah in hong gum.
chorus:
A manpha pen suang ke’n mu ing
Lungdamin la kasa
Zeisu kei aa ci’n la sa ning!
Khazih la in sa ning.

verse1:
Kham ahih keh ngun a kihel kei hong gupna’n
Leitung hauhnate’n ka kha hong gum zo kei
Zeisu singlamteh si bek ke’n ka beel ding hi.
Ka Topa hong sihna’n tu’n kei hong gum hi
verse2:
Kham ahih keh ngun a kihel kei hong gupna’n
Ka lungsung mawhna te pungin hong khang sak
Zeisu singlamteh si bek ke’n ka beel ding hi
Ka Topa hong sihna bekin hong gum thei
verse3:
Kham ahih keh ngun a kihel kei hong gupna’n
A siangtho thu ciamna ka nai ding hong kham
Zeisu singlamteh si bek ke’n ka beel ding hi
Ka Topa hong sihna’n ka launa na bei sak
verse4:
Kham ahih keh ngun a kihel kei hong gupna’n
Vantung gam sung tun’ nang hong leisak zo kei
Zeisu singlamteh si bek ke’n ka beel ding hi
Ka Topa hong sihna’n gup khiatna hong pia.
chorus:
Hong gumzo, Hih hang ngun hi kei
Hong leizo, kham tawh hilo,
A si tawh kei hong gum zo hi
Hong itna kigen nai kei

engTitle: Crown Him With Many Crowns (Tune: Diademata)
verse1:
Tokhom tunga Tuuno, Kumpi namkim pia zo
Ngai un, a ngaih vantung lapi! La dang teng meng khin hi
Ka kha aw, tho in la, Nang aading hong si Pa
A lian bel Kumpipa ci in, A phatna la sa in
verse2:
Ki-itna Kumpipa, En un, Ama liamma
A’ khut, A’ pang kimu lai hi, Minphatna in tuam hi
Hih thu lamdang lua hi, Phawk zawk lohin thuk hi
Vantung mi’n zong en zolo in, Kun hi nuailam en in
verse3:
Kilemna Kumpipa, Gal kidona bei-a
Thumna le phatna’n suah khia in, Vannuai kilem na’ngin
Hong uk tawntung ding-a, Vantung khua nuam sungah
A Liam Ama khe kiimkot ah, Paak tawh kidawn ding ta
verse4:
A tawntung-a Kumpi, Hun bawl-a uk Mangpi
Leitung pumpi Na piangsak zo, Gen theih loh Na Siangtho
Hong tan ka Topa aw, Kei’ tang Nang hong si maw!
Nang min phat tawp ngeilo ding hi’ng , A tawntung sa ding hi’ng

zoTitle: Ka Lung Sungah La Ngaih Hong Kisa
verse1:
Ka lungsung ah la ngaih hong kisa
Zeisu’ hong hopihna hi
Lau ke’n, nang kong ompih tawntung na
Lungnuam takin om in, ci
verse2:
Ka nuntakna mawhna’n sugawp zo;
Lung lem loh natna damsak
Zeisu’n a sia teng hong lepsak zo
A ngaih la khanglo kiksak
verse3:
Hong hehpih na pha tawh kivakin
A kha nuai ka beel ta a
A maitai ka muh tawntung manin
Kiko nuamna la ka sa
verse4:
A sawt loin hong pai kik ding hi
Vanah hong la to dingin
Theih loh gamah ka leeng to ding hi
Amah tawh maang khawm dingin
chorus:
Zeisu, Zeisu, Zeisu
Min teng pan ngaih pen
Lunggulh teng kicin’na,
La hong sasa nuam sak den

verse1:
Topa’n ka tuu cingpa hi a
Bangmah ka kisam kei
Lono na ah hong lum sak in
Tuidam kiang hong pai pih
verse2:
Ka nuntakna tha hong dim sak
A ma min hang bekin
Keimah Ama thumaan lampi
Zui in hong pai thei sak
verse3:
Sihna guam sung ka kheng zongin
Natna ka kihta kei,
A molhtum leh A ciangkhut in
Kei hong lungmuang sak ding
verse4:
Ka galte a om laitak in
A mai’an hong lui-in
Ka lu sathau hong nilh sak a
Ka hai a dim let hi
verse5:
Hoih na leh migitnate in
Ka khan tawntung kei hong
Zui den ding-a Pasian inn sung
Ka ten’ na’ng hi den ding

verse1:
Pha bel Zeisu aw, Na khempeuh na uk hi
Pasian le mihing ta na hi
Nangmah ka muang hi, Nangmah ka phat hi.
Ka kisak theih nading na hi
verse2:
Pawn pha mahmah hi, Tulak zong a pha thei
Tuklai amaute’ hing lai hi
Dahna thuak mite, la sa sak Zeisu
Na khempeuh sang a pha zaw hi
verse3:
Ni taang a pha mahmah, Kha taang a pha zaw hi
Aksite zong te ding hoih hi
Van a na khempeuh sangin Zeisu in
A pha zaw in a taang thei hi.

verse1:
Phat un, phat un, eite hong hon thupha Zeisu
Sa un, sa un hong itna thangsak un
Dawn un, dawn un, Vantung mi a lianbelte aw
A min siangtho pahtawi in liansak un
Tuucing bangin, Zeisu’n naupangte cingin
A ma angah tawi hi sun nilohin
Phat un, phat un, A liatna pha demzo omlo
Phat un, phat un, nuamna la tawh phat un
verse2:
Phat un, phat un, eite hong tan thupha Zeisu
Gimna, sihna, ei mawhna hong thuak hi
Dawn un, dawn un, Singlamteh thuak Topa Zeisu
Suahtak nading lametna Suangpi hi
Eite' dahna hong puaksak Zeisu hi a,
Bei thei lo hi, lamdang hi hong itna
Phat un, phat un, A liatna pha demzo omlo
Phat un, phat un, nuamna la tawh phat un
verse3:
Phat un, phat un, eite hong tan thupha Zeisu
Amah phatna’n vantung innpi thawn hi
Maang tawntung ta eite hong hon Topa Zeisu
Kamsang, Siampi, Kumpiza ngah ta hi
Khazih hong kum ciang leitung zo gawp ding a,
Ukna, vaangliatna khempeuh Ama aa
Phat un, phat un, A liatna pha demzo omlo
Phat un, phat un, nuamna la tawh phat un

zoTitle: I Ngak Laitak Hong Tuak Diam?
verse1:
Topa Zeisu nuamna hong pia dingin
Sun kim zan kim hong pai leh
Lungsim dikin, meivak a baihsa in,
I ngak laitak hong tuak diam?
verse2:
Zingsang khat peuh phalvaak tung pan laitak
Khat khatin hong sam pak leh
Hong kep sak talen i piak kik laitak
"Pha hi," nang hong ci na diam?
verse3:
Hong vaikhakna bangin i hih zo leh,
I siamna zah siit kei leeng
I lungsim kisuan’na a om kei leh
Nopna pha i ngah ding hi
verse4:
A ngak zote in thupha ngah ding hi
Vantung khua-ah maang khawm ding
Sun kim zan kim A hong pai kha ding hi
I ngak laitak hong tuak diam?
chorus:
Ute naute, i kiging ciat zo hiam?
I kha inn nuam lut nading
Nangmah le kei kiging sa’n hong mu diam?
Ngak in, Topa hong pai ding ngak in

verse1:
Zingsang, zingsol a tum ma diak ahi zongin
Khua hong vaak in, ni a suah ciang ahi zong in
Min than’na tawh dim in, Zeisu hong pai mu ding
Amah a umte a khop ciang.
verse2:
Sun hun hi ta leh, zan kim laitak hi ta leh
Zan khuamial sung ih-sip laitak hi ta leh
Pasian khuavaak tawh minthang Zeisu hong pai ding
Amah a umte a khop ciang.
verse3:
Vantung mi in, Hosanna ci’n a otna aw
Mun khempeuh ah kiza ding hi, Vantung tum ciang,
Vantung mi siangthote in a cing ding uh hi
Amah a umte a khop ciang.
verse4:
Si loin, lungdam in vantungah i pai ding
Dahna, gentheihna, natnate om nawn lo ding
Pasian tawh meii tung tuang in vantung i pai ding
Bangzah in a nuam diam, i lung
chorus:
Aw, Topa cik ciang hi ding hiam
Ko kiang nong pai kik ding
Hong pai kik ding, Haleluiah, Haleluiah,
Amen, Haleluiah Amen.

engTitle: When the Roll is Called Up
verse1:
Topa Zeisu hong pai kik ciang vantung peengkul aw za a,
Zingtung khuavaak tawntung nuamtak taang ding hi.
Kiphelna ngah mihingte in gun gal hong kikhop ciangin
Min hong sap laitak keimah zong om ding hi’ng
verse2:
Zingtung meiikai omlo khuavaak Zeisu min tawh si tho a,
Topa tawh nungta kik-a nuam sung tum hi
Sihna a ngah mihingte in vantung inn-ah tum ciangin
Min hong sap laitak keimah zong om ding hi’ng
verse3:
Topa a na hong seemsak a zing nitum dong matengin
Kidopna tawh ama itna gen sak ni
Leitung sihna hun hong kheng ding hi na sepna tang zo in
Min hong sap laitak keimah zong om ding hi’ng
chorus:
Vantung-ah min hong sap laitak
Vantung-ah min hong sap laitak
Vantung-ah min hong sap laitak
Min hong sap laitak keimah zong om ding hi’ng

verse1:
Topa hong pai ding, nung ciangin: Kithawi in hong pai ciang!
Van inn nuam pan in hong pai ding: Kithawi in hong pai ding!
Amah thumaan i Topa hi, A teelsate thupha pia ding
A Pa Kumpi tokhom tu ding: Kithawi in hong pai ciang!
verse2:
Amah leitung hong pai baih ding: Kithawi in hong pai ding!
Gual zawh nading hun hong tung ding: Kithawi in hong pai ding!
Halleluijah van pan ging ding, Zeisu’n  gup khiatna hong puak ciang
Meivak hoihte’n Topa mu ding!: Kithawi in hong pai ciang!
verse3:
En in, nang leh kei aading hi: Kithawi in hong pai ding!
A sawt loin peengkul za ding: Kithawi in hong pai ding!
Ei hong sam ding thu khen ni ciang, Gam khempeuh pan mun khempeuh ah
A kumpi tokhom mai ding ding! Kithawi in hong pai ciang!
chorus:
Mopipa hong pai ciang na kithawi diam?
Mopipa hong pai ciang na kithawi diam?
Zingsang, sun le zan hi zong, Na mei vakte taang pha in,
Mopipa hong pai ciang na kithawi diam?

verse1:
I meivakte baih sa’n om diam?
Mopi hong pai ciang
I meivakte taang sa’n om diam?
Mopi hong pai ciang
Tua zan-ah, (tua zan-ah), tua zan dai-ah (tua zan dai-ah)
I meivak taang pha’n om diam?
Mopi hong pai ciang
verse2:
Vaitutna aw i za ding hiam?
Mopi hong pai ciang
Nuamna otna aw i za diam?
Mopi hong pai ciang
Tua zan-ah, (tua zan-ah), tua zan dai-ah (tua zan dai-ah)
I meivak taang pha’n om diam?
Mopi hong pai ciang
verse3:
Hong khen kha ding ahih ciangin
Mopi hong pai ciang
Na kithawina zekai kei in
Mopi hong pai ciang
Tua zan-ah, (tua zan-ah), tua zan dai-ah (tua zan dai-ah)
I meivak taang pha’n om diam?
Mopi hong pai ciang
chorus:
A baih sa’n om, a baih sa’n om
A baih sa’n om, Mopi hong pai ciang

zoTitle: Zeisu Leitungah Hong Kum Kik Ding
verse1:
Zeisu leitungah hong kum kik ding
Tuni hi kha leh maw
Itna tawh hong uk ding hong pai ding
Tuni hi kha leh maw
Kikhen-a om leitung tenga
A tatsa a sian’tho saksa
Hong la ding Ama lawm teelsa
Tuni hi kha leh maw
verse2:
Dawi mangpa’ uk te bei ta ding hi
Tuni hi ta leh maw!
Dahna, khuisiatna bei ta ding hi
Tuni hi ta leh maw?
Mi site khazih sung tho ding
Van kim lai-ah Amah dawn ding
Cik ciang hihte eite’n mu ding
Tuni hi ta leh maw
verse3:
Lungkip thumaanin hong mu tam maw
Tuni in hong pai leh
Laulo kipakin hong mu tam maw
Tuni in hong pai leh
Hong pai ding lim tam semsem ta
Zing khuavaak ding mual kiseem ta
Vil giugiau un a hun nai ta
Tuni hong hi kha leh
chorus:
Nuam si’ng! nuam si’ng! Hong lungdam sak ding hi
Nuam si'ng! nuam si'ng! Amah Kumpi ding hi
Nuam si’ng! nuam si’ng! Lampi puah mengmeng ni
Nuam si’ng! nuam si’ng! Zeisu hong pai ding hi

zoTitle: Ngai Un! Tul Sawm Gawsem Leh Aw Ging
engTitle: Hawk! Ten Thousand Harps and Voices (Tune: Harwell)
verse1:
Ngai un! tul sawm gawsem le aw
Van pan phatna aw ging
Zeisu’n uk, vantung a lungdam hi
Zeisu’n uk, itna Pasian
Itna galah Tokhom tung tu
Zeisu bekin leitung uk
Haleluiah! Haleluiah! Haleluiah! Amen
verse2:
Min thang Kumpi tawntung uk hi
Sia ngeilo Kumpi lukhu
Tua itna sutat zo om lo
Nang aading a na bawlsa
Na hehpihna kigal muh
Pai ding Na Mai kiang tun dong
Haleluiah! Haleluiah! Haleluiah! Amen
verse3:
Gumpa hong zekai lua kei in
Na min than’ ni tung sak in
A lamdang thu sitna hun ciang
Leitung, vantung a bei ding hi
Tua ciang kham gawsemtum in
Thang hen (thang hen, ka Kumpi!)
Haleluiah! Haleluiah! Haleluiah! Amen

zoTitle: Gam Minthang Hong Piang Ding Hi
verse1:
Vantung ah gam a minthang bel eite aading in om hi
Kum sim-in mi siangthote kikhawm uh hi
Gam minthang tawh kinai theih nading in, ni in hong kheng hi
Gam minthang piang ding hun hong tung dek tak hi
verse2:
Topa bawlsa vantung a gam minthang phual lung ngaih na in
Hong gum Topa hong pai ding hun i ngak hi
I thang awkna hih leitung kol tan'na sungah hong phel hi
Gam minthang piang ding hun hong tung dek tak hi
verse3:
Sawtvei i ngak ciangin hih leitungah lung khamna tam hi
Meii kai man in mihing lungsim kisia hi
Gam minthan'na thu gen in la, la pha sa in hansuah ni
Gam minthang piang ding hun hong tung dek tak hi
verse4:
Topa bawlsa vantung gam hong tun’ ciang i Topa mu ding,
Hong pai manin vantung gam i mu ding hi
Hallelujah A si tawh hong gum i Topa minthang hen,
Gam minthang piang ding hun hong tung dek tak hi
chorus:
Gam minthang hong piang a hun tung dek ta hi.
Gam minthang hong piang a hun tung dek ta hi
Kisa kholin ka kha aw, sawtlo peengkul tum ding hi
Kumpipa minthang tawh hong pai ding hi.

verse1:
La sa un, "Zeisu in hong pai ding" ci
A si tawh a gup mihing ta dingin
Hong kum-a hong uk ding a min thang hi
Zeisu hong pai kik ding hi
verse2:
Zeisu hong pai ciang misi a tho ding
I it i ngaih i lawmte kimu ding
Vantungah ei hong paipih na-dingin
Zeisu hong pai kik ding hi
verse3:
Zeisu hong pai ding a mi siangthote
Leitung lung damna nuam pia suk ding hi
Bei ding hi, lung khamna sin khamnate
Zeisu hong pai kik ding hi
verse4:
Zeisu hong pai ding thuciamna om hi
A teelsa mihingte la to dingin
Ngak in, lawp in, a kisa in om in
Zeisu hong pai kik ding hi
chorus:
Zeisu hong pai ding, hong pai kik ding hi
Zeisu hong pai kik ding hi.
Lung damin, la pha sa un nuam ding hi
Zeisu hong pai kik ding hi

zoTitle: En un, Mopipa Hong Tung Zo
verse1:
En un, Mopipa zankim laitakin hong tung zo hi.
A kiging khol meivak mit ngei lote’n thupha ngah ding hi.
Topa hong pai kik cianga a muh mihai na seem pa’n
 Meivak vaaklo meitui thun lo a tawntung lusu hi.
verse2:
Na kilim gin kholh kei leh na ihsip pai suak kha ding.
Sihna hun sungah lutin kham lukhu na taan kha ding,
Hoih takin kiging khol in a hun ding ngak tawntung ding,
Siangtho, siangtho, siangtho Topa kote nong huh den ding
verse3:
Tua ni a lauhuai ni, theih kholh lohin hong tung ding hi,
Meivak vaak in na meivak tui a dim takin thun in,
Zingsang nitak sunkim zankim a hun ding kithei lo,
Zipipa hong tung zo a dawn ding kuankhin un ci ding.

zoTitle: Pasian’ Kha Siangtho Hong Kum Suk In La
engTitle: Spirit of God, Descend Upon My Heart (Tune: Ingleside)
verse1:
Pasian’ Kha Siangtho, hong kum suk in la,
Ka lungsim siang semsem ding hong heii in
Ka zawn’ khalna hong hehpih sukin la
Nang Kong it ding bangin hong it sak in
verse2:
Kong it ding Nong deih, ka To Pasian in,
Pilna, thatang, kha, lungsim kheempeuh tawh;
Nangma singlamteh hong beel thei sak in
Nang mai hong zongin hong muzo sak aw.
verse3:
Nong nai tawntungna kei hong phawksak in
Lungsim sung lem lohna, lungmuan’ lahna
Nial nopna lungsimte hong zosak in
Hong ngak zosak un thunget ngah lohna
verse4:
Van mite bang Nang kong it theih na’ngin
Ka pumpi’n itna siang hong zen sak in
Na Kha Siangtho sung kei hong phum ta in
Nang itna ka sung mei bang lum sak in

verse1:
Kha Siangtho meivakna tawh
Keima lungsim sung taang aw
Khuamialna na hawl khia in
Khuamialna khua vaaksak in
verse2:
Kha Siangtho vangliatna tawh
Kei lungsim na sawp siang aw
Khialhna in a sawt veipi
Ka lung sungah uk zo hi
verse3:
Kha Siangtho lungdamna tawh
Ka lungsim sung nuamsak aw
Gimna kheempeuh hawl khia in
Dahna lungsim damsak in
verse4:
Kha Siangtho a dik mi aw
Ka lungsim sungah om aw
Milim khempeuh susia in
Nangmah guak bek na maang in

verse1:
Lungdam thu zeelsak un, mi omna citeng ah
Mihing lungsim omna, mihing gal tamna ah
Tapidaw leii khempeuh lungdam thugen sak un:
Huhpa hong pai khin ta!
verse2:
Zan hun saupi bei ta, zing khua hong vaak zo ta
Lungsim vangik pi teng, hehna hu ging veng ta
Ni taang kham mual panin, hong suah khiat tak ciangin
Huhpa hong pai khin ta!
verse3:
A kha suang zatui tawh, kumpite’ To hatpa’n
Thongkia kha keempeuh tung hong puak, hotkhiat kicing
Thongpi hawm sung tengah, zawhna la pi hong ging
Huhpa hong pai khin ta!
verse4:
Gen zawh loh itna siang! ka leii in bang ci in
Gen zawh loh hehpihna, mi vakvai tung gen ding
Amah leh A meel taang, sungah ka om theih na’ng
Huhpa hong pai khin ta!
chorus:
Huhpa hong pai khin ta!
Huh-pa hong pai khin ta!
Vantung Kha Siangtho pen, Pa’n piak ding hong ciam pen
Lungdam thu zeel sak un, mi omna citengah
Huhpa hong pai khin ta!

engTitle: Holy Spirit, Faithful Guide (Tune: Faithful Guide)
verse1:
Thumaan lamhilh Kha Siangtho
Tapidawte nusia lo;
Vantung gam zuan zin mite
A khut tawh hong len gige
A gimte tawntung pha tuam
A zak ciang Ama aw nuam
"Vantung innpi lam zong mi
Hong zui in, Kong kha ding hi."
verse2:
Hong ompih den Lawm pha pen,
Ko guak hong zawt tawm sak ke’n
Khuamial, lungman’, launa sung’,
Nangmah’n hong ompih tawntung
Huihpi nasia mahmah in
Lungkia laitak hong ci in
"Vantung innpi lam zong mi
Hong zui in, Kong kha ding hi."
verse3:
Nasepna hun bei ta a
Vantung tun’ ding bek om ta
Kei min zong a om buang tam
Zeisu si bek ka paulam
Sihna gun ka ngah laitak
Hong ci lai, siangtak, teltak:
"Vantung innpi lam zong mi
Hong zui in, Kong kha ding hi."

engTitle: Breathe on Me, Breath of God (Tune: Trentham)
verse1:
Pasian nun’na hong pia’n
Hihna thak hong dim in
Nang deih bang hong deihsak thei in
Nang bawl bang bawl dingin
verse2:
Pasian nun’na hong pia’n
Lungsim siang ka neih ding
Nang tawh sin khat lung khat suah dong
Bawl khawm, thuak khawm dingin
verse3:
Pasian nun’na hong pia’n,
Nang' mi ka hih khit dong
Leitung na khat a hi kei sung,
Na thu mei bang kuang hen
verse4:
Pasian nun’na hong pia’n
Si ngei nawn lo dingin
Nang tawh hong nungta khawm sak in
Hin’ tawntungna gamah, Amen.

zoTitle: Vakhu Bangin Kha Siangtho Hong Pai In
engTitle: Come, Holy Spirit, Heavenly Dove (Tune: St. Agnes)
verse1:
Kha Siangtho vakhu bangin ah
Hong pai in vaang lian tawh
Na itna mei bang hong tawh in
A dai ko lung sungah
verse2:
Kote la sak ngei bangin ah
Tho to in sa zo lo
Hawsiana ci’n ko aw ging lo
Kote biakna si ta
verse3:
Topa tua bang ko si ding lo
Hehpih huai mahmah in
Ka hong itna uh a neu hang
Nang hong itna lian zaw
verse4:
Kha Siangtho vakhu bangin ah
Hong pai in vaang lian tawh
Gumpa itna hong buak in la
Tawh kuang sak in ko mei, Amen.

verse1:
Kha Siangtho a migi kha,
Nong hilh ding ka deih pen uh
Pentekoh ni aa Nong piak
Vantung ki-itna
verse2:
Ki-itna in lung duaisak
Ki-itna in niam khiat sak
Ki-itna in singam sak
Vantung ki-itna
verse3:
Gen kholhna thute khempeuh
Khuavaak bangin mangthang ding
Ki-itna thu bek kip ding
Vantung ki-itna

verse1:
Kumpipa, hong makai in,
Kuan ding ni hong tung zo
Tu-a kipan gal sungah
Nang’ buk ko’ inn hi zo
Kigin’ sung nong hehpih na’n
Kote hong hatsak zo
Hing tawntung Kumpipa aw
Gam do la ko sa zo
verse2:
Kumpipa’n hong masuan in
Mawhna gal bei mateng
Gal kilemna nuam om a,
Siangtho thu kim mateng
Thau, tei le nam, khuang ging tawh,
Pasian gam piang hi kei
Ki-it ki hehpihna tawh
Pasian gam hong tung thei
verse3:
Kumpipa’n hong kuanpih in, Lau lo Kong zui uh hi
Na mai kimuhna peuhah
Lungdamna khuavaak hi
Na singlamteh ko tungah
Lam pai na’ng hong taang in
Gal zawh lukhu’n hong ngak hi
Pasian aw hong pi in

verse1:
Khazih galkapte’n ah, Gal sim ding kuan un
Eite mai-a masa, Zeisu mitsuan un
Khazih eite Mangpa, Makai hilo mawh
En un, A’ dial paina, Gal phual lam manawh!
verse2:
Zeisu’ min a zak ciang Dawi mite tai uh
Nawt un, tua a hih ciang, Na mualsuah dong uh
Phatna aw kizak ciang, Dawi gam kiliing hi
Lawmle, tua ahih ciang, Awngun phatna pi.
verse3:
Galkap honpi bangin, Pawlpi’n masot hi
Tang mi siangte bangin i totna khat hi
Eite kikhen loin Pum khat bek i hi
Lawp le zuih kikhat in hong ki-it sak hi
verse4:
Kumpi'za sia thei hi, Kumpigam kip kei
Hih hang Zeisu’ pawlpi cikmah’n sia thei kei;
Dawi in Pasian’ Pawlpi cik ciang zo ngei kei
Khazih hong ciamsa hi. A ciam peel ngei kei.
verse5:
Tua hi-a hong pawm un mi khempeuh inah
Ko tawh hong sa khawm un gal zawh nuamna la
A minthang pahtawi un leitung vantungah,
Tatsat loin phat un Khazih Kumpipa
chorus:
Zeisu galkapte’n ah, Gal kap ding kuan un;
Singlamteh pua un la, na mailam nawt un.

engTitle: The Lord Bless You and Keep You
verse1:
Topa’n thupha hong pia hen,
Topa’n nangmah hong en in hong kem hen
Lung nopna zong hong guan’ta hen: Topa’n
 A mai nang tung' hong taan’suk hen,
 Hong hehpih hen, hong hehpih hen, hehpih hen
Topa'n hong hehpih, hong hehpih ta hen
Amen, Amen, Amen, Amen, Amen, A...men

Tho in, tho in, Topa’n hong sam in om hi.
Ei ding in, um in, um in Ama thute.
Pai in, pai in, gen in jubili kum pawipi la in
Khazih Topa hong itna thu a pha.
verse2:
Ko in, ko in, sihna pan hong taang a thei lo,
Mite hong tung tuipi hong galkah hi.
Zeelkhin gawp hen, leitung kheempeuh na pai in la
Hih omna tengah kial-a zawng mite omna.
verse3:
Pasian in nungta a tawi bang-a
Na hong gup nading mi mang mualtung
Khumial sungah Topa gupna na khut kha in
Tua mi kiangah mi mawh hong paipih in
Topa Na inn sungah
verse4:
En in, en in, thuciam ni hong nai zo ta hi
Hong gum Topa a lian bel Kumpipa
Na khempeuh a zo khin a niam lak khin ding hi
A lian bel, "Haleluiah," ci’n kiko ding hi.
chorus:
Sa in, sa in a la hong taang ta hi
Lamhilh zingsol i tungah paipai un
I mailam-ah, lam hong hilh, hong hilh
Hong gum Topapi A min,
A min thang kiza tawntung hen la
"Hawsiana, Hawsiana" kiko tawntung ni.
A galkap mite'n ngai un, Zeisu Topa bek thei ni,
"Haleluiah" kiko ni paina tengah

zoTitle: Topa Na Gam Ka It Hi
engTitle: I Love Thy Kingdom, Lord (Tune: St. Thomas)
verse1:
Topa Na gam it ing,
Gamlapi aa Na inn
Thupha a piaksa A Pawlpi
Ama si tawh lei zo
verse2:
Na Pawlpi ka it hi,
Na ding, a kulhpi mai,
Hawm thawhna leh a-na mit tawh,
En in, khut tawh hong len.
verse3:
Pawlpi ka it manin,
Luang sak luankhi tui bang,
Keem in, cing in, A na seem ning,
Leitung bei ni ma-teng.
verse4:
Ka lungdam theih zah in,
Vantung ka tun’ ciangin
Amah tawh ne khawm nuamsa in,
Hong itna ka phat ding
verse5:
Na thumaanna bangin,
Zion mualah na sang ding
Leitung minthannate bei in,
Nuam zaw vantung thupha

verse1:
Ni khat, Ama min phatna van dim na-pi’n
Leitung ah mawhna zan bang mial manin
Nungak sung suak in Zeisu hong pai suk in,
Mi lak hong teeng hi, lam pha lak dingin
verse2:
Ni khat, Kalani mual kah to sak uh a,
Sing tung kilh cip uh khai lum dingin ah
Mawhna teng pua in, simmawh, bawlsiat, huatna
Nakpi thuak sak uh hi, kei hong tan Pa.
verse3:
Ni khat, huan sungah Amah kinusia a,
Ni khat, thuakna tawh pengin tawlnga a,
Vantung mite in A han hong cing suk a
Lametna bei te muan’ kei hong honpa
verse4:
Ni khan Amah han in siin zo nawn lo a,
Han kongvang khakna suangpi tuk khia a
Sihna zo gawp in sihna pan tho kik a
Tu’n vantung kah zo, tawntung kei’ Topa.
verse5:
Ni khat Amah peengkul in hong masuan ding
Ama vaang lian vantung pan hong taang ding
Ka it ka ngaihte Amah’n hong tonpih ding
Angtan huai hi, tua Zeisu kei aading.
chorus:
Nungta in hong it, si in hong hon hi
Kivui in ka mawhna a pua khia hi
Thokik in hong dik sak, khawnkhong tawntung hi
Lungdam huai bel hi, hong pai kik ding ni!

engTitle: I Know Whom I Have Believed
verse1:
Pasian’ hong hehpihna thupha
Kei kiang hong tun theihna
Ka kilawm lohpi hong deihna
Bang hang hiam thei zo ke’ng
verse2:
Hong honkhia zo thei hih upna
Kei tung a hong piakna
A thu um leeng lungnop theihna
Bangci bang hiam thei ke’ng
verse3:
Kha Siangtho in mi lungsim hei
Mawhna hong phawk sak thei
Zeisu hong mu sak, um sak thei
Bangci bang hiam thei ke’ng
verse4:
Topa mai ke’n ka muh ma in
A pha a sia tuah ding
Gentheih nading, nopsak nading
Bang ka sunsiah thei ke’ng
chorus:
Ahih hang ka Uppa ka thei hi.
Amah muan'huai hi, ke'n ka thei zo hi
Ama tung kapiaksate zong
Keem zo ding hi tua ni dong.

engTitle: Faith of Our fathers! Living Still
verse1:
Tanglai pate’ upna hing lai
Mei sung, humpi kua sung khiat thuak
Tuazah upna lian i zak ciang
Aw bangzah in i lungdam hiam?
Pate’ upna, upna siangtho!
Ei zong sih dong i thuak ngam ding
verse2:
Tanglai pate’n kol bulh thuak in,
Thong sung khuamial mun ah kikoih
Hih hang lungsim siang tak tawh om
Tua bang mi’ tapa i sun ding!
Pate’ upna, upna siangtho!
Ei zong sih dong i thuak ngam ding
verse3:
Upna i cih pate’ up bang
Tual leh gal kidona sungah
Bang hangin tel tak theihna tawh
Gitna itna kammal tawh lak
Pate’ upna, upna siangtho!
Ei zong sih dong i thuak ngam ding

engTitle: Glorious Things of Thee Are Spoken (Tune: Austrian Hymn)
verse1:
Zion khua kongpi suak dingin
Lai Siangtho a genzo hi
Ciampel ngeilo i Topa in
A om nading hong bawl hi
A kip tawntung suang om tung ta
A kiliing zo kei ding hi
Gup nading thu tawh om khawm 
A galet-in kilawm thei hi
verse2:
A hong it tawntung na panin
A hong luang hin’na luitui
Khua tanu le tapate in
Dawn uh a, lungdam uh hi
Tua bang luitui om ngei hi leh
Kuamah thakiam lo ding hi
Thupha hong pia Pasian bangin
Khang khat pan khang khat kip hi
verse3:
Tua khuapi laibu sung panin
Keimna min a kikhum leh
Lawkite’n hong ko hangin ah
Kisathei in om ning kei
Mawhna tawh nuam a omte in
Kisak theih na mang ding hi
A manpha bel nop sakna in
Tua khua bekah om ding hi

engTitle: How Pleased and Blest Was I (Crusaders Melody)
verse1:
Bangzah in ka lung nop
Mi honpi’ aw ka za
Tuni in Topa va zong ni
Lungnop takin om ni
Zion mualah pai ni,
Kiciam in To pa min phat ni
verse2:
Zion mualah nopna
Hehpihna tawh kidim
A muan’huai kulhpi tawh ki-uum
Tua mun va beel ciat ni
Ama min phat ding leh lung damna
La ngai ding pai ni.
verse3:
Tua-ah Davuih Topa’n
A kumpi tokhom koih
Hehpihna tawh thumaan khen ding
Mi siangthote phat ding
Mawh neite dahsak ding
Kiniam khiat in lungdam tek un
verse4:
Lung nopna hong tung hen
Lung damna’n hong zui hen
Mi kheempeuh in thupha ngah in
Topa nopna saang hen
A pha deihna khangin
Gen zawh loh thupha hong tung hen

verse1:
Phat dingin kong pai hi
Na Biak inn siangah
Hehpih hong pia Topa
Na kiang hong kha in
Na tokhom kiang tung ding
Ka kilawm kei hi
Kong' biak na thupha hang
Na min thang ta hen
verse2:
Kiletsakna lungsim
Kiphasak lo in
Na min thang pahtawi ding
Nang kiangah kong pai Khazih lungsim pha leh
Lung neemna tak tawh
Na min thanna muangin
Na min kong phat hi
verse3:
Kha Siangtho hong ompih
Naangin kong thuum hi
Ka kisapna khempeuh
Na kiangah kong ap kong biaknate sangin
Na min than’ nading
Na thupha ka theih na’ng
Lungsim hong guan in
verse4:
Phat dingin kong pai
Na biak inn siangah
Hehpih hong pia Topa
Na kiang hong kha in
Kong thuciamna khempeuh a thakin bawlin
Nasep lian sep nading
Kote hong sawl in.

engTitle: In Christ There Is No East or West (Tune: St. Peter)
verse1:
Khazih sungah, kikhen lo hi
Nisuah, nitum, sak, khang;
Leitung khempeuh kua mi kua mi
Lawm khat pawl hi hang
verse2:
Khazih sungah, lungsim maante’n
Pawl ngah kawikawi ding hi
Ama nasepna, mi teng hen khawm,
kham khauzang bang hi
verse3:
Khut kilen ni up kikhat teng
U le nau bang hi hang;
Bang nam hi leeng, Pa’ naseem teng
Beh khat phung khat hi bang
verse4:
Khazih sungah, i kimat hi
Sak mi, khang mi, pam mi
Khazih lungsim bang a nei mi
Kheempeuh pum khat suak hi.

verse1:
Pawlpite a bul in-ah i Topa Zeisu hi.
A si le a thu in-ah Pawlpi hong bawl zo hi
A si siangtho piang dingin Vantung pan hong kum hi
Hong bua a si’n hong lei a Hin’ nading a hong si
verse2:
Mi lak pan hong teel khia a Pum khat hong bang sak hi
Pasian thu tawh hong suak suk Amah khat bek om hi
Zeisu a min siangtho in Tua min bek a phat hi
Muan na lametna khat bek Phat na’ng a hahkat hi
verse3:
Pawlpi sung kilem lohna Thu sia a om ciangin
Lawkite’n hong ko ding a hong simmawh hangin ah
Mi siangtho hong cing lai in "Sawtpi lo ding," a ci.
Zan in hong kheng khuavak ciang Nopna hong tung ding hi.
verse4:
Hong bawlsia thei galkapte Pawlpite’n a do leh
Bei ngeilo nop saknapi a ngah ding uh ve
A pha bel mahmah nate a muh uh ciangin ah
Lungdamna a lianpite a ngah ding uh in pha

engTitle: Be Ye Strong in the Lord
verse1:
Topa leh A vaang liatna sungah thahat un!
Ama thumaan sungah kip tak ding un;
Gal kidona sungah Amah’n lam hong kai ding
Topa min tawh nang na gual zo ding hi
verse2:
Topa leh A vaang liatna sungah thahat un!
Galte mai panin kihei ngei kei un;
Thumaan gal sim laitak Amah na kiang ding ding
Ama vaang liatna sungah mainawt un!
verse3:
Topa leh A vaang liatna sungah thahat un!
Ama thumaan nate pel ngeilo ding
Thumaan gal sim laitak na taklam khut len ding
Amah muang in, na gual zo tawntung ding
chorus:
Thumaan in kip tak ding
Kumpipa thu piakna tawh zawh dong,
Topa minthan’na ding leh Ama thu gual zawhna ding,
Topa thahatna sung kip tak ding

verse1:
Lai Siangtho, Pasian thu bu
Ka neih manpha pen na hi
Koi pan ka piang hong gen ding
Bang ka hi hiam, hong hilh ding
verse2:
Lam ka pial ciang, hong tai ding
Honpa’ itna hong lak ding
Lam hong hilh ding hong cing ding
Hong thuhilh ding, hong phat ding
verse3:
Hih leitung gam simtham ah,
Hong hehneem ding, dahna ah
Hong hilh hi nei leeng upna
Mi in zong zo thei, sih na.
verse4:
Nong hilh hi nopna ngah na’ng
Lang pan’ mi mawhte thuak na’ng
Ka neih manpha pen na hi
A siangtho Lai Siangtho bu.

zoTitle: Van in Na Min Than’na Pulaak
engTitle: The Heavens Declare Thy Glory (Tune: Uxbridge)
verse1:
Van in na min than’na pulak
Aksi tengah Na pilna taang
Na kammalte mit tawh et ciang
Na min a tel zaw in kimu
verse2:
A kihei Ni, kilaih khuavaak
Sun leh zan hun, Na vaang bawlsa
Gen zawh loh Na hehpihna thu’n
Na dikna, hehpihna langsak
verse3:
Thumaan thutak Ni hong suak hi,
Leitung mial lak van khuavaak pia’n
Lungdamna thu’n mite pil sak
Na thu tangin, na thu khen maan
verse4:
Na lam dan’na hi pan mu ung
Khate thak suah, mawhna maisak
Topa, ka mawhna sil sak in la
Vantung tun’ dong Na thu’n
Hong keem in. Amen

zoTitle: Lai Siangtho Beel In Ka Nau Aw
engTitle: Cling to the Bible, My Boy
verse1:
Han khuk lam a khualzin a na paipai lai in
Kong deihsak khat om: nasep ding tawh kisai in
Tua thu kong gen lai in limtak na ngai in
"Lai Siangtho beel in ka nau aw."
verse2:
Kamsiatna, dahna, kahna, thuak kha ta lecin
Satan tawh kum tampi kido do ta lecin
Limtak thu zui in, lau ke’n, mai nawt tawntung in
"Lai Siangtho beel in ka nau aw."
verse3:
Na sim sial in thu thak khat thei khia den ni teh
Sing tunga Zeisu’n hong sih lawhna thu hi veh
Topa le vantung le nangma tung thumaan ve
"Lai Siangtho beel in ka nau aw."
verse4:
Tua Laibu khuavaak le upna sikkawipi hi
Zan khuamial a, lam hong lak khuavaak aksi hi
Hong sawlna bang mang leci’n, na maan den ding hi
"Lai Siangtho beel in ka nau aw."
chorus:
Lai Siangtho beel in, ka nau aw,
Lai Siangtho beel in, ka nau aw,
Hin’ hun le sih hun in, na dang teng sangin,
Lai Siangtho beel in ka nau aw

verse1:
Kei hong sak kik leuleu dih in
Lamdang Nuntakna thu
A hoihna hong lak lailai in
Lamdang Nuntakna thu
Nuntakna thupha hi
Gamtat na’ng hong hilh hi
verse2:
Zeisu’n mi khempeuh hong lui hi
Lamdang Nuntakna thu
Hong sam hi, ngai un, mawhnei mi
Lamdang Nuntakna thu
Hong pia khong hih thu gol
Vantung khua lam hong zol
verse3:
Lungdamna thu na gen sawn in
Lamdang Nuntakna thu
Mawh phel, lung nopna, mi ko in
Lamdang Nuntakna thu
Zeisu bek hong hon thei
Tawntung siangtho sak thei
chorus:
Thu hoih mahmah, thupha mahmah
Nuntakna thu mahmah
 Thu hoih mahmah, thupha mahmah
Nuntakna thu mahmah

zoTitle: Leitung Aading Lai Siangtho Bu Kihong
engTitle: An open bible for the world
verse1:
Leitung aading Lai Siangtho Bu
Hih pen zuih kim, cih kim hi hen!
Huihkhi laan’ ciang, tua dial kipeei
Manpha thupha kizeel thaang hen!
verse2:
A tun na peuh kham khuavaak hi
Kiliah zo lo ni taang bang hi
Meei bang liahte tui mang ding hi
Mawhna sepna a phel ding hi
verse3:
Pa’ mai tangah mi teng puak a
Mawh maisak itna tawh taang hi
Adam khang pan a mangthang sa,
Hehpihna thu van pan thang hi
chorus:
Pasian kammal, Leitung, tuitung mun kheempeuh ah
Khualmial sunga vakthap mite
Pasian vantung hong tun’ Thu Bu

verse1:
Ci damin nipi khat sung
Pasian in hong keem lai a
Tuni in Ama inn sung
Thupha saang ding i ngak ta
Ni sagih sung nuam bel hi
Vantung tawl damna lim hi
Ni sagih sung nuam bel hi
Vantung tawl damna lim hi
verse2:
Mawh phelna ding hehpihna
Hong tanpa’ min in kong ngen
Hong mu sak in Na maipha
Mawhna zumna bei ta hen
Tuni lung khamna bei in
Nang sung hong tawldam sak in
Tuni lung khamna bei in
Nang sung hong tawldam sak in
verse3:
Na min kong phat laitak un
Nong naina hong phawksak in
Na mai kong kilak lai un
Na vaanglian hong musak in
Ko ngah ding vantung nuamna
Hong ciam khol sak in, Topa
Ko ngah ding vantung nuam na
Hong ciam khol sak in, Topa
verse4:
Nangma lung damna thu in
Mi sia puah, mipha hehneem
Na thupha’n ta tam tawi in
Siatna kheempeuh a pha’n lem
Tua bang piang hen, Nipi teng
Vantung Pawlpi tun’ mateng
Tua bang piang hen, Nipi teng
Vantung Pawlpi tun’ mateng

engTitle: O Day of Rest and Gladness (Tune: Mendness)
verse1:
Tawldamna le lungdam ni,
Khuavaakna, nuamna ni
Lung khamna dahna damsak
A vaak a hoih pen ni, Tanglai a kipan tuni
A lian a neu kituak "Siangtho, siangtho, siangtho," ci’n
Thum gawm Pasian phat ni
verse2:
No khempeuh a pian cil in
Khuavaak suak hi, tuni’n
Eite hong hon khia Zeisu
Hong hin’ kik ni, tuni
Gal zo i Topa’n tuni
Hong puak ni, kha Siangtho;
Tua hi-a hih Nipi ni
Thupha nam thum ngah ni
verse3:
Tuni in mi namkim tung
Vantung khomun hong tung
Mi siangtho kikhopna ah
Lungdamna thu kihilh
A gim a tawlte kisil
Tawldamna lui sungah
Lungdamna thupha a vaang
Mi siangte mai-ah taang
verse4:
Vantung gam mi siang te bang
Hehpihna a dangdang
Tawldam ni Nipi ni pan
A thuapthuap i ngah hi
Tuni’n phatna kiza hi
Pawlpi mite kam pan
Phat un thum gawm a siangtho
Pa, Ta le Kha Siangtho

verse1:
Nipi Topa na inn sungah
Kiciam in Nang tung kong kipia
Kote hong biakna hong saangin
Gamdai takin Nang kong phat uh
verse2:
Nong piak Nipi ni ka it uh
Tuasang ni thupi zaw om lo
Nasep nusia in hong bia ung
Nangmah phatnopna lungsim tawh
verse3:
Lungkham, sinkham om nawn lo in
Mawhna gimna om nawn lo in
Thumna, tauna om nawn lo in
Na min phat ding thadah lo in
verse4:
I lamet ni hong tung zo ta
Khuavaakpi in ei hong taan’ zo
Leitung haksa nusia ta ni
Tawldam na’ng ihmu phot dih ni

engTitle: Here, Savior, We Would Come (Tune: Trentham)
verse2:
Kote thupha hong pia’n,
Nang kiang kong tun' nangun,
Ka ni bangun tha hong pia in,
Tha hatna hong guan' in.

zoTitle: Luangdam Huai Hi, Nang Kong Teel Ni
verse1:
Lungdam huai hi, Nang kong teel ni,
Keimah hong hon ka Pasian aw.
Keima lungdamna a lianpi,
Mi tung gen lo om thei ding maw
verse2:
Nasep pi bel kikhin zo hi:
Kei Topa aa ka hizo ta,
Hong kaih na-na, ke'n ka zui hi,
Ama' thu gen leng nuam ka sa.
verse3:
Ka lungsim aw, lungka nawn ken.
Hih thupha ah kiptak khawl ta’n
Topa kiang pa’n lungleeng nawn ke’n.
A pha khempeuh nei hi, Amah’n.
verse4:
Lunggsim takpi tawh ka ciamsa,
Ni simin ka ciam phapha ding;
Lungdam huai bel hih kiciamna,
Ka sih ciangin thupha pia ning.
chorus:
Ka nuam hi, Ka nuam hi,
Zeisu’n ka mawh hong phel zo hi.
Thungetna zia a hong hilh hi,
Ni simin hong lungdam sak hi.
Ka nuam hi, Ka nuam hi,
Zeisun’n ka mawh hong phel zo hi.

engTitle: O God, Thy Summons Still Is Heard (Tune: Serenity)
verse1:
Galilee tui gei-a Na thu hilhna kiza lai hi.
Mi tampi in, Topa hong zuan,
"Hong zui un," na cih ciang
verse2:
Mihing lungsim tu ni’n saang in,
Nang sapna a donte,
Amau upna bangbang saang in,
Ki suan-na beisak in
verse3:
Tu ni’n damna tui hong luan' in,
Gupkhiatna lim lah na’n,
Lungsim mawhna teng suakta sak,
Na thu tawh sawp siang in.
verse4:
Mi khempeuh Na mipha suak hen,
Leitung bei hun dongin,
Nang tawh kizopna kip ta hen,
Na min kong phat uh hi. Amen.

engTitle: Down to the Sacred Wave (Tune: State Street)
verse1:
Kha Siangtho hong luangsuk,
Topa nuntakna puak,
Amah zuante’n Kha suahtak ngah,
Zawdan ah a lu nga.
verse2:
Lungsim tak tawh i zui,
Topa totna lam teng,
Makai Pa tat bang i ta nuam,
Minthang Pasian Tuuno.
verse3:
Nang tung, Nang tung bek mah,
Muang in, um in, lam en,
Aw, mawhna Na sil siang zo hi,
Mi mah aading Na si.
verse4:
Nong kipiakna ka muang,
Na singlamteh ka delh.
Aw, mawh in ko si lai ding maw?
Tho in Nang sung hing nung, Amen

engTitle: Break Thou the Bread of Life (Tune: Bread of Life)
verse1:
Nun' takna khomun kei hong pia’n, Topa.
Galilee tuili gei Na hih bangmah,
Ka lungsim vah zo kei, Lai simna tawh.
Nangmah tak ka lung deih, hin’na Thu aw.
verse2:
Thumaan, thutak hong pia’n, ka Topa aw,
Khomun Na piak bang zia’n, Na thupha tawh.
Tua hi leh kol teeng kia’n, Ka suakta ding;
Thumaan in hong khahkhia’n, Ka lung nuam ding.
verse4:
Topa aw, Kha Siangtho kei hong puak in,
Keima mit khua mu lo vaak sak dingin;
Nu thu thuk Lai Siangtho hong tel sak ding,
Na Thu sung pan Nang, ko hong mu sak ding.

zoTitle: Bang Dang Hilo Zeisu' Si Hi
engTitle: Nothing But the Blood of Jesus
verse1:
Bang in ka mawh sawp siang thei,
Bang dang hilo, Zeisu' si in.
Bang in hong damsak kik thei,
Bang dang hilo, Zeisu' si in.
verse2:
Ka sian’na ding hih ka muh,
Bang dang hilo, Zeisu' si hi;
Ka mawhna kiphel na’ng thu,
Bang dang hilo, Zeisu' si hi.
verse3:
Mawh mai sak bang dang hilo,
Bang dang hilo, Zeisu' si hi;
A pha ka bawl hang hilo,
Bang dang hilo, Zeisu' si hi.
verse4:
Kei lametna, lung nopna,
Bang dang hilo, Zeisu' si hi;
Kei in dikna ka ngahna,
Bang dang hilo, Zeisu' si hi.
chorus:
Manpha hi hong luang si,
Vuk bang hong ngo sak si;
Tui dang ka thei kei hi,
Bang dang hilo, Zeisu' si hi.

engTitle: I Gave My Life For Thee
verse1:
Nangmah tat khiatna ding, Nun’na na ngah na ding,
Kei' nun' takna kong pia,
Ka sipha Kong bua khia. Ke’n Ka nun' takna Kong pia zo,
Nang Kei bang nong pia zo.
verse2:
Khang tawntung-a nuamna, na ngah theih na'ng in ah,
Gentheihna kum sawtpi,
Nang aading Kong thuak hi. Nang aading kum sawtpi Kong gim,
Kei hang bang tan na gim.
verse3:
A taang Ka Pa' inn nuam, Ka tokhom vaanglian tuam,
Nusia’n leitung Kong thuak,
Lungzuan' dahna Kong thuak. Nang hang hih zahta Ke’n nusia,
Kei hang bang nang nusia.
verse4:
Dawi gam sung pan nangmah Kong hot khiat na’ng in ah,
Ka thuak gimna pite,
Gen khin zo kei niteh.
(Nang aading gen zawh loh Ka thuak,
Kei aading bang na thuak.)x2

verse1:
Nong hehpihna lian hang, kong phat uh hi, Topa,
Tua in kote tu dong hong keem hi;
Na hoihna leh itna lian ka zahtak uh a,
Nangma sungah, lungsim pia in, kong kun uh hi.
verse2:
Na hinna moh, a them vui kiate nangawn zong,
A ne ding ka kilawm loh hang un,
Nangma hehpihna tawh, kote Nong piak khong,
Nangma hoihna suangin, tua an ko ne ung, tu’n
verse3:
Lungsim hong bun in, ka tha uh hong hat pah hen,
Hi banga ka bawlnate uh tawh,
Topa, Nong pai dong, Na sihna hong lak hen,
Nang tawh maan khawm hun dong, Ko hong thakhauh sak hen aw.
chorus:
Nang Nong vaikhaksa mah bangin,
Topa tuni’n, Na ankuang kong umpih uh hi, tu’n;
Kote tung a Nang Nong gen thu phawk in:
"Kei nong phawk denna un hih un."

zoTitle: I Topa Hong Itna Lamdang Hi
verse1:
I Topa hong itna lamdang hi,
Mawhna, khialhna i neih hang tampi,
Lian zaw tham lai hong hehpihna si,
Kalani mual tungah hong bua hi.
verse2:
Mawhna lung kiatna’n tui khang bangin,
Ka kha hong sut nuam hong to laitak,
Gen zawh loh, lian zaw hehpihna in,
Ka belh ding singlamtehpi hong lak.
verse3:
Kiseel zo nawn kei i mawhna nin;
Bang a om diam hong sawp zo lai ding.
En un, hia a luang sisan gunpi’n,
Vuk sang hong ngo zaw sak pah thei ding.
verse4:
Lamdang kicing hehpihna lian zaw,
A um kheempeuh, A hong pia khong hi.
A mai a mu nuamte kheempeuh aw,
Saang pak ve un hong hehpihna hi.
chorus:
Hong hehpihna,
I mawhna hong maisak, siangsak hi.
Pasian, itna,
I mawhna teng sangin lian zaw hi.

zoTitle: Zan Kim Ta-A, Olive Mual Tung
engTitle: Tis Midnight; And On Olive’s Brow (Tune: O Live's Brow)
verse1:
Zan kim ta a, Olive mual tung,
Aksi taang tu’n mial kik leuleu.
Zan kim ta a, en un, huan sung,
Hong honpa kia’n thu ngen ngiu-ngeu.
verse2:
Zan kim ta a, Hong Honpa in,
Amah guak launa tawh kibuan.
A it nungzui pa nangawn in,
Don lo hi, Topa khitui luan'.
verse3:
Zan kim ta a, Mi Gentheipa,
Mi dang' mawhna hang sisan kap.
Ahih hang, Amah khuk din' a,
Pasian deihna sungah ki-ap.
verse4:
Zan kim ta a, Pa Pasian in,
Mihing Tapa nusia sam lo.
Vantung mite in hehneem in,
Mihing Honpa in dahna zo.

engTitle: From Every Stormy Wind That Blows (Tune: Retreat)
verse1:
Huihpi nakpi'n a nun sim in,
Dahna tui bang a khan' sim in
Zuat ding tawldam huai,
Lung muan' huai mun om,
Hehpihna tokhom nuai.
verse2:
Eite i lu tungah, Zeisu’n,
Lungdam sathau hong nilhna mun,
Mun dang teng sang
Nuam pen mun om, hong suah 
Sisan baang hehpihna tokhom.
verse3:
Khat le khat lungsim kigawm na,
Lawm le gual tawh kikholh theihna,
Kikhen hang pum khat bang hong suah
Hehpihna tokhom kiim kituah.
verse4:
Pumpi' utna le mawhnate’n
Hong nawngkai sak zo nawn lo den;
Vantung in hong dawn tuah suk ta,
Vaang taang in tua tokhom tuam ta.

verse1:
Zingsang tuh ding hi, Ki-itna khaici tuh in.
Sun-a tuh bang zanin zong tuh in a ci.
A at hun ngak in la, a khop hun zong ngak in.
Lungdamna tawh buh lomte i khawm ding hi.
verse2:
Nisa sungah tuh in, a liap sung zong tuh in.
Phalbi le tuuklai lung man’na om lo pi.
Na sepna zawh ciangin kikhop hun hong tung ding.
Lungdamna tawh buh lomte i khawm ding hi.
verse3:
Kap kawm in pai in la, Topa aading tuh in,
Kisiatna in a hong dah sak hang a ci.
Kahna khit ciangin ah, Topa hong sam ding a,
Lungdamna tawh buh lomte i khawm ding hi.
chorus:
Buh lomte khawm in, buh lomte khawm in.
Lungdamna tawh buh lomte i khawm ding hi.
Buh lomte khawm in, buh lom te khawm in.
Lungdamna tawh buh lomte i khawm ding hi.

verse1:
Ngai un, gamlak khuamial sungah,
Tuu cingpa aw, kiza thei hi.
Tuu khumna sung pan a pu suak,
A mang tuute a sam kik hi.
verse2:
A mang tuute a zon' nading,
Tuu cingpa kua in huh ding hiam.
Khua dam om lo tuu khumna sung,
Kua in tuute hong tum sak hiam.
verse3:
Gampa lak-ah le mual tungah,
Amau kahna aw hong ngai in.
Topa in, nangma kiangah ci.
"Keima tuute na zong ding hi."
chorus:
Hong paipih’n. Hong paipih’n.
Khialhna mun panin hong paipih’n,
Hong paipih’n. Hong paipih’n.
A mangte Zeisu kiang paipih’n

verse1:
Gimna sung pan lamet gam nuam
Cik ciang ka tung ding hiam.
Cik ciang galvan ka koih ding hiam,
Lai lung ka muang ding hiam.
verse2:
Sim leitung lai lungdam om lo,
Lum bang sung om lo tawh,
Sim leitung sau nuam a hilo
Gam bang daihna a hi.
verse3:
Lim bel siangtho ngah dingin ah,
Lam bang na pial ke’n ci.
Leeng van siang nuam ka tun’ mateeng,
Nuamna hong pia ding hi.
verse4:
Lim bel nen-ah khawl zo ta in,
Lamdang ka pial kei ding.
Amah bang a ka pham nung ciang,
Leeng vansiang nuam tung ning.
chorus:
Zeisu hong tun' mateng,
Zeisu hong tun' mateng,
I nasep zawh ciangin,
Inn nuam sung om khawm ding.

verse1:
Topa hong sapna tu in ngai in,
Buh at dingin hong sam;
Buh at ding tampi in hong ngak zo,
Hih hang a at ding tawm.
verse2:
Mawhna khualmial sung om mite kiang,
Pai in va khah khia un,
Pai in mawhna kol va sut khia un.
Mawhna hencip mi kiang.
verse3:
Lunggim mite lungdamna sungah,
Itna tawh va zol un;
Amah nuntak tawntung na khomun,
Tua lai ei hong dawn ding.
chorus:
Topa min in na mailam nawt un,
Itna deih sakna tawh.
Ei hong Gup khiatna thupha letsong,
Leitung teng thangsak un.

verse1:
Mawhna lo lai-a a hoih buh lom teng
A kaikhawm ding an late a om.
Nasepna dingin, thumaan phiaukawi keng,
Kuamah khawl lo ding an lak khit mateng.
verse2:
Zawi neu zong zui in zong in pha takpi,
Lopa a sau hang buh om thei ding hi.
Lam lian zong zui in la nusiat nei ke’n,
Vantung innpi sung hong tum khin uh hen
verse3:
Lo teng khempeuh ah an min khin ta hi,
Leitung kheempeuh in lak ding bek ngak hi;
Ahih hang a la ding tawm, lak ding tam,
La mengmeng kei leeng lah a sia ding tam.
verse4:
Tua ahih ciang hong pai un phiaukawi tawh,
An pha kaikhawm un, no mihingte aw;
An nei Topa hong pai mateng sem un,
Tua ciang an lak pawi ah lungdam khawm un.

verse1:
Lo laiah nasep ding a om laiah,
Buh at hun zo, Na seem dingte tawm pha.
Tuni thumaan na seemte a kiangah,
Topa sawlna bangin ta un.
verse2:
An kholna buhtang tawh na dim sak un.
Lungdamna tawh la pha takpi sa un.
Nitum-a khua a hong mial mateng in,
Pha takpi na seem niloh un.
verse3:
Nasepna haksa, ni a sawt hangin,
Na seemte in nopna lian a ngah ding.
Topa in a teel sa mita dingin,
Nopna pha bel hong pia ding hi.
verse4:
Vangtung khuapi sungah nop pha mahmah,
Haksa na seem kheempeuh in ngah ding hi.
Topa, itna thu in hong tun' ciangah,
Amau nasep a tawp ding hi.
chorus:
Na seeem un, na seem un,
Nopna pha na ngaihsun un.
Topa in thahatna a hong pia ding hi,
Ni tum mateng in na seem un.

verse1:
Tuni in ah tua gam nuam ke’n ka ngaihsun hi,
Ni tum ciangin ah ka tung ding hi;
Hehpihna tawh Honpa kiang ka din’ ciangin ah,
Ka lu tung aksi taang a om diam?
verse2:
Topa hatna sungah na seemin thu ngen ding,
Ka ngah mi bang kei hong hong hi sak in,
Minthan' ni’n aksi taang kei aading hi kha ding
Amah phatna tuihual bang om ciang.
verse3:
Ama mai ka et ciang, bangzah in lungdam ding,
A khe phungah suangmanpha koih ding;
Kham khuapi sungah lungdamna hong khang sak ding,
Ka lu tung aksi taang a om diam?
chorus:
Ka lu tung aksi taang, aksi taang a om diam?
Nitak a ni a tum ciangin ah,
Tawldamna inn sungah, ka khan lawh ciangin ah,
Ka lu tung aksi taang a om diam?

engTitle: Why Do You Wait, Dear Brother?
verse1:
U leh naute’n bang ngak hiam?
Sawtpi bang ding khawl lai uh hiam?
A sian’tho sak omna mun pia ding,
Topa Zeisu’n hong ngak lai hi.
verse2:
Khawl lai lecin bang ngah ding,
Bang lamen lai uh ahi hiam?
Zeisu longal hong gum dang om kei,
Zeisu lam lo, lam dang om kei.
verse3:
Lungsim Kha Siangtho sawlna,
Nangmah in thei lo na hi hiam?
Bang ding gupna sang lo na hiam?
Mawhna vangik suah lo ding maw?
verse4:
U leh naute’n bang ngak hiam?
An lak hun in hong kheng ding hi,
Gumpa’n thupha nang hong pia nuam hi.
Zia nei leeng, sihna gal om hi.
chorus:
Bang ding? Bang Ding?
Tu in hong pai lo hiam?
Bang ding? Bang ding?
Tu in hong pai lo na hiam?

zoTitle: Hong Kiu, Hong Kiu, Kua Om Hiam?
verse1:
Hong kiu, hong kiu kua om hiam?
Hong ngak, hong ngak, nang hong ngak!
Khualzin pa in midik pa hi,
Amah bang na mu ngei maw!
Ka lungsim in lamdang sa hi.
Kongkhak hon’lo ding na hiam?
verse2:
Hong kiu, hong kiu, hiah om lai,
Hong ngak, hong ngak, na um hiam!
Kongkhak hon' ding haksa mahmah.
Singkung lopa’n tuam cip a.
Khuamial khaugui in kancip hi,
Kiimkot tengah len kip hi.
verse3:
Hong kiu, hong kiu, bang om hiam?
Hong ngak, hong ngak, nang hong ngak!
A kilhcip khut in hong kiu lai,
A Kumpi lukhu nuai pan,
A lungneem leh a migit mai,
Hong Gum Topa’n hong ngak lai.

verse1:
Tuni Zeisu hong sam: "Hong pai in," ci.
"Vantung lam thei lo mi, Kha hilh ding hi."
verse2:
Tuni Zeisu hong sam, Tu in ngai in,
Zeisu Topa mai ah, Nangmah pai in.
verse3:
Tuni Zeisu hong sam, Ama kiangah
Nangmah na tai kei leh, Si ding lauhuai.
verse4:
Kha Siangtho zong hong sam, Amah nial ke’n.
A hong hehpih nuam hi. Pai khia sak ke’n.

verse1:
Hin' gim-a mang mi aw, Hong kihei in,
Tuucing hoih pa’n hong sam, ngai in, Tuni’.
Hong hon ding hong zong, sawp siang ding hong ngak,
Amah sang meng in, uaikai nawn kei in.
verse2:
Hong ngak lai hive’n bang hang mangthang ding?
Tuu buk pan gamla na vak khit hangin.
A nun’ takna si tawh hong tan veve,
Hong thuak pihna lian gen zawh loh lamdang.
verse3:
A thupha ngaihsun in, A thu ngai in,
Mawh neilo pa’n sing tung mawhna pua khia;
Mawh maina kician nun’tak tawntungna,
A sisan luan: na tawh nangmah hong pia.
verse4:
Thuman lampi zui in, tangtak pai in,
Zeisu sung lut in, nuntakna kongpi;
Zeisu in lungneem takin hong sam hi,
Pai in lut un, a mangthang nawn lo ding.
chorus:
Hong sam hiauhiau hi, hong thum lailai hi,
Tuucing hoih pa’n nang hong sam za in;
Hong thum nget-ngut hi, hong sam lailai hi.
Itna tawh hong sam, "Hong pai in," ci.

verse1:
A zaknop huai penpen thu, thupha khat a om hi,
A lamdang thuciamna thu, kuama theih ngei loh thu!
Dah ta le hang nuam ta leeng, tua thu um ta kei leeng,
"Hong pai un," ci in hong sam, A singlamteh zuan ni.
verse2:
Bang hangin hong it lawmpa kiang pan na tai khia hiam?
Ama kiang beel mengmeng in, A tawntung in kip in,
Huh ding neilo in ka om, mawhna sungah ka om,
Amah ka taisan hangin, tu in ka zuan kik hi.
verse3:
Ama hong sap mah bangin, A kiang nai semsem ning,
A aw neu kha za peuh leng, ka kinai semsem ding.
Tuipi gal khat mual pang khat, inn tawh ka gamlat hang,
Na khut len in hong zui ning, "Hong pai in" na cih bang.
chorus:
Hong pai un ka kiang, Hong pai un ka kiang,
Lungkham vangik puate, Ka kiang hong pai un,
Ka kiang hong pai un, Ka kiang hong pai un,
Lungkham vangik puate, Ka kiang hong pai un.

zoTitle: Hong Honpa Kiangah Hong Pai Meng in
verse1:
Hong Honpa kiangah hong pai meng in,
Lai Siangtho ah lam hong lak bangin;
Eite laizang ah tu ni’n ding in:
"Hong pai ve," ci’n hong sam.
verse2:
Ngai sin! "Naute hong pai vevua," ci:
I vekpi in kipaak in diang ni,
Eite in Amah va teel tawm ni;
Zekai ke’n, pai ni, tu’n.
verse3:
Ngaihsun pha in, tu ni’n hiah om lai;
Hong thu piakna pha lim takin ngai!
Migi mahmah tu’n zong hong sam lai:
"Nong pai nai uh hia," ci.
chorus:
Mawhna khialhnate siangtho nungah,
Topa mai-ah kikhop ciangin ah,
Tawntung inn nuam vantung khua sungah,
Nuam pha mahmah ding hi.

verse1:
Pasian sap lai ka za kei diam,
Leitung nopna ka kheng lah diam;
Nuntak hun a beibei lai in,
Ka kha ka koih diam, ihsip in?
verse2:
Pasian sap lai ka tho kei diam,
A itna aw ka nial thei diam,
Hong sapna ka awlmawh kei diam,
Hong sam lailai ka uaikai diam.
verse3:
Pasian sap lai hong kiukiu in,
Ka lung ka khak diam a kip in?
Hong ngak lai hong saang ding hi zo,
Ka dah sak ngam diam Kha Siangtho?
chorus:
Hong sam lai! Aw, za in!
Hong sam lai! Aw, za in!
Pa in hong sam lai, aw za un,
Pa in hong sam lai, Hong Sam lai! Aw, za un,
Hong sam lai! Aw, za un,
Pa in hong sam lai! Aw, za un, sam lai!

verse1:
Zeisu’n kong kiu nang hong sam,
"Lunggim mi’n hong zuan un," ci,
Hong gum thei Amah bek hi,
Na kong za hon’in.
verse2:
Zeisu’n kong kiu hong gum ding,
Nang aading A pumpi pia;
Hing kik in han pan tho khia,
Na kong za hon’in.
verse3:
Zeisu’n kong hong kiukiu lai,
Na lungsim Amah pia in,
Lung damna hong pia ding hi,
Na kong za hon’in.
verse4:
Zeisu’n kiu hunte beibei,
Gup khiatna a nai lai in,
Gumpa’n hong paisan ma in,
Na kong za hon’in.
chorus:
Na kong za hon’in, Na kong za hon’in,
Na kong za hon’n, Na kong za hon’n,
Hong gum thei Amah bek hi,
Na kong za hon’in

zoTitle: Tu Nitak Na Ciah Ding Hiam?
verse1:
Inn nong ciah diam, vakthap mi?
Hong gum dingin Zeisu si
Lungkham, gimna thuak mi.
Mawhna si baang na puante
Tuuno si sung na sawp diam?
Na puante paak ding vuk bang.
Na un diam, hong ciamna thupha?
Tu nitak na ciah ding hiam?
verse2:
Inn nong ciah diam, a mang mi?
En in, Topa’n hong ngak hi.
Pai in lunghei nawn ke’n
Ciah in na zekaai kha ding!
Pai in Ama kiang beel in,
Hong itna tha muang in la,
Nong pai diam, ci’n hong samsam lai,
Tu nitak na ciah ding hiam?
verse3:
Inn nong ciah diam, mawhnei mi?
Kua in na mawhna van pua?
Pua lam sawt khawl nawn ke’n,
Tu’n hong ciah in kisik in,
Topa thu ciamna muang in.
Amah’n hong gum pha sak ding
"Hong pai in," ci’n Zeisu’n hong sam:
Tu nitak na ciah ding hiam?
chorus:
Tu nitak na ciah ding hiam?
Tu nitak na ciah ding hiam?
Khuamial sung pan khua vaakna sung,
Zeisu’ inn na ciah ding hiam?
Tu nitak na ciah ding hiam?
Tu nitak na ciah ding hiam?
Hong it vantung i Pa kiangah,
Tu nitak na ciah ding hiam?

verse1:
Hong Honpa in hong kun: Na tha hatna neu hi,
Tha neemte’n thu hong ngen un,
"Cing tak na ngah ding," hong ci.
verse3:
Hehpih ka ngah nading, Phatna khat zong nei,
Ka puan vuk baang paak nading,
Tuuno si sung hong sawp leng.
verse5:
Topa tokhom mai ah, Kicingin ka din' ciang,
Min phatna puak ning Amah,
Nga suk ning Zeisu’ khe kiang.

verse1:
Omna om lai Tuuno innpi sungah,
A vaang lianpi tawh nang hong sam ta hi.
Tum in, tu in tum in, omna om lai.
verse2:
Ni taang bei dek zo, ni in liap ta hi.
Hong liap ta hi, manlang in-ah pai in.
Omna om lai, tum in, tu in tum in.
verse4:
Dim khin dek hi, lungdamnna inn sungah,
Manlang a na lut leh ngah lai ding hi.
Omna om lai, tum in, tu in tum in.
verse5:
Omna om lai, kong kihon’ laitak hi.
Pai in tum lecin na lap lai ding hi.
Omna om lai, tum in, tu in tum in.
verse6:
Tum in, tum in tua pawi nang aading hi.
Ki it tawntung na hai kidawn ding hi.
Tum in, tu in tum in, omna om lai.

zoTitle: Zeisu' Omna Ding Na Nei Hiam?
engTitle: Have You Any Room for Jesus?
verse1:
Na mawhna tang a thuak,
Zeisu om nading mun a om hiam.
Kongkhak kiu in lut ding hong tu,
Mawh neite’n a ngai na diam.
verse2:
Na lung sungah na om sak leh,
Nuamna hong bawl sak ding hi.
Om na’ng na om sak loh hangin,
Na mawhna tang ding si hi.
verse3:
Topa zeisu in a hun ciang,
A thupha tawh hong sam ding.
Tu ni’n a thupha saang in la,
Zingciang ngak kei leteh pha.
verse4:
Om na’ng thu a hun na pia in:
A nuam ding ni kheng sak ke’n.
Sawt loin a hong sam ding leh,
Na lungsim khauh sak kei ve’n.
chorus:
Topa Zeisu minthang Kumpi,
A om na’ng mun tu’n bawl in.
Na lungsim kongkhak tan zau in
Hong in na lut sak ding hi.

verse1:
Zeisu’n hong huausim lai in, Pai’n mawh neite!;
Nang aading thu nget lai in, Pai’n mawh neite!
Tu’n Amah nang aading hi, Pai’n mawh neite!
Tu’n Amah na thei ding hi, Pai’n mawh neite!
verse2:
Nang zong na van gik hiam? Pai’n mawh neite!
Zeisu’n na van hong puaksak, Pai’n mawh neite!
Zeisu’n nang hong nial kei ding, Pai’n mawh neite!
Zeisu in nang hong saang ding, Pai’n mawh neite!
verse3:
Aw, za in A hong thumna, Pai’n mawh neite!
Pai in thupha saang dingin, Pai’n mawh neite!
Zeisu’n hong huausim lai in, Pai’n mawh neite!
Nang aading thu nget lai in, Pai’n mawh neite!

verse1:
Hong gum Topa kei tangin si zo hi.
Mawh tan' na pan kei hong suakta sak hi.
Pasian Tapa a um kheempeuh te in,
Nungta tawntung ding hi.
verse2:
Topa tung mawhna tam ke’n nga zo hi.
Ka mawhna leiba bang hong loh sak hi.
Topa thu a um mi kheempeuh te in,
Hing tawntung ding uh hi.
verse3:
Ka zawngkhal hangin ah thupha um ning.
Ka mawh, ka khial zong hong thupiak muang ning.
Pasian thu umte lungdam nading in.
Hing tawntung ngah ding hi.
verse4:
A kilawm kei zong um khial ngei kei ning.
A pai nuam pai un, hong ngai ding ci in,
Na kiko un Topa thu a umte,
Hing tawntung ding uh hi.
chorus:
A maan takpi a nang kiangah kong cih in,
A maan takpi a nang kiangah kong cih in;
Pasian Tapa a umte maan takin,
A hing tawntung ding hi

zoTitle: Na Kongbiang Pua Lam Ka Ding Hi
engTitle: Behold Me Standing at the Door
verse1:
Na kong biangah ding in ka om,
Kong sapna za in kong en in,
"Kong lut ding hiam," damtak kong ci,
Mawh neite Nong tum sak ding hiam?
verse2:
Nang taa’ng ling lukhu ka khu hi.
Lungduait in sawtpi kong ngak hi.
Kong lut ding hiam? Kong lut ding hiam?
Mawh neite aw hong dawng ve un,
verse3:
A hong mawk sap ka hi kei hi,
Gimna ka thuakna ngaihsun in,
Na mawh phel ding, Ka pum ka pia,
Kong lut ding hiam? Kong lut ding hiam?
verse4:
Nangmah kong it kong ngaih man in,
Na nuam nang vantung pan kong puak,
Kong lut ding hiam? Kong lut ding hiam?
Mawh nei, gimna thuakte’n gen un.
chorus:
Na kong biangah dingin ka om,
Hong en in, dam takin kong sam,
"Kong lut ding hiam? Kong lut ding hiam?"
"Mawh neite aw hong gen kik un."

engTitle: The Light of the World Is Jesus
verse1:
Hih leitung mawhna khuamial bangin zing hi.
Leitung khuavaakna Zeisu hi.
Sun a ni taang bangin ah a vaang taang hi,
Leitung khuavaakna Zeisu hi.
verse2:
A kiang a omte in khuamial mu lo hi.
Leitung khuavaakna Zeisu hi.
Lam hilhpa a zuite in lam tang tawn hi,
Leitung khuavaakna Zeisu hi.
verse3:
Khualmial sung a om mawhna a mittawte,
Leitung khuavaakna Zeisu hi.
Thu hong piak bang na mu ding hi hong sap leh.
Leitung khuavaakna Zeisu hi.
verse4:
Vantung khua-ah ni taang deihna om lo hi.
A taang ding Topa Zeisu hi.
Vantung kham gam sungah a siangtho khuapi.
A vaang taang nading Zeisu hi.
chorus:
No aading in khuavaak a taang hi.
"Khuamial sungpan hong pai in." ci hi.
Mittawte in tu’n khua mu zo hi.
Leitung khuavaakna Zeisu hi.

engTitle: The Gate A jar for Me
verse1:
Kongpi kihong sa-in om a,
A sung panin a vaangpi,
Singlamteh pan hong taang khia a,
Topa' itna hong lak hi.
verse2:
Hot khiatna zong mite kheempeuh,
Tua kongpi hon' sa'n om hi;
A hau, a zawng, a lian,a neu,
A kua, ci lo lut thei hi.
verse3:
Hehpihna kong kihon' lai in,
Nang zong, lau ke’n, delh in la,
Itna' piak lukhu ngah na'ngin,
Singlamteh na saang ding ta.
verse4:
Leitung ah hong piak singlamteh
Sih gun gal-ah i khia ding;
Hin’na lukhu hong piak tak teh,
Amah i it zaw sem ding.
chorus:
Hi takpi zo diam tua kongpi,
Kei aading a hon’sa’n om maw.
Keimah takpi, keimah hong kihon maw.

zoTitle: Nang Leh Keimah Hong Sam Hi
engTitle: Softly And Tenderly Jesus Is Coming
verse1:
Mai taii in damtak Zeisu in hong sam hi.
Nang leh keimah hong sam hi.
Topa Zeisu’n lungduai takin hong ngak hi.
Nang leh keimah hong ngak hi.
verse2:
Bang khawl i hiam Topa Zeisu’n hong thum hi.
Nang leh kei kiang hong thum hi.
Hong hehpihna bang thu’n don lo i hi hiam?
Nang leh kei thupha hong pia.
verse3:
A hun in a man langin hong kheng thei hi.
Nang leh kei hong kheng ding hi.
Khua mialna leh sihna natna hong nai hi.
Nang leh kei hong nai ding hi.
verse4:
Nong itna leh a lamdang thuciam napi,
Nang leh kei aading koih hi.
Gamtat khialhna Topa’n hong phel sak ding hi.
Nang leh kei-aa phel ding hi.
chorus:
Innah ciah un, Gimna thuak te hong ciah un.
Lungdam takin Topa Zeisu in hong sam.
"Mawh neite hong pai un," ci.

verse1:
Zeisu in itna tawh inn-ah hong sam.
Tu ni’n hong sam, tu ni’n hong sam;
Ni bang taang hong itna panin pua lam
Bang ding kidai thahna hiam?
verse2:
Zeisu hong pia nuam a gimte tawldam:
Tu ni’n hong sam, tu ni’n hong sam;
Na van va puakin la, ngah in lungdam,
Nang A hong nial kei ding hi.
verse3:
Zeisu’n hong ngak hi, pai in tu laitak:
Tu ni’n hong sam, tu ni’n hong ngak;
Na mawhna mah tawh va kuan in niamtak,
Pai in, kizekaai sak ke’n.
verse4:
Zeisu in hong zol hi, A’ aw ngai in:
Tu ni’n za in, tu ni’n za in;
Nuamna ngah ding hi, Amah umte in,
Tho in pai pah vingveng in.
chorus:
Tu ni’n hong sam, Tu ni’n hong sam,
Zeisu in hong sam,
Hong it manin, tu ni’n hong sam.

verse1:
"A zate kheempeuh" in hih thu taangko un,
Letung khempeuh ah hih thupha tung sak un,
Mi na muh khempeuh hih nuam huai thu ko un;
"A ut kheempeuh hong pai thei."
verse2:
Hong paite in zekai nading thu om lo,
Lut theih lai-in lut un, kong hon' sa’n om zo;
Zeisu lo thumaan hin'na lampi om lo,
"A ut kheempeuh hong pai thei."
verse3:
"A ut kheempeuh te" thuciam a maantak hi,
"A ut kheempeuh te" thuciam a kip ding hi,
"A ut kheempeuh te" nuntak tawntung na hi;
"A ut kheempeuh hong pai thei."
chorus:
"A ut khempeuhte, a ut khempeuhte,"
Cihna thu a mual a guam va thawn sak un;
Hong it i Pa in hong sam kik lam khialte,
"A ut kheempeuh hong pai un."

verse1:
Mawh neite Zeisu’n ngai hi.
Hih thupha na thang sak un;
Vantung lam khial a puk mi,
Lunghei nei mi va hilh un.
verse3:
Tu’n sinsung kisuang nawn lo,
Thukham mai ah ka siang ta;
Amah’n hong siangsak khin zo,
Thukham kalhna cin’, khin ta.
verse4:
Mawh neite Zeisu’n ngai hi,
Kei nangawn a mawh pi mah;
Vantung ah hong lut pih hi,
Mawhna teng siangta in ah.
chorus:
Sa sa un, sa kikkik un:
Mawh neite Zeisu’n ngai hi;
Hih thu tel tak tangko un.
Mawh neite Zeisu’n ngai hi.

zoTitle: Hong Gum Topa Lut Sak In
verse1:
Zinpa kong kiangah om hi, lut sak in.
Tam veipi hong pai zo hi:
Lut sak in. A pai ma’n lut na’ng pia in
Siangtho Topa lut sak in
Pa Pasian a Tapa in, lut sak in.
verse2:
Lungsim kongkhak tu’n hon’in, lut sak in.
Ngak leh Amah paikhia ding.
Lut sak in. Lut sak in nangma lawmpa
Nangma lungsim kem dinga,
A tawp dong hong gum ding pa, lut sak in.
verse3:
A kam khum na ngai in la, lut sak in.
Tu’n piangsak in nang teelpa.
Lut sak in. Kongkhak kiang ding hi,
Amah khang sak ding na lungdamna,
Ama min na phat ding a, lut sak in.
verse4:
Tu in vantung khua zinpa lut sak in.
Nang vakna pawi kham dinga,
Lut sak in. A hong phel ding na mawhna,
Lawmte tawh kikhen ciangah,
Hong kha ding vantung innah, lut sak in.

verse1:
Hong ciah’n, hong ciah’n!
Na lungsim gimzo hi. Lampi mialzo hi.
Lauhuai in gamdaai ta,
Aw a taaimang ta hongciah’n Aw, hong ciah’n.
verse2:
Hong ciah’n, hong ciah’n!
Hong ngakin kong vil uh kongpi ah ka ding a,
Liim in hong khengkheng ta.
Aw a taaimang ta hongciah’n Aw, hong ciah’n
verse3:
Hong ciah’n, hong ciah’n!
Mawh sakna dahna pan, mawhna maizumna pan,
Kheempa nuihmai na pan,
Aw a taimang ta hong ciah’n Aw, hong ciah’n
verse4:
Hong ciah’n!, hong ciah’n!
Neek ding an tampi om, Vaitutna nuam zong om
Lawmte tawh kipawlna.
Aw, a taaimang ta hong ciah’n! Aw, hong ciah’n!
chorus: Hong ciah’n Aw, hong ciah in.

verse1:
Mawhna a neite hong pai in, Topa in hong hehpih,
Ama thupha bel up ciangin, Nuamna i ngah ding hi.
verse2:
Nuamna a hong pia ding Zeisu, A sipha bel luang sak.
Vuk sangin hong ngo zaw sak thei, A si sung hong phum ta'n.
verse3:
Nopna sung tun' nading, Zeisu Thumaan lampi a hi.
Topa na um ding khawl kei leh, Lung damna ngah ding hi.
verse4:
Mi siang tho kikhopna tum leh, Mi phatna mun pai ning.
Lungdam om tawntungna sungah, Nuamna nangmah'n ngah ding.
chorus:
Amah muangin. Amah muang la Tu in-ah muang in
Hong gum ding hi, hong gum ding hi. Tu in hong gum ding.

verse1:
Pasian kiang pan gam la ka pial.
Tu in hong ciah ing,
Mawhna lam sawt lua ka tawn khial.
Topa hong ciah ing.
verse2:
Hun pha tampi mawk bei sak ing,
Tu in hong ciah ing,
Tu'n kapin kisik taktak ing,
Topa hong ciah ing.
verse3:
Mawhna lam pial, ciam tang Topa,
Tu in hong ciah ing,
Muang ning Na itna leh thupha,
Topa hong ciah ing.
verse4:
Ka kha cina, ka lung meima,
Tu in hong ciah ing,
Hong dip kik in, ka lawpna tha,
Topa hong ciah ing.
chorus:
Hong ciah ing, Hong ciah ing,
Vak khia nawn lo ding,
Thupha tawh Nang aa hi ning,
Topa hong ciah ing.

verse1:
Mawhna neite aw, Zeisu'n hong sam,
A kiangah pai un.
Hong pai un mawhna kisik kheempeuh
Zeisu kiang khia un.
verse2:
A umte pai un nopna zong un,
Topa kiang pai un.
Na lungsim gimna, van gikna peuh
Zeisu kiang khia un.
verse3:
Na upna in hong nuam sak ding hi.
Zeisu kiang pai un.
Na kha aading gimna a tampi,
Zeisu kiang khia un.
verse4:
Hong pai un, no om na'ng om lai hi,
Zeisu kiang pai un.
Na van neih kheempeuh a gik phapi
Zeisu kiang khia un.
chorus:
Khai un, mawh neite khia un,
Topa Zeisu kiang pai un.
Khia un, mawh neite khia un.
Topa kiang khia un.

zoTitle: Na Mawh Phel Nading Om Hi
verse1:
Hong gum Topa min um in a kiang pai in
Lungsim hong bawlthak sak ding hi.
A pha a hong bawl nop lai in pial kei in
Nang aading mawh phelna om hi.
verse2:
Sihna phual tung na mawhna lampi zuihna
Bang zui nuam semsem na hi hiam?
Itna kam khum tawh hong sap na nial ding hiam?
Mawh phelna thu nang hong pia hi.
verse3:
Hong tung ding gal pel in, singlamteh nai in.
Singlamteh in nang hong phel ding.
Na up ciangin thakhat in Kha Siangtho in,
Kisik in, thupha hong pai ding.
chorus:
Na mawh phel nading om hi.
Na mawh phel nading om hi.
Hong gum dingin Zeisu si zo hi.
Na mawh bei na'ng thu hong pia hi.

zoTitle: Gupna Ngah Na'ng Bang Ka Hih Diam?
engTitle: What Shall I Do To Be Saved?
verse1:
Gupna ngah na'ng bang ka hih diam?
Dahna sung ka kha vangik pua bang,
Tuipi kilok bangin,
Huihpi hong nung bangin,
Dahna kei tungah hong kihual-a
Gupna ngah na'ng bang ka hih diam!
Aw, gup ngah na'ng bang ka hih diam?
verse2:
Khangno lungsim a bei ciangin,
Gupna ngah na'ng bang ka hih diam?
Ka it ka lawmte in,
Leitung a nusiat ciang,
Han pualah dahin ka kapkap hi.
Gupna ngah na'ng bang ka hih diam!
Aw, gup ngah na'ng bang ka hih diam?
verse3:
Cinat in hong bawlsiat ciangin,
Gupna ngah na'ng bang ka hih diam?
Leitung tawl khat bek hi,
Meei bangin theng thei hi,
A hun bei ngeilo muh theih na'ngin.
Gupna ngah na'ng bang ka hih diam!
Aw, gup ngah na'ng bang ka hih diam?
verse4:
Hong hehpih in la, hong en in.
Nopsakna keimah hong khiat suk in.
Topa kiang lo mun dang,
