Kua kiang ka zuan ding hiam,
Lungsim kitam Topa'n damsak thei,
Hi bang hih ning! Hi bang hih ning!
Gupna ngah na'ng Zeisu beel ning.

zoTitle: Pai In La Zeisu Kiang Gen In
verse1:
Zeisu kiang pai in, na mawhna gen in.
Na nuntakna ding Ama thu um in.
Na lungsim vangik hong zang sak ding hi,
Topa en in na mawh hong phel ding hi.
verse2:
Zeisu kiang pai in, na mawhna lian hi.
Na mawhna mual cia in a liat hangin,
Mawhna phel ding hi, nuamna ngah na'ngin
Topa Zeisu a si luang ciamteh in.
verse3:
Zeisu kiang pai in, na launa gen in.
Na lau loh nading a ang hong pom ding,
Upna khang sak in, na khitui nul hi.
A tawntung nuamin na lungdam ding hi.
chorus:
Zeisu kiang pai in, na mawhnate gen in.
Ama lam nga in na mawh hong phel ding hi.
Zeisu kiang pai in, Ama lam zuan in,
Na mawh gen in, Topa'n hong phel thei ding hi.

verse1:
Dahna, lung khamna a tun' ciang,
Topa hong sapna ngai in.
Khazih Topa thupha um ing,
Tu ni'n a kiangah pai ning.
verse2:
A Siangtho kiniamsak Topa,
Na kiang keimah kong pai hi.
Hong kem in hong cing in Topa,
Na khut nuai hong om sak in.
verse3:
Ka Kha nopsak na'ng Topa aw,
Nangma kiang kong beel ding hi.
Vantung ah mi siangthote tawh
Ka maang khawm tawntung nuam hi.
verse4:
Ka kiangah hong om in Topa,
Lung khamna huih dai sak in.
Lungdamna piang sak in, dahna
Khuamial, ni taang bang sak in.
chorus:
Kei hong pai ning, kong pai ding hi.
Topa thupha sang dingin.
Kei hong pai ding, kong pai ding hi.
Topa kiang maan' ngah dingin.

zoTitle: Nih Vei Na Suak Kik In
verse1:
Upa khat zan lai Zeisu kiangah pai a,
Gupna ngah nading kuavak lampi dong hi.
Topa in a tel takin a hilh kik-a,
"Nih vei na suak in," ci.
verse2:
Topa Zeisu thu hilh kikna a pha hi.
Leitung mihingte ngaihsut ding kilawm hi.
A thu piakna a mawkna hilo ding hi.
"Nih vei suak kik in," ci.
verse3:
A teel mite tawh lung damin la sa ta.
Mi phate'n a min thang lung damin nuam-a,
Hin' tawntung lungdamna, nuamna ngah nop leh,
"Nih vei suak kik in," ci.
verse4:
Na muhnop mihingte vantung khuapi ah,
A siangtho kong biangah nang hong ngak uh hi.
Tua bang na muh nang hih thu piakna ngai in.
"Nih vei suak kik in," ci.
chorus:
Nih vei na suak kik in.
Nih vei na suak kik in.
A maan takin kong ci hi, kong hilh kik hi.
Nih vei na suak kik in.

verse1:
Khialhna a nei gimna thuak mi ka hi.
Vantungah ka et leh tum nuam ka hi.
Hih hang tua sungah khial nei om thei kei.
Hih hang "Hong pai in," cih aw khat ka thei.
verse2:
Nisim ka pai lai, vantung khua lampi,
A tawntung mawhna, khialhna'n hong kheem hi.
Hih hang "Pu lak in, na kisik kik leh,
Mawh kiphel ngah ding," cih thu ka thei hi.
verse3:
Kihhuai mi ka hih ciangin bang ci in,
Tua khua siangtho sungah ka lut ding hiam.
Pasian tokhom maiah ding thei ding hiam.
Hih hang, "Hong nai in," khut tawh hong sam in.
verse4:
Zeisu Topa a aw, ke'n ka za hi.
Ama khut in kei hong nai sak thei hi.
Ama si in ka mawhna ka khialhna,
Hong phel thei vantungah hong lutsak ta.
verse5:
Topa aw ka hong thumna hong ngai in.
Na hehpihna in kei aading kicing.
Na ling lukhu in kei kumpi lukhu,
Ka nuntakna ding Nang nun'na Nong pia.
verse6:
Neihsa bangmah nei keng, Nang kong puak ding;
Ka lungsim pumpi'n Nang kong kipia khin.
Ka lungsim teng bang ci'n kong pia thei diam,
Mawh phel nading thu'n ka lung hong nuam sak.

zoTitle: Tuuno Si Tawh Na Kisawp Zo Hiam?
verse1:
A siangtho ngah ding Zeisu kiang na pai hiam?
Tuuno si tawh na kisawp zo hiam?
A thupha kicing dingin na um nai hiam?
Tuuno si tawh na kisawp zo hiam?
verse2:
Nisim in Topa kiangah lam na zui hiam?
Tuuno si tawh na kisawp zo hiam?
Kithat a thuak Topa kiang na beel ta hiam?
Tuuno si tawh na kisawp zo hiam?
verse3:
Mopipa hong pai ciang na puan siang dingin
Tuuno si tawh na kisawp ding hiam?
A bawl innpi nuamah lut theih nading in
Tuuno si tawh na kisawp ding hiam?
verse4:
Mawhna khialhna a baang na puansilh pai in
Tuuno si tawh na kisawp ding hiam?
A siang lo na lung sung ciktui luang sak in
Tuuno si tawh na kisawp ding hiam?
chorus:
Tuuno a, sipha tawh
Nangmah in na kisawp siang zo maw?
Na puansilh vuk bangin ah na ngah zo hiam?
Tuuno si tawh na kisawp zo hiam?

verse1:
Dahna khanen'niam sung ka khawivak zo hi,
Tu in lungnuam takin ka tawl a dam hi.
Zing tung pan nitak dong in la ka sa hi.
Kumpipa tawh ka ton khawmna thu hang hi.
verse2:
Kum tampi mawhna hen cip in ka om hi,
Leitungah hong hon zo om lo ka thei hi.
Tu in vasa bangin ka suakta zo hi.
Lungdamin Kumpipa tawh ka ton khawm.
verse3:
Leitung kibuaina sunga cimawh kha aw,
En to in, Zeisu na sungah lut sak in,
Lungdam huai gupkhiatna a hong puak ding hi.
Ni taang sung zuan in Kumpi tawh ton khawm in.
chorus:
Kumpi tawh ton khawm, Haleluiah
Kumpi tawh ton khawm A min phat
Ka kha vakthap nawn lo inn lam a zuan
Kumpi tawh ton khawm kikum khawm

zoTitle: Lam Khial Tuu Ka Hi A
engTitle: I Was a Wondering Sheep (Tune: Lebanon)
verse1:
Lam khial tuu ka hi a, Tuu khumna ka deih kei,
Hong cingpa aw ka deih lo a, A thu ka ngaih nuam kei.
Gilo ta hi’ng, ka Pa' inn ah om nuam lo in,
Ka Pa' aw ka ngai nuam kei a,Gamla pai nuam kha ing
verse2:
Tuu cing pa’n tuu zon’ bang, Pa in ta hong zong hi
Mual tung guam sungah va pai hi,Gamla vak kawikawi hi
Ka si dek ta hong mu, gilkial in ka om hi
Ki-itna tawh Amah’n hong pua, lam khialpa hong gum hi
verse3:
Tuucing pa’n Zeisu hi, Amah’n ka kha it hi
Ama si tawh a hong sawp zo, A hong cingsak zo hi
Amah’n lam khial mi zong, tuu mangthang a mu hi
Amah in tuu khumna hong pi, Tu in hong kem thei hi
verse4:
Lam khial tuu hi zo ta’ng, Kuama thu ke’n ngai ke’ng
Tu in tuu cing aw ngai nuam ta’ng, Tuu khumna om nuam ning
Ta gilo ka hi a, ka vak kawikawi nuam hi
Ahih hangin tu’n ka Pa’ inn sungah ka om nuam hi

verse1:
Singlamteh tung aa Zeisu en in
Nang aading leh kei aading hong si
Ngai in itna’n A kiang hong sap lai,
En in, hing ta in!
verse2:
Na mawh van gik kha hong gum ding hiam?
Nun’tak tawntungna na nei ding maw?
Zeisu bekin hong hon zo thei hi
En in, hing ta in!
verse3:
Han pan a tho Zeisu en leci’n
Manlang in inn dei sung om lai in
A mai nuam in hong lungdam sak ding
En in, hing ta in!
verse4:
Zeisu’n van nun’nuam hong bawl sak hi
Lungkham mawhnei mi’ sapna hong thei
Na paina peuhah hong kha ding hi
En in, hing ta in!
chorus:
En in, hing ta in! En in, hing ta in!
Nang aading sing tung sihna en in
En in, hing ta in!

zoTitle: Kei’ Dahna, Khuamial, Kol Tan’na Pan
verse1:
Kei’ dahna, khuamial, koltan’na pan
Zeisu, kong pai!, Zeisu, kong pai!
Nang’nuamna khuavaak, suahtakna lam
Zeisu, Nang kiang kong pai!
Ka natna pan Nang' damna sungah
Ka zawn’na pan Nang hauhna sungah
Ka mawhna sung pan nangma sungah
Zeisu, Nang kiang kong pai!
verse2:
Zumhuai lelhna, supna panin ah
Zeisu, kong pai!, Zeisu, kong pai!
Vaanglian Na singlamteh meetna ah
Zeisu, Nang kiang kong pai!
Leitung dahna pan Nang khoina sung
Huihpi sung pan Nangma daihna sung
Lunggimna pan nuam la sakna sung
Zeisu, Nang kiang kong pai!
verse3:
Pha thei lo kisak theihna panin
Zeisu, kong pai!, Zeisu, kong pai!
Nang ma deihna bangbang mang dingin
Zeisu, Nang kiang kong pai!
Ka pumpi nusia’n Na itna sung
Lungkiatna pan vantung nuamna sung
Saang semsem leeng toning a tawntung
Zeisu, Nang kiang kong pai!

zoTitle: Ka Nun’ Sung Ka Tat Khialhna
verse1:
Ka nun’sung ka tat khialhna tam zo a
Ka lungsim mawhna tam zaw sem ta
Ka kahna in khua mu lo pi
Kong hon’sa ka va kiu ding hi
verse2:
Amah itna lakah kei a neu pen
Thungetna ah zong a zawngkhal pen
Hong sap bang ke’n ka zuan mawk hi
Amah in hong nial lo ding hi
verse3:
Ka khialhte hehpihna in siin ding hi
Ka mawhna Amah’n sil khia ding hi
Meidawi-a kiplo keima khe
A taang kongpi lam zuan gige
verse4:
Ka nun’sung ka tatkhialhna tam zo a
Mawhna hang ka lungsim sung min ta
Ka kahna in khua mu lo pi
Hong Honpa’n hong tum sak ding hi
chorus:
Ka mawhna ka ginat lohna
Tampi ka phawk semsem ta
Ahih hang Zeisu’n hong sap ciang inn sungah
Ka tum ding kongpi hon’ sa

verse1:
Topa, ka za Na aw
Nang kiang a Nong sapna,
Kalani Na si manpha tawh
Keimah hong sawp nuam a
verse2:
Zawngkhal, kihhuai hangin
Ka tha Nong khauh sak hi
Nengkha zong kihbaang nawn loin
Mawhna nong sawp sak hi
verse3:
Leitung vantung aading
Upna, itna, lawpna
Lung nopna, muan'na a kicing
Zeisu hi hong guan’Pa
verse4:
Mawhna a manna sa
Keima lungsim sungah
Thupha nasepna hong pantah
Hong kipsak Zeisu mah
verse5:
Zeisu in hong pia ding
Hong khapsa khempeuhte
A thu mantak a zui ta ding
Upna tawh ngen peuh leh
verse6:
Thang hen, mawh maina si
Thang hen, hong tan itna
Thang hen, Pasian’ hong piak Khazih
Eite’ Tha le Dikna
chorus:
Kong pai hi, Topa
Kong pai hi, tu in
Kalani a Na sipha
Keimah hong sawpna in

zoTitle: I Mawhna Hangin Zeisu Kap Maw?
engTitle: Did Christ O’er Sinners Weep? (Tune: Boylston)
verse1:
Mihing mawhna hangin, i To Zeisu kap maw?
Mi khempeuh kap in om kei un
Ka khitui taak ciangin
verse2:
Zeisu khitui luangin, vantung mi’n hon en a
Haksatna thuakin khitui luang
Nang taang ding Topa’n thuak
verse3:
A kah bang kap un la, mawh mai na’ng khitui hi
Vantung ah mawhna om nawn lo
Khitui luan’na om lo
verse4:
Tuunno Zeisu a hi, a tawntung in phat un
Hong thuciam bangin nungta in
Van le lei Topa hi

zoTitle: Kah Hang Hong Gum Zo Lo!
verse1:
Kah hang hong gum zo lo!
Khitui in ka mai sawp zong
Ka launa dai sak tuam lo
Mawhna kum sawp siang thei lo
Kah hang hong gum zo lo!
verse2:
Sep hang hong gum zo lo!
A hoih pen ka seem thei zong
A siang pen ka ngaisun zong
Ka kha thak suak sak thei kei
Sep hang hong gum zo lo!
verse3:
Ngak hang hong gum zo lo!
Huh theih loh mawhna nei zong
Ka bil sung hehpih’n hong sam
Ngak lai leng ka si ding hi
Ngak hang hong gum zo lo!
verse4:
Khazih upna’n hong gum!
Hong um sakin Na Tapa
A bawlsa nate um in
A khut in kei hong pom ding
Khazih upna’n hong gum!
chorus:
Zeisu kap, kei tang ding si
Singkhuam tungah khaina thuak
Kei hong hon dingin hong ngak
Amah bek hong hon thei

engTitle: I Am Coming to the Cross
verse1:
Singlamteh kiang kong pai
Tha le sum lo mittaw pi
Na dang bangmah man lo pi
Hotna cing ka zong ding hi
verse2:
Nang kong lung gulhna sawt hi
Ka gitloh sawt lua zo hi
Zeisu in damtak hong ci
"Na mawhna Kong sawp ding hi"
verse3:
Ka vekpi’n kong kipia ta
Ka lawm, ka hun, ka neihsa
Ka vekpi’n ka pum ka kha
Nang aa ka hi khin nuam ta
verse4:
Na thu ciamte ka muang hi
Na sipha tu’n ka phawk hi
Ka lungsim ka niamkhiat hi
Nangmah tawh ka si khawm hi
chorus:
Topa, Nangmah kong muang zo
Singlamteh tung si Tuuno
Na singlamteh kong beel zo
Hong hon aw, tu’n hong hon aw

verse1:
Ka hi bangin paulap nei lo
Kei aading Na si luang sim loh, Nangmah in nong sapna thu tawh
Pasian' Tuuno, kong zuan, kong zuan
verse2:
Ka hi bangin misia, mittaw
Khua muhna hauhna, damna tawh
Ka sapna teng ngah dingin aw
Pasian' Tuuno, kong zuan, kong zuan
verse3:
Ka hi bangin mawhna baangin
Kisil tawm dingin khawl loin
Na si’n hong siang sak thei manin
Pasian' Tuuno, kong zuan, kong zuan
verse4:
Ka hi bangin Nong sang mah ding
Nong phel, Nong sawp, Nong huh mah ding
Na thuciam ka um zo manin
Pasian’ Tuuno, kong zuan, kong zuan

verse1:
Kong sapna ngai in, tu’n hong hehpih in
Hong Honpa hong pai in
Ka lunggim zo, Nang kong ngai ta tu in
Hong Honpa hong pai in
verse2:
Zan khualmial sung, ka belh ding ka nei lo
Hong Honpa hong pai in
Khatvei Nong et hin'na khuavak hi zo
Hong Honpa hong pai in
verse3:
Lam gamdai a, ka khe zong gim zo ta
Hong Honpa hong pai in
Ka dak leh Na it mai mu zenzen a
Hong Honpa hong pai in
verse4:
Na nial ngeikei lung tamkhamte’ thum na
Hong Honpa hong pai in
Na ngai in lung niam khiat a kong thumna
Hong Honpa hong pai in
chorus:
Ka va gammang mual tung khuadam lakah
Inn pan gamlapi ka pial khin
Tu’n hong la in, nong ciahpih’n nang innah
Hong Honpa hong pai in

zoTitle: Na Kheempeuh Khatvei In Zo Hi
verse1:
Thukham sung pan suakta nuam mahmah ing
Zeisu in a si tawh a hong sawp hi
Thukham sung pan ka suahtak nading
Hong itna tawh hong gum zo hi
verse2:
Thukhamna pan i suakta zo khin a
Zeisu’n gupna kicing hong pia zo ta
Kam siamin hong sam: "Hong pai un" ci
Khatvei hong gum leh kicing hi
verse3:
Pasian' Tapa cihna i ngah zo ta
A pukte itna tawh hong phong zo ding
Hong sap ciang sihna pan hing kik ding
Zeisun’ cing ding khatvei gum hi
chorus:
Cing ding hi mawh neite’n um ta un
Cing ding hi, u ten nau te’n um un
Singlamteh beel leeng mawhna kia ding
Zeisu’n cing ding khatvei gum hi

verse1:
Kiphat sakna’n kum sawt ka bei sak
Kei aading kithat Topa don lo,
Kei aading hong sih lam ka phawk kei
Kalvari ah
verse2:
Pasian thu in ka mawhlam phawk sak
Bang ka hi ka phawk ciang ka liing a
A mawh ka kha thumin, ka kihei
Kalvari lam
verse3:
Tu’n Zeisu a vekpi’n ka pia khin
Tu’n Amah ka Kumpipa hi ta
Tun’ a sia sa kha in la a sa
Kalvari mah
verse4:
Aw, gup khiatna thu a geel itna!
Aw, mi tung dong hong puak suk thupha
Aw, a khauh kizopna lei hong dawh
Kalvari ah
chorus:
Man piak loh hehpihna a lian leh
Mawh mai sakna kei tungah khang a
Ka kha vangik tu in suakta hi
Kalvari ah

verse1:
Kei aading tam Khang Suangpi
Nangma sung kong beel ding hi.
Na pang vang pan hong kizui
Thakhat luang khia, "si le tui"
Mawh kiphel thuapna hi hen
Hong sut hen la hong sawp hen
verse2:
Ka khut in ka sepna tawh
Thukham, deihna cin’ zo lo
Hahkat den zo mah lengzong
Tawp lo khitui luang hang zong
Mawhna kiphel zo sam lo
Nangmah bekin Nong hon zo
verse3:
Khut sung bangmah keng lopi
Na singlamteh kong beel hi
Puan nei lo Nangmah’n Nong guan
Cimawh hehpihna kong zuan
Kihhuai tuinak kong delh hi
Nong sil ke’h ka si ding hi
verse4:
Ka nuntak lai hi ta leh
Ka sih laitak hi ta leh
Theih loh gam ka kaiciang zong
Thu khenna mai kong tun’ dong
Kei taang kitam Suangpi aw
Nangma sung hong beel sak aw

verse1:
A pha takpi in na do in
Zeisu’n lung khauhna hong pia ding
Nun'takna pha takpi lem a
A hi ding nangma lung damna
verse2:
Pasian upna tawh kidem in
Dak to, Ama maitang en in
 Nun'takna lampi a om hi
Zeisu’n lampi leh nuamna hi
verse3:
Lung man'na paai in la um in
Zeisu in hong hehpih ding hi
Nuam in muang in la, Zeisu in
Nangma nun'takna hi, thei in
verse4:
Tha zawng kei in na nuam in la
Zeisu kiang mipha na hi a
A thu na up leh Zeisu in
Nangma deihna a thei ding hi

verse1:
I galte’n ah hong zo ci’n na lau hiam
Pau lam khuamial sangin sungah mial zaw hiam?
Khuavakna kongvangte khempeuh hong in la
Nitaang khauvaak lut sak in
verse2:
Na nasep laitak na upna a kiam hiam
Nangmah na thu ngetna in hong ngai lo hiam?
Khuavakna kongvangte khempeuh hong in la
Nitaang khauvaak lut sak in
verse3:
Nuamna tawh lampi na pai to nuam ding hiam
Ni sun lai khua mialna thei lo na deih hiam?
Khuavakna kongvangte khempeuh hong in la
Nitaang khauvaak lut sak in
chorus:
Nitaang khuavaak lut sak in
Nitaang khuavaak lut sak in
Khuavakna kongvangte khempeuh hong in la
Nitaang khuavak lut sak in

zoTitle: A Sangna Lam Ka Kah To Hi
verse1:
A sangna lam ka kah to hi
Nisim a thak ka tung to hi
Kah to kawm kong thum lai Topa
"Hong suan to in a sangzaw ah"
verse2:
Lung man’na, launa, tamna ah,Mi dangte a ut hangin ah
Kei ka lungsim a ut kei hi
Kei' tupna a sangzaw na hi
verse3:
A sangzaw a mi siangte' la
Upna tawh keimah in ka za
Dawi mangpa’n thal in hong kap hang
Ka sangzaw nuam hi leitung sang
verse4:
A sang pen dong ka kah nuam hi
Vaangliatna taang ka mu nuam hi
Vantung ka muh dong, Topa aw
A sangzaw ah hong pi to aw
chorus:
Topa aw hong dom to in la
Ka muh ngei nai loh van zangah
Upna tawh hong ding to sak in
A sangzaw ah hong suan to in

verse1:
Hong phat ung, Topa
Kote Nong it manin
Si a tu’n van a om
Zeisu Nong piak man in
verse2:
Hong phat ung, Kha Siangtho
Khuavaak Nong piak man’
Ko Honpa Nong lak a
Khuamial nong bei sak man'
verse3:
Thahna thuak Tuuno
Minthang hen, phat ciat un
Mawhna pua a, nitna
Hong sawp siang Pa phat un
verse4:
Hong hing kik sak in
Na itna hong guan’ in
Ko khate van pan mei tawh
Hong kuang kik sak in
chorus:
Haleluiah! Nangma minthang
Haleluiah! Amen
Haleluiah! Nangma minthang
Hong hing kik sak in

zoTitle: Topa Pasian, Na Na Seem Ding
engTitle: Thy Work, O God, Needs Many Hands (Tune: Manoah)
verse1:
Topa Pasian, Na na seem ding
Mitam kisam tawntung
Tuate in seem kim zolo ding
Huhna puak kei le ung
verse2:
Topa Nangmah kong it man un
Nasepna dingin ah
Kong piak uh zangin Nangma thu’n
Zeisu min dingin ah

zoTitle: Si A Khut Guak Masuan Ding Maw
engTitle: Must I Go and Empty Handed?
verse1:
Si a khut guak masuan ding maw
Topa mu ding hi bangin
A' na ni khat beek zong sem lo
Puak ding bangmah keng lo in
verse2:
Sih ding kihta ka hi kei hi
Topa in hong hon zo tah
Ahih hangin guak pai ding pen
Ngaihsut ciang sin lung kha lah
verse3:
Mawhna sung aa mawk bei kum teng
Khatvei sam kik thei leng maw
A vekpi in Topa piain
A' deih bang mang nuam sing maw
verse4:
Hahkat un, dingun, mi siangte
Sun lai na a citakin seem
Sihna zan in hong phak ma in
Mi ngah na’ng sep theih lai seem
chorus:
Si ding a, khut guak masuan in
Hong Honpa mai mu ding maw
Amah dawnna ding mikhat zong tonpih lo
Guak pai ding maw

engTitle: A Charge To Keep I Have (Tune: Boylston)
verse1:
Sep ding ka neih tavuan
Pasian minthan’ sak ding
Gumkhia thei si ngeilo Kha khat
Vantungah ka bulh ding
verse2:
Tu hun ka kipia ding
Hong sapna ka saang ding
Ka hih theih khempeuh ka zang ding
Ka Topa deih bangin
verse3:
Nang hong iplah sak in
Na muhna sung hing sak’n
Aw, Na na seem pa, kiging sa’n
Sazian lak ding om sak’n
verse4:
Vil in thunget hong huh’n
Nang tung bek mah muangin
Kei muanna bang piang kei kha leh
A si den ding ka hi

zoTitle: A Sia Ding Hon Khia In
verse1:
A sia ding hon khia in, a si ding don in
Mawhna le sihna pan in dok khia in
Kah in lamkhial mite, Phong in a pukte
Zeisu' hotna theisak in amaute
verse2:
Amau don ta kei leh, Amah’n ngak lai veh
Saang lai ding hi, amau kisik peuh leh
Va sam in citakin, damtak va zol in
Um peuh le uh mawh kiphel maan takin
verse3:
Dawi mangpa netcipsa, Mihing' lungsim pha
Hehpihna thupha in phong kik thei a
Itna tawh va zol in, Phong leeng dam takin
Khuang khau tatsa peh bang ngaih ngei bangin
verse4:
A sia ding hon khia in, phamawh sep lohin
Sep zawh nang tha hong pia ding Topa in
A kawcik lampi-ah, zol teitei in la,
Hilh in ama ta'ng Topa si khin ta
chorus:
A sia ding hon khia in, A si ding don in
Zeisu in hehpih hi, A hon ding hi

verse1:
Na seem un, na seem un, Pasian sawltak hi hang
I Topa totsa lampi mah a zui hi hang
Ama thu nuam in ei hong thahat sak ding hi
Na sep ding i muh peuh thahatna tawh seem ni
verse2:
Na seem un, na seem un, gil kialte an vaak un
Nun’takna tuinak ah mi gimte paipih un
Singlamteh le lung damna thu tawh kipaak ni
Tangko un, "Man ngen lo, a khawn khong hong hon hi"
verse3:
Na seem un, na seem un, om hi mi kim sep ding
Theihkhialhna khumial gam hi eite sukmang ding
I Topa Pasian min i pahtawi ding a hi
Tangko un, "Man ngen lo, a khawnkhong hong hon hi"
verse4:
Na seem un, na seem un, Topa’ tha tawh seem ding
Kumpi puan le lukhu nuamna eite’n saang ding
Tatkhiatsa mi dikte tawh eite’n i vekpi'n
Sa khawm ding, "Man ngen lo, a khawnkhong hong hon hi"
chorus:
Na seem un, na seem un
Na seem un, na seem un
Lam-en un, thungen un
Topa hong pai mateng seem un

verse1:
Kumpipa galkapte’n a et dingin ah
Dial pei khat a kilak hi
Gupna ngah mite’n la a sak khawm laitak
Hih dial na saang sak ding hi
verse2:
Galkapte in tui bang tam a om hangin
Dial peina na lak sak un
Dial peina nuaiah Topa galkap bangin
Lau loin na do ta un
verse3:
Leitung, tuitung, mite omna khempeuh ah
Lung damna thu za sak un
Topa in Ama thu a umte lak na’ng
Dial peina tangthu hilh un
verse4:
A kinaina khua a vaak laitakin ah
Kumpipa a galte in
A tai uh ama singlamtehna in ah
Leitungah maang ding hi
chorus:
Pai ta un, mai nawt un
Zeisu aading khempeuh pai un
Hahkatna seem un, la sa un
Zeisu Kumpipa'n koih un

zoTitle: Hiah Om Ing, Hong Sawl In
verse1:
Topa hong sapna aw ngai in
Tuni’n kua pai na seem ding?
An vuite kuai zo, lak ding ngak
Kua’n a si te haih khia ding?
Topa in nakpi in hong sam
Thaman tampi pia dingin
Kua’n lung damna tawh hong dawngin
"Hiah om ing, hong sawl in!"
"Hiah om ing, hong sawl in!"
verse2:
Tua tuipi na kan zawh kei leh
Lawkite gam na tung ding
Tua gam sung nai zaw’n na mu ding
Na huh thei ding na kong biang
Tul tampi na piak zawh kei leh
A neu pen in na hih thei
Meigong nu bangin na pia thei
Nang ma aading a man pha!
Nang ma aading a man pha!
verse3:
Van mi bang na gen thei kei zong
Pawlu bang na siam kei zong
Zeisu hong itna na gen thei
Kei tang ding si na ci thei
Lamdang a thu khen nading tawh
Thaneem khan’lawh zawh kei leh
Naupangte na makaih thei ding
Topa hong khut zaakna sung!
Topa hong khut zaakna sung
verse4:
"Ka sep thei bang mah om kei" ci'n
Kuama kiang gen ngei kei in
Mi dangte a sih laitak in
Topa in nang hong sam hi
Lungdam in nasep ding hong pia
Lungdam in A na sem in
Hong sap ciang manlang in dawngin
"Hiah om ing, hong sawl in!"
"Hiah om ing, hong sawl in!"

verse1:
Topa it teng pai ni, Lang sak ni i nuamna
Kituak takin la sa khawm ni,
Kituak takin la sa khawm ni
Topa' tokhom kiim ah,
Topa' tokhom kiim ah
verse2:
Ei' Pasian thei lote’n phat nuam ta kei le uh
Ei vantung Kumpipa' tate’n,
Ei vantung Kumpipa' tate’n
Thang sak un nuamna thu,
Thang sak un nuamna thu
verse3:
Vantung gam sung tum ma, Kham khua sung sik ma in
Hong maleep hi siangtho nuamna,
Hong maleep hi siangtho nuamna
Zion mual kah lai in,
Zion mual kah lai in
verse4:
Tua hi a, la sa un, Nul un dahna khitui
Vantung gamah a nopna mun,
Vantung gamah a nopna mun
Tun’ nading lam i zui,
Tun' nading lam i zui
chorus:
Zion khua i pai hi
A kilawm khu pha pi Zion
I tun' mateng kah toto ni
Kilawm Pasian’ khuapi Zion

verse1:
Singlamteh galkap ka hi hiam
Topa' nungzui hi hiam?
Ama nasepna dingin ah
Ka maizum thei ding hiam?
verse2:
Midangte’n nopna ngah dingin
Sih dongin a do hi
Paak tawh kibawl lupna tungah
Van a kipua ding hiam
verse3:
Gal do ding galte a om hiam
Tui luan’na thuak ding hiam
Leitung gitlohna in Pasian
Kiang hong paipih ding hiam
verse4:
Mang dingin ah ka kido na’ng
Hong hangsak in Topa
Nangma thupha’n hong huh ta in
Gimna ka thuak ciangin
chorus:
Kei taang ding a si mipa (A min pha tawh ka do ding)
Singlamteh ka puak hangin ah
Zawhna lukhu ngah ding

engTitle: Must Jesus Bear the Cross Alone? (Tune: Maidand)
verse1:
Zeisu kia’n singlamteh pua a
Guak pai ding maw lei mi
Hi lo, mi kim puak ding om a
Kei' puak ding zong om hi
verse2:
Singlamteh ke’n ka pua ding hi
Sihna’n hong khah mateng
Kumpi lukhu ka ngah ding hi
Vantung innpi tung leng
verse3:
A kikhen let Zeisu khe kiang
Lim lang suangphah tungah
Ka kham lukhu ka ngah suk ciang
Nuam in phat ning Amah
verse4:
Aw manpha hi, tua singlamteh
Vaanlian kumpi lukhu
Ka ngah ding hi hin’kik ni teh
Hong lak ding lawpna thu

verse1:
I Topa Pasian muangin, Mai nawt un! Mai nawt un!
Hong ciamna kammal muangin, Mai nawt un!
A minthangna nial ngei ke’n, Hi kei leh na maizum ding
A minthan’na kizelh dong, Mai nawt un!
verse2:
Amah’n lo lai hong sam zo, Mai nawt un! Mai nawt un!
Zan hong tung ding tu’n um in, Mai nawt un!
Upna, itna, biakna sung, Amah hatna tha suangin
Khotak i ding tawntung ding, Mai nawt un!
verse3:
Kham khaici hong pia zo hi, Mai nawt un! Mai nawt un!
Vawh in na at kik ding hi, Mai nawt un!
Na Topa lam na sial in
Ngakna ding leh khawlna ding
Na thumna za'n hong saang ding, Mai nawt un!
verse4:
A beina hong nai zo hi, Mai nawt un! Mai nawt un!
Launa tawh Topa phat un, Mai nawt un!
Khazih na pum a ten’na
Vantung khomun lampi ah
Minthan'ni ciang dong hong kha, Mai nawt un!

zoTitle: At Hun Ciang Bang Aci Diam?
verse1:
Ki-itna khaici zingsang vawh un
Nisun lai takin zong na suan un
Nitak lam in zong na hahkat un
Zan ciang in zong khaici na vawh un
At hun ciang bang a ci diam?
At hun ciang bang a ci diam?
verse2:
Khaici kim khat lampi ah kia hi
Khaici kim khat suang lakah kia hi
Khaici kim khat ling lakah kia hi
Khaici kim khat lei hoih ah kia hi
At hun ciang bang a ci diam?
At hun ciang bang a ci diam?
verse3:
Gimna thuakin khaici pha vawh un
Lungsim siat hang khaici na vawh un
Mi mai siat thuak hangin hahkat un
Mai zumna thuak hangin lungkia ke’n
At hun ciang bang a ci diam?
At hun ciang bang a ci diam?
chorus:
Sun ahi zong, zan ahi zong vawh un
Tha khauh lai bang, thaneem lai zong vawh un
Nun'tak sung hi leh, sih khit hi leh
A khop hun khatvei tung ding hi
At hun ciang bang a ci diam?
At hun ciang bang a ci diam?

verse1:
Tapidaw limtak pai, launa hong nai
Launa, lin'na sung-a khual na zin lai
A pua-ah thang, a sungah ze-etna
Tum kik sak ding, hong zol mawhna sungah
Tapidaw limtak pai, Tapidaw limtak pai
Tapidaw limtak pai, Launa hong nai
verse2:
Tapidaw nuam in pai, huihpi lak dong
Ging ngeingai in, mial in a lauhuai hang
Huihpi leh meiipi hong theng kik pah ding
Tua ciang na Honpa tawh tawlnga den ding
Tapidaw nuam in pai, Tapidaw nuam in pai
Tapidaw nuam in pai, Huihpi lak dong
verse3:
Tapidaw ngen in pai, na puk zel hang
Honpa na koh khialh leh na puk zel ding
Thungetna galvante nang na silh leh
Ze-etna haksa kantan zo ni teh
Tapidaw ngen in pai, Tapidaw ngen in pai
Tapidaw ngen in pai, Na puk zel hang

verse1:
Paak tampi a om tui a pha takpi luan'na
Mual kuam ah hong gum Topa tawh ka pai ding a
Lam a hong hilh khempeuh Ama nung ka zui ding hi
Amah tawh kawi pai a vantung tung ding hi.
verse2:
Huihpi a nung a tuipi nakpi a luan'na
Mual kuam ah hong gum Topa tawh ka pai ding a
Amah in ka khut hong let ciangin ka lau kei ding
Topa in hong nai laitak ka lau thei kei
verse3:
Mual kuam a hi a, mual sangpi tung ahi zong
Hong gum Topa tawh kinai in ka om ding a
Pasian mual tungah mihingte a kikhopna ah
Ama tot sa lampi ah hong kha ding hi
chorus:
Kong zui ding hi, Zeisu kong zui ding hi
Gamlapi gam khempeuh ah kong zui ding hi
Kong zui ding hi. Zeisu kong zui ding hi
A hong hilh lampi tengah ka zui ding hi

engTitle: Open My Eyes That I May See
verse1:
Hong mu sak in, Nangma thumaan, Keima aading Na koihsate
Ka khut sungah hong pia in, Nangmah'n hong khah khia thei kol sutnate
Nangma deihna muh theih nading, Kong ngak hi, Topa Pasian aw
Hong mu sak in, Hong vaak sak in, Kha Siangtho aw
verse2:
Hong za sak in, Nangma thumaan, Tel tak a Na gin' sak thute
Tua hi leh thu tampi ka zak hang, Leeng mang ding hi a maan lote
Nangma deihna tel theih nading, Kong ngak hi, Topa Pasian aw
Hong za sak in, Hong vaak sak in, Kha Siangtho aw
verse3:
Hong za sak in, Nangma thumaan, Mun khempeuh ah lungdam takin
Ka lungsim hong puah sak, hon' sak ta’n Nangma mite ka it na’ng in
Nangma deihna hih theih nading, Kong ngak hi, Topa Pasian aw
Ka lungsim sung, Hong vaak sak in, Kha Siangtho aw

zoTitle: A Nai A Gamla Lote Ah
verse1:
A nai a gamla lote ah,
Ante min khin zo ta hi
Sim le zo, mual lo zang lo ah,
An vuite min zo ta hi
verse2:
Zingsang phalvak tuung a hi zong,
Sun kim ciang a hi zongin
Hong kuan sak lai in nitak zong,
Lo lai teng an khawm dingin
verse3:
Kuan meng un, Topa' sawltakte,
An vuite kuai zo ta hi
An kaikhawm khin, ni hong tum teh,
Lungdam in na ciah ding hi
chorus:
Topa aw, kote hong thumna,
Hong ngai in, an nei Topa
An la ding mi hong kuan sak in,
An lak hun a kheng ma in

zoTitle: Seem Un, Khua Hong Mial Ding Hi
engTitle: Work, for the Night is Coming
verse1:
Seem un, khua hong mial ding hi, Zingsang tungin seem un
Zing dai nom lai in seem un, Khua tung lai seem un
Vaiham saan' ciang zong seem un, Ni sa sung zong seem un
Mihing nasep kizawh hun, Zan hong tung ding hi
verse2:
Seem un, khua hong mial ding hi, Sun ni taan' lai seem un
Khua vaak laiteng hahkat un, Om ding hi, khawl hun
A hun bei khong sak kei un, Na manpha khat seem un
Mihing nasep nawn loh hun, Zan hong tung ding hi
verse3:
Seem un, khua hong mial ding hi, Ni kai ciang zong seem un
Ni vaang kimuh lai seem un, Ni’n hong kheng ding tu’n
Hong taang kik nawn loh ding hun, Ni tum siang dong seem un
Khuamial kuan in zong seem un, Tawp hong hun ding hi

zoTitle: Thu Maan Ngam, Hang Ngam in
engTitle: Dare To Be Brave, Dare To Be True
verse1:
Lau lo, hang in, thu maan ngam in
Thu maan han ciam nang tawh Topa om hi
Hang tak do in, Na tha khauh sak in
Khazih'n lam hong lak maanlo bek kihta’n
verse2:
Lau lo, hang in, thu maan ngam in
Pasian na Pa hi, na tung hong cing hi
Na thuakna thei in, Na lungsim thei
Hong hon ding sam in, Don lo cih om kei
verse3:
Lau lo, hang in thu maan ngam in
Na zawh nading, Pasian in tha hong guan
Mi dangte huh in, Gi tawntung in
Hong lang pan'pha pen, Na lawm suak sak in
chorus:
Do in, gal kap siam, Do in hang tak
Khazih’n hong makaih, hong gum ding hi

verse1:
Thukham bang zui dingin ah
Guih theih kham thei zu
Phat un a taang Danzila
Amah’n phatna a mu
verse2:
Danzila bang hilo a
A lau-a om mi
Zum-a a lau mi in ah
Kisiatna sung tung hi
verse3:
Huaiham, hehna, gitlohna
Tampi om hangin
Danzila zuite in ah
Do ciangin a mang ding
verse4:
Dawi mang gilo kihta ke’n
En in, Danzila
Khai in lung damna dial pei
Belh ciang na zo ding ta
chorus:
Khat guak om hangin ah Danzila bangin
Guih theihte tan na’ngin ah, lau lo in gen in

engTitle: Yield Not to Temptation (duest S le A)
verse1:
Mawhna' zol zui kei in, Na zuih leh khial ding
Khatvei zo phot lecin, A zom zawh nop ding
Pasal! nakpi’n do in, lung gulhna mialpi
Zeisu en gige in, Hong zawhpih ding hi
verse2:
Kholhpih gilo peel in, Kam hoih lo zang ke’n
Pasian' min zahtak in, A mawkna’n zang ke’n
Thu khualin citak in, thumaan in migi
Zeisu en gige in, hong zawhpih ding hi
verse3:
A zote Pasian in, kham lukhu pia ding
I puk kha zel hangin, Upna tawh zo ding
Eite hong Honpa in, Tha hong guan' ding hi
Zeisu en gige in, Hong zawhpih ding hi
chorus:
Hong huh nading thungen in, Tha hong pia hong keem ding hi
Hong huh nuam hi Topa in, A hong zawhpih ding hi

verse1:
Launa nam kim omna mual kuamthuk sung a hi zong
Launa om lo ni taang khuvaak sung mah a hi zong
Khua sia ta leh, khua pha ta leh ke’n khat thei ing
Zeisu’n hong zui peuh leh koima peuh pai ning
verse2:
Nuntak lungdamna thupha ka puak pelmawh ding hi
Sehnel ni so kan tan in, mawhna dim buaina ah
Keima mel bang pua in tua mun ka pha ding hi
Zeisu’n hong zui peuh leh koima peuh pai ning
verse3:
Mi dangte in a mau van gik pua in a om lai
Ke’n ka singlamteh pua in, inn ah ka om ding a
Ama aading teci pang in upna lak ning
Kei tawh hong om peuh leh koima peuh om ning
chorus:
Zeisu tawh ton peuh leng pai ning, (pai ning)
Koima peuh kei aa’n vantung hi,
Koi ah om ta leng, Hong om peuh leh,
A singlamteh ka pua ding
 Kei (hamphat) hamphatna hi (na hi),
Zeisu'n hong zui peuh leh, Pai ning koi ma peuh!

verse1:
Aw lawmte aw, dial pei en un, Vantung-a a khai
Hong huh ding Mangpa hong kuan ding,
I zawhna a nai
verse2:
En un gal tampi hong pai a, Dawi mang hong masa
Thahatte a kim si zo a
Han’na bei dek ta
verse3:
A vaang lian dial pei kimu hi, Peengkul aw kiza
Hong uk Mangpa a min pha tawh,
Galte ka zo ta
verse4:
Gal kapna sawt vei haksa a, Huhna hong nai hi
Hong uk Mangpa hong pai laitak,
Lungdam khin un, ci
chorus:
Gal do in tu’n ka hong pai ding, Zeisu dial hong lak
A thupha tawh om tawntung ning, Dial na lak kik sak

verse1:
Gal van a tawi tangvalte i hih ciangin
Kumpipa thupiak aw i ngai ding hi
"Kuan un" cih na thu i zak ciangin ah
Galkap maangpa kiang pan gal I do ding hi
verse2:
Gal van a tawi tangvalte i hih ciangin
Galkapna sungah galkap van cing ni
Gal kapna kiko aw i zak ciangin
"Hih lai ah kei ka om hi," ci in gen ni
verse3:
Gal van a tawi tangvalte i hih ciangin
Vaanglian sung Kumpi lukhu ngah ding hi
Gal kapna pha takpi’n gal i do ciang
Nuamna thaman sang kei hong saang sak ding hi
chorus:
Kuan, ci kiko na aw na ngai ta un
En un, a zawngkhal mite lungkia hi
Gal van a tawi tangval i hih ciangin
Galkap maangpa in ei hong muang ding hi
Gal van a tawi tangval i hih ciangin
Galkap maangpa in ei hong muang ding hi

zoTitle: Ding Un, Ding Un, Zeisu' Mi
engTitle: Stand up, Stand Up For Jesus (Tune: Webb)
verse1:
Ding un, ding un, Zeisu’ mi, Singlamteh galkapte
A kumpi dial saang khan un, Lelhna thuaksak lo e!
Gal khat khit khat a ban-in, Amah’n hong zawh pih ding
Gal khempeuh zawh khit ciangin, Khazih Topa'n maang ding
verse2:
Ding un, ding un, Zeisu’ mi, Mang un, peengkul sawlna
Galpi phualah va kuan un, Tuni Topa' ni pha
Pasal, kisa teng kuan un, Galte a tam hangin
Tha le tha kisi sak un, Hang seem un lau ciangin
verse3:
Ding un, ding un, Zeisu’ mi, Ama tha bek suang un
Mihing tha’n hong lel sak ding, No-mau tha muang kei un
Pasian thu gal van bangin Silh in, vil in, thungen
Gal le sep ding om ciangin a baih sa’n om khial ke’n
verse4:
Ding un, ding un, Zeisu’ mi, gal bei hak nawn lo ding
Tu’n gal kap nading zingciang, Gal zawhna la ging ding
A zote khempeuh in ah, nun’tak lukhu ngah ding
Vaanglian Kumpipa kiangah, A tawntung maang khawm ding

verse1:
Min than’na tawh Topa hong pai, ka mit in mu khin zo
Amah in hehna leenggah kikoihna lo, tuancil khin zo
Kihtakhuai, a zaptel khuaphelep
A' namsau khah khin zo, I Pasian’n mai nawt hi
verse2:
Giahphual za khat kiim-a mei taang ah, Amah mu khin ing
Nitak dai nom lakah biakna tau lam uh
Ama aading Ama thukhenna maante,
Mei taang kiaukiau ah sim thei ing, I Pasian’n mai nawt hi
verse3:
Nung kik dinga, sam ngeilo ding peengkul Amah’n mut hi
A thukhenna tokhom mai ah mihingte' lungsim sit hi
Ka kha aw, Amah dawng meng in! nuam in, ka khe! Nuamhuai hi, I Pasian’n mai nawt hi
verse4:
Tuipi gal khat, unok paak hoih, lakah Khazih suak khin hi
Nang le kei hong kikheel sak A’ang sung minthan‘na tawi hi
Mite siangsak ding hong sih bangin, mi’ suahtak na’ng si ni. I Pasian’n mai nawt hi
chorus:
Min thang, min thang, Haleluiah!
Min thang, min thang, Haleluiah!
Min thang, min thang, Haleluiah!
I Pasian mai nawt hi

verse1:
Gal dona awng un, gal nai zo, en un!
Topa' dial khai un Sang takin
Gal dal silh in la, Kip tak ding in la
Lai Siangtho' hilhna, na siksan in
verse2:
Eima lammah in zo ding thei khol in
Galte ngap thawhin i kuan hi
I lum le i dial Ni-ah te zialzial
Thumaan in thukhial lel ngeilo hi
verse3:
Mi khempeuh' Pasian, hehpihna hong pia’n
Ko a neu a lian hong huh in
Gal zawh ciangin ah Nangma mai tangah
Hong suak nung zawhna lukhu khu in
chorus:
Khai leh! ding un, dial kiim hong kikhawm un
Lim tak, kiging! na kihilh sawn un
Kuan un, mai nawt, Hawsiana kiko un
Khazih in makaih hi galkap hon

zoTitle: I Lungnuam Hi Zeisu Muang Leng
engTitle: Tis so Sweet to Trust in Jesus
crossrefs: Jer. 17:7;Pau. 16:20, Louisa M.R. Stead 1850-1917, S.H. 221, William J. Kirkpatrick, 1838-1921
verse1:
I lungnuam hi, Zeisu muang leeng
Ama hong gen bang um leeng
Ama hong kamciamna muang leeng
Topa’ hong cihna thei leeng
verse2:
I lungnuam hi, Zeisu muang leeng
Hong sawpna A si muang leeng
Hong dam, hong siangsak thei A si
Sungah upna tawh bual leeng
verse3:
I lungnuam hi, Zeisu muang leeng
Mawhna pumpi nusia leeng
Nuntak, lungnop, tawldam, nuamna
Zeisu’ khut tung pan sang leng
verse4:
Zeisu kong muang theih ka nuam hi
A manpha lawmpa na hi!
Hong Honpa aw, a tawp dongin
Nong ompih ding ka thei hi
chorus:
Zeisu, Zeisu, ke’n ka muang hi
A muanhuai-na thei zo hi
Zeisu, Zeisu, manpha Zeisu!
Amah muang semsem nuam ing

engTitle: Who Is On the Lord's Side? (Tune: Armageddon)
verse1:
Topa lam kua pang ding? A na kua’n seem ding?
Kua in Amah huh ding? Mi dang kua’n puak ding?
Kua’n leitung na nusia? Kua’n gal do ding?
Topa lam kua pang ding? Kua kithawi pai ding?
A hehpih na’n hong sam, Hehpih in hong sam
Topa lam ah i pang, Gumpa ko Nang aa.
verse2:
Minthan’ nopna hilo, Lukhu deih hilo
Na gal kap ding tum in, Gal hang laam to ding
Na nuntakna pia a, Nong sihna hang hi
Ama lam a pangte, Zeisu’n min ciamteh
Itna khau tawh hong khih, Hehpih in hong sam
Topa lam i pang hi, Gumpa ko Nang aa.
verse3:
Zeisu ko nong lei zo, Sum tawh lei hilo
Nangma sisan nong bua, Lukhu aading in
Na hehpihna dim hi, nang kiang hong pai peuh
Kote Nong lawp sak a, Ko Nong suakta sak
A lian Gupkhiatna tawh, Hehpih in hong gum
Topa lam ah i pang, Gumpa ko Nang aa.

zoTitle: Kei Ka Singlamteh Zeisu'n Pua Khin
engTitle: Jesus, I My Cross Have Taken (Tune: Ellesdie)
verse1:
Zeisu’n  puak sak ka singlamteh, Van gik khia’n Amah ka zui
Cihmawhna, gentheina ka thuak, Tu pan Nang aa ka hi ta
Lametna teng khempeuh siat hang, Zon'teng, lamet teng mu khin
Hauhna khempeuh kicing khin pah, Pasian le van kei aa hi ta!
verse2:
Leitung mudah, nawlkhin thuak in, Gumpa nangawn a deih lo
Mihing lungsim in hong kheem hang, Na hi kei, maan lo mi bang
Kei tung' Nong nuihmai ciangin ah, itna, pilna, thahat Pa,
Lawmte galten hong pelh uh hang, ko Nong lak hi vaang taang Na mai
verse3:
Simmawh bawl siat ka thuak ciangin, Nang ang hong tun' tuate hi
Nuntak haksa’n hong netcip hang, Van pan tawldamna Nong puak
Na itna kei kiang om ciangin, dahna om hang na sa lo
Nang kihel lohna mun peuh ah, lungnop hehnepna omlo hi
verse4:
Hehpihna tawh minthan’na ah, Upna lum tawi thu ngen ding
Tawntung vantung nuntakna sung, Pasian khut in hong kha ding
Leitung nasepna hun bei in, Vantung khual zinna bei ciang
Lametna hong kikheel dinga, Upna’n mu thu ngen in phat ding

zoTitle: Mi Nam Kimte’ Pa Le Topa
engTitle: Dear Lord and Father of Mankind (Tune: Elton)
verse1:
Minam kimte Pa le Topa, Ka hai tuntun uh tawh
Lungsim ngei hong guan'pha in la
Hong guan' in siangtho gamtatna
Zahtakna a thuk zaw
verse2:
Syria tui gei-a mite in, Nangma sapna thupha
A zak uh ciang mang pah bangin
Ko zong kam khat beek nial lo in
Hong zui pah nung, Nangmah.
verse3:
Kote’ thuakna bei hun mateng, Daitui hong taak lai-in
La khia’n lung ung noplohna teng,
Nangma lung nopna a pha teng
Ko tung kilang sak in
verse4:
Kote’ lung sung deihna a sa, Hong mut khing sak ta in
Pumpi’ deihnate nial zo a
Huihpi, meikuang, zinling sungah
Nang’ aw hong za sak in

engTitle: More Love to Thee, O Christ
verse1:
Hong it zaw ning Topa, Hong it zaw ning
Khuk din’ a kong thumna, Nang hong ngai ding
Hih bang hi kong thumna, Khazih hong it zaw ning
Hong it zaw ning, Hong it zaw ning
verse2:
Ni dang leitung nopna, Ka lunggulh pen
Tu in kong deih Nangmah, a hoihpha pen
Tu in kong deih Nangmah, Khazih hong it zaw ning
Hong it zaw ning, Hong it zaw ning
verse3:
Dahna natna thuak hang, Phanmawh sa lo
Nangma sawltakte bang la ka sa zo
Ka sa khawm amau bang, Khazih hong it zaw ning
Hong it zaw ning, Hong it zaw ning
verse4:
Ka sih laitakin ah, Nang kong phat ding
Ka hu tawpna in ah, Ka vaikhak ding
Ka ngen lailai hih mah, Khazih hong it zaw ning
Hong it zaw ning, Hong it zaw ning

verse1:
Sian'tho na'ng hun zang in, Thu ngen zelzel in
Ama sungah om in, A Thu'n kivaak in
Pasian Tate pawl in, A nangte huh in
Na khat na hih ciangin, Dong khial ngei kei in
verse2:
Sian'tho na'ng hun zang in, Mi a kin zongin
Zeisu bek tawh om in, Hun tampi zangin
Amah na sut na'ngin, Etteh tawntung in
Ama lim lang sak in
Nang tatna panin
verse3:
Sian'tho na'ng hun zang in, Hong pina zui in
A maiah tai kei in, Bang a ci zongin
Na nuam na dah zongin, Topa mah zui in
Zeisu en tawntung in, Ama thu muangin
verse4:
Sian'tho na'ng hun zang in, Lung hi dide in
Ngaihsut a nam kimin, Amah uk sak in
Kha Siangtho tua bangin kikai sak lecin
Vantung na seem dingin, Siam ding sawt loin

engTitle: Prayer is the Soul's Sincere Desire (Tune: Lambesh)
verse1:
Thungetna in lungsim sunga, Lunggulh takin a hi
Mei bang hong lum sak awm sunga,
Deihna lian pen a hi
verse2:
Khuisatna, khitui luan'na zong, Thungetna mah a hi
Pasian lamet tohna bek zong,
Thungetna mah a hi
verse3:
Mawhnei mi khat lungsim tak tawh, Kisikin phun bek leh
Vantung mite'n nuam la kiko,
"En vaw, thu ngen ta ven"
verse4:
Thu zuita ding thungetna in, Hin'na hu bang a hi
Thungetna tawh sih kong panin,
Vantung khua ah lut hi
verse5:
Nangmah, hin'na, thuman lampi, Pa kiang tun nading in
Nangma totsa thunget lampi, Kote zong hong hilh in

zoTitle: Nang Tawh Nai Zaw Nuam Ing
engTitle: Nearer, My God, To Thee (Tune: Bethany)
verse1:
Nang tawh nai zaw nuam ing, Ka Pasian aw
Singlamteh thuak ta leng, Hong dom to aw
Thuak hang ka sasa ding, Nang tawh nai zaw nuam ing
Nang tawh nai zaw nuam ing, Ka Pasian aw
verse2:
Zakoh bang ka vak a, Ni tum ta hang
Khuamial-a suangtum bek, Ka lukham hang
Ka mang hong nai nuam ing, Nang tawh nai zaw nuam ing
Nang tawh nai zaw nuam ing, Ka Pasian aw
verse3:
Ka mai ah hong lak in, Vantung lampi
Nong ngah sak khempeuhte, Hehpihna hi
Vantung mi hong sam ding, Nang tawh nai zaw nuam ing
Nang tawh nai zaw nuam ing, Ka Pasian aw
verse4:
Nangma min phatna tawh, Ka khanglo ding
Ka dahna teng Pasian phat na'n nei ning
Tua bangin dahna hang, Nang tawh kinai zaw na'ng
Nang tawh kinai zaw na'ng, Ka Pasian aw

verse1:
Hong paisan ke'n, migi Topa, Kong thum hong ngai in
Midangte kiang na baan' bangmah,
Kei hong kheng kei in
verse2:
Hehpihna Na tokhom mai ah, Kisik kong khukdin
Nang hong huhin ka up lahna, Noptuam hong pia in
verse3:
Nangma phatna bek ka suang hi, Na mai muh nading
Na thupha tawh Nong phel ding hi, Lung zan damna ding
verse4:
Ka nuamna teng bulpi Nangmah, Hin'na sang pha zaw
Leitung vantung om lo kuamah, Nang sanga pha zaw
chorus:
Topa, Topa, Kong thum hong ngai in
Midangte kiang na baan bangmah, Kei hong kheng kei in

verse1:
Hong gum Topa thupha piak na'ng, Guah zu ding thu kiza hi
Lei keute a nel kik nading, Kei zong guah hong kha sak in
verse2:
Pa Pasian aw, hong taisan ke'n, Keimah ka lung tom hangin
Taisan ding ka kilawm zongin, Keimah hong lung ngai lai in
verse3:
Hong gum Topa hong taisan ke'n, Nangma kiang kong beel nuam hi
Na thupha ka ngah nuam lua hi, Na deih bang hong piang ta hen
verse4:
Kha Siangtho aw, hong taisan ke'n, Mittaw khua na mu sak in
Zeisu thupha bel hong lak in, Keima tungah hong taang in
chorus:
Keimah zong, keimah zong
Kei zong guah hong kha sak in

zoTitle: A Hoih Huan Sung Thu Ngetna
verse1:
Zeisu hong ngakna mun huan sung khat om
Tua in a lamdang mun hoih khat hi
A vaang liatna khua vaakpi a taang hi
A hoih huan sung thungetna mun ah
verse2:
Zeisu hong ngakna mun huan sung khat om
Vangik pua kawm in Amah ka zuan
A kam sung pan hehnepna aw ka za
A hoih huan sung thungetna mun ah
verse3:
Zeisu hong ngakna mun huan sung khat om
Amah tawh kimu dingin hong sam
Topa tawh kimu kiho khawm dingin
A hoih huan sung thungetna mun ah
chorus:
Aw, a hoih huan sung, Huan sung thu ngetna a hi
Aw, a hoih huan sung thu ngetna hi
Hong Gumpa'n hong ngak a, Kongkhakpi hong hon' sak
A hoih huan sung thu ngetna mun ah

zoTitle: I Mawhna Leh I Dahna Teng
engTitle: What a Friend We Have in Jesus
verse1:
I mawhna leh i dahna teng, A pua ding Zeisu i Lawm
Pasian kiangah i sapna teng, Thuum theih na'ng thupha a om
Lung nopna tampi i taan a, Thuak loh ding pi i thuak hi
Na kheempeuhte Pasian kiangah, Thuumin i koh loh hang hi
verse2:
Ze-et, bawl siat a hi zong in, Lung khamna khat peuh om maw
Cikmah ciang lungkia ngeilo in, Topa kiangah ko in aw
Dah teng thuakpih nuam Zeisu bang, Lawm maan dang mu zo ding maw
Zeisu'n thei khin i sap bangbang, Ama kiangah ko in aw
verse3:
Lung khamna van gik bang lel in, Zawngkhalin na tha neem maw
Manpha Honpa i belh hi in, Ama kiang thu ngen in aw
Mi'n hong simmawh hong huat ciangin, Zeisu kiang i pai ding hi
A' ang sung hong pom hong dal in, Lung nopna hong pia ding hi

zoTitle: Topa Aw, Kei Hong Mangngilh Kei In
verse1:
Kei hong Honpa A si luangin, Ka Kumpi hong si maw?
Tangtel bang bek keimah aading, A' lutang hong zang maw
verse2:
Keima git lohnate hangin, Singlamteh tung tau maw
Lamdang hehpihna le itna, Bang tawh teh thei ding maw
verse3:
Ama pian' sak mi mawhna hang, A piang sak Pa Khazih
Hong sih laitak, khuamial sungah Ni a buk mah ding hi
verse4:
Kei zong singlamteh ka muh ciang, Zum in ka kiseel diam
Lung damna tawh lung nehno in, Ka khi ka luang sak diam
chorus:
Nang tung kong thumaan zawh na'ng in, Topa kei hong huh in
Kumpi tokhom Na luah ciangin, Kei hong mangngilh kei in

verse1:
Nang kong deih tawntung hi, Migi ka To.
Lung nopna hong pia thai, A dang omlo
verse2:
Nang kong deih tawntung hi, Nai tak kei kiang.
Ze-et na'n hong zo lo, Nang Nong nai ciang
verse3:
Nang kong deih tawntung hi, Nuam leng, dah leng.
Nuntak na'n man nei kei, Nang hong taan leng
verse4:
Nang kong deih tawntung hi, Hong thuhilh in.
Nong khapsa a phate, Hong ngah sak in
verse5:
Nang kong deih tawntung hi, Siang pen Pa aw.
Nang aa tak hong hi ning, Tapa pha aw
chorus:
Kong deih hi, Nang kong deih hi,
Nang kong deih tawntung hi.
Thupha hong pia'n, Topa aw,
Nang kong zuan hi.

verse1:
Hin'na tawntung Topa Pasian,
Lawmte sang ka it zaw hi.
Vantung lam kazon' laitak ah,
Topa kiang ka tawn nuam hi.
(Nang kiangah)x4
Vantung lam ka zon' laitak ah,
Nang kiangah ka tawn nuam hi.
verse2:
Leitung ah hauhna le nuamna,
Minthang thu ka ngen kei hi.
Nangma kiang ka om laitak ah,
Lung damin ka seem ding hi.
(Nang kiangah)x4
Nangma kiang ka om laitak ah,
Lung damin ka seem ding hi.
verse3:
Mualkuam khua mialna sung hi hang,
Tuipi galah hong kha in.
Hin' tawntung na kongpi sungah,
Nangmah tawh hong lut sak in.
(Nang kiangah)x4
Hin' tawntung na kongpi sungah,
Topa kiang ka lut ding hi.

zoTitle: Na Deihna Bang Hi Ta Hen
verse1:
Ka Topa aw, Nangma kiangah,
Lampi haksa pai khawm lai ah
Hong ci sak thei in,
"Na deihna bang hi ta hen."
verse2:
Dahna ka thuak, lawmte si ta,
Hih hang Na thu ngaihsun lai ah
Hih bang gen ding hi'ng,
"Na deihna bang hi ta hen."
verse3:
Na Kha Siangtho in keima hong kha,
Hong kip sak ding hong pai sak in
Hih thu gen lai hi'ng,
"Na deihna bang hi ta hen."
chorus:
Nangma deihna, Bang hi ta hen.
Hong ci sak thei in,
"Na deihna bang hi ta hen."

engTitle: Saviour, More Than Life to Me
verse1:
Topa bek hong phel thei hi,
Keimah in ah Na kiang ka beel hi
Na sipha tawh hong sawp in,
Na kiangah hong om sak tawntung in
verse2:
A kisia thei leitung ah,
Dam takin keimah lam hong hilh ta
Topa bek i up ciangin,
Cikmah hunin lam khial nawn lo ding
verse3:
Sih ding hun hong tun' mateng,
Vantung innpi nuam sung tun' mateng
Nang kong up na'ng khang sak in,
Topa tawh kikhen nawn lo dingin
chorus:
Ni simin, nai simin
Sipha than'na thei sak in
Hehpih a, Nong itna tawh
Khau bangin ah keimah hong hen in

zoTitle: Nang Ading Thu Ka Ngen Hi
verse1:
Hong gum Topa in kei aading thu ngen hi.
Topa it huai hih leitung ah zui tawm hi.
Tu in Topa in, nuamtak kei hong cing lai hi.
Amah in nang gumpa piang ta hen, ka ci.
verse2:
Nuam tawntung ding i lawpna maan takpi hi.
Hehpihna hong pia Topa Pasian om hi.
Topa mai muh ding hong sap hong sawtlo ding hi.
Nangmah hong hilh hen keimah tawh pai khawm ni
verse3:
Gunpi bang nopsakna kei aading om zo.
Hih nopsakna leitung mite'n thei lo hi.
Hong gum Topa in hong uk hong pia zo bek hi.
Nang zong hong pia hiam keimah'n ka thei nuam hi
verse4:
Topa Zeisu in hong zong hong muh ciangin,
It huai Topa in nang hong phel thu gen in.
Topa min mi lakah a than' na'ng thu ngen in
Nang taang nget kingah zo nang zong ngah ding hi
chorus:
Nang aading thu ka ngen,
Nang aading thu ka ngen.
Nang aading thu ka ngen,
Nang aading thu ka ngen.

crossrefs: Late 55:17, C.W. 337, Rev. William W. Walford 1772-1850, William Batchelder Bradbury (1816-1868)
verse1:
Thunget hun nuam, thunget hun nuam,
Lung khamna pan hong samkhia a
Ka deih ka sapna a tuamtuam,
Ka gen theih hun ka Pa mai-ah
Dahna hong tun ciang thungen leng,
Ka lungsim hong nuamtuam sak a
Mawhna'n hong zol ciang thungen leng,
Dawimangpa' thang pan ka suakta.
verse2:
Thunget hun nuam, thunget hun nuam,
Va lenpih in keima thumna
Keima kha thupha a pia nuam,
Thuman a dik Pasian kiangah
Keima mai ah um in, muangin,
Hong pai in, hong cih khit nung sang
Thunget hun nuam hong tun sim in,
Lung khamna teng Amah suan tang.
verse3:
Thunget hun nuam, thunget hun nuam,
Kei lungsim hong hehnem lai in
Pasian hong ciam Kanan gam nuam,
Luah ding ka lentoh mateng in
Hih ka pumpi puanbang suah a,
Sang dingin tul ngeilo noptuam
Ka lentoh ciang kha ning mangpha,
Thunget hun nuam, thunget hun nuam.

engTitle: Tis the Blessed Hour of Prayer
verse1:
Thungetna hun pha hi a, lungsim i niam khiat ciang
I lawm leh Honpa Zeisu kiang i kikhop ciang
Ama hutna ngah ding muan'na tawh zuan leng Amah
Tua laiah va kihel leeng, damna zatui hi pah
verse2:
Thungetna hun pha hi a, ze-et na a thuakte
Honpa kiangah a dahna uh hong puak uh teh
Amah'n hong khasiat in, hong paih sak i hak satna
Tua laiah va kihel leeng, damna zatui hi pah
verse3:
Thungetna hun pha hi a, Honpa a hong pai ciang
A mite ngai dingin ah Amah hong om ciang
I hak satna teng kheempeuh i va puak ciang Amah
Tua laiah va kihel leeng, damna zatui hi pah
verse4:
Thungetna hunpha sungah, A thupha i ngette
Peel loin ngah ding cih kip takin i up leh
Nopna kidim sungah bei pah ding i hak satna
Tua laiah va kihel leeng, damna zatui hi pah
chorus:
Thungetna hun nuam, Hun nuam thu ngetna
Tua laiah va kihel leeng, damna zatui hi pah

verse1:
Lunggim mi aw, inn nuam om hi
Lung khamna, gimnate galah
Kikheel ngei nawn lohna innpi
Kua tung nuam lo ding tua lai ah
verse2:
Leitungah na thuak ding a hi
Van gik lel-a na kun hangin
En in, na tun' nading innpi!
Ngak in, lung neemin ah ngak in
verse3:
Na lampi ah ling a om leh
A' lu tunga khu Pa phawk in
Lung gimna, dahna na tuah leh
Nang sang siang zaw Pa'n zong thuak khin
verse4:
Sem in, na thuakna, na thumna
Hong zak loh khat beek om lo hi
Na ngah nading hi tawldamna
Lung neem takin na ngak ding hi
chorus:
Ngak in, thuakin thum loin ngak in
Ngak in, thuakin thum loin ngak in
Ngak in, ngak in, Thum loin ah ngak in

verse1:
Hong gum Topa, ngai in, Nang kiang kong nai hi
Ka leiba loh dingin, Nangmah na si hi
Na minpha tawh mawh phelna,
Nang kong up ciang ka ngah hi
Topa hong beel dingin, Na kiang kong nai hi
verse2:
Hong gum Topa ngai in, Hehpihna kong ngen
Thupha tawh hong gum in, Launa beisak in
Na thu ciamna ka um hi,
Na thupha bel ka muang hi
Hong gum Topa Pasian, Na kiang thu kong ngen
verse3:
Topa aw, hong it in, Keimah hong la in
Keimah bek leitung ah, Hong pai sak kei in
Keima lam hong taang sak in,
Na minthang ka kimkot ah
Nang aading taang sak in, Ka belh suangpi aw
verse4:
Topa aw, hong liah in, Na kiang hong koih in
Na nasep zawh mateng, Lampi hong hilh in
Tua ciangin lung damna la,
Ka sa ding hi, vantungah
Topa tawh tua munah, Om nuam tawntung ing

verse1:
Gup khiatna ngah ding Pasian in thu hong ciam zo
Ama Tapa Zeisu min a um kheempeuhte
verse2:
Tua lampi gamdai in a lauhuai hangin ah
Topa Zeisu in kei hong paipih zo ding hi
verse3:
Ka it ka ngaih tampi vantung gam sung tung zo
Lungmuang tak tua gamah hih lapi sa uh hi
verse4:
Naupang note Ama kiangah dinguh ka mu
Gup khiatna la sa uh, Amah na nui hiuhiau
verse5:
Kikhopna sung kumpite kamsangte ka mu
Kham kongzing lampite zui in la sa uh hi
verse6:
Nang leh kei aading in tua laiah la om hi
A tawntung in tua lai i phat tawntung ding hi
chorus:
Haleluiah khin zo, Tapa min ka um zo
Ama sisan in kei hong gum khia khin zo ta
Haleluiah khin zo, Tapa min ka um zo
Ama sisan in kei hong gum khia khin zo ta

verse1:
Sum haupa a inn pha bel kongkhak kiangah
Topa Pasian ta khat a tu hi
Leitung ah gimna, tawlna kheempeuh a ngah
A sih khit ciang a nuam bel ngah hi
verse2:
Gim in bei in si leeng, bang i piang ding maw
Eimah in sin sungah ngaihsun hi
Leitung ah nuntakna vangik pua bang hi
Dahna khitui luan'na te om hi
verse3:
Zeisu nungzuite in sum a tawm hangin
Vantung khua-ah om sum lamdang hi
Ze-et bawl siatna teng i paisan ding hi
Nung ciang kikhel ding lung damna hi
verse4:
Topa Pasian omna mailam pai ta hen
Pilna a hun tawh Topa hilh in
Na sepna a tawm hang za ngahna a lian
Singlamteh pua kham lukhu khu in
chorus:
A nopna sungah vantung mite'n paipih
Van kim lai ah la sa aw dim hi
Vantung inn nuam sungah Topa in la hi
A it-te tawh nopna a ngah hi

verse1:
Keimah ka muanna a bulpi,
Zeisu si leh siangthona hi
A dang thu teng ka um ngam kei
Zeisu a min bek ka um thei
verse2:
Khuamial in a mai liah ciangin,
A hong hehpihna ka muang ding
Huihpi nakpi a nun' ciangah
Mun liahna  sungah sik kip khia
verse3:
A thu ciamna te Ama si,
Tuipi kan lai ka muang ding hi
Ka kiimkot teng a siat ciangah
Ka muan'na in Zeisu Topa
verse4:
Peengkul aw tawh A pai ciangin,
Amah mai-ah ka ding nuam hi
A hong siangtho sak khit ciangin
Mawh neilo in ka om ding hi
chorus:
Keima din'na Zeisu Suangpi,
Omna dang teng sehnel bang hi
Omna dang teng sehnel bang hi

verse1:
Topa thu ciamna pha muang takin om ning
A tawntung in hong gum Topa vaang um ning
A minthang hi ci in-ah ka kiko hi
A thu ciamna pha ka muang ding hi
verse2:
A sia thei lo Topa thu ciamna ka muang
Up khialh man-a launa huih bang hong nun' hang
Nuntak na'ng-a a thupha bel tawh zawh na'ng
A thu ciamna pha ka muang ding hi
verse3:
Tu in a thu ciamna muangin ka om hi
A sipha tawh hong sawp leh ka siang ding hi
Mawhna sung pan suahtak ding thu ka ngah hi
A thu ciamna pha ka muang ding hi
verse4:
Topa Zeisu na thu ciamna ka muang hi
A thupha tawh khau bangin hong hen ding hi
Kha Siangtho tawh dawi mangpa ka zo ding hi
A thu ciamna pha ka muang ding hi
chorus:
Muang in, om ning
Hong gum Topa Pasian thu ciamna pha muang ning
Muang in, om ning
Hong gum Topa Pasian thuciam muang ning

zoTitle: Zeisu Bek'n Nuamna Hong Pia Thei
verse1:
Aw Topa Zeisu kei lungsim
Na thu ka um man a
Sawtpi ka zong a nopna in
Lung damna ka ngah ta
verse2:
Lung damna ka zon' laitak in
Topa ka mangngilh hi
Hong gum Topa ka nial ciangin
Hong it a hong zol hi
verse3:
Leitung aa nopnate deih in
Lung kim ngah dingin ah
Hahkat in-a ka zon' hangin
Lung kiatna teng ka ngah
verse4:
Zeisu hong it thupha in-ah
Keimah ka ngah ma in
Si thei nopna lungsim neih hang
Topa ka ngaihsun ke'n
chorus:
Tuni Zeisu sim loh in-ah,
Deihna dang om lo pi
Itna, hinna, tawntung nopna,
Topa kiang ka ngah hi

verse1:
Topa thu kiciamna thei a
Up khialna ka paai ding hi
Lung kiatna thuak loh na'ngin ah
A thupha ka um ding hi
verse2:
Kimawh sakna Zeisu in ah
A sipha tawh hong sawp hi
Keimah hong siangtho sak zo ta
Innpi ah hong kha ding hi
verse3:
Topa Zeisu hong hehpih man
Kihtak launa om lo hi
Ka lampi ah khua a mial hang
Khuavak hong taang sak ding hi
verse4:
Ka nuamna teng Zeisu ka pia
Amah bek ke'n ka deih hi
Amah in leitung teng uk a
Deihna teng A kiang om hi
verse5:
Ka vekpi in Zeisu ka pia
Ka lungsim ka pum kheempeuh
Ka lametna a om kheempeuh
Tawntung Ama kiang om hi
chorus:
A kicing hi, a thupha pi
Keimah in ah ka um hi
A kicing hi, a thupha pi
Keimah in ah ka um hi

verse1:
Um un, a umte'n um un
Gal dona a sawt hang
Nangma zawh theih nading in
Nang lam Topa pang hi
verse2:
Um un, gal a tam hangin
A lauhuai lampi ah
Ze-etna a tam hangin
Lam hong hilh ding, Topa
verse3:
Topa'n hong gum zo ding hi
I zawl Pa pha bel hi
Um un, a umte'n zo ding
I zawl Pa pha bel hi
chorus:
(Um un, um un)x2
Khuamial a lauhuai hang
(Um un, Um un)x2
Khua hong vak dek tak hi

engTitle: The Way of the Cross Leads Home
verse1:
Singlamteh lam tawn in ka ciah kul ding hi
Tua lo lam dang om lopi
Tua khuavaak kongpi tung thei ngei kei ning
Singlamteh lam ka khialh khak leh
verse2:
Singlamteh phung ka van teng tolhkhia khin hi
Topa mai ka muh ciangin
Lungtaii tak tua lam tawn ding kong kipan
Ka lung sung phatna tawh kidim
verse3:
Si kithehna lam tawn ka ciah suak ding hi
Topa totsa lampi mah
A dawn dongin kei ka kahtoh theih leh, Pasian inn sung ka kha teeng ding
chorus:
(Singlamteh'n inn lam hong hilh)x2
Mailam ka pai ciangin nuam semsem ding
Singlamteh in inn lam hong hilh

engTitle: There's a Wideness in God's Mercy (Tune: Wellesley)
verse1:
Pasian hehpihna zai lua hi
Tuipi lian bangin zai hi
A thu khenna ah thumaan hi
Suah takna sang zai zaw hi
verse2:
Mi mawhte dawnin vai tut hi
Hehpihna thu Honpa kiang
Tam sem hi, miphate aading
A si sung damna om hi
verse3:
Bang hang hiam cih leh, teh zawh loh
Pasian hong itna hang hi
Nuntak tawntung-na lung tangin
A migitna lamdang hi
verse4:
Ei itna, a neem ngi-ngei leh
Ama thu bang zui ding a
Topa' citna ciamna sungah
I nuntakna taang ding hi

zoTitle: Topa Zeisu Nang Hong Muang Ding
engTitle: I Am Trusting Thee, Lord Jesus
verse1:
Topa Zeisu Nang hong muang ing
Nang bek hong muang ing!
Gupna ngah ding Nang hong muang ing
Khawnkhong, cing
verse2:
Mawh maina ding Nang hong muang ing
Na khe mai kong kun
Na hehpihna leh na thupha
Muang ing, tu'n
verse3:
Tha hatna ding Nang hong muang ing
Nang tha puk ngeilo
Nangma'n kei nong piak ding thu te'n
Zo den zo
verse4:
Topa Zeisu Nang hong muang ing!
Hong puk sak ngei ke'n
Vekpi aading Nang hong muang ing
Tawntung den
verse5:
Hong sawp siang ding ci'n ka um hi!
Sisan gunpi sung
Hong siang sak ding ci'n ka um hi
Na si tawh
chorus:
Ke'n hong muang ing, Nang bek hong muang ing!
Ke'n hong muang ing, muang ing,
Nang bek hong muang ing

zoTitle: Lam Tawntung A Hong Paipih Hi
engTitle: All the Way My Saviour Leads Me
verse1:
Lam tawntung A hong paipih hi,
A dang bang kangen nawn diam
Khan' tawntung lam hong hilh zo hi,
Hong itna ka muang khial diam
Amah muang leng leitung ah zong,
Vantung nopna pha ka nei
Kei tungah bangbang hong tung zong,
Zeisu'n a pha bawl ka thei
Kei tungah bangbang hong tung zong,
Zeisu'n a pha bawl ka thei
verse2:
Lam tawntung A hong paipih hi,
Lam haksa hang lungnuam sak
Ze-etna zawh na'ng hong hehpih,
Hin'na Anlum in hong vak
Ka kha tui duh dangtak in vul,
Ka khe tawl puk dek laitak
Ka maiah Suangpi pan hong phul,
En un lungdamna tuinak!
Ka maiah Suangpi pan hong phul,
En un lungdamna tuinak
verse3:
Lam tawntung A hong paipih hi,
Kicing lamdang hong itna!
Tawl damna tak, hong khaam zo hi,
Vantung ka Pa' inn sungah
Sih nawn lohna puan bang silh in,
A taang gam ka kai ding hi
Tua ciang sa ning a tawntungin,
Zeisu'n hong kha mualsuak hi
Tua ciang sa ning a tawntung in,
Zeisu'n hong kha mualsuak hi

zoTitle: Thupha Guah Bang Hong Zu Ding Hi
engTitle: There Shall Be Showers of Blessing
verse1:
"Thupha guah bang hong zu ding hi"
Itna tawh hong ciam bangin
Tha malhna hun hong tung ding hi
Hong buak suk ding Topa in
verse2:
"Thupha guah bang hong zu ding hi"
Tha hat kikna a manpha
Hong ging zuazua ding hi, tampi
Mual tung, guam sung, mun tengah
verse3:
"Thupha guah bang hong zu ding hi"
Hong buak suk in Topa aw
Tha thak tu in, Nong guan' ding hi
Nong ciamsa hong tung sakaw
verse4:
"Thupha guah bang hong zu ding hi"
Tu ni'n hong zu ta leh maw
Zeisu kiangah thu i ngen hi
Pulak in Pa kiang i mawh
chorus:
Thupha guahzu bang, Thupha guah i kisam hi
Hehpihna mal hong kia teei hang, Hong zu suk hen a tampi

zoTitle: A Ki Gelh Hiam Ka Min?
verse1:
Topa hauhna ngaihsun ke'ng, Kham le ngun lunggulh ke'ng
Vantung gam ciam masa ning, Tuu kuam sung lut nuam ing
Vantung gam laipi sungah, Na' ciamtehna sungah
A kigelh hiam keima min, Zeisu aw, hong gen in.
verse2:
Gun gei a, sehnel bangin, Ka mawhna tam hangin
Topa aw, Nong tatna si Kei aading kicing hi
Na thu-ciamtehna laipi mual thei lo ding taang hi
"Na mawh si bang san hangin, Paak sak ning vuk bangin"
verse3:
A siangtho khuapi sungah, Inn pite taang mahmah
Vaang liatna ngah a mite, A puansilh uh a tee
Tua a phate sia sak ding, bangmah tum thei lo ding
Vantung mite' cin'na ah, Ka om ding hi keimah
chorus:
Gam ciamtehna sungah, Nuntakna lai sungah
Vantung ka tun' theih na'ngin
A kigelh hiam ka min

crossrefs: Word: S.S. 627, Tune: S.S. 1099, Ira David Sankey (1840-1908), Jessie H. Brown (1861-1921)
verse1:
Zeisu tawh mun khempeuh ka pai khawm ding hi
Kikhen loin hong khakna ka zui ding hi
A khe kiangah tu leng launa om lo a
Zeisu tawh pai khawm ding hi
verse2:
Mun khempeuh kei guak hi keng, Zeisu tawh hi'ng
Lawmte'n nusiat hangin Zeisu kei a' hi
Lam haksat hang, A khut tawh hong kha ding a
Zeisu tawh pai khawm ding hi
verse3:
Zeisu tawh mun khempeuh kei ka lum thei a
Sihna a liim in hong kiimkot hangin ah
Ka thawh ciang kawivak nawn lo ding ka thei hi
Zeisu tawh pai khawm ding hi
chorus:
Pai khawm, Zeisu tawh pai khawm ding
Pai khawm, mun khempeuh pai ding
Pai khawm, Zeisu tawh pai khawm ding
Mun khempeuh ah Zeisu tawh pai ding

zoTitle: Ka Kha Aading A Hoih Hi
engTitle: It Is Well With My Soul
verse1:
Gunpi taang lo bang nuam na'ng nong hilhna in
Dahna tui bangin hong let hi
Topa hong hilhna pha hi ka kha aading
Hoih bel hi, kha aading, hoih bel hi
verse2:
Dawi in hong khem a, bawlsiatna hong tun' hang
Ka up ding a thuciam om hi
Topa Zeisu in ka tha neem hong en hi
Hoih bel hi, kha aading, hoih bel hi
verse3:
Hong itna a nuam i ngaihsut ciangin ah
Ka mawh ka khialhna sung panin
Ka suahtak nading singlamteh tung si hi
Ka lungsim in ka phat hi Topa
verse4:
Topa Zeisu tu nung ciang hong pai ding hi
Ka lung khamna teng bei ding hi
Topa hih leitungah hong pai dingin ah
Ka Kha Siangtho aading a pha hi
chorus:
Hoih bel hi, hoih bel hi,
Kha aading, kha aading
Hoih bel hi, hoih bel hi, kha aading

verse1:
Jerusalem khua, nang in bawngnawi khuaizu omna
Nangmah ka lung ngaih laitak, Ke'n lamdang ka sa ta
Keima aading lung damna, leh nopna a tampi
Ke'n ka theih loh min than'na, tua san takah om hi
verse2:
Zion khua innpi sungah, bawlsiat a thuakte leh
Puan paak silh vantung mite bangin ah la sa veh
Topa in amau kiangah, A om tawntung ding hi
Thupha a ngahte omna, Ni a taang tawntung hi
verse3:
Davuih tokhom a om leh, gimna bei khit ciangah
Gal zo leh a lam mite', la sakna aw kiza
Hih mite in Topa aw, galdona ah zo ci
Tawp ngeilo tawntung in ah, puan paak silh ding uh hi
verse4:
Gam lamdang a pha bel in, Pasian thu zui omna
Gam lamdang a pha bel in, A muang mite' deihna
Zeisu na hehpihna in, Tua khua hong paipih in
Pasian le Kha Siangtho tawh, minphatna ngah ta hen

zoTitle: A Tawntung Ihmu Cip Ding I Hi Kei
engTitle: We Shall Sleep, But Not For Ever
verse1:
Ihmu leeng khangma cip loin,
Min than'na khua hong vak ding
Hin'kik ni ciang kimu kik leeng,
I kikhen nawn kei ding hi
A thuk bel gunpi sung pan in,
Sehnel gam khampi pan in
Mual dawn, mual kuam gamlak pan in,
Mi tampi hong tho ding hi.
verse2:
Paak hoih bang-a i deih mahmah,
I lung hihmawh phat mahmah
I ang sung pan i lak khiat ciang,
Lian mahmah hi, i dahna
Ni a tum dek mateng in ah,
Han kiang ngak-a om i hi
Eite paak i it manin ah,
Lam etna bei bang kisa
verse3:
Eite a tawntung han sungah,
Khangma cip ding i hi kei
Hong sap ciangin, thupha a pia,
Topa'n thupha ngah ta hen
Sihna om ngei nawn lohna mun,
A kip tawntung khuapi ah
Omna inn nuam ngah dingin ah,
Hong deih leh hong sam ding hi
chorus:
Ihmu leeng khangma cip loin,
Min than'na khua vak ding hi
Hin'kik ni ciang kimu kik in,
I kikhen nawn kei ding hi

verse1:
Thupha khuavaak sungah, Zeisu tawh pai lai-ah
Eite paina lam hong taang sak hi
A deih bang zuih ciangin, Amah tawh pai khawm in
A thu ngai a muang a om ding hi
verse2:
Van a gikte pua a, Gimna tawlna thuakna
Topa hong hehpihna kicing hi
Eite launa dinga, Dawimangpa hong khemna
Zeisu thu ngai in muang leeng bei hi
verse3:
Ni liim ahih hangin, Meei kai ahih hangin
Zeisu in thakhat a hawl khia hi
Launa leh kihtakna, Tauna leh kahnate
Zeisu i muan'lai in om thei kei
verse4:
Ki-itna pha tawh mah, Topa Zeisu mai ah
Kikhawm ciangin lam pai khawm ding hi
Thu hong piakna ngai a, Hong sawlna pai ding a
Cikmah hun lau loin nuam ding hi
chorus:
Muang un, ngai un. Lampi dang omlo hi
Zeisu kiang nuam ngah dingin,
Muang in a thu ngai un

verse1:
Lungdam thu khatvei ngai dih in
Gumpa kiang pan, na za hiam
Hong sapna dawng lo ding na hiam?
Topa lam na kihei diam?
verse2:
Khua hun tampi bei sak zo teh
Tam veipi tuuktung thei teh
Khua khal in phalbi vuk tui tah
Nang lah mawh sung kawi vak teh
verse3:
Zeisu in nang deih bang hong ngak
Vakvak lo khentat pak in
Kha Siangtho hong hah zol lai in
Gumpa lam zongin zui in
verse4:
Na lungsim Pasian kiang pia in
Khazih si um in muang in
En to in, Zeisu vantung om
A kamciam pelh sak lo hi
chorus:
A umte'n zuan, A umte'n zuan,
Zeisu zuan in hing ta un
A umte'n zuan, A umte'n zuan,
Zeisu zuan in hing ta un

verse1:
Hih leitung-a dahna khempeuh paai khia in
Nitak hun ciangin ah, damdam lung ngai in
Thukpi in phumin la, Pha takpi'n seel in
Zeisu kiangah gen in, Thupha hong pia ding
verse2:
Zeisu kiangah gen in, Na dahna thei hi
Zeisu kiang gen lecin, Huhna hong pia ding
Na lampi hong taan' ciang, Pai in kaikhawm in
Thu ngen in na dahna, Na van zang ding hi
verse3:
Dahna lung khamna tawh, Khua a mial hangin
Nang sang-a a gim zaw, Mi dangte huh in
Na dahna paai khia in, Thupha ngah nading
Mi dangte aading zong, Zeisu kiang gen in

verse1:
Nisim in Zeisu a min, Um in, huihpi nun' ciangin
Thu upna a tawm hangin, Zeisu bek um in muang in
verse2:
Kha Siangtho keimah tungah, Hong taang hi, ka sin sungah
Lam hong hilh leh puk zo lo, Zeisu bek thu um khin zo
verse3:
Lam a nop leh la sa ta, Khua hong mial leh thumin la
Gimna thuak ciang thu ngen in, Zeisu bek um in muang in
verse4:
Ka nun'tak lai van le lei, Bei mateng um khial nawn kei
Tun' mateng vantung khuapi, Zeisu bek i um ding hi
chorus:
Nisim in Zeisu Topa, Um in beelin muangin la
Lai Siangtho hong hilh bangin, Zeisu bek um in muang in

zoTitle: Aw, Zeisu Bang Zah'n Ka It
verse1:
Ka zaknop min khat a om hi
Tua min la'n sak tham hi
Tua min bil-ah la bang ka za
Leitung-a min ngaih bel
verse2:
Hong Gumpa itna hong gen hi
Hong tankhia ding si hi
Ama si manpha hong hilh hi
Mawhnei mi mawh maina
verse3:
Pa neih kheempeuh kei hong hilh hi
Nisim sapna kheempeuh
Khuamial sung lam ka pai khak ciang
Lampi in hong taang sak
verse4:
Hong itna lung tak hong gen hi
Khialhna kheempeuh phawk sak
Dahnate Amah'n hong puakpih
Puakpih nuam dang om kei
chorus:
Bang zah'n Zeisu ka it, Bang zah'n Zeisu ka it
Bang zah'n Zeisu ka it
Hong it masak hang hi

verse1:
Ciamna' kip thupha, Zeisu kei a!
Pasian vaanglian bang hong ciam sakna pha
Hot khiatna luahpa, Pasian' leisa
Kha Siangtho a suak, si a sawpsa
verse2:
Thu man'na cing a, cing hi nuamna
Ka mit kha'n ka mu hi lianpi nuamna
Vantung mite in, ka bil sungah
Hehpihna, itna, hong gen ka za
verse3:
Thu man'na cing hi, tawlnga khin hi
Hong Honpa sung lung nuamin ka om hi
Vil kawm, ngak kawmin, ka ento hi
Ama hoihna, itna hong dim hi
chorus:
Ka gengen ding hi, ka sasa ding
Hong Honpa phatna sun ni lohin
Ka gengen ding hi, ka sasa ding
Hong Honpa phatna sun ni lohin

verse1:
Thupha khuavaak mual sang tungah, Pasian' mite dingun
Zan khuamial hong liah ma-in ah, Mai nawtin ah kuan un
Mual kuam sunga galte sim ding,
Tha neih teng siit kei ni
I thei hi, leitung zawh nading, Upna i nei ding hi
verse2:
Ama hong itna dial nuai-ah, A Thu tem bang zangin
A zosa mi siangte' khap mah, A zui lai eite in
Upna tawh huihpi nung ban ah,
Galte nawk gawp uh a
Sihna a zawhna uh upna mah, hi lai ei muan'na
verse3:
I ziat, i vei, i kiimkot ah, Galte in hong pang hi
Noptat maan'na nusia in ah, Pai un, do ding kuan ni
Hot khiatna lukhu khuin ah,
Thumaan i teeng ding hi
Lei liing ding hi i khe nuai-ah, I aw'n mual thawn ding hi
chorus:
Upna in zawhna hi, Upna in zawhna hi
Upna in zawhna ding hi, Leitung zawh gawp nading

verse1:
A dahte hong pai un, na vulna pan un
Hehpih tokhom mai ah, hong khuk din' un
Na lung liamna, natna, hong pai hong gen un
Vantung' damsak lah dahna om lo hi
verse2:
Lungsim hawmte' nuamna, lam khialte' khuavak
Vul ngeilo, mual ngeilo, lawpna hong lak
Kha Siangtho Huhpa in hong neem hi nuam tak
"Vantung' damsak lah dahna om lo hi"
verse3:
En un, Hin'na Anlum, en un, Hin'na tui
Pasian' tokhom mai pan hong luang suk tui
Hong pai un, hih lai-ah, itna pawi kilui
Vantung' damsak lah dahna om lo hi

zoTitle: Zeisu In Nangma Dahna A Thei Hi
verse1:
Dahna a om kheempeuh Topa Zeisu'n thei
Lungsim kisikna le thungetna zong thei
Lau keei loin um in, na lung khauhsak in
Na van Topa suan in, hong nuamsak ding hi
verse2:
Zeisu lungsim sungah nang pha hong sa hi
Na galte khut sungah nang hong gum ding hi
Ama deihna bangin lam hong hilh ding hi
A vaang taan'na mun ah na tung thei ding hi
verse3:
Gal na do Zeisu'n thei, na thumna za hi
Na lung gim lam thei, na kikona za hi
Na kha tha khauh na'ngin, na tai loh na'ng in
Lungsim nuam hong pia ding, na khitui nul ding

crossrefs: 1 Peter 1:8, SS. 659, W.R. Featherston (1846-1873), Rev. Adoniram J. Gordon (1836-1895)
verse1:
Zeisu aw, kong it hi, kei aa Na hi ta!
Nangma hang, mawhna nuam nam cin ka khia ta
Keimah hong Tanpa, hong Honpa Na hi ta!
Kong it ngei leh zong, tu'n kong it pha sem ta
verse2:
Tun' Nang kong it hang Nangma'n Nong it masa
Nong it ma'n singlamteh tung Nong tan zo ta
Ling lukhu na tal tungah kikhen zo ta
Kong it ngei leh zong, tu'n kong it pha sem ta
verse3:
Hong it tawntung ning hinna, sihna sungah
Hong phat tawntung ning, hu Nong kawm lai-in ah
Sihna daitui ka tal-ah kaai ciangin ah
Kong it ngei leh zong, tu'n kong it pha sem ta
verse4:
Nuamsak tawntungna minthang innpi sungah
Na min hong phat tawntung ning a taang van-ah
Zawhna lukhute khu in sa ning hih mah
Kong it ngei leh zong, tu'n kong it pha sem ta

verse1:
Hih Zawdan gunah tui kiphum dingin ah
Mawh neite kheempeuh hong kikhawm ta
Topa thupha a umte khempeuh in-ah
Zawdan gunah a sam uh a pha
verse2:
Hih Zawdan gun geiah ding-a omte in
Vantung la aw tawl khat ngai uh hi
Mihing kheempeuh mawhnate a phel Topa
Vantung tokhom kiangah hong mu hi
verse3:
Vantung pan-a thu hong piak a aw in-ah
"Ka Pa in nang hong mu hong pai in
Ka Pa zong nang hangin ah a lungdam hi"
Vantung khua siklongpi tum sak in
verse4:
Ni tumta zingsang in hong tum kik mateng
Tu in tate aw hong ciah meng un
Ka Pa in zong vantung mite kiangah gen
A lamdang thupha na thei sak un
chorus:
"Vaang lian, vaang lian," vantung mi'n ci hi
La sa uh hi min phatna la hi
"Haleluiah vaang lian minthan'na pha ci," ci
Vantung sang innpi zel sak uh hi

zoTitle: Zeisu In Ka Lung Sungah Tum Hi
engTitle: Since Jesus Came into My Heart
verse1:
Topa Zeisu ka lung sungah hong lut phetin
Ka lungsim hong kikheel pah hi
Topa Zeisu ka lung sungah hong tum phetin
Ka lung sung khua hong vaak pah hi
verse2:
Topa Zeisu ka lung sungah hong lut phetin
Lam ka khial nawn kei pah ding hi
Topa Zeisu ka lung sungah hong tum phetin
Ka mawh kheempeuh hong sawp siang hi
verse3:
Topa Zeisu ka lung sungah hong lut phetin
Upna a kip ka ngah pah hi
Topa Zeisu ka lung sungah hong lut phetin
Up khialhna teng bei khin pah hi
verse4:
Topa Zeisu ka lung sungah hong lut phetin
Sihna kuam pan khuavaak pah hi
Topa Zeisu ka lung sungah hong lut phetin
Khuapi kongkhak kimu pah hi
chorus:
Topa Zeu ka lung sungah,
Hong tum hong khawl khit phetin ah
Tuipi kilok bang ka lung sungah khuavaakna
Tha khatin a hong taang pah hi

verse1:
Hong it Zeisu Topa aw, Tuihual hong nailai takin
Huihpi nung daih nai loh tawh, Na ang sung hong om sak in
Nuntak huihpi kam mateng, Hong Honpa aw hong liah in
Keima kha Nong lak mateng, Khawlmun nuam ah hong kha in
verse2:
Belh ding dang khat beek nei keng, Cimawhin Nang kong beel hi
Hong nusia peuhmah ngei ke'n, Nong huh, Nong neem lai ding hi
Kong muang hi Topa, Nangmah, Huhna Nang kiang ka ngah hi
Topa aw, Na kha nuaiah, Keima lu nong liah ding hi
verse3:
Kei deihna teng kicin'na, Khazih Topa Nang Na hi
Pukte phong, mittawte khat, Na damsak lungsim, pumpi
Nang Na dik, Nang Na siangtho, Kei kihhuai, mawhna ka dim
Ka pumtang sian'na neilo, Nang thutak, hehpihna dim
verse4:
Ka mawh siin khin zo dingin, Hehpihna Nang kiang kicing
Damna gun tui hong luan in, Ka lung sung siang den nading
Nang nuntakna Nak Na hi, Nangmah hong dawndawn sak in
A tawntung nuntak tui li, Ka lung sung hong phul sak in

verse1:
Topa' min le Ama thu ah,
Ka maizum ngei kei ding
Ama Thu le A singlamteh,
Ka pahtawi ngitnget ding
verse2:
Zeisu ka Pasian' min ka thei,
Tua min bek hi kei' muan
Hong maizum sak ngeilo ding kei,
Lam etna A hong guan
verse3:
Ama thuciam kip tawntung a,
A khut sung ka piak teng
Amah'n phatak na kem ding ta,
A hun a tun mateng
verse4:
Tua ciang A Pa Pasian mai ah,
Ka min hong sam ding a
Jerusalem khua thak sungah,
Omna hong pia ding ta
chorus:
Singlamteh! Singlamteh! Khuavaak ka muh cilna
Ka lung sung a vangik teng bei khin na
A thu ka up ciang khua ka mu thei ta
Tu in ka lung a dam tawntung ta

verse1:
Ka lampi sau in a gim huai a
Vangik pua in kikeem khial in
Lungdam la sa in, lungsim a nat ciang
Zeisu in kei a hong keem hiam?
verse2:
Sun khuavaak in a hong mial ciangin
Kei kiangah a hong nai om hiam?
Ka lampi mialin, lauhuai a tam ciang
Zeisu in kei a hong keem hiam?
verse3:
Haksa ze-et ka thuak laitak in
Zan tawntung khitui luan na tawh
Hong hon' ding omlo ka dah laitak in
Zeisu in kei a hong keem hiam?
verse4:
I itte tawh mangpha kipia in
Lungkham lutang nat a bei ciang
Topa in ei bang ci in hong mu diam
Zeisu in kei a hong keem hiam?
chorus:
A hong keem hi, Ke'n ka thei hi
Ka dahna hong phawkpih hi
Sun in om nuamlo in, zan a lauhaui' laitak
Hong Gumpa'n hong keem

verse1:
Kei guak huan sungah ka vak a
Paak tunga daitui a kaai lai in
Ka bil sungah, ke'n Ama aw ka za
Hong hopih Pasian' Ta in
verse2:
Ama' thugen khum kisa in
Vasa te'n dai takin ngai lialua
A ngaih mahmah la keimah hong pia ta
Ka lung sung hong ging ziazua
verse3:
Amah tawh tua huanah giak ning
Zan khuamial in hong kiimkot hangin
Ahih hang Amah'n mawhna aw sung pan
Hong sawl hi, pai ta in, ci'n
chorus:
Amah'n hong tonpih, Amah'n hong tonpih
Kei Ama aa ci in hong gen
I neih bangin i lungdam ding tualai
Kua mah'n ciam kha ngeilo hi

engTitle: I Will Guide Thee (Tune: Precious Promise)
verse1:
Thu ciamna pha hong pia zo hi,
Lung khamna na thuak zawh ciang,
Leitung pan vantung lampi ah,
Ka mitin nang kong cing ding.
verse2:
Ze-et nate na zawh khit ciang,
Na muan’nan hong ngak zawh ciang,
Hih kiciamna khutbuh na nei,
Ka mitin nang kong cing ding.
verse3:
Na lamet nate kisia in,
Lawpna kumte a bei ciang,
Hih kiciamna na let lai in,
Ka mitin nang kong cingding.
verse4:
Nun’takna ding hun hong bei in,
Sihna ding hun hong tun’ ciang,
Topa hong sapna na za ding,
Kamit in nang kong cing ding.
chorus:
Nang kong cing ding, nang kong cing ding,
Kamit in nang kong cing ding,
Leitung pan vantung lampi ah,
Kamit in nang kong cing ding.

zoTitle: A Mah'n Ka Mawhna Teng Lakhia Zo
engTitle: He Had Taken My Sins Away
verse1:
Lungsim leh aw in Topa phat ning,
Ama sung ka kipaak ding,
La in sa ning lamdang hong itna,
Ke’n sasa ning hih la.
verse2:
Nopna khawlna ngah ding Ama kiang,
Ka mawhna tawh ka pai ciang,
Ka nget hong za in, hong khahkhia ta,
Ke’n sasa ning hih la.
verse3:
Ka hu tawpna tawh Amah phat ning,
Sihna ka zawh man inah,
Amah phat ning a tawntung inah,
Ke’n sasa ning hih la.
chorus:
Amah’n ka mawhna teng lakhia zo (khia zo),
A min siang phat un, a min siang phat un,
A mah’n ka mawh na teng lakhia zo (khia zo),
Halleluijah Min phat un’

verse1:
Keima Pa in inn leh lo a hau hi,
Leitung sum kheempeuh a khut sungah omhi,
Suang hoih, a san, a kang, kham, ngun, a vekpi,
Kisim zolo in Amah a hau hi.
verse2:
Keimah ka Pa ta hong gum Topa in,
Mizawngte bangin leitung ah a vak hi,
Tu in vantungah tawntung in-ah mang hi,
Nung ciang ei vantungah inn hong pia ding hi.
verse3:
Masa-ah leitungah zin mi ka hi,
A mawhnei mi a lawmte tawh khen mi hi,
Tu in innluah min than’na ngah nading in,
Vantung khua sungah keima min ki-at hi.
verse4:
Puanbuk ahih hangin phamawh lo hi,
Keima aading kumpi inn a lam ta hi,
Inn pan gamla hangin la sa thei ding hi,
Keimah in Kumpipa a tapa ka hi.
chorus:
Keimah in Kumpipa a tapa ka hi,
Honggum Zeisu tawh Kumpipa ta ka hi hi.

verse1:
Nun’takna tuipi tungah huih nun’ ciangin,
Si ding cih ngaihsun in na lung kiat ciangin,
Thupha khat nungah khat na ngaihsun in la,
Topa in tampi hong pia na thei ding ta.
verse2:
Lung man’na van gik bangin na thuak ngei hiam,
Singlam teh hong pua sak in a gik thei hiam,
Thupha khat nungah thupha na ngaihsut leh,
Ni simin a tawntung la na sa ding hi.
verse3:
Mi dangte a sum a paai na et ciangin,
Zeisu kiangah na ngah ding sum ngaihsun in,
Vantung khua sungah na omna inn hi zong,
Kuamah in lei zo kei sum a om ding hi.
verse4:
Tua ahih ciangin gal kido laitak in,
Pasian in na kheempeuh uk hi, Lau kei in,
Vantung mihingte in nang kiangah om hi,
Lampi tawp dongin nang a hong huh ding hi.
chorus:
Thupha khat nungah khat ngaihsun in,
A tampi hongpia in theita in,
Thupha khat nungah khat ngaihsun in,
Pasian in a tampi hong pia thei ta in.

verse1:
Kei in lawmpa khat ka mu hi,
Ka theih ma in hong it ta,
Ki-itna khau tawh hong kai hi,
Tua khau tawh hong paipih ta,
Keima lungsim a hong khih hi,
A kuamah’n a phel zawh loh,
Topa in keimah hong uk hi,
A tawntung ding hi khinzo.
verse2:
Kei in lawmpa khat ka mu hi,
Hong gup nading hong si ta,
Nun'takna tui hongpia zo hi,
Topa mah in hongpia ta,
Keima neihsa bangmah om kei,
Topa bek a hi ding hi,
Lungsim tha tang, hin'na sumte,
Topa-a hi tawntung hi.
verse3:
Kei in lawmpa khat ka mu hi,
Vang lian kheempeuh hongpia hi,
I pai laitak vantung lampi,
Innpi ah hong kha ding hi,
Vaang lian tawntung gamla panah,
Hong huh dingin hong tan in,
Tu’n ngak in, um in, do inla,
Nung ciang nopna nangah ding.
verse4:
Kei in lawmpa khat ka mu hi,
Hong it, hehpihna, nem hi,
Lam hong hilh hong ngaihsun sak hi,
Hong liah na’ngin, vaang lian hi,
Hih zah hong it Topa kiangah,
Khen sak thei vaang lian om kei,
Hin’na, sihna, leitung gimna,
Hong khen zoding na om kei.

verse1:
A migi tuucing pa en un,
Tui khuk kiang a din' lai in,
Tui leh an a duh-te pai un,
Gam hoihna vantung khua ah.
verse2:
Nuntakna lam a zuite bek,
Pasian in lungdam pih ding,
Topa Zeisu sihna hangin,
Nuntak thak hong pia ding hi.
verse3:
Tuu khumna buk sungah om te,
Ama tuu taktak te hi,
Amah in Pasian a up bang,
Ei zong Topa i um ding hi.
chorus:
Hong paipihna peuh zui un,
Hong paipihna peuh zuiun,
Haleluiah, haleluiah,
Hong paipihna peuh zui un.

zoTitle: Hong Khah Ngei Lo Ding Itna Aw
engTitle: O Love That Wilt Not let Me Go (Tune: St. Margaret)
verse1:
Hong khah ngeilo ding itna aw,
Ka lung gimna teng kong nga ta,
A pha zaw, cing zaw thei nading,
Nong piak sa keima nuntakna,
Nang kong ap kik ta ding.
verse2:
Hong tonpih tawntung Khuavak aw,
Keima mei mit dek kong ap ta,
Nang sungah taang pha zaw nading,
Nong kawm sak keima khua vaakna,
Nang kong ap kik ta ding.
verse3:
Keimah hong zong khia Nuamna aw,
Keima lungsim nang kong hon ta,
Dahna sung pan nuam muh nading,
Kip ding hi Nangma thuciamna,
Dahna bei theih nading.
verse4:
Ka lu hong phong Singlamteh aw,
Nang kong taisan ngam nawn lo ta,
Nuntak bei in leivui suak ding,
Lei pan paak bang Nong tawi to ta,
Ka hin’ tawntung nading.

verse1:
Tuni in keima lungsim sungah,
Khuavaak a hong taang hi,
Leitung ni sang a vaang taang zaw,
Ka khuavaak Zeisu hi.
verse2:
Tuni in keima lungsim sungah,
Kumpi phatna la sa,
Kei sak theih loh langiahte zong,
Zeisu’n ngai leh a za.
verse3:
Tuni in keima lungsim sungah,
Topa hong tum man in,
Lung nopna le gamtatna pha,
Hong po, hong palh pan in.
verse4:
Tuni in keima lungsim sungah,
Nuamna, lawpna, dim hi,
Hong piaksa leh hong piak lai ding,
Thupha, nuamna, hang hi.
chorus:
Aw ka lung sung, lung khuavaakna,
Lung sung nopna, nuamna hun pha hi,
Zeisu mainuam ka muh ciangin,
Ka lungsim sung hong taang hi.

zoTitle: Keen Sang Tawn Vantung Kah Lo Ding
engTitle: We May Not Climb the Heavenly Steeps (Tune: Serenity)
verse1:
Keen sang tawn,
Vantung kah lo ding,
Khazih Topa la ding,
A thuk pen zong zon’ hang mu lo,
Ama sung lau om lo. Amen.
verse2:
Itna siangtho, itna kicing,
Tu mah’n hong huh theih hi,
Itna, upna hong lah bangin,
Galilee tui geiah. Amen.
verse3:
Mong neilo damna puan silh in,
A dah lupna kiangah,
Amah i lawn’khak ding hong om,
Hong damsak kik ta hi. Amen.
verse4:
Kote kheempeuh To leh Siapa,
Kote’n bang min puak hang,
Nong sapna za’n nang aa hi nuam,
Nang aading hong sit in.
verse5:
Ama min suangin thu ngen leeng,
Naupang bangin thum leeng,
Sihna in ei a hong phak ciang,
Ama min i suang ding.

verse1:
Lungsim a pha mihingte aw,
Topa tungah na lungdam un,
Topa a teel mihingte aw,
Dahna lungman’na paisan un.
verse2:
Lungdam ve un Topa in ah,
Leitung, vantungah pha bel hi,
A thupha a la phate tawh,
Hong uk a eimah hong phel hi.
verse3:
Topa aading galkapna ah,
Galte hong zodek hang a ci,
Topa galkap mangte in ah,
Galte sangin a tam zaw hi.
verse4:
Sunlai in khua hong mial hangin,
Zanlai van hong khup hangin ah,
Na lungsim na mawh lo ding hi,
Um in gal bei mateng thupha.
chorus:
Nuam un, nuam un,
Topa tungah na lungdam un,
Nuam un, nuam un,
Topa tungah lungdam khin un.

verse1:
Nang aa hi’ng, Topa, Na aw za zo ing,
Kei nong itna hong gen hi,
Ahih hang upna tawh hong kah to in,
Kong kinai zaw lai nuam hi.
verse2:
Hong siangtho sak in hehpihna vaang tawh,
Na’na semding hong zang in,
Lungkia ngeilo in lametna kip tawh,
Nang' deih bang hong deih sak in.
verse3:
Na tokhom mai ah tawl khat sung bek mah,
Thu ngenin kong khuk din’ zong,
Lawmta bangin lungsim kum khawmin ah,
Kalung hong nuam mahmah khong.
verse4:
Gun gal kah bang sihna galkai mateng,
Itna thuk phawk khin zolo,
Nangmah tawh nuamtak kong khawl khawm mateng,
Nuamna sang kiban nai lo.
chorus:
Hong nai sak in thupha Topa aw,
Na sihna singlamteh tawh,
Hong kai in Na kiangah thupha Topa aw,
Nai takin Na pang si tawh.

engTitle: Saviour, Thy Dying Love (Tune: Something For Thee)
