verse1:
Hong Honpa, Na sih dong kei Nong it zo,
Nang aading na khat zong ka hong it lo,
Itna tawh hong kun ning,
Ka ciamna tangtun’ ning,
Nang kiang tu’n hong tun’ ning,
Na khat teitei.
verse2:
Hehpih tokhom mai ah hehpih kong ngen,
Upna neih sunin ah Zeisu kong en,
Thuak ding, gen ding, sak ding,
Na khat peuh nang aading,
Kei hong hih zo sak in,
Na khat teitei.
verse3:
Lungsim maan hongpia in, Nangma-aa’ bang,
A ni kipeel loin, Kahih theih na'ng,
Itna tawh nasepna,
Khatpeuh tung mi gitna,
Lam khial khat ngah zawhna,
Na khat teitei.
verse4:
Keimah le ka neih sa, Nong piaksa hi’ng,
Hih lai ka nuntakna, Nangma aading,
Na mai kong muh ciangin,
Tat khiatsa ka kha in,
Hi hen, nang aading in,
Na khat teitei.

verse1:
Gal dona tam hih leitung pan,
Zeisu in hong sam hi,
Nisim in a ma aw ging hi,
"Kei nunghong zui in" a ci.
verse2:
Leitung sum leh paai bia lo ding,
Zeisu in a hong sam hi,
Hong khaam milim hawlkhia ta in,
"A mau sang hong it in" ci.
verse3:
Dahna sung, lung damna sungah,
Nasep lai tawlnga lai ah,
"Tuate sangin kei hong it zaw’n,"
Ci in a mah’n hong sam hi.
verse4:
Topa’n hong sap ciang ka ngai ding,
Topa hong hehpih ta in,
Nangma itna na seem dingin,
Topa aw, hong huh ta in.

zoTitle: Zeisu Ading Nuntak Maan Ka Nungta
verse1:
Zeisu aading nuntak maan ka nungta,
Sepna ah nuam sak ding ka hanciam ta,
Lung damna tawh, A deihna ka' seem hi,
Hih bang hihna in kei lung damna hi.
verse2:
Kei tang si Zeisu aading ka nungta,
Kei mawh kei zumna Kalani pua ta,
Hong itna in, Amah hong zui nuam sak,
A lam lahna zui in ka kibup piak.
verse3:
Omna peuh Zeisu aading ka nungta,
A min siangtho sungah na ka sem ta,
Gimna supnate ke’n ka thuak nuam hi,
Hih bangte Zeisu aading thuakna hi.
verse4:
Tom kha sung Zeisu aading ka nungta,
Amah nuih mai mah manpha pen ka sa,
A mangte zongin gum ding a si hi,
A gimte a sung tawldam ding la hi.
chorus:
Zeisu, Topa, Honpa aw, Nang tungah kong kipia,
Nong gup khiatna dingin ah,
Kei aading Nong kipia,
To dang kuamah ka nei lo,
Ka lung sung hong teeng in,
Ka nuntakna,
Nang tung kong pia, Khazih Nang aading in.

zoTitle: Na Kheempeuh Zeisu Kiangah Ka Pia Ding Hi
verse1:
Hong gum Topa keimah inah,
Na kheempeuh paai in zui ning,
Ka Topa aw, Nangmah inah,
Lam hong hilh Pa Na hi ding.
verse2:
Hong gum Topa keimah inah,
Nangma kiang ka hong nai hi,
Kisik a thupha kong ngetna,
Ngai in hong gum in, kong ci.
verse3:
Hong gum topa keimah inah,
Leitung nopna ka nusia,
Kha Siangtho le Topa Pasian,
Hong om in ka lung sungah.
verse4:
Hong gum Topa keimah inah,
Nong gupna la pha sa ning,
Vantung gun gei kong tun' mateng,
Nang hangin ka lungdam ding.
chorus:
Na kheempeuh paai a,
Na kheempeuh paai a,
Na kheempeuh Topa khut sungah,
Keimah’n hong pia ning.

engTitle: My Faith Looks Up to Thee (Tune: Oliver)
verse1:
Kong up kong muan'na lian,
Hong hon Topa Pasian, hong tan Tuuno,
Kong thumna hong ngai in,
Ka mawhna teng paai in,
Tuni-a kipan in hong tang khin aw.
verse2:
Keima lungsim zawngkhal,
Hong guan'in tha le ngal, tha nuam sak in,
Kei aading Nong si ta,
Kei zong Nang kong itna mit ngeilo,
Ka sungah lum den sak in.
verse3:
Lungman’ khuamial lakah,
Dahna tampi lakah, lam hong hilh aw,
Khuamialna vaak sak in,
Dahna khitui siak in,
Pial lo, hong nai sak in Nangma kiang tawh.
verse4:
Leitung nun’ tom bei a,
Sihna gun ka tungah hong tuum ciangin,
Launa, lung himawhna,
Hong paih khiatsak inla,
Na tatsa keima kha hong pua to in.

verse1:
Nungta Topa hong hopih in,
Topa aw, Na aw za nuam ing,
Nong zon’ bangin, a mangthang sa,
Cimawh ta te hong mu ta in.
verse2:
Hih theih na’ng Topa hong hilh in,
A manpha Na gen khiat thu te,
A thuk mahmah mi lungsim sung,
A tun’ dongin hong paupih in.
verse3:
Na thu tawh kei hong dim ta in,
A dimlet dong hong guan’in la,
Mit ngeilo Na thu taang sak in,
Na itna leh phatna lak in.
verse4:
Hong zangin, Topa hong zangin,
Deih hun, deihna peuh hong zangin,
Na hehpihna mai ka muh dong,
Na min than’na hong hawm ta in.

engTitle: O Jesus, Thou Art Standing (Tune: St. Hilda)
verse1:
Aw, Zeisu, kong pua’h nading,
A kikhak cip kongpi,
Lungneem takin na ngak hi,
Tua kong kihon' mateng,
Ama min pua u le nau,
Tapidaw te zumhuai,
Zumna tungah zumhuai hi,
Tua tan vei i din' sak'
verse2:
Aw, Zeisu’n konghong kiu hi,
En un na muh sak loh,
Liamma leh a khuk ling kual,
A maiah khitui luang,
Itna theihna a gawm khawm,
Lungduai takin hong ngak!
Aw, mawhna tunga, mawhna,
Kongpi khakcip mawhna.
verse3:
Aw, Zeisu, kiniam khiatna,
Kam tawh nong hopih a,
"Nang ta'ng si ing, ka tate ding’ Kong bawl zo," na ci,
Topa aw tu’n maizum za’n,
Kong ka hong hon’ uh hi,
Ko it Gumpa aw, tum in,
Hong nusia ngei nawn ke’n.

zoTitle: Hong Paipih Na Peuhah Zui Ning
verse1:
Topa hong sapna ka za hi,
Topa hong sapna ka za hi,
Topa hong sapna ka za hi,
"Singlamteh pua in hong zui in" ci.
verse2:
Lung gimna huanah zong zui ning,
Lung gimna huanah zong zui ning,
Lung gimna huanah zong zui ning,
Lam tawntung ah Amah zuizui ning.
verse3:
Thu khenna munah zong zui ning,
Thu khenna munah zong zui ning,
Thu khenna munah zong zui ning,
Lam tawntung ah Amah zuizui ning.
verse4:
Min pha le hehpih hong pia ding,
Min pha le hehpih hong pia ding,
Min pha le hehpih hong pia ding,
Lam tawntung ah hong tonpih pih ding.

zoTitle: Nang Tawh Ka Pai Ding Hi
engTitle: O Master Let Me Walk with Thee (Tune: Maryton)
verse1:
Nasepna lam lung nemna tawh,
Nang tawh ka pai ding, Topa aw,
Gimna, tawlna ka thuak dingin,
Nangmah in kei hong huh lai in.
verse2:
Nangma thu umlo mite in,
Thu hilh nading in hong huh in,
Lam khial mite vantung lampi,
Hilh kik nading thu hong hilh in.
verse3:
Hehpihna thu hong hilh in la,
Nang tawh lampi pai dingin a ah,
Lam dangah pai lo nading in,
Hong gum Topa aw, honghuh in.
verse4:
Nangma lawpna, muan’na, itna,
Nun’tak laitak ke’n ka deih mah,
Nangma lung damna zong deih hi,
Nangmah tawh kei ka pai ding hi.

zoTitle: Nang Aading Ka Nungta Ding Hi
engTitle: My Life, My Love, I Give to Thee
verse1:
Ka nun'takna leh ka itna,
Nangma kiangah keimah’n ka pia,
Nangma thu ka ngai ding,
Topa hong gum Topa Zeisu.
verse2:
Nang hong saang ding ke’n ka um hi,
Ka nu’ntak na’ng Na'ng na si zo hi,
Tu nung ciangin ka lawp ding hi,
Hong gum Topa Zeisu.
verse3:
Ka kha honggum dingin topa,
Na si Kalani mual tungah,
Ka pum vekpi, nang kahong pia,
Hong gum Topa Zeisu.
chorus:
Nang aading ka nungta ding hi,
Nangmah in kei tang ding na si,
Keimah ka lung a dam ding hi,
Hong gum Topa Zeisu.

engTitle: Take My Life, and Let It Be (Tune: Hendon)
verse1:
Topa aw ka nuntakna,
Tang in, siangtho tak zang in,
Itna tawh Nangma sawlna,
Ka khut mang sak, sem sak in,
Ka khut mang sak, sem sak in.
verse2:
Ka phei phung hong zang in la,
Nang ading ngal hat sak in,
Ka aw zong Nang tangin la,
Ngaih tak Na min phat sak in,
Ngaih tak Na min phat sak in.
verse3:
Ka kam ka muk hong zang in,
Na thupha gen theih nading,
Ka sum ka paai tang khin in,
Neu kha beek hong it kei ning,
Neu kha beek hong it kei ning.
verse4:
Ka itna teng hong sang in,
Na khe maiah hong sung ning,
Ka pumpi in hong tang in,
Nang aa bek hi khin den ning,
Nang aa bek hi khin den ning.

engTitle: My Jesus, As Thou Wilt (Tune Jewett)
verse1:
Zeisu, Nangma deih bang,
Keimah’n zong deih nuam ing,
Nangma itna khut sung,
Hong ki-ap khin nuam ing,
Dahna nuamna sungah,
Nang mah’n hong tonpih in,
Ci zo nuam ing, Topa,
"Nang deih bang hi sak in."
verse2:
Zeisu, Nangma deih bang,
Luan khi’n liah zel zongin,
Ka upna aksi taang,
Mual sak, mang sak kei in,
Nang zong hih leitung ah,
Na dahna kap manin,
Nang tawh kap dingin ah,
"Nang deih bang hi sak in."
verse3:
Zeisu, Nangma deih bang,
Kei aading pha khin hi,
Mailam a piang bangbang,
Nangmah kong ap khin hi,
Lung patau lo keimah,
Tang tak ka zuan van inn,
Hin’ lai, sih ciang, kala,
"Nang deih bang hi sak in."

verse1:
Zeisu aw ka sih dongin,
Nangma nasem dingin,
Kiciamna kip ka koih zo,
Nangmah ka Lawm ka To,
Hong panpih tawntung ke cin,
Nanglam hong hilh le cin,
Gal dona kihta kei ning,
Lampaam siikkhial kei ning.
verse2:
Nong nai hong phawk khial sak ke’n,
Thudang te’n hong neh den,
Muhnop huai te’n hong leng hi,
Zaknop huai hong meng hi,
Ka galte hong nai tawntung,
Ka kiim leh ka lung sung,
Tuate sang hong nai zaw in,
Mawhna pan hong dal in.
verse3:
Nangma pau hong zasak in,
A siang a tel takin,
Lungsung huihpi nun' ciangin,
Mang lo phun nuam ciangin,
Ka lung muan’ theih na’ng in ah,
Nong sawlna Nong khaamna,
Hong thei sak hong ngai sak in,
Ka lungsim hong cing in.

zoTitle: Ka Hi Bang Hong La In
verse1:
Topa Zeisu ka thu ngai in,
Na hong phel kei leh ka si ding,
Kiphelna thu hong pia suk in,
Ka hi bang hong la in.
verse2:
Phelna mulo mawhna tampi,
Ka neih manin Topa a si,
Nong hehpih leh Nong phel thei hi,
Ka hi bang hong la in.
verse3:
Bangmah a pha ka bawl zo lo,
Ka thu ciamna ka sia sak zo,
Na min tawh hong phel sakin aw,
Ka hi bang hong la in.
verse4:
Na khe mai-ah kong kun Topa,
Nong muh bangin kei ka hi hi,
Nasep kipan kiman khin zo,
Ka hi bang hong la in.
chorus:
Ka hi bang hong la in,
Ka hi bang hong la in,
Nangma sih keima phatna hi,
Ka hi bang hong la in.

verse1:
Topa tawh kibang zaw nuam lai ing,
A kiniam khiat bang, a migit luat bang,
A thanop bang, a thumaan mah bangin,
Hong vaikhak mah bangin, kipia’n seem nuam ing.
verse2:
Topa bang nisim thu ngen nuam ing,
Thahat nuam lai ing, singlamteh pua ding,
Hanciam nuam lai ing, Ama gam aading in,
Kha Siangtho sam lai, a vakthapte aading.
verse3:
Topa bangin nungta’n khang nuam ing,
Amah bang midang itna lak nuam ing,
Galile ah pumpi deih a nial bang,
Topa tawh a tawntawn in kibang nuam ing.
chorus:
Ka lungsung ah, Nangaa bek hi nuam ing,
Ka lutang la in la, Nangaa suak hen,
Ka mawh teng sil sak in, Topa, tu in,
Sil siang in Nang aading hong keem den in.

engTitle: Have Thine Own Way, Lord (Tune: Adelaide)
verse1:
Nang’ deih bang Topa, Nang’ deih bangbang,
Nangmah beel seekpa, kei tungman bang,
Nangma deih bangin kei hong bawl in,
Taang lo, mang dingin Nang kong ngak hi.
verse2:
Nang’ deih bang Topa, Nang’ deih bangbang,
Tuni in Topa, hong sit in Nang,
Vuk sang ngo zaw in tu’n hong sawp in,
Lungsim neem takin Nang' mai kong kun.
verse3:
Nang’ deih bang Topa, Nang’ deih bangbang,
Ka liam gimna, hong huh in, Nang,
Vang liatna khempeuh, Nang ma’n Na nei,
Hong damsak in, kei. Hong Honpa aw.
verse4:
Nang’ deih bang Topa, Nang’ deih bangbang,
Keimah nuntakna hong uk in, Nang,
Khazih keima sung, mi’n muh nading,
Hong guan'in kei sung, Na Kha Siangtho.

zoTitle: Zeisu Thu Hong Hilh Dih In
engTitle: Tell Me The Stories of Jesus
verse1:
Zeisu tangthu hong gen dih in, ke'n za nuam ing,
Hih lai-ah hong om hi leh, bang ka gen ding hiam,
Lam gei-a muh teng, tuipi' tangthu,
Zeisu’ tangthute, kei hong hilh in.
verse2:
A masa in naupangte tawh a ki-kholhna,
Tuaciang, Ama thupha piakte kei tung om hi,
Gitna kam bek dim, hehpihna dim,
Itna khuavak taang, Zeisu mai tang.
verse3:
Khuapi sungah ka zui ding hi, naupang hon tawh,
Dial lek in, nisuh hiang tawi in, khut tawh lam in,
Ci in, "Hosiana" Zeisu Kumpi!,
Amah phatna la nakpi takin.

verse1:
Van pan leiah kua hong kum?,
Zeisu Khazih i To!,
Hong suak naungek kiniam khiat,
Zeisu Khazih i To.
verse2:
Singkhuam tungah kua kikhai?,
Zeisu Khazih i To!,
Nang leh kei damna dingin,
Zeisu Khazih i To.
verse3:
Kua’n maisak ding ci, mawhna?,
Zeisu Khazih i To!,
Um in, hing un, kua’n hong ci?,
Zeisu Khazih i To.
verse4:
Tu’n van tokhom tung kua tu?,
Zeisu Khazih i To!,
Kua Thu zui-in, kua it ding?,
Zeisu Khazih i To.
verse5:
Van pan kua hong kum kik ding?,
Zeisu Khazih i To!,
A mite hong khawm dingin,
Zeisu Khazih i To.
chorus:
Sa un, A min phatna la,
Gupkhiatna hong tung zo hi,
Tua bang itna pha om kei,
Zeisu Khazih i To.

verse1:
Zeisu in eite khuai meivak bangin,
Zan khua mialna sungah taangin hong zaw hi,
Hih leitung khuamial sung, ei i taang ding,
Nang na omna kiim-ah, Kei, kei’ kiim-ah.
verse2:
Zeisu’n hong taang sak, Ama aading in,
I meivak a mial ciang Amah’n hong mu hi,
I meivak taang van pan, Amah’n en suk,
Nang na omna kiim-ah, Kei, kei’ kiim-ah.
verse3:
Zeisu’n hong taang sak, miteng aading in,
Khuamialna tampi tawh kidim hih leitung,
Mawhna, dahna, natna sung i taang ding,
Nang na omna kiim-ah, Kei, kei’ kiim-ah.

verse1:
Zeisu’n hong it ka thei hi,
Lai Siangtho in hong gen hi,
A neu a hat lo mite,
Amah hat hong huh na ve.
verse2:
Zeisu’n hong it man si a,
Vantung kong hong honsak ta,
Ka mawhna hong sawp sak ding,
Vantung ah hong lut sak ding.
verse3:
Zeisu’n ka zawngkhal hangin,
Hong it lailai veve in,
A taang vantung tokhom pan,
Ka lupna hong vil Amah’n.
chorus:
Zeisu’n hong it hi,
Zeisu’n hong it hi,
Zeisu’n hong it hi,
Lai Siangtho in gen hi.

verse1:
Hong pai ciangin, hong pai ciangin,
Suang manpha khawm dingin,
Ama it-te, Ama aa-te,
A suang manphate.
verse2:
Hong khawm ding hi, hong khawm ding hi,
A' gam sung om ding mi,
A siangthote, A taang phate,
A suang manphate.
verse3:
Naupang note, naupang note,
Hong Tanpa a it-te,
Ama aa hi, Ama it hi,
A suang manpha hi.
chorus:
Zingsang aksi sol bangin,
A taang ciat ding uh hi,
A Kumpi lukhu tungah,
Te diamdiam ding hi.

verse1:
Vantung a i Pa in A hong itna,
Hong piak Lai Siangtho sungah hong gen ta,
Lai Siangtho sungah thu a ngaih pha pen,
Zeisu in kei hong itna mah hi pen.
verse2:
Amah mangngilh in ka taisan hangin,
Hong it lailai hi, ka mangthang hangin,
Zeisu in hong it ke’n ka phawk kik a,
Ama ang sung ka delh kik vingveng ta.
verse3:
A phatna teng tawh A' mai ka muh teh,
La khat bek sa thei ding hong kici leh,
Bang la ka sa zaw diam hih lo a dang,
"Zeisu in kei hong it piandang lua sa’ng."
verse4:
Zeisu’n hong it a, kei zong ka it hi,
Ka kha hehpih in tan ding hong kum hi,
Hong it manin singlamteh tung si a,
Tua ahih ciang hong it takpi hi ta.
chorus:
Zeisu’n hong it man ka nuam pha hi,
Kei hong it hi, kei hong it hi,
Zeisu hong it man ka nuam pha hi,
Kei nangawn hong it hi.

zoTitle: Tua A Zaknop Tangthu Ka Ngaihsut Ciang
engTitle: I Think When I Read That Sweet Story (Tune: Sweet Story)
verse1:
Tua a zaknop tangthu ka sim ciang kaphawk,
Mite lak-ah Zeisu om lai,
Naupang note, tuuno hon tawh a genteh lai,
Amah tawh tua bang om nuam mah sing.
verse2:
Ka lu tung A khut hong nga leh ut mah sing,
A baan tawh hong angpom hen la,
Tua ciang Ama hong itna maitang en to in,
"Hong pai un," a cih kam za nuam ing.
verse3:
A hi zong Ama khekhaap zui in pai ning,
Ama itna ka ngah zawh na’ng,
Lungsim takpi tawh Ama nuaiah ngento leng,
Amah mu in, tung pan hong dawng ding.

engTitle: Rejoice, Ye Pure in Heart (Tune: Marion)
verse1:
Nuam un, lung siangthote,
La sa’n lung damna pia’n,
Na galkap te'n dial pei sang kha’n,
Na Kumpipa Khazih.
verse2:
Vantung mite’n la sa,
Leitung mi siang teng tawh,
Lung damna thu zeel sak un la,
Lung kimna manpha zaw.
verse3:
Na sianna sang sak in,
Khauh takin mai nawt in,
Khuamial sungah galte’n na seem,
Kham khua hong vak mateng.
chorus:
Nuam un, nuam un,
La sa'n lung damna pia'n.

verse1:
Hahkat pawlpi gamla nai a,
Kikhawm dingin a hong pai un,
Tawpna a nuam a om nate,
I gen ding hi, Pasian thupha.
verse2:
Khazih Topa phat dingin ah,
La sa dingin hong kikhawm un,
Mi neute in hih mun panah,
Hing tawntung muh nading in-ah.
verse3:
Topa Pasian' na seem dingin,
Kiciamna pha a thak koih ni,
Vantung inn nuam tun' mateng in,
Upna behlap in na seem ni.
chorus:
Hahkat pawlpite aw,
Topa kiang kikhawm un,
Lungsim kituak pha tawh,
A min phatna gen un,
Topa leh a gampi,
Aa dingin hahkat in,
Pawlpi a hahkatte,
Huh nading thu ngen ni.

verse1:
Tapidaw ihmu nawn ke'n,
Mi ngah nang sep theih lai seem,
Khut zepin ding mawk ding mawk?,
Topa in thu hong pia leh.
verse2:
Topa min na it ding hiam?,
Hong ciamna na um zo diam?,
Sapna teng a kiang ngen in,
Hong sapna na nial ding maw?
verse3:
Na san’sa bangin um in,
Hong hilh bangin nungta in,
Ama aa bek hi den in,
Sepna tawh upna lak in.
verse4:
Singlamteh i puak ding om,
Kham Lukhu na khuk nop leh,
Thathak tawh ma i sawt ding,
A hun tom, a nite tawm.
chorus:
Pai in seem! ding kipan in,
Pai in, zong a mangte gum,
Khuamialna sung mawhnei mi,
Tua pawi-ah, hong paipih in!

verse1:
Topa tawh ton khawm in, bangbang piang ta leh,
Na lampi khua mial hang, Ama nung zui in,
Na galte’n hong neh in a lauhuai hangin,
Zeisu tawh ton leteh kihtak ding om kei.
verse2:
Topa tawh ton khawm in, na paina peuh-ah,
Khua mialna liim sungah lam hong hilh ding di,
Ama vaang in na lampi hong taang sak ding,
Keugaw gam zong lo nona hong piang sak ding.
verse3:
Topa tawh ton khawm in, nang thu’n tawlnga ke'n,
Hong thu piakna bangin na gamta ding hi,
Hong sawlna bang mang in, Ama tha muang in,
Zeisu nung na zuih leh na khial ngei kei ding.
chorus:
Ton khawm in, hang tak mai nawt in,
Na tha hong khauh sak ding hi,
Nisim in Amah tawh pai in,
Na khual zinna lam hong pi ding hi.

engTitle: Now In the Days of Youth (Diademata)
verse1:
Tuna khangno lai in, Hun hoih zat theih lai in,
Topa ko lung sung hong om in, vekpi’n hong kipia ung,
Kong kipiakna bangun, kilawm bang hong saang in,
Nuntak sung teng sepna peuhah, Pa deihna bang hi hen.
verse2:
Hong hilh in Na deih bang, Ka gamtat theih na’ng uh,
Nang deih bangbang gamtat theih nang, Ka lungdam ding uh hi,
A lian pen teel tuan lo, A neu pen paai tuan lo,
Ko sepnate Nang sep bangin, Hong thupi khin sak in.
verse3:
Thu hoih thupha deihna, Kote hong hilhhilh in,
Hun tomcik no khat sung bek zong, ka siat khak loh na’ng uh,
Ka tha uh tawh din zawh na’ng hong panpih ta in,
A siangtho nate bek deih ung, a siate deih kei ung.
verse4:
Ka suah tung bang mah un, Kha Siangtho hong pi in,
Itna gamtat hoih neih theih na’ng, lungnop hithiatna tawh,
Kum tampi sung man’ ding, ka kigin’ kholh na’ng uh,
Tawntung nuntakna hun nuampi, Pa innah ka zong ding.

engTitle: Tell Me the Old, Old Story
verse1:
Tanglai thu hong genta in, A kimu ngeilo na,
Zeisu leh a vang lian ci’n  Amah in hong itna,
Tangthu teltak hong gen in, naupangte hilh bangin,
Hong hilh in ka gim zo hi,
Ka khial gawp khin ta hi.
verse2:
Tua tangthu damtak gen in, ka theih baih nading in,
Amah in hong tat khiatna, mawh kiphel nading in,
Thu tangthu hong gen kik in ka mangngilh theih loh na’ng,
Daitui bang zingsang om hang, sun ciangin mang thei hi.
verse3:
Tua tangthu damdam gen in, nuamna aw tawh gen in,
Mawhna pan hong phel nading Zeisu honggum phawk ning,
Tua tangthu gen laitakin gimna khat hong tun' leh
Hehnepna hong pia ding ci’n tu’n tangthu gen ta in.
verse4:
Lawkite nopsakna in vantung gimna om hi,
Kei tang ding lung hihmawh leh tua tangthu hong gen in,
Hong zolna zui dek ciangin, hih leitung nopsakna,
Zeisu’n hong len kip ding hi, tangthu om bang gen in.
chorus:
Tua tangthu hong gen ta in,
Tua tangthu hong gen ta in,
Tua tangthu hong gen ta in,
Zeisu leh hong itna.

zoTitle: Na Omna Mun-Ah Taang Sak In
engTitle: Brighten the Corner Where You Are
verse1:
Na sepna lian bel seem dingin, lawm aw zekai ke’n,
Khuavaak na taang sak dingin khawl ke’n,
Na hih ding ngeina om bangin thupha om sak in,
Na omna mun-ah taang sak in.
verse2:
Lungkia a, dahna thuakna a kipsak kik theih leh,
Nang aading a pha bek ngaihsun ke’n,
Khat bek hang a na lungsim om noptuam nasak leh,
Na omna mun-ah taang sak in.
verse3:
Na omna mun-ah na khuavaak na taang sak theih leh,
Omna mun a ding zong taang sak in,
Na khutah a lim khomun hawm-a na vak theih leh,
Na omna mun-ah taang sak in.
chorus:
Na omna mun-ah taang sak in,
Na omna mun-ah taang sak in,
A kisia dinga om mi khat peuhmah gup nading,
Na omna mun-ah taang sak in.

zoTitle: Na Hi Zo Diam, Topa'n Hong Ci
engTitle: Are Ye Able? Said the Master
verse1:
"Na hi zo diam," Topa’n hong ci,
Amah tawh kikhai khawm ding,
Sih dong Na deih bang gamta ding,
Lungsim ah khentat zo ung.
verse2:
"Na hi zo diam," tua thu phawk ding,
Gutapa khuadakna mun,
Mawhna khempeuh kimai sak zo,
Pazadih mun nuam tung zo.
verse3:
"Na hi zo diam," haksat hun ciang,
Na kiimkot khua a mial ciang,
Amah na kipiak theih nading,
Na lungsim zo masa in.
verse4:
"Na hi zo diam," Topa’n hong sam,
Nangmah hong sam lailai hi,
Galile gam aa sap bangin,
Lungsim hang takin dawng in.
chorus:
"Hi zo mah nung," Topa Nang aa hi ung,
Hong bawl pha in, Nang tawh kibang in,
Lam Nong hilhna vaang taang ka muh uh ciang,
Na meel bangin, hong it in, na thumaan nung.

zoTitle: Ka Lung Sungah La Ngaih Ka Za
engTitle: In My Heart There Rings a Melody
verse1:
Zeisu hong puak la khat ka ngah hi,
Tua la van pan hong puak hi,
Tua sang a ngaih zaw la om ngeilo hi,
Tua in ki-itna la hi.
verse2:
Kalani aa si Khazih it ing,
Ka mawhna hong sawp sak hi,
Ka lung sungah la ngaih khat hong koih hi,
Ka thei, tua la teeng den ding.
verse3:
A tul ngeilo min than’na la hi,
Vantung mite tawh sa ding,
Tua la in a kilem mahmah la hi,
Vantung zum panin hong ging.
chorus:
Ka lung sung la ngaih khat ka za hi,
A kilem mahmah vantung pan hong kisa hi,
Ka lung sung la ngaih khat ka za hi,
Tua la in ki-itna la hi.

verse1:
Khazih leh pawlpi aading la sa ni,
Thupha eite Kumpipa Amin pahtawi ni,
Khangno tha hat lai utna tawh na sem ni,
Vantung gam thumaan aading teci pang ni.
verse2:
Khazih le pawlpi aading thungen ni,
Nisim singlamteh puain a dial khai zui ni,
Kha Siangtho vaang liatna, hong sawlna zui in,
Nuntak sung hun hoih laitakin na sem ni.
verse3:
Khazih le pawlpi a ding utna tawh,
Neihsa, siamna keh hun, Topa min tawh ap ni,
Cikmah hun bei ngeilo, lungsim thuk itna,
I neihsa pha bel Topa kiangah pia ni.
chorus:
Khazih it huai hong Gumpa,
Ei hong tan dinga si,
Si tawh lei sa Pawlpi aading,
Topa hong hang sak in.

zoTitle: Honpa, Tuu Cing Bang Hong Pi In
engTitle: Saviour, Like a Shepherd Lead Us
verse1:
Honpa, tuu cing bang hong pi in,
Nong huaina ko kisam pha,
An tam gam nuamah hong vak in,
Hong bawl kholh sakin omna,
Thupha Zeisu, thupha Zeisu
Nong lei zo, kote nang aa,
Thupha Zeisu, thupha Zeisu,
Nong lei zo, kote nang aa.
verse2:
Hong pawl in, Nang’ neihsa kote,
Ko paina lampi cing in,
Hong kem, hong hu in, Na tuute,
Lam khialh ciang hong zong kik in,
Thupha Zeisu, thupha Zeisu
Ko thu ngetna hong za in,
Thupha Zeisu, thupha Zeisu
Ko thu ngetna hong za in.
verse3:
Mi zawng, mimawh ka hih uh hang,
Nong ciam zo hong saang dingin,
Mawhna phel na’ng, sia’n na'ng, dal na’ng,
Hehpihna Na nei cing in,
Thupha Zeisu, thupha Zeisu
Nang lam hong kihei sak in,
Thupha Zeisu, thupha Zeisu
Nang lam hong kihei sak in.
verse4:
Ka neulai un Nangma pahtak,
Na awi bang hong ta sak in,
Hong hon Topa pha aw, dim tak
Nangma itna hong guan’ in,
Thupha Zeisu, thupha Zeisu
Nong it zo, hong it lai in,
Thupha Zeisu, thupha Zeisu
Nong it zo, hong it lai in.

engTitle: Where Cross the Croowed Ways of Life (Tune: Geremany)
verse1:
Nun tak lam tam kituahna ah,
Nam khat beh khat kielna ah,
Huaiham kitotna aw tungah,
Mihing Tapa, kong za uh hi.
verse2:
Gentheihna, sapna, tamna ah,
Launa khuamial dimna inn ah,
Huaiham duhgawh bukna lam ah,
Nangma khitui luang ko mu thei.
verse3:
Nangma aading tui suahna hai,
Nangma hehpihna gim nam lai,
Ahih hang Nangma migit mai,
Mi honpite’n mu nuam lai keei.
verse4:
Mual tung pan hong kum in, Topa,
Damsak pak ven mi lung gimna,
Lungsim tawldamna om lohna,
Khua sung kongzing hong siik kik aw.

engTitle: For the Beauty of the Earth (Tune: Dix)
verse1:
Lungdam huai leitung meel pha,
Lungdam huai vantung et lawm,
Suah tunga kipan itna,
Kote kiim-ah hong om khawm.
verse2:
Sun le zan, a nai sim a,
Ka muh uh lamdang nate,
Mual le kuam, singkung, paak pha,
Ni, kha, a taang aksite.
verse3:
Sanggam, suangpih, nu le pa,
Ki-it diamdiam a nuamna,
Lei le van-a lawm a pha,
Migitna, ngaihsutna pha.
verse4:
Nangma pawlpi a tawntung.
Mun kheempeuh, gam kheempeuh, pan,
Siangtho biakna itna lung,
Khut siangtho tawh hong puak man,
Hih teng hang, khazih Topa,
Kong sak uh lungdamna la.
chorus:
Hih teng hang, Khazih Topa,
Kong sak uh lungdamna la.

verse1:
A nuam Khamtung gam,
Tuisiangtho tam, paak zong a tam,
Mual leh guam tengah,
Vasate’n nuam sa’n la a sa.
verse2:
Khamtung mi’n ka suak,
Khamtung mi bang ka nuanta ding,
Gam leh mi aading,
Pilna, siamna, hatna pia ning.
chorus:
Ih vekpi in kipaak in la sa ni,
Khua kheempeuh ah nuamna la sa un,
Khamtung eimaute Khamtung,
Khamtung ginalo gam hi kei.

zoTitle: Ei Inn Bek Mah Nuam I Sa
engTitle: Mid Pleasures and Palaces (Tune: Home Sweet Home)
verse1:
Bangzah a nuam Kumpi inn sung i om zong,
Bangzah’n nop tuak ta leh ei inn mah nuam i sa,
Van gam leimong khatah a nopna om hi,
Ci in leitung min’a zon’ hang mu zo tuan kei.
verse2:
Gam lak, tu lakah pai in, khuapi en in,
Ka nu in zong a tapa tu’n ngaihsun kawm in,
Ka bukno khat uh sung pan, khapi en in,
Hih hang gam lak sing leh nate’n hong don tuan lo.
verse3:
Inn pan taikhia in mun dang nopna zon’ hang,
A nuam zaw mun om lo, ka bukno bekmah nuam,
Nuamtak vasa’n lasa ka sap hong dawng hang,
Lung nepna hong pia in, tua sang nuam zaw om kei.
chorus:
Inn, inn, a nuam inn,
Inn dang nuam om kei,
Aw! Ei inn bekmah nuam.

verse1:
I kiimkot teng ki lawmna, innkuan ki it leng,
Aw ging kheempeuh lung damna, innkuan ki it leng,
Lung nopna le kicin'na, kiheina teng maitaina,
Hun kheempeuh nuam mahmah a, innkuan ki it leng.
verse2:
Bukno khat sung zong nuamna, innkuan ki it leng,
Huatna, en’na om lohna, innkuan ki it leeng,
I paina tengah nuamna, leitung kheempeuh lung damna,
Lung damna dim nuntakna, innkuan ki it leeng.
verse3:
Pasian zong hong lungdam pih, innkuan ki it leeng,
Leitung teng ki-itna dim, innkuan ki it leeng,
Lui ging bek zong la ngaihpi, vandum bek zong maitaina,
Pasian van pan hong nuih pih, innkuan ki it leeng.
chorus:
Innkuan sung ki it leng,
Hun kheempeuh nuam mahmah a,
Innkuan ki it leeng.

verse1:
Vuk a paak mual dawn pan in, khang lam lei mong dong in,
A mual a guam a zang-ah,Tui tung leitung tengah,
Teeng-a a om mite in, Pasian lam khial khin a,
Tua khialhna kol sut dingin, hong sam in om uh hi.
verse2:
Khua lumna gamah huih in, pha takpi in a nung hi,
Et ding hoih a tam hangin, Mihingte’n kihuai hi,
Pasian in hehpihna tawh , na tampi hong pia hi,
Lawkite’n mittaw bangin, suang le sing bia uh hi.
verse3:
Vantung pan in khua vakna, i lung sungah taang hi,
Khua mialna sunga omte, Pasian meivak pia ni,
Gamlapi mite in-ah, Zeisu min thei mateng,
"Hong gum hi, hong gum hi," ci’n lung damna kiko in.
verse4:
Ama lungdamna thu in, huih aw na paipih in,
Mi vekpi’n theih mateng in, tapidaw paipih in,
Khial neite tang ding sih thuak, Tuuno in hong pai ding,
Leitung kumpipa bangin, lungdamna tawh mang ding.

engTitle: The Morning Light is Breaking (Tune: Webb)
verse1:
Zingsang khua hong vaakta hi, Khua mialna beita hi.
Leitung mite tho khin hi, dah in khitui luang hi.
Gam lapi pan huih hual in, lung damna thu hong puak,
Leitung minam khempeuh tung, Zion gal a do ding.
verse2:
En un lawkite zong kuan, i it Pasian mai-ah,
Van pan lung damna thu hang, Tul tampi lungdam hi.
Mawh neite mawhna kisik, lung damna thu zui uh,
Gumpa thupha piak zongin, leitung tha khat in zui.
verse3:
Gup khiatna gun tui luang hi, na mai uh nawt tek un,
Gam khempeuh ah luang un la, hauhna tawh khawl kei un.
A zawngkhal pente dongin, zawhna tawh inn tun’ dong
Amah phatna la sa in, "Topa hong pai," ci un.

zoTitle: Topa In A Maang Ding Hi
verse1:
Ni in a taang thei gampi ah,
Topa Zeisu a maang ding ta,
Tuipi khat pan tuipi dongin,
Ama gamin a zai ding hi.
verse2:
Nisim tawntung Ama kiangah,
Mihingte’n thu a ngen dinga,
Lukhu bangin minphat napi,
Ama lu tungah om ding hi.
verse3:
Kam tuam a gen pawlte in-ah,
Min phatna la sa ding uh a,
Naupangte in a neu laitak,
Ama min a thang sak ding hi.
verse4:
Ama ukna sung lungdam ta,
Thong sung aa omte suahtakna,
A ngah, gimna a thuak mite,
Tawlngak nading uk ahi hi.
verse5:
Leitung mihing kheempeuhte in,
Ei Kumpipa' min thang sak un,
Vantung mite’n la sa dingin,
Leitung ah hong kum suk kik un.

verse1:
Zion lungdam ni zingsang dawn tek ta un!
Khuamial zawh loh gam hangin lungdam hang!
Dahna kahna awte haihkhia khin ta un,
Zion in zawhna tawh hong uk ding hi.
verse2:
Zion lungdam ni zingsang dawn tek ta un!
Itazila kamsangte’n gen zo hi!
Tul, then, tampi kol bulhsa tu’n suakta ciah,
Zudah, Zentail, a kibang khuavaak ngah.
verse3:
En un sehnel gam zong paak na gam po tah!
Lui hawmte zong, tui a dim in luang hi,
Mual sangte dawn pan, lungdam aw thawn kiza,
Lungsim kituak kigawmna la sa khawm.
verse4:
En un gam khempeuh pan, tui, tuikulh dongin,
A kahto Zahova Topa phat un,
Gal vanteng puk khin in gamlumna bei hi,
Gup khiatna aw vantung thawnin ging hi.

zoTitle: Leitung Aading Khazih! La I Sa
engTitle: Christ for the World! We Sing (Tune: Italian Hymn)
verse1:
Leitung aading Khazih, Khazih aading i sa,
Late lawp tak’n, a zawng, dah-a kapte cih nang thei lo lung mang,
Mawhna hang lung khamte, khazih’n damsak.
verse2:
Leitung aading Khazih, Khazih aading i sa,
Late ngen kawm, lam zui leh lam pialte, itna in domto in,
Loh zawh loh tawh hong tan, khuamial sung pan.
verse3:
Leitung aading Khazih, Khazih aading i sa,
Nate kituak’n, a kibang seem khawm in, neh in i ngenngam a,
Singlamteh i pua tek, Khazih min ding.
verse4:
Leitung aading Khazih, Khazih aading i sa,
Lungdam takin, A suak thak i khate, Mawhnate nusia in,
Lam en i lungsim bun, Khazih ei aa.

verse1:
Lungdamna thupha ka za, "Zeisu in hong gum hi.",
Tua thupha na gen in la, "Zeisu in hong gum hi.",
Gam khempeuh ah pai in la, mual kal, gun kal kan dinga,
Na gen in Topa thupha "Zeisu in hong gum hi."
verse2:
Gunpi kan in kiko in, "Zeisu in hong gum hi.",
Gamla, nai mi kiang gen in, "Zeisu in hong gum hi.",
Tui lai lei-ah kiko in, a gal khat na tawn sak in,
Leitung ah lungdamna in, "Zeisu in hong gum hi."
verse3:
Gal kapna sung kiko in, "Zeisu in hong gum hi.",
Singlamteh tung sihna in, "Zeisu in hong gum hi.",
Hehpihna i deih ciangin, tua thute na ngaihsun in,
Sihna zo man la sa in, "Zeisu in hong gum hi."
verse4:
Leitung ah na kiko in, "Zeisu in hong gum hi.",
Mi khempeuh lungdam sak in, "Zeisu in hong gum hi.",
Mual tung leh kuam thuk sungah, hong phelna thu gen in la,
Hih zawhna thu la sakna, "Zeisu in hong gum hi."

verse1:
I Topa hong hehpihna in,
Suum pempam in hong taang hi,
Tua khuavaak eite hong pia hi,
Tui tung tengah taang sak in.
verse2:
Mawhna in khua hong mial sak hi,
Tuihualpi hong kilok hi,
Hoih takin khuadak pha in la,
Tui dung teng phatak en in.
verse3:
Na meivak phatak vaak in la,
Tuihual in mi taai kha ding,
Noptakin suahtak theih nangun,
Tawl ngakna mun tun' theih nang.
chorus:
Meivak teng a vekpi’n vaak in,
Tuihual teng kimuh nading,
A cimawh tuikia om kha ding,
Gum khia in la kai khia in.

verse1:
Taang sak in, taang sak mengmeng in,
Tuipi kilok kantan in,
Hot khiatna thu zeel sak meng in,
Migi gum khia Pa' min in.
verse2:
Taang sak in, khate’ sihna ah,
Tuazan khuamialna mun ah,
Hat meng in, hunte beibei veh!
A nai, a nai in bei ta.
verse3:
Taang sak in, Topa’ hong sawl hi,
A thu siangtho lim ngaih dih!
"Pai khia in, ka thu va gen in,
Hong ompih den ning," a cih.
chorus:
Taang sak in, taang sak mengmeng in,
Tuipi gal, tuikulhte dong,
Taangthu lamdang va za sak in,
Itna, hehpihna khawnkhong.

verse1:
Leitung teng Zeisu thu gen un,
Gun gal khat pan gal khat ah,
Mawh neite, Zeisu thu gen un,
A khuavaak pha taang sak un.
verse2:
Lungdam thun’n gamlapi zeel hen,
Khua mialna mun gam khempeuh,
Lung damna khuavaak thei sak un,
Thang sak un khuamial gam ah.
verse3:
Tuipi tung leh mual tung tengah,
Lungdamna Thu thang sak un,
Mun khempeuh Zeisu Thu gen un,
Hong sapna thu thang sak un.
verse4:
Mi khempeuh aading thu ngen in,
Lung damna tawh huh ciat un,
I gam aading zong thu ngen in,
Zeisu ei gam aading in.
chorus:
Thang sak un, leitung tengah,
Lungdam Thu gun gal khat ah,
Leitung teng Zeisu thu gen un,
A tawntung A min phat un.

verse1:
Lung damna thupha ngai in, gamla a nai gen in,
Sihna thuak Topa Zeisu, hong gupna thu gen in,
Om tawntung hi Ama thu, A thuciam kip ding hi,
Topa Zeisu a umte, A min thang sak ding hi.
verse2:
Sawt vei khuamial-a omte, mawhna lam a zuite,
Topa Zeisu’n tan napi, en in thupha bel hi,
Lungsim na neih zahin ah, A thu ciamna um in,
Topa kiangah thu ngente, kisia ngeilo ding hi.
verse3:
Leitung ah vangik puate gimna tawlna thuak mi,
Na vangik a pua dingin Topa in hong ngak hi,
Thupha lamdang hong pia A mi khempeuh hawm sak hi,
Topa Zeisu thu umte a min thang sak ding hi.
chorus:
Topa Pasian kiangah, hehpihna ngente in,
Gupna thupha maantak a ngah thei ding uh hi,
Topa Pasian kiangah hehpihna ngente in,
Gupna thupha maan tak a ngah thei ding uh hi.

zoTitle: Mial Lak Tuipi Hual Tung Pan Kiko
verse1:
Mial lak tuipi hual tung pan kiko aw in,
Khuavaak hong puak un ci,
Khuamial sungah a cimawh mi tampi in,
Khuavaak hong puak un ci.
verse2:
Makedawni gam pan a sapna aw in,
Khuavaak hong puak un ci,
Singlamteh mai ah, i biakna koih suk in,
I khuavak va puak ni.
verse3:
Zeisu hong hehpihna mi’n ngah kim nading,
Khuavak hong puak un ci,
Khazih lungsim bang kimuh kawikawi nading,
Tang sak ni, tang sak ni.
chorus:
Taang sak ni! Nuamna thupha khuavak,
Taang sak ni, mun khempeuh ah,
Taang sak ni! Nuamna thupha khuavak,
Taang sak ni, tawl ngalo in.

zoTitle: Mite Tung Gen Ding Thu Khat I Nei Hi
engTitle: We've Story to Tell the Nations
verse1:
Mite tung gen ding thu khat i nei hi,
Aman lungsim Aman hei ding,
Thumaan leh hehpihna tangthu,
Kilemna, khuavaakna thu, kilemna, khuavaakna thu.
verse2:
Mite tung sak ding la khat i nei hi,
Topa lam lungsim nga sak ding,
Siatna a zo ding la khat hi,
Tei le namsau susia ding, tei le namsau susia ding.
verse3:
Mite tung thu puak ding khat i nei hi,
Vantung ah a maang Topa in,
Eite gum dinga A Ta hong sawl,
Pasian’ itna ei hong lak, Pasian' itna ei hong lak.
verse4:
Mite lah ding Honpa khat i nei hi,
Dahna lampi a tawn khin Pa,
Leitung mihing lian khempeuhte,
Pasian’ thumaan-ah pai na’ng, Pasian' thumaan-ah pai na’ng.
chorus:
Zan khuamial, zing khuavaak suak ding a,
Zing khuavaak, sun nitaang suak ding,
Khazih gam leitung’h hong pai ding hi,
Itna leh khua vaakna gam.

zoTitle: Hat In, Zion Seem Meng In Na Nasep Ding
verse1:
Hat in, Zion, seem meng in na nasep ding,
Mi' teng tungah, khuavaak Pasian hilh in,
Mihing khat zong khuamial sunga mangthang ding,
Phal het lo hi mihing piang sak Pa in.
verse2:
En ven, mawhna khuamial thong inn mial sungah,
Mi tul tampi, kihen in om uh hi,
Khat beek va pai lo a mau ko dingin ah,
A suah tak na’ng uh Topa’ si napi.
verse3:
Mi nam kim, pau nam kimte kiang va gen in,
Amau’ hin’na in itna Pasian hi,
Kiniam sakin a bawlsate hon dingin,
Van nun’ nuam piakna ding hong si suk hi.
verse4:
Na tate sawl in tua thupha gen dingin,
Na sum tawh huh in manlang theih nading,
Na lungsim teng tawh nakpi’n thu ngetsak in,
Na zat kheempeuh Zeisu’n hong dim kik ding.
chorus:
Lung damna thupha, nopna thupha,
Zeisu, hong tatna Thupha, va gen meng in.

verse1:
Lung damna thu ging sak in,
Gam khat pan gam khat dongah,
Suahtakna thu zel khin sak in,
Kei leh nang aading bawl ta,
Leitung hong it manin, A Tapa a hong pia hi,
A thu-um mite kheempeuh in, nuntak tawntung ngah ding hi.
verse2:
Lungdam thu’n hong sam hi,
"Mi kheempeuh hong paita hen.",
A hong sapna na nial kei in,
Pasian hehpihna lian hi,
"Ke’n hin'na ka hi hi, lungsim khial a nei mi in,
A mawhnate a san hangin, tuu mul bangin a ngo ding."
verse3:
Lung damna thu ngai lo mi,
Bang gimna a thuak ding hiam,
Tua lung damna thu a khum in,
Kikepna hong hilh lai a,
Hi’n na gup khiat na’ng in, khawl loin ah tai in la,
Na nung lam kihei kik kei in, hi kei leh na si ding ta.
chorus:
Lungdam thu ging sak in,
Gam khat pan gam khat dongah,
Lungdam thu, man neilo.,
Nangmah leh kei aading hi.

zoTitle: A Thu Ka Gengen Nuam Hi
engTitle: I Love to Tell the Story (Tune: Tidings)
verse1:
Athu ka gengen nuam hi, muh nai loh vantung na,
Zeisu le Ama vaangpi, Zeisu le hong itna!
Tua thu ka gengen nuam hi, thumaan ahih manin,
Ka lungsim hong kim sak in, thu dangte bang lo in.
verse2:
Athu ka gengen nuam hi, lamdang semsem ka sa,
Ki ngaihsun thei nawn lopi, tua sang lam dang zaw na,
Tua thu ka gengen nuam hi, hong noptuam sakna lian,
Tua hang mah’n kong gen sawn hi, Tu in lawm aw, nang kiang.
verse3:
Athu ka gengen nuam hi, gengen leng nuam semsem,
Ka gengen sa hi napi, gengen leng ngaih semsem,
Tua thu ka gengen nuam hi, hot khiatna thu a pha,
A za nai lo mi om hi, Pasian’ hong gen thupha.
verse4:
Athu ka gengen nuam hi, a thei pente in zong,
An duh tui duh bang duh hi, mi dangte sangin zong,
Vantung vaang liatna sungah, la thak ka sa ding hi,
Tua ciangin hih thu lui mah, kei in ka sa ding hi.
chorus:
Tua thu ka gengen nuam hi,
Gengen lai ning vantung ah,
Hih thu tul thei ngeilo pi,
Zeisu le hong itna.

verse1:
Khaici manpha vawhun, zingsang phalvak kipat tungin,
Khaici manpha vawh un, sun khuaphat laitak,
Khaici manpha vawhun, khangno lungsim zep nading in,
Khaici manpha vawh un, dawmin lungduai tak.
verse2:
Khaici manpha vawh un, ni a kai laitak in-ah zong,
Khaici manpha vawh un, khua muina sungah,
Khaici manpha vawh un, phunlo, um lah loin om un,
A vekpi’n Pasian ap in Amah muang un.
verse3:
Khaici manpha vawh un, lawpna leh hanciamna tak tawh,
Khaici manpha vawh un, kham khaici manpha,
Khaici manpha vawh un, khut te thazaw sak ngeilo in,
Pasian in ni le guah puak ding thu ngen un.
chorus:
Khaici manpha vawh un,
Khaici manpha vawh un,
Gamla naiah vawh un,
Lungduai itna khut tawh,
Nuntak khomun balnen,
Lung damna tangthu genta un,
Khaici manpha vawh un, i it gam sungah.

engTitle: Go Ye Into All the World
verse1:
Gamlapi a mawhna khuamial gam sungah,
Mi tul le then gam mangin om uh hi,
Kua pai dinga gup khiatna thu va gen ding,
Khazih en in, gimna ding ngaihsun ke’n.
verse2:
Khuadak le ci’n kong honsa in hong ngak hi,
Khazih galkapte aw pai in lut un,
Tha neihzah teng gawmin kikhen thang loin,
Thupha hilh in mawhna kol va sut un.
verse3:
Bang hang note si zenzen sing hong ci in,
Pasian hong sapna thu va ko sawn un,
Hot khiatna leh hin'na na ngah nading in,
Zeisu si in hong tan zo va ci un.
verse4:
Pa Pasian aw, hong tung sak mengmeng ta in,
Mi namcin in Na min phat nading hun,
Hot khiatna la lung damna tawh kiko in,
Halleluiah, Topa Kumpi phat un.
chorus:
“Vaang liatna kei tung hong pia zo!
Vaang liatna kei tung hong pia zo!
Vak kawikawi un la, lungdam Thu va gen un,
Note tawh ka om khawm tawntung ding.

engTitle: When the Mists Have Rolled Away
verse1:
A siangtho mahmah mual tungah, meiilum a then’ ciangin ah,
Nisa a vaang taan’na vak pha, cik leh lui neute tung tu’n,
Sakhi tuihup a vaang in ah, itna pha lai kisim ta,
Eite kimu dingin a hun meiilum a then’ ciangin ah.
verse2:
Mihingte khuamial sungah khial, leitung mi ahih mangngilh,
Phatna dinga hah katna a, ki-itna thupha pai khia,
Nopsak na'ng Topa'n hong phel ding, eite khempeuh hong liah ding,
I ngak dingin zingsang hun hi, meiilumte a theng ding hi.
verse3:
Meiilumte ei khempeuh tungah, a leen’ toh laitakin ah,
I it khempeuh lawmte tawh, eite i kimu ding maw,
Khuamial cipna gun gal khatah khuavak nitang hong tungta,
A lamdang khuavak i muhna, meiilum a then’ ciangin ah.
chorus:
Eite i kimu ding hi, leitung ah kimuh bangin,
Tua thupha leh lung damna ni,
Zingsang-a phalvak ciangah,
Eite kimu dingin a hun meiilum a then’ ciangin ah.

engTitle: Beyound the Smiling and the Weeping
verse1:
Nuihna leh kahna kheng gal khatah,
Man langin ah ka tung ding hi,
Ihmutna leh thawhna kheng gal ah,
Tuhna leh atna kheng gal khatah,
Man langin ah, ka tung ding hi.
verse2:
Palhna leh vulna kheng gal khatah,
Man langin ah ka tung ding hi,
Khuaval leh khuamial kheng gal khatah,
Lawpna leh launa kheng gal khatah,
Man langin ah ka tung ding hi.
verse3:
Khuadam leh khualum kheng gal khatah,
Man langin ah ka tung ding hi,
Suang mualte leh gunte gal khatah,
Tawntung leh tawntung lo gal khatah,
Man langin ah ka tung ding hi.
chorus:
Nong itna pha innpi pha ah,
Om dingin hong kha in Topa aw.

zoTitle: Thu Tuikhuk Ah Kei Nong Mu Diam?
engTitle: Will You Meet at the Fountain
verse1:
Tua tuikhuk ah kei nong mu diam?
Min than’na gam ka tun ciang,
Tua tuikhuk ah kei nong mu diam?
Lungdam in khut i beeng diam?,
I lawmte’n tua lai hong dawn in,
Lawm it dangte aw za ding,
Tua tuikhuk ah la i sa ding,
Nang zong tua lai nong mu diam?
verse2:
Tua tuikhuk ah kei nong mu diam?
Tua lai kong thei takpi ding,
Migi i kha kikhawl khawm in,
Ka thiehna sate sangin,
A ngaih zaw la ka za ding hi,
Ka bil sung hong gin' ciangin,
Vavtung gam bang nopna kicing,
Na kam khum aw ka thei ding.
verse3:
Tua tuikhuk ah kei nong mu diam?
Nang tawh kinai zaw sem ding,
Ka it Topa ka muh ciangin,
Hong dawnna kam ka zak ciang,
Amah’n tuikhuk hong mu ding hi,
Amah’n kei hong angpom in,
Tua tuikhuk min than’na om ding,
Nang zong tua lai nong mu diam?
chorus:
Hi hi, tua tuikhuk kong mu ding,
A hoih a taang tuikhuk ah,
Aw tua tuikhuk ah kong mu ding,
Hi hi, kong mu ding, mu ding.

zoTitle: Amaute In La Thak A Sa Uh Hi
verse1:
Vantung inn sungah i lawmte’n la sa hi,
Hong gum Topa Amin a phatna uh hi,
Leitung ah lung khamna teng mangngilh khin a,
Mi siangtho te'n lung damna la thak a sa.
verse2:
Hong hehpihna phat na’ng la thak om kim hi,
A um ta ding thupha bel ahi ding hi,
Topa si-a a piang kik Amin than'na,
Ka gen masa nuam bel hi Pasian kiangah.
verse3:
Tuni sipha awh a kisil lote in,
Tua la thak kuamah in sa thei lo ding hi,
Mawh neite mawhna phel-a hong hehpihna,
Phatna lung damin lim takin la sa ni.
chorus:
Zeisu min phat ni, Kalani mual tungah si zo hi,
Zeisu min phat hi, sihna zo a hing kik ta hi.

engTitle: We Shall Stand Before the King
verse1:
Kumpipa’ mai i ding ding,
Vantung mi tawh la sa ding,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin,
A taang gun gei lam zui ding,
Topa’ min phat tawntung ding,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin.
verse2:
Vantung khua siklong tum ding,
Kumpipa' mai i ding ding,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin,
Dah nate paisan ding a,
Sa tawntung ding min phatna,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin.
verse3:
Ka kha in manpha puak ding,
Kumpipa' mai i ding ding,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin,
Zawhna A' khemai nga ding,
Amah bang meel kicing ding,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin.
chorus:
Kumpipa' mai i ding ding,
Vantung mi tawh la sa ding,
Kumpipa A' min phat ding,
Haleluiah! Haleluiah!
Kumpipa’ mai i ding ding.

engTitle: Safe in the Arms of Jesus
verse1:
Gal omlo Zeisu’ ang sung, Kham khut tawh hong kawi ding,
Hong itna aa lim beel leh, ka lungsim nuamsa ding,
Ngai un vantung mi aw in, a vaangtang vantung ah,
Mual tung tuipi gal panin, la sa bang hong tung ta.
verse2:
Gal omlo Zeisu’ ang sung, gimna tawlna a bei,
Leitung ze-etna khialhna in-ah hong zol zo kei,
Lung siatna leh dahnate, kihtakna zong dai hi,
Leitung ah khitui luan’na, neu kha bek om lai hi.
verse3:
Kei taang ding Topa’ Zeisu, singlamteh na thuak hi,
A om tawntung suangpi bang, ka belh niloh ding hi,
Zankim lai hong kheng mateng, thuak in nangak ding ci,
Zingsang-a phalvaak mateng, lamen ka om ding hi.
chorus:
Gal omlo Zeisu' ang sung, kham khut tawh hong kawi ding,
Hong itna a lim beel leh, ka lungsim nuamsa ding.

verse1:
I omna inn ngaihsun in la,
A taang gun gal khatah om a ci,
Mi siangthote nuamna a om a,
Puanpak tawh kizem a om hi.
verse2:
Nangma lawmte ngaihsun in la,
A mailam amau te’n a zui hi,
Lung damna tawh amau te'n la sa,
Vantung khua dongin kiza hi.
verse3:
Vantung hong gum Topa’ kiangah,
Keima lawmte nuamsa a om hi,
Tua munin gimna om nawn lohna,
Keima kha in a tung nuam hi.
verse4:
En in, i lawmte vantung ah,
Amau in vantung khua a lut zo,
A lung khamna teng bei khin ding a,
Gimna tawntung mu lo om zo.
chorus:
Vantung ah, vantung ah,
I om nading inn vantung ah,
Vantung ah, vantung ah,
Vantung ah, vantung ah,
I om nading inn vantung ah.

zoTitle: Tua Lai Ka Om Nuam Hi
verse1:
A sap mi gam nuamah om nuam ing,
A nopna kam in gen zawh hilo,
Ni sangin a taang zaw gam nuamah,
Zeisu tawh a tawntung om nuam ing.
verse2:
Lai Siangtho sung thu ka theih ciangin,
Tawntung nuntak nopna thu hi ding,
Gimna tawlna dangtakna khempeuh,
Tua gam i tun' ciang om nawn lo ding.
verse3:
A nuam a hoih tua gam nuam sungah,
Sihna lung khamna om nawn lo ding,
Kahna khitui luan'na om nawn lo,
Sihna omlo nunnop gam nuamah.
verse4:
Tua gam nuam sungah om thei dingin,
Pasian in mawhnei mi hong hehpih,
A thuciam bang a um kheempeuh te,
A tawntung tua gamah om ding hi.
chorus:
Hih lam-ah, hih lam-ah,
Zeisu tawh a tawntung om nuam ing,
Hih lam-ah, hih lam-ah,
Zeisu tawh a tawntung om nuam ing.

verse1:
Vantung inn nuamah kikhawm dingin ah,
Ni nuam, zingsang gun gei cikkhuk ah,
Kikhawm ding hong ngakte tawh kimu leeng,
Lungdam nuamsa in la i sa ding.
verse2:
Hong tel Topa hong hehpihna pha a,
I lawmte ei hong ngak in omta,
Dahna tawh kipelh in i om ding hi,
Kimuh ciang lung damin la i sa ding.
verse3:
Hong gum Topa Zeisu tokhom tungah,
Lawmte aw a mai kikhawm in-ah,
Hong itna hong hehpihna a pha a,
A min than'na phatin la sa ni.
chorus:
Kikhawm ding innpi ah,
A nuam gunpi leh ciktui gei ah,
Hong ngak i lawmte tawh,
Nuam in Topa min i phat ding hi.

verse1:
A tawntung Topa tawh, "Amen" hong ci sak in;
Sihna pan nun'takna kammal; Tua nun’tak tawntung na
I pumpi hong kep sak, Vakthap in, tai khia in,
Zan thapai tuipuan buk lam-in, Ni khat sang’ inn nai zaw’ng
verse2:
Vantung ka Pa’ inn ah, Ka kha inn tawh kinai,
Khat veivei ka upna mit in, Kham kongpite mu in!
Ka kha a sihbup ciang, Ka utna mun tung ding;
Mi siangthote’ luah ding a taang, Jerusalem khua thak.
verse4:
Zingsang nitak ka za, Sun leh zankim ciang zong.
A ngaih mahmah van mite’ aw, Lasakna ke’n ka za
Tua thawh kikna kammal, Tua gual zawhna aw ging!
Khatvei, "A tawntung Topa tawh," Amen, ci sak lai in.
chorus:
Inn nai zaw’ng, Inn nai zaw’ng,
Ni khat sang inn nai zaw’ng.

verse1:
Sun sang a phazaw gam nuam om a,
I upna in kigal muh thei hi.
Ei aading, tua gampha vantung ah,
I Pa'n omna hong bawl kholh sak hi.
verse2:
Eite in tua gun gal gampha ah
Thupha ngah mite'n la ngaih sa in,
Dah ngei nawn lo ding i lung sungah,
Khuisa ngei nawn lo ding tawldam khin.
verse3:
Hong piak sa vaanglian hong itna pi,
Hong siang sak thupha, pahtawina la
Tawl ngalo phatna i sa ding hi,
Hong it vantung Pa Pasian mai ah.
chorus:
Nung ciangin a nopna
Tua gampha ah i kimu ding hi
Nung ciangin a nopna
Tua gampha ah i kimu ding hi

verse1:
Ze-etna leh nasep nate bei ciang,
A hoih tuipi geiah muangtak om ding,
Ka it mahmah Topa kiang nai om ding.
Tanglai pekpan min than'na kei aading.
verse2:
A bei ngeilo hehpihna hong piak ciang,
Vantung khua-ah omna khat ka nei ding,
Topa maitang tua mun ka mu den ding.
Tanglai pekpan min than'na kei aading.
verse3:
Sawtpi a muhnop lawmte na om ding,
Lung damna kiimkot ah gun bang luang ding,
Gumpa maiah nuihmai bek om ka thei.
Tanglai pekpan min than'na kei aading.
chorus:
Aw, kei aading tua min than'na
Tua min than'na, tua min than'na
Hong hehpihna, Amai ka en ding ta,
Tua min than'na in keima aading hi

zoTitle: Kham Gam Nuamah Ka Teeng Hi
verse1:
Gamlapi a gal dona thu ka bil in ka za hi
Tua ciang leitung mawhna'n van nuai zeel ding ka thei hi
Muan'lahna launa leitung na te'n kei hong zol uh hang!
Hong ngah khia lo ding hi, Kham gam nuam pan
verse2:
Gamlampi a om leitung ah lung man'na huih nung a
Leitung mite in sawt veipi gal a do uh hi
Kei ka hih leh Pasian inn muan'huai sungah ka om a
Gal dona'n hong ban kei, Kham gam nuam ah
verse3:
Huihpi nakpi nun' hangin phamawh kasa kei ding hi
Pasian khut nuai kiliah in, lung muangin ka om hi
Hih lai-ah ni taang tawntung a, hong sia sak ding om lo
Tawntung ka lungmuang hi, Kham gam nuam ah
verse4:
Pasian na sepna mu in, ka lung ka ngaih ciangin ah
A aw, ka za a, lampi hong puah sak ka mu hi
Kha Siangtho ka ngah khin a, gupna thu ka tel khin hi
Lungdam in om den ning, Kham gam nuam ah
chorus:
Mual tungah meii kai lohna, a nopna ah ka teeng hi
Tuinak pha pan a hong luang, tui kang ngeilo dawn ing
Hi hi, bei hun neilo a hong piang mana tawh ka kivaak hi
Kei in kham gam nuamah ka teeng hi

verse1:
Lim ngaihsut dide khat, Lungsim hong phawng pahpah
Inn lam naih zaw'ng, tuni'n, tuni'n,
A beisa nite sang
verse2:
Omna tampi omna, Ka Pa inn lam naih zaw'ng
Kumpi' tokhom naih zaw'ng, tuni'n,
Suang paak tuipi naih zaw'ng
verse3:
Van gikte kingakna, Nuntak gamgi naih zaw'ng
Singkhuam ngak ding nai zaw'ng, tuni'n,
Lukhu ngah ding naih zaw'ng
verse4:
Lam ke'n ka sik khialh ciang, Ka kiangah hong nai in
Inn tawh ka kinai zaw tuni'n,
Ka ngaihsut sangin ah
chorus:
Inn tawh nai zaw'ng, Inn tawh nai zaw'ng
Inn tawh nai zaw'ng tuni'n, tuni'n
A beisa nite sang

verse1:
Zeisu si in hong sawp siang hi
I khawm ding sihna gun gal ah
Natna hong tun' kik ding nai lo
Nuamna thu kikum in om ni
Sihna gun gal khatah
verse2:
Dahna hong tun' ding ka lau lo
Upna'n ka mu, vantung ka en
Ka za hi vantung mi'n la sa
Khitui kheempeuh Topa'n nul khin
Sihna gun gal khatah
verse3:
A itte tawh kikhop nuamna
Bang aw ka za ding hiam tua-ah
Ka lungsim hong vut hong tho sak
Na dang deihna tua mun mang sak
Sihna gun gal khatah
verse4:
Topa hong hilh bang ka zuihna
Lungdam ka ngah a kicin'na
Khawl ngeilo in ka phat ding hi
Khitui kheempeuh hong nul sak hi
Sihna gun gal khatah
chorus:
Sihna gun gal khatah, Sihna gun gal khatah
Sihna gun gal khatah, I tung ding hong nai ta
I tung ding hong nai ta, I tung ding hong nai ta
I tung ding hong nai ta, Sihna gun gal khatah

verse1:
Zawdan gun gei ah ka ding a, A gal lam ka en hi
Khanan gam nuam hong kilang a, Ka luah nading gam hi
verse2:
Tua gam pha bel sungah inn ah, Khuavaak tawntung om hi
Pasian leh Zeisu vaang in ah, A taang tawntung ding hi
verse3:
Cik ciang tua gam ka tung ding hiam, Khuamial om lohna ah
I Pa maitang lung damna dim, Cik ciang ka mu ding hiam
verse4:
Ka sin sungah lungdam nading, Leitung sawtpi om lo
Zawdan gunpi kilok hangin, Lungdam in ka tung zo
chorus:
Tua gam nuam sungah ei i khawl ding hi
A nop tawntung gun gal lam in ah
Nung ciangin Mawsi le Tuuno la sa ding hi
Zeisu tawh mang tawntung ding hi

zoTitle: A Nung Ciangin I Zo Ding Hi
verse1:
Topa Zeisu'n hong sam hi, I maiah koih khin zo hi
Thaman la ding pai un ci, Vantung pan
Itna kam khum tawh hong sam, Mawhna khuamial sung om mi
Dam takin Topa'n hong sam, hong nai hi
verse2:
Lam hong hilh bang zui ding hi, I tun' nading inn nuam ah
Hong zui un, ci'n hong sam hi, Vantung pan
Tua ciang kikhen nawn lo ding, Lawp a i lam-etna bang
Upna bangin khial loin, hong nai hi
verse3:
Ze-et bawlsiat i thuak zong, I inn ding vantung om hi
Zeisu'n hong it veve hi, Vantung pan
Topa siamna a lianpi, A kamciam peel ngeilo hi
A tawntung i phat ding hi, hong nai hi
chorus:
Nung ciang a kiang kimu ding, Nung ciang a kiang kimu ding
Nung ciang a Topa Zeisu tawh maang ding hi
Nung ciang a kiang kimu ding, Nung ciang a kiang kimu ding
Nung ciang a Topa Zeisu tawh maang ding hi

engTitle: When We All Get to Heaven
verse1:
Zeisu'n an bang hong itna pha, Lam bang paak zaila sa ni
Thang van inn taang sau siang nun nuam, Ko aading ngo bang lang hi
verse2:
Thang vantuang lam i zuih laitak, Zaitha tawlna om ding hi
Hi zong i pai khit ciangin ah, Zaitha tawl om lo ding hi
verse3:
Zang ni suah sim i um ding a, Lim bel sawl sang i leeng ding
Sau mang nun nuam kuam bang luah na'ng, Gua bang hin'lai ngaih khua-ah
verse4:
I mai nopna lai lung damna, Va bang leeng tung nuam ing ci
Thang van kankil i tun ciangin, Kham vaang khuapi i mu ding
chorus:
Thang van dong, i tun' ciangin,
Deih teng leh lai lung damna ngah ding hi
Kum khua in, la sa ni, Topa Zeisu i phat ding hi

verse1:
Vantung gam lam ka zin nading in
Zeisu in hehpih in lam hong sial
I gal kheempeuh a vek in zozo
Hih lamah hong pai un u le nau
verse2:
Hehpihna lam tu in zong un la
Tua zawh ciang khua mialna hong bei ding
A umte in vantung gam tung ding
Na up leh hih vantung gam lamah
verse3:
Zeisu in hehpih in-ah hong sam
A um lo mite um sak dingin
Hong hehpihna lianpi i mu ding
Pasian gam nuam sungah i lut ding
chorus:
Gam nuamah om dingin, om dingin, om dingin
Hih lamah, hong pai un u le nau
Gam nuamah om dingin, om dingin, om dingin
Hih lamah hong pai un u le nau

verse1:
Ni tumna gal-ah, Aw a nuam zingsang
Topa hong om ciang, vantung hi zo
Khual zinna bei in, min than'na mu ding
Ni tumna gal-ah, lei bei ni ciang
verse2:
Ni tumna gal-ah, Meii kai ngei lohna
Huihpi om nawn lo, launa bei ta
Aw lung damna ni, Aw bei ngeilo ni
Ni tumna gal-ah, tawntung nopna
verse3:
Ni tumna gal-ah, Khut tawh hong kha ding
I biak i Topa, Pasian kiangah
Ama min than'na, Hong dawnna kam khum
Kei aading hi ta, Tua gun gal-ah
verse4:
Ni tumna gal-ah, Lungdam kikhawlhna
A tungsa i it, i lawmte tawh
Tua a nuam gam sung, kikhen nawn lo ding
Ni tumna gal-ah, a tawntung in

verse1:
Tua lai gam om ni tum lohna,
Van ah ni taang tawntung
Tua lai nitak om ngeilo hi,
Topa vaang in taang hi
verse2:
Tua lai mun om kilemna gam,
Gimna om nawn lohna
Tua lai huihpi zong nung hiauhiau,
I tun' na'ng tua mun ah
verse3:
Tua lai inn om, minthang inn om,
A kigen van inn nuam
I tun' nading vantung inn nuam,
Ei hong dawn ding tua lai
verse4:
I pum lui na i nusiat leh,
Manlang in hong kheng ding
A taang van zinpa kiang zuan leng,
I lung nuam tawntung ding
chorus:
Singlamteh e'n i puak leh,
Kham lukhu i khu ding
Mi hoihte sung i ten' leh,
Khuavaak sung i om den ding

verse1:
It aw, nuamtak ihmu in tawlnga in
I Topa dip tung lukham in nei in
Nang kong it hang, Topa'n hong it zaw sem
Mangpha! Mangpha! Mangpha!
verse2:
Naungek bang nuamtak ihmu hithiat in
Dahna, kahna te'n anng hong phawng lo ding
Nang aa a nuam hithiat ihmut nahi
Mangpha! Mangpha! Mangpha!
verse3:
Hih leitung ah niliim a bei mateng
Topa'n A tuu buk sung hong khop mateng
Ni vaang taang khuamial a hong bei mateng
Mangpha! Mangpha! Mangpha!
verse4:
Pasian tokhom mai kimuh kik mateng
A sia thei lo puan a hong piak mateng
Tu'n i theih bangin i kitheih mateng
Mangpha! Mangpha! Mangpha!
verse5:
Min than'na thawh kik zing khuavaak mateng
Khazih sung a site thawh kik mateng
Ginalo bek tawh hong pai kik lo ding
Mangpha! Mangpha! Mangpha!

verse1:
Sihna kuam gal khatah khua lianpi khat om hi
Min than'nate kigen khin zo lo
Tua munah ni tum lo, singtehte vul ngeilo
Tua Pasian kham khuapi hoih sungah
verse2:
Tua mun'n i it Kumpi, hong tanpa Topa om
Thumaan mite'n lungdam'n en uh hi
Tua munah thumaan mite aksi bang taang ding
Tua Pasian kham khuapi hoih sungah
verse3:
Singlamteh phung i tun'pih khitsa kha kheempeuh
Tuubuk sung i tun'sa tuu kheempeuh
Lukhu zep nading suangmanpha bang kikem hi
Tua Pasian kham khuapi hoih sungah
chorus:
Tua munah, ni tum lo, Singtehte vul ngeilo
Tua munah thumaan mi maitang Topa'n en ding
Tua Pasian kham khuapi hoih sungah

verse1:
Vantung vaang lian hehpihna gam, Mi siangthote inn a hi
Ama kiangah om tawntung ni, Leitung na kheempeuh paai ni
verse2:
Tawntung inn nuam vaang lian gamah, I lawmte tua gam om ding
Tua inn nuam sungah om dingin, Mi nam cin a khawm ding hi
verse3:
Hong gupna sipha vaang lianpi, Hehpihna gam tang zel sak
Hih gal gamah i om lai in, Hong hehpihna thu gen in
verse4:
Khat tang hih hang pai in gen ni, Leitung dahna kiam ding hi
Lungsim deih teng tawntung omna, Kim takin a om ding hi
chorus:
Leitung ni a bei ciangin ah, Nung ciangin inn nuamah
Mi siangthote omna lam-ah, Vantung khua om ding hi

zoTitle: Tua Lai Dahna Om Nawn Lo
verse1:
Vantung ka ngaihsun hi, Topa Pasian omna
A kham maitang nisim mu ding, Nop kicing man ngahna
verse2:
Vantung ka ngaihsun hi, Hong teel Topa omna
Hong itna pha phat nading la kisa tawntung ding hi
verse3:
Vantung ka ngaihsun hi, Vantung mihingte in
Puanpak silh in a om uh hi, Ei zong i om ding hi
verse4:
Vantung ka ngaihsun hi, A tungsa i lawmte
Mu-a kikhen nawn lo ding a, Nuam tawntung ding hi veh
chorus:
Dahna kipelhna mun, Dahna kipelhna mun
Itna kicing, vantung kham gam, Dahna kipelhna mun

zoTitle: Ka Om Na'ng Khua A Hi
verse1:
Ni a taang khatna gam lamah
Nopsak na'ng gam lamah
Aksi zong a taan'na gamah
Ka om na'ng khua a hi
verse2:
Gimna thuakna gun gal khatah
Lung gim tamna lamah
Kikhel-a i nopsak na'ngah
Ka om na'ng khua a hi
verse3:
Sihna tuipi gal khat lamah
Khua mialna gam sungah
Lungdam nuamna i ngah nading
A taang in ka mu hi
verse4:
Mawhna leh hehna leitung ah
Hong liah-a mang sak hi
Tawntung tua khuapi nuam sungah
Zeisu tawh om khawm ning
chorus:
Tua khuapi nuam, khut tawh bawl lo
Tua gam, eima aading,
Tawntung vantung mi'n la a sa
Eima omna ding hi

verse1:
Hong tung ding leitung hin' bei ni
Tu'n ka theih bang la salo ding
Ka thawh kik ciang ka nuam ding hi
Topa Kumpipa tawh om ning
verse2:
Leitung ka inn puk ding ni om
Cikciang ding hiam gen thei lo hi
Hih hang ka thei kei aading om
Vantung ka om na'ng ka thei zo
verse3:
Ni a taang hong liap sak ciangin
Ni tum khawvaang taang lim nuai-ah
Ka Topa'n kei pha hong ci in
Hong lut sak ding hiam khawlna ah
chorus:
Ka mu ding hi, Topa' maitang
Gupna thu itna tawh hong gen
Ka mu ding hi, Topa' maitang
Gupna thu itna tawh hong gen

zoTitle: Keima Aading Vantung A Hi Ding Hi
engTitle: That Will Be Heaven for Me
verse1:
A bawl innpi ah hong paipih dingin
Topa hong pai ding hun kithei lo hi
Ahih hang Topa om a khuamial taang sak hi
(A min than'na kei aading hi)x3
Ahih hang Topa om a khuamial taang sak hi
A min than'na kei aading hi.
verse2:
Ka theih nai loh vantung mite'n la sa
Kham gawsem tawh Pasian min phat uh hi
I Kumpi Topa Zeisu a phatna uh la
(Tua la kisa kei aading hi)x3
I Kumpi Topa Zeisu a phatna uh la
Tua la kisa kei aading hi.
verse3:
Innpi hoih a lim ka thei nai kei hi
Bang min ka ciahpih ding ka thei kei hi
Hih hang hong gum Topa Zeisu hong ngai ding hi
(Vantung in keima aading hi)x3
Hih hang hong gum Topa Zeisu hong ngai ding hi
Vantung in keima aading hi.

zoTitle: A Sawt Loin Innah Ciah Ding
engTitle: In a Little While We're Going Home
verse1:
Lampi ah hong lung nuam sak ding la khat sa ni
A sawt loin ah innah ciah ding
Zan khuamial bei ding, ni taang tawntung na sungah
A sawt loin ah innah ciah ding
verse2:
Sep ding i muh peuh i khut in i seem ding hi
A sawt loin ah innah ciah ding
Pasian' hehpihna in i tha hong khauhsak ding
A sawt loin ah innah ciah ding
verse3:
A gim khete' aading lam i maai sak ding hi
A sawt loin ah innah ciah ding
Itna lungsim kizel kim in hoihna lawh hen!
A sawt loin ah innah ciah ding
verse4:
Lungkhamna pengin tawldamna gal khatah om
A sawt loin ah innah ciah ding
Tua khuapi nuam sungah khitui luan'na om lo
A sawt loin innah ciah ding
chorus:
A sawt loin ah, a sawt loin ah
Tuipi hual i kantan ding
Eite kimu ding huihpi nung a ven' ciangin
A sawt loin ah innah ciah ding

zoTitle: Inn Pha Bel Ah I Pai Ding Hi
verse1:
Mi siangthote pai nading lampi in
Pasian maiah a om ding hi
Vantung khua mualah i pai ngitnget a
Zingsol i tungah hong taang hi
verse2:
Lam nuam tawn mi siangtho honpite in
Zion khua-ah a pai kik ciang
Meivak sungah namgim tui thun khol un
Vantung khua-ah i pai ding hi
verse3:
Lam nuam tawn dinga i ngaihsut tek leh
Khat leh khat i ki-itna in
Pasian tawh eite i om khawm ding a
Nuam in i om tawntung ding hi
verse4:
Zawdan gun gei-a a votna gei-ah
I din' hangin a gal khatah
Topa Pasian tawh i ngap khawm ding a
A min i phat tawntung ding hi
chorus:
Inn pha belah i pai dinga
Lung damna tawh i kimu ding hi
Khua munnuam bel eite'n i phak ciang
Dahna om nawn lo hi

verse1:
Zan khua mialna ah i vakthap nawn kei ding
Kilawm, kongpite kihon' ciang
Pasian' khuavaak ahih na khua i pai ding
Kilawm, kongpite kihon' ciang
verse2:
Natna, satna, dahnate om nawn lo ding
Kilawm, kongpite kihon' ciang
Taangte bangin i lawmte tawh kipawl ding
Kilawm, kongpite kihon' ciang
verse3:
Gen khiat zawh loh lawpna kei aa hi ta ding
Kilawm, kongpite kihon' ciang
Amah en leng tua zah a siangtho kicing
Kilawm, kongpite kihon' ciang
verse4:
Leitung vangik mi nawngkai sak nawn lo ding
Kilawm, kongpite kihon' ciang
Nuam tawntung na-ah Khazih tawh i teeng ding
Kilawm, kongpite kihon' ciang
chorus:
A kilawm kongpi kihon' ciang
A kilawm kongpi kihon' ciang
Tua'h Topa mu ding, Tua tawh i lung nuam ding
A kilawm kongpi kihon' ciang

zoTitle: A Nung Ciangin Kimu Kik Ding
engTitle: We Shall Meet By and By
verse1:
I kimuh na'ng gun gal khatah,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin
Khuamial hun om ngei lohna ah,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin
Khual zin gimna bei khin a,
Min than'na tawh gal zo in
Ni bangin i taang ding hi,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin
verse2:
Min than'na gawsem i tun ding,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin
Ei hong gupna la i sa ding,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin
A kisia ngeilo vantung,
Lungdam gualnop denna mun
Gun gal thawn in la sa ding,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin
verse3:
Zeisu mu in kibang ta ding,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin
Kisia thei lo lukhu ngah ding,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin
A thu bang kicing ding a,
Vantung mi na seemte in
Ei' na hong sep sak ding hi,
Nung ciangin, nung ciangin

verse1:
An le leengtui gam ka tungzo,
A phatna teng kei aa hi zo.
Lungdam huai ni taang tawntung hi,
Keima khuamial leeng mang zo hi
verse2:
Hong Honpa kei tawh hong vak khawm,
Nuam takin kei tawh hong om khawm.
A' Khut in dam takin hong kai,
Vantung gamgi ciang dong ka nai
verse3:
Gamgi gal panin pak namtui,
Huih nung hiauhiau tawh hong kizui
A vul ngeilo paakte palhin,
Hin'na lui luang a tawntung in
chorus:
Aw gam nuampi, a pha gampi,
Mual sang tung pan ka galet a
Kei aading bawl kholhsa innpi,
Tuipi galah ka galmuh ta
Ka ten' nading, vantung khuapi,
A taang pha hi tuipi gal-ah

verse1:
Zeisu maiah mi tampi kikhawm uh a,
A min phatna la sa in, gawsem tum uh hi.
verse2:
Mawhna nei ngeite tua mihon mai tangah,
Puanpaak silh in, sa uh hi, A min phatna la.
verse3:
A sim mawhte siampi, kumpi suak sak hi.
A sipha tawh lei in, la thak pha , sa sak hi.
verse4:
Hong tat khiatna om kha zenzen lo hi leh
Mawhnei mite bangzah in i cimawh ding hiam.
chorus:
Ei hong it a, i mawhna hong phel sak Topa,
Ama min thang tawntung ta hen! Amen, Amen.

zoTitle: Topa In Ei Hong Kha Ding Hi
verse1:
Vantung Kumpipa tate,
Na pai lai la sa un aw.
Hong gum Topa' vaangpi tawh,
Phat in-ah la sa un aw.
verse2:
En un aw, khuavaak mite
Zion khuapi mu dek hi.
Tua a Topa tawh nuamsa.
Topapi mu kim nu aw.
verse3:
Launa tam kikhen nuam un
Leitung lam tawpah ding un.
A ta Zeisu Topa hi.
Hangin ah a pai nuam hi.
verse4:
Leitung a omte nusia,
Ngai in a Khazih nuam hi.
A nung ka zuih na’ngin ah 
Topa in lam hong hilh aw.
chorus:
Vantung inn ah pai ding om 
Tanglai mi paina lampi. X2
Tu lai mi nuamsa un aw,
A sawt lo eite’n mu ding.

engTitle: Sweeter as the Years Go By

zoTitle: Kum Tawn Kha Tawn Nong Kep Manih Topa
engTitle: God of Our Life, Through All the Circling Years
verse1:
Kum tawn kha tawn, Nong kep manin Topa kong muang uh hi.
A beisa hun launa, dahna khempeuh, Nang Nong huh hi.
Zingsang khua vaak, Nitak hong suak sial in
Topa hehpihna bek kong ngak uh hi.
verse2:
A beisa hun teng zong Na khut sung om, hong ompih in.
Upna tawh thuciamna gam sung tun' na'ng, lam hong hilh in.
Khua mialna ah khuavaak hong taang sak in,
Upna lungsim khuavaak hong nei sak in.
verse3:
Mailam hun ding zong a thei khol Topa, kong zui uh hi.
Muan'huai mah le ung zong hon ompih in, Hong beelbeel nung.
Nun'tak lai teng Nang nun'takna Khomun.
Ko hun bei ciang inn nuamah hong kha in.

zoTitle: Kum Lui Bei Naang, A Thank Dak Sat
engTitle: Ring Out the Old Ring In The New (Tune: Waltham)
verse1:
Kum lui bei na'ng a thak dak sat,
Mun khempeuh ah tua dak sat un.
Kum lui bei ding teng bei vet hen,
A hoih lo teng pai khiatpih hen.
verse2:
Damdam in dak sat dialdial un,
Kum lui bei lam kithei sak un.
Gam tatna hoih zaw neih theih na'ng,
Nuntak siangtho zaw neih theih na'ng.
verse3:
Kum lui kum sia, a kihhuai kum,
Duh-hop, huaiham, kih-huai kum hi.
Gal kisim simna teng bei hen,
Mailam kilemna hong tung hen.
verse4:
Galhang mipha mi suaktate,
Lungsim hoihte, mi hehpihte,
Gam sung khuamial khempeuh bei hen,
Khazih deih bang hong piang ta hen.

verse1:
Topa' kum dang khat hong tung, Kumpha hong hi sak in.
Nang tawh a nuam khawm thei ding, Nang tawh hun zang khawm ding;
Khantoh zawk na'ng kum dang khat, Na min phat na'ng kum dang.
Nangma Nong ompih tawntung, Tel zawk theihna kum dang.
verse2:
Topa' kum hoih khat hong tung, Lungnop hehpihna kum,
A lungdam huai kum dang khat, Na maipha muh theih kum.
Kipiak theih na'ng kum dang khat, Nang belh theih na'ng kum dang.
Nangmah kong muan' theih na'ng uh, Lungnop hiit-hiatna kum.
verse3:
Topa' na sep theih na'ng kum, Nang Nong itna hangin,
Nangma na sep siam zawk na'ng, Hoih zaw kicin' theih na'ng.
Topa' kum dang khat hong tung, Kumpha hong hi sak in.
Vantung leitung koimah peuh, Nangmah tawh kum pai khawm.

zoTitle: Ni Tampi Kheng Zo Ta Hi
engTitle: While the Days are Going By
verse1:
A lung mangte hong hehpih in, Ni tampi kheng zo ta hi.
Gimna lung khamna thuakna in; Ni tampi kheng zo ta hi.
Khual zinna leh kikal a, Nuamna lung damnate tawh.
Thu a pha ka bawl uh maw; Ni tampi kheng zo ta hi.
verse2:
Mawkna in a hun bei sak ke’n, Ni tampi kheng zo ta hi.
Namai zingsang khuavaak bang hen; Ni tampi kheng zo ta hi.
Leitung ah dahna sungah, Lung khamna kahna om a.
Na unau te phong in la; Ni tampi kheng zo ta hi.
verse3:
Itna tawh a kikhih khempeuh, Ni tampi kheng zo ta hi.
Eite in i nusia ta hi; Ni tampi kheng zo ta hi.
Khaici pha kituh khempeuh, A vak pha a lim nuaiah.
Hong po a, i lung damna; Ni tampi kheng zo ta hi.
chorus:
Ni tampi, kheng zo hi. Ni tampi, kheng zo hi.
Thupha gamtat theih nading.
Ni tampi kheng zo ta hi.

engTitle: Come, Ye Thankful People, Come (Tune: St. George’s, Windsor)
verse1:
Thupha theite hong pai un. Buhphual pai in la sa un.
Sal sungah kisia thei lo. Buhtangte kikhawm khin zo.
Kicingin deihna khempeuh Pasian in hong pia leuleu,
Topa biak inn sung, tum un. Buhphual paina la sa un.
verse2:
Topa Pasian, lo cing pi. Leitung pumpi khempeuh hi.
Lopate buh lo lai-ah. Kihelin min zo ta hi.
Lei leh van bei mateng in. Buh pha a pian’ nading in.
Kote ading a uk Pa, Topa aw hong hehpih in.
verse3:
Kote hong la to ding a, Hong pai ning, na cih thupha.
Ko in ka thei ciat uh hi. Gamlak lopa tanghum teng.
Mei tawh na hal tum khit ciang, Sal sungah buh koih dingin.
Vantung ah na mihingte, A sawl ding Topa Pasian.
verse4:
Hong pai in thusiam Topa. Vantung ah mang khempeuh tawh,
Vantung pan na mihingte. Hong sawl in ka Topa aw.
A siangtho mihing phate, Buhphual paina la sakna.
A sang vantung innpi ah. A vekpi kikhawm sak in.

engTitle: We Plow the Fields, and Scatter (Tune: Dresdeh)
verse1:
Mihingte in lo lai in, khaici pha i tuh hi;
Ahih hangin Pasian in, Tui buakin khang sak hi.
Phalbi lai vuk hong pia in,
Ni taang, khua lum, huihkhi, guah neel tawh
Kithuah sak in, An vui tak suak sak hi.
verse2:
Amah bek a bawl-Pa hi. Gamla, nai, na nam kim:
Van sang dawn-a taang aksi, i kiim paak palh nam kim:
Huihpi, tuipi’n zong mang hi,
Vate zong an pia kim; Ei Ama ta A ma mi.
Hong vak sem ve, ni sim.
verse3:
Hi mah-a Pa aw, nuam ung, A hoih teng Nong piaksa:
Lo pawi hun leh an lak hun, Nun'takna leh damna.
Nong it Nong hehpih hangin. Kote' lung damna lim,
Kong puak uh tawh hong saang in,
Na deih pen ko lungsim.
chorus:
Eite kiim le paam a, Na a hoihte vekpi,
Van a Topa’n hong piak hi a.
Nuamhuai kim hi.

verse1:
Honpa itna thu ka za hi,
Itna lamdang hi mah hi ding hi,
Hih hang, itna hehpihna tawh,
Van pan kei aading hong kum suk maw?
Van pan kei aading hong kum suk maw?
verse2:
A thuakna si luan’na ka za,
Singlamteh tung thuak lah a sihna;
Hih hang cih theih hiam? Hih bangin:
Kei aading hong thuak sak hi, ci in.
Kei aading hong thuak sak hi, ci in.
verse3:
Zeisu tate in a ngah ding,
Vantung ah inn nuam om cih za ing;
Hih hang kei aading bawlsa diam:
Kei aading tua lai mun a om hiam?
Kei aading tua lai mun a om hiam?
verse4:
"Nang lo, ke’n kua zuan ding?" ci a,
Kong dotna thu hong dawng in, Topa
Na Kha Siangtho tawh hih hong ci’n.
"Honpa leh vantung om, nang a ding."
"Honpa leh vantung om, nang a ding."
chorus:
Hi hi, hi, kei aading in,
Hi hi, kei aading, Topa’n hong it man,
Hong tuak suk hi, van pan,
Sing tung si, nang leh kei hong gum ding!

zoTitle: Hehpihna Tawh Note Hong Hon Zo
verse3:
A um takpi mite, Pasian in hong thei sak.
Khazih hangin hot khiatna cing,
"Tate" cihna ngah sak.
chorus:
Upna tawh gupna i ngah, Up man, up man
Nang dikna hilo upna tawh,
Nang dikna hilo upna tawh,
(Sep hilo) x6
Hi leh mi kisial ding,
Pasian hong piak khong hi.
Sep hilo, hi leh mi kisial ding.
(Pasian hong piak khong hi.) x4
Hong piak khong hi.

zoTitle: Gumpa I Cih Hi Bang Hi, Hallelujah
verse1:
"Gimma thuakpa" mawh neite, Gum khia dingin,
A pumpi pia Pasian Tapa min hi.
Haleluiah! Hi bang gumpa!
verse2:
Bawlsiat, maizum a thuak hi,
Kei hangin, paihkhiat a thuak;
A si tawh kei hong lei hi.
Haleluiah! Hi bang gumpa!
verse3:
Mawhna dim in i ci mawh,
Mawh baang lo Pasian Tuuno;
Hong gum khia zo takpi maw
Haleluiah! Hi bang gumpa!
verse4:
Sianglamteh in khaina thuak,
"Ka zo zo hi," ci’n kiko;
Van pan phatna aw ging hi.
Haleluiah! Hi bang gumpa!
verse5:
Minthang Kumpi hong pai ciang,
A tatsate hong la ding;
A thak hih la i sa ding.
Haleluiah! Hi bang gumpa!

verse1:
Tho un, no hot khiatna tate,
Lutang Khazih beel khempeuh;
Tho un, no minam vaang liante,
Zion ah gal hong pai ma’n.
verse2:
Eima aa mi siang gal hangte,
Hi thu bekah kip uh hi.
I tung aa dial kipeei mu un,
Zeisu si hang gual zote.
verse3:
Si loin, i lau kei ciat hi,
Nuntakna Pasian sung om.
Ama hong kilat zingsang ciang,
Min than'na tui hong luang khia.
verse4:
I vek A mai i ding baih ding,
Minthang i to i mu ding.
Lung damin Amah phat baih ding,
Thaman ciat ding saang ciat ding.
chorus:
A vaanglian la ging sak ta un,
Tuipi nak pi ging bangin.
Ei hong tatna Khazih si hang,
(Gual zo pente i hi hi.) x3
Ei hong tatna Khazih si hang,
Gual zo pente i hi hi.

verse1:
Kei taang ding, a si nuam mipa khat hiah om hi,
Ka kha ginalo, nungta sak ding,
Singlamteh tawn lampi khat Amah’n zui nuam hi,
Ka mawhna teng hong puak sak dingin.
verse2:
Amah dik-in hong it a, kei aading nuam hi,
Ka lungsim hong sawpsiang sak ding hi,
Hih hang mawh sakna om lo ka suakta ka thei,
Kei mawhna taang ding sing tung kilh hi.
verse3:
Ama tungah kipia ning, kikhen nawn kei ning,
A nisim lungdam A nung zui ning,
Ka lung sung la sa in ka kam tawh zong phat ning,
Ka mawhna teng pua khia khin zo hi.
chorus:
Singlamteh tung kilh hi. Singlamteh tung kilh hi,
Aw, bangzah in Amah’n gimna thuak!
Khuavul sisan suak in, Zeisu’n singlamteh pua!
Ka mawhna teng singkhuam tung pua khin!

verse1:
Aw itna lian, mihing ngaihsut zawh loh dong,
Na tokhom maiah thu ngen kong khuk din’,
Mong neilo itna tua munah a om ding,
Nong kipawl a tawntung khat suak dingin.
verse2:
Aw hin'na lian, amau muan' lian bel na hi,
Upna kip leh a duai ngi-i-ngei itna,
Lawpna tawh thuak zo a, hang takin thuakna,
Si zong, na zong naupang bang um in muang.
verse3:
Leitung dahna bei sak in, lungdamna pia’n,
Leitung kisiatna bei, kilemna pia’n,
A kithei lo zingciang nuntakna ni ah,
Taikhua val sak, tawntung hinna, itna.

engTitle: Send Out Thy Light (Tune: Lux Fiat)

verse1:
Aw Pasian Nang thusiam pen,
Deihna teng kicin'na, Nuntakna thu laigil pen,
Amau sung lut sak in, Sih ciang om khawm thei dingin,
A thuciam kip sak in.
Na vang liatna ngaihsun in,
Na thupha mu sak in.
verse2:
Leitung a na om lai in,
Kana khua na pai lai, Kiten'na pawi va sim in,
Tui leenggah na suak sak, Tu-a mopina pawi zong,
Thupha hong pia in la,
Amau deihna bang piang hen,
Na min ki pahtawi hen.
verse3:
Nangmah hong muan theih na’ng un,
Pasian aw hong huh in, Hak satna thuaknate ah.
Nangmah’n hong ompih in, Amau nuntakna bei in,
Leitung nusia ta leh,
A tawntung hong ompih in,
Na innah hong pi in.

verse1:
Pasian in kiten'na pawi bawl khin zo hi,
A siangtho innkuan a suak dingin,
A kicing innkuan khat a suah nading in,
A siangtho nuntakna a nei ding.
verse2:
Zeisu in Tapidawte a it manin,
A nuntakna a hong piak bangin,
Hih zi neipa in zong tua bangin hih hen,
A siangtho thu hilhna zui ta hen.
verse3:
Topa Nang' khut sungah hihte om ta hen,
Amau sungah khantohna om hen,
Kithu tuahna lungsim om tawntung ta hen,
Tha hatna teng Nang aading zang hen.
chorus:
Lungdam takin nuampih ciat ve un,
I lawmte kiten’na pawi sungah,
Hih lungdamna thu vantung dong thang sak un,
Leitung nuntakna a bei ciangin.

verse1:
Leitung bei dong, i Kawlgam,
Ei pupa gam, i luahsa it ciat ni,
Kawlgam bup hut na'ng, hin'na paai ngam ning,
Hih ei gam, hih ei lei, eima neihna,
Ei gam, ei lei phattuamna’ng,
Ei kilung-tuak in, i hanciam ding hi,
Eima sep ding, i gam manpha.

Pasian minpha ta hen! Hong itna lian hi.
Leitung hong it manin, A ta hong pia hi;
A ta’n mawhphel nangin a luang hong paai a,
Vannuai lut theih nading hin kongpi hong ta.
verse2:
Sisan a hong lei sak tat khiatna kicing.
Pasian hong ciamsa hi a umte ading.
Gilopen khat in zong a up taktak leh.
Mawh maina ngah pah hi a up phetmah teh.
verse3:
Thu manpha a lianpi ei hong thei sak hi,
Ei aading na lianpi hong sepkhiat sak hi;
Lung damna a lianpi hong ngah sak a Ta’n.
Mai i muh ciang lamdang ding hi ei! Nuam na.
chorus:
Phat ve vua! Phat ve vua!
Leitung ah kiza hen!
Phat ve vua! Phat ve vua!
Mi khempeuh lungdam hen!
A Ta Zeisu tawnin A Pa kiang lut un,
Sianmang hawm siamna hi,
Amin thang sak un.

crossrefs: Arr. by Adolphe Adam, Alfred Judson
verse1:
Zan a min siang, aksite bang te kelkel!
Pasian' Tapa ong suah zan mah dingin pha!
Mi a min piang mawhna lel a vul ningniang,
Pasian' Tapa’n lungkia ke’n, ong ci a,
Lungsi khinsa, tha khat thu’n ong khanglo sak,
Hotkhiat nading lametna khua vak sak.
Ngai dih ve vua, Mi siangte la in ka za bang!
Na za uh hia! A ngaih dan lamdang lua.
Vana Pasian in ei ong itna la.
verse2:
Mipilte’n zong lam hilh aksi tang zui in,
Bawng ankuang kiang a va tun uh mah bangin,
Eite in zong upna khuavak lam zui-in,
Lunggulh tunna phualah tu’n khuk dinin,
En un, kumpi khempeuh tung Kumpi lian pen,
Deihna sapna ong thei i Lawm pha pen.
Kuun in bia un, Amah sang lian zaw om lo,
I lawm, i To, Khazih ong it i To.
Kuun un, kuun un, bia un, i Kumpino.
verse3:
Ama maanna sungah ki-it lo om lo,
Ama mite kilem diamdiam uh a hi.
Kideidan-na sila le to, cih om lo,
U le nau bang kiho thei a vekpi.
Lungdam nuamna la a ngaih zaw kipaih ni,
A min siangtho phatna la ngaih sa ni.
Ngai un, la pha, Van a mi siangte’n la sa;
Sa un, sa un, Khazih min phatna la.
Sa un, sa un, no zong min phatna la.
chorus:
Van a Pasian, Ei ong ompih hi zo ta,
Kilemmna Mang, leitung ong uk ta hen.
Ama thu nuam mi in ciam kim ta hen.

zoTitle: Van A Pa Aw Ka Hong Pahtawi Uh Hi
verse1:
Van a Pa aw, Nang kong pahtawi uh hi,
Van a Pa aw, Nang kong pahtawi uh hi;
Hong it ung, hong bia ung, Na maiah hong kun ung,
Van a Pa aw, Nang kong pahtawi uh hi.
verse2:
Pasian Ta aw, Na min hong lian sak ung,
Pasian Ta aw, Na min hong lian sak ung;
Mawhna pan Nong sawp a, Kha Siangtho Nong guan zo,
Pasian Ta aw, Na min hong lian sak ung,
verse3:
Kha Siangtho lamdang hehnem Pa na hi,
Kha Siangtho lamdang hehnem Pa na hi,
Ka lampi Nong hilh a, Ka sungah Nong teeng hi,
Kha Siangtho lamdang hehnem Pa na hi.

engTitle: As the Deer Panteth for Water
verse1:
Sakhi te’n ciktui luang sialsial a lunggulh bang,
Nang hong lunggulh ing.
Nangmah bek ka lungtup na hi,
Nangmah bek hong bia nuam ing.
chorus:
Ka hatna, dalna lum na hi,
Nangma sung bekah kong kipia hi.
Nangmah bek ka lungtup na hi,
Nangmah bek hong bia nuam ing.

zoTitle: A Gen Bang Hong Pai Kik ding Ka Um Hi
verse1:
Mual sang tung khat panin Topa van kah to a,
Puanpak silh mi nih in. Nungzuite hehnem hi,
"Lungzuang kha peuhmah kei un,
Tu a kilato Zeisu in,
Van a kah na muh bang un hong kum kik ding."
verse2:
Topa hong kilat ding, Nai mahmah ta kha ding,
Tuni zong hi thei hi, Tu hun zong hi thei hi,
Tua hun teh mi siang khempeuh
Leitung in huup zo nawn lo ding,
Van kim lai-ah lak tohna ngah ding uh hi.
chorus:
Hong gen bang hong pai kik ding ka um hi.
Vantung mi’n peengkul hong tum in
Misite tho ding cih ka um hi.
Mit phiat sung kikal in ah,
Vantung hong kek in ah,
A gen bang hong pai kik ding ka um hi.

engTitle: Cleanse Me, Search Me, O God
crossrefs: Late 139:23, J. Edwin Orr (1936 -), G.M. 168, B.H 266, Xt. 176, Maori Melody
verse2:
Nong siang sak a, ka nuam hi Nangma tung.
Na Thu ong dim in, siang den hen ka sung.
Zumhuai, kih-huai, nidang ka lung sungah,
Tu’n Nang min phatna mei bangin kuang ta.
verse3:
Kei nuntakna Nangmah’n tang khin ta in.
Kei lung gina lo itna ong dim in.
Ut pen, deih pen, tup pen teng suahkhia in.
Kong tokaai hi; kei sung ong luah ta in.
verse4:
Kha Siangtho aw, Lawpna thak hong guan in;
Lawpna thanuamna hong khanglo sak in.
Kote sapna, ngah ding, Na cih sa hi,
Tu’n hong pia in. Na thupha, kong thum hi.

zoTitle: A Hong Itna Hi A Lencip
engTitle: Love Held Him to the Cross
crossrefs: Ephet 5:2, G. M 223, Xt. 226, Rupert Cravens
verse1:
Keima mawhna teng panin,
Ong sawp siang nading in ah,
Ka Topa’n ong bua hi Ama si.
Gen zawh loh ong it manin,
Vangliatna nusia in ah,
Singlamteh A hong thuak ta zen hi.
verse2:
Mawhna sung si ding kimlai,
Ong dawn ding A hong pai a,
Kei sih tang dingin A hong si hi.
Phatphat mah ning ka nun lai,
Sasa mah ning ka nuamna,
Ama hang bekin ka suakta hi.
verse3:
Ka sung ong puah siangsak-in,
Ka sungah ong ompih a,
Nisim in lungsim ong kumpih hi.
Khual gam pan a ciah bangin,
Inn tun kaal ka ngaklah ta,
Ka tun ciang A mai ka mu ding hi.
chorus:
Singlamteh tung a khen cip,
Siiktukkilh na sak khak leh,
Kei A hong itna hi a lencip.
Kei sih taang A sih manin,
Kei a suakta thei ka hi;
Zeisu longal in thuak zo ken teh.

crossrefs: Ephet 2:8, John Newton (1725 - 1807), S.H. 195, Xt. 279, Arr. by Edwin O. Excell (1851 - 1821)
verse1:
Lamdang lua hi, ong hehpihna!
Kei bang peuh ong hon a;
A gammang sa lam maan ong lak,
Mittawkhua ong mu sak.
verse2:
Hehpihna in ong lah ka mu,
Kei ading lauhuai thu;
Tua lauhuai pan suahtaak lampi,
Hehpihna thu mah hi.
verse3:
Lauhuai thang kam sa lak panin,
Hehpihna thu mah in;
Ong kaikai in ong tun, hih dong,
Ong kha lai ding inn dong.
verse4:
Vanah eite ni bang taanga,
Phatna sasa dinga;
Nuam mahmah ding kum tuul, kum then,
Veng ngeilo nuam denden.

zoTitle: Zeisu Khe Ah Ka Va Tu A
engTitle: Sitting at the feet of Jesus
verse1:
Zeisu' khe-ah ka va tu a, Ong hona kam nuam lamdang!
Lungdamna tua bang om thei ta! A nisim va khawl nuam tang.
Zeisu' khe-ah ka va khawl a, Sawt lai thu ka phawk san hi;
Ong it mahmah na hi khong ta! Ka lung ong zo peet ta hi.
verse3:
Ong hon Topa aw, Na thupha tu in kei ong ngah sak in;
Itna tawh ong en suk in la, Na mai nuam ong mu sak in.
Nangma lungsim bang ong guan in,
Nang' sian bang ong siang sak in.
Nong ompih cih ka lah na'ng in. Nangma hoihna ong guan in.

crossrefs: Hebia 4:9, William O. Cushing (1823 - 1902), S.S 908, Xt. 364, William F. Sherwin (1826 - 1858)
verse1:
Etlawm mual kuam Eden gam nuam:
Sunkam bang daihna nuam;
Gim-a vulte' lungzuan damna,
Nuam khua huihkhi zaamna.
verse2:
Nangma sun ni kham bang taang hi,
A dah a kap tungah;
Lungnop huai la ong kiza hi.
Gamla pek pan in ah.
verse3:
Ong Honpa' innpi nuam sungah,
Mi siang honpi te’n la,
Tua van sang gam nuam tung tengah.
La thak kihual ka za.
chorus:
Etlawm mualkuam Eden gam nuam!
Mi siangthote omna! Omna!
Tuihual lauhuai in ong lok laitak.
Ngai sing ey na daihna nuam.

zoTitle: Beel Ong Tawm Ken' Kha Ke'n
engTitle: Bring Your Vessels, Not a few
crossrefs: Mrs. C. H. Morris, T. H. 110, Xt. 488
verse1:
Tuni’n Topa thupha cing takin,
Ngah ning ci’n lamen in,
Nang na lunggulh giugiau hiam?
Ong khap sa hi, ci-in ah,
Ong genna tawh kituak takin,
Ngen lel in i Pa' kamciam.
verse2:
Leibeel hawm teng ong keng un,
Zeisu' si-a sawp siang sa in,
Thupha deih peuh ong pai un;
Pum le lung siangsa sungah,
Kha Siangtho ong sun mateng in,
Pa' maiah kuunin ngak un.
verse3:
Bing sung sathau kilawi ngeilo,
Ong hehpihna mah bangin,
Ong itna zong dang ngeilo;
Topa' ong ciam sa mah bangin,
Vang i neih theih nading in,
Ong dim ding hi Kha Siangtho.
chorus:
Topa in na sung a dim dong ong sun ding hi,
Beel ong tawm ken kha ke’n ci,
"Tampi tak ong keng in" ci,
Topa in tuni’n a dim dong ong sun ding hi,
Kha Siangtho le vangliatna.

crossrefs: Late 34:17, Elisha A. Hoffman (1839 - 1929), S.H. 295, Xt. 237, Elisha A. Hoffman
verse1:
Zeisu va ko ning, ka lung kham lua hi,
Kei guak in ka van puak hak lua hi;
Amah’n A mite don khial ngeilo hi,
Kei zong ong huh nuam ding ka thei hi.
verse2:
Ka lung gimna teng, Zeisu va puak ning,
Amah lo om kei, Lawm a migi;
Amah ka lungsim teng va ko khin ning!
Ka lung gimna teng bei pah ding hi.
verse3:
Ze-etna haksa, Vangik hih zah tawh,
Kisam hi veeng aw, ong panpih ding;
Zeisu lo om kei, a dang ka muan zawk,
Amah’n ka van teng ong dawn zo ding.
chorus:
Zeisu va ko ning! Zeisu va ko ning!
Kei guak in ka van puak hak lua hi;
Zeisu va ko ning, Zeisu va ko ning,
Kei ong huh zo ding, Amah bek hi.

zoTitle: Lam Ong Hilh In, Tung Pasian Aw
engTitle: Guide Me, O Thou Great Jehovah
crossrefs: Isaiah 58:11, John Hughes, Rev. Haugo, William Williams
verse1:
