Lam hong hilh in tung Pasian aw,
Nang' gam zuan kong zinlai un;
Ka hat loh hang nang na hat hi,
Na khut taklam ong len in,
Van khomun aw, Van khomun aw,
Ka kham dongin hong vaak in,
Ka kham dongin hong vaak in.
verse2:
Lim lang tui naakah hong khah in la,
Damna tui siang ong luan in;
Meii lum kai le kammei khuampi,
Lam tawntung ong pi sak in,
Hon zo Pa aw, Hon zo Pa aw,
Ong dal in tha ong pia in,
Ong dal in tha hong pia in.
verse3:
Jordan gunpi gei ka phak ciang,
Ka launa hong dai sak in;
Ong ngah pih in sihna tui khang,
Gal a Canaan dong takin,
Na min phatna, Na min phatna,
Tawlnga lo ka sa ding hi,
Tawlnga lo ka sa ding hi.
verse4:
Topa, na vangliatna kong muang,
Na khutmate lamdang lua;
Saltaang na mite na honkhia.
Na gel bang na tangtung sak;
Sihna hankhuk, Galpa satan,
Nang na zogawp khin zo hi.
Nang na zogawp khin zo hi.

verse1:
Ka za hi a lui tangthu,
Van pan Honpa hong paina thu.
Kalvary ah sihna hong thuak hi,
Misia kei hong hon hi;
A si hong luankhiat man a,
Gim in A tauna thu ka za,
Ka mawhnate ka kisik a,
Tu’n zawhna ka ngah hi.
verse2:
A damsak theih thu ka za,
Ama vangliatna langsak a,
Khebaite hoihtak lam pai sak hi,
Mittaw khua musak hi;
Tua ciang ka it Zeisu kiang,
"Kei hong damsak in" ka cih ciang,
Amah ka kiangah hong pai a,
Zawhna a hong pia hi.
verse3:
Van a inn nuam thu ka za,
Topa’n kei ading bawlzo ta,
Kongzing khempeuh ah kham bek kiphah,
Lim lang tuipi gal-ah;
Vantung mite' lasakna,
A hong tat khiatna thu ka za,
Khatvei ciang ken zong tua lai ah,
Zawhna la ka sa ding.
chorus:
Zawhna om hi, a tawntung, Ka Honpa Zeisu sung,
A si tawh kei mimawh, Hong zong in hong lei zo;
Ka theih ma’n hong it zo a,
Kei zong ka it kik thei ta,
Gualzawhna ka ngah nading
A si sung hong phum zo.

crossrefs: Ephet 2:10, G.B.S, HFG 13, George Beverly Shea
verse1:
Nitak a ni a tum lamdang sa ing,
Nisuah zong lamdang sa seem ing;
Ka lungsim hong khoih kha a lamdang peen in,
Pasian in hong itna hi, nuam sing!
verse2:
Tuk hun, an lak hunte lamdang si ee,
Vantung aksi, nite zong ee;
Ka lungsim hong khoih kha a lamdang peen in,
Hih ka phawk thak hong itna hi ee.
chorus:
O hih mah lamdang pen sa'ng!
Hih mah lamdang pen sang! Pasian in kei hong it zenzen!
O hih mah lamdang pen sa'ng!
Hih mah lamdang pen sang!
Pasian in kei hong it zenzen!

crossrefs: Psalms 37:23, W.E.M, M. P. 259, W. Elmo Mercer
verse1:
Kalsuan simin Honpa ka maiah pai hi,
A itna khut tawh hong makaih a;
Husan simin Topa, Nangmah kong bia hi,
Nangmah tawh ton khawm leng nuam ka sa.
verse2:
Ka upna tha khat veivei a hong kiam ciang,
Ka etna khempeuh lungkiatna hi;
Kihei kikin kei hong Honpa ka et ciang,
Hong ompih manin ka tha hat hi.
verse3:
Bangbang hong piang ta leh Pasian ka muang hi,
Nuntakna Ama sungah om hi;
Amah, lampi a hong honsak thei Pa hi,
Khapsa gam nuamah hong tun ding hi.
chorus:
Kalsuan simin A hongpi ding ka thei a,
A sangzaw ah hong paipih tawntung hi;
Khatvei ni ciang lam tawpna ka tung ding a,
Kalsuan simin inn ka nai seemseem hi.

zoTitle: Pasian Ei Lam Hong Om Leh
crossrefs: Zawmah 8:31, G.M.J, S.S. 508, PH. 189, James McGranahan
verse1:
Topa sung nuam un! Hong hehpihna phat un,
Hong hencip khempeuh phelkhia hi,
Si tawh hong tan zo, lau nawn peuhmah kei un,
Zeisu ah deihna teng cing hi.
verse2:
Topa sung hat un! A thahatna suang un.
Nisim thumanin citak ni,
Siatna’n hong nawk ciang thuman aading hang un,
Amah i tha le bukna hi.
verse3:
Ama thu muang un! A kamciam peel ngeilo,
Khazih sung "Amen" hi khin ta,
Lei a bei zongin A thu bei thei ngeilo,
Lai Siangtho in gen khin zo ta.
verse4:
Topa sung kip un! A ang muanhuai sungah,
Tawntung nunna kipatna hi;
A thaneem peen zong A khut sung pan in-ah,
Kuamah in sut zo lo ding hi!
chorus:
Ei lam ah Pasian, Ei lam ah Pasian,
Ei lam hong om leh, Kua i lang pang zo ding?
Kua?, kua?, kua?
Kua i lang pang zo, kua pang zo ding?

crossrefs: Hosea 6:3, E.E. Hewitt, GM. 22, Jno. R. Sweney
verse1:
Zeisu' thu thei semsem nuam ing,
Hong itna thu gengen nuam ing;
Kei tang a si Pa' hong itna,
A cing zawin ka thei nuam hi.
verse3:
Zeisu' kammal zaza nuam ing,
Topa tawh ho limlim nuam ing;
A aw ngai ning vai khempuh ah
A gen teng ka pom kim nuam hi.
verse4:
Van tokhom ah a tutna thu,
Van hauhna teng a neihna thu,
A gam zai nang le hong pai na'ng,
Za nuam ing Kumpi a suah nang.
chorus:
A thu zaza nuam ing, A thu zaza nuam ing,
Kei tang-a si Pa' hong itna
A cing zawin ka thei nuam hi.

crossrefs: Piancil 49:10, F. J. Crosby, Ira D. Sankey
verse1:
Mihing' Tapa hong pai kik na'ng tua khuavak pha zingsang le,
A min than’na taangpha eite’n i mu ding;
Mi cin nam cin lak pan a, Ama' mite hong ciahpih teh,
Hotkhiat sa te' kikhopna lianpi hi ding!
verse2:
Ama sung a ihmu sa mi Zeisu’n A thawhsak hun ciang,
A gam dai hankhuk le tuipi sung panin;
Siangtho pumpi nei-in van ah kila to ding Ama' kiang,
Hotkhiat sa te' kikhopna lianpi hi ding!
verse3:
Omna tampi a omna mun tua khuapi lian i et ciang,
A khawnkhong a luang nuntakna gun mu ding;
Sihna in hong khensa lawnte nuamna tawh i muh hun ciang,
Hotkhiat sa te' kikhopna lianpi hi ding!
verse4:
Kumpipa hong pai taktak ding, a hun hong nai khin zo ta,
Hong nai zo hong ciamsa ni thupi muh ding;
"Mitphiat kalsung hun tomno ah" eite i kikheel khin ding,
Amah tawh a tawntung in i om khawm ding!
chorus:
Kikhopna lian! Kikhopna lian!
Hotkhiat sa mite tawh kikhopna lian itna gam sungah,
Kikhopna lian! Kikhopna lian!
Hot sa mite kikhopna lian vantung ah!

zoTitle: Gunpi Ah I Kikhawm Ding Hiam?
engTitle: Shall We Gather at the River?
crossrefs: Kilakna 22:1, R. L, Rev. R. Lowery
verse1:
Gunpi ah kituah ding hiam?
Van mite tot sa mun ah;
A tawntung in a tee dialdial
Pasian' tokhom pan hong luang.
verse2:
Tua gunpi pang dungdung teng in,
Ngun bangin kisil siang a;
Lam pai in i bia den ding a,
Tua nopna hun i ngah ciangin.
verse3:
Tua gunpi a taan-na sung pan,
Honpa' mai tang kilang sawn;
Sihna’n a zawh loh mi siang te’n
Hotna la sa in kithawn.
verse4:
Tua gunpi ei zong tung pah ding,
Hong bei pah ding i khual zinna;
I lungsim lawpin kipaak ding,
Nopna la ngaihpi i sa ding.
chorus:
Hi hi, gunpi ah kikhawm ding,
Kilawm mahmah a hoih mahmah gun ah;
Pasian' tokhom pan hong luang gun ah,
Mi siangte tawh kikhawm ding.

crossrefs: 1 Kawlentu 13:12, F. J. Crosby, S.S. 967, Jno R. Sweney
verse1:
Leitung ka nasep bei a tuihualpi ka kan tan ciang.
Vaanglian taangpha zingsang ka muh hun ciangin;
Ka Honpa ka thei ding hi gun gal khat lam ka tun ciang,
A nuihmai kei Hong dawnna masa hi ding.
verse2:
A mai tang ka et cianga ka lungsim hong dim lawpna,
A mithah kilawm ka et hun ciangin ah;
Van a keima ading omna hong bawl kholh sak itna,
Thupha hehpih Hong piak man phat ning Amah.
verse3:
Aw! Van a ka it te’n hong pai in ci’n hong khut van uh,
A maute tawh gun a kikhen lai phawk ing;
A et lawm Eden mualah dawn-na la hong sak ding uh,
Aih hang ka Honpa mu masa bel nuam ing.
verse4:
Ni bang a taang puan silh in khuapi kongpi kantan in,
Kah nawn lohna munah kei hong tonpih ding,
Nuamin kipaak ning khang tawntung hong tuum ding la ngaih in,
Hih hang, ka Honpa mu masa bel nuam ing.
chorus:
Amah thei ning, Amah thei ning,
Hot ngah a, A kiang ka din ciangin;
Amah thei ning, Amah thei ning,
A khut a kikhetna pawn pan in.

zoTitle: Et Lawm Mual Kuam Unok Paak
crossrefs: Solomon Late 2:1, I. G. Martin, Arr. by I. G. Martin
verse1:
Zeisu in ka lawm hoih pen hi, bang ka kisam nawn diam?
Mi tul tampi sangin Amah manpha zaw;
Mualkuam, Unok, paak bangin. A hoihna ka mu ta,
Ka mawh hong sawp in hong siangtho sak zo hi.
Ka dah ciang hong hehnem hi, ka lau ciang ka bukna,
"Na vangik teng kei hong suan in" hong ci.
verse2:
Ka lungkhamna teng la khin, ka dahna teng zong pua,
Ze-etna hong pai ciang a ka belh mun hi;
Na khempeuh nusia khin ta ing, Ngaihsut hoih lo teng zong,
Ama vangliatna in kei hong kem ta hi.
Ka lawm te’n hong nusia in, Satan in hong khem hang,
Zeisu hangin ka tupna taang tun ding,
verse3:
Kei hong nusia nusia lo ding, zong hong taisan lo ding,
Upna tawh nungta in Ama na sem ding;
Ka maiah lauhuai om hang, Bangmah kihta nawn keng,
Nisim ka kham khop an Aman hong pia hi.
Tua ciang kei hong ciah pih in, Ama maitang mu ding, Lungdamna ciktui tawntung luanna ah.
chorus:
Et lawm mual kuam unok pak le a tang zingsol aksi
Mi tul then tampi sangin, Amah hoih zaw.

zoTitle: Bang Zah In A Nuam Ding Hiam!
verse1:
Zingsang phalvak tung pan laitak, Khanglo in ngaihsun zel ing,
Pengkul sapna aw a ging hiam? ci’n ngai ing;
Mei san ciangin khua pha ding cih ih gen kholh theih mah bangin,
Pengkul sapna aw, ka za tam ci in geel ing ka sun mangin.
verse2:
Leitung ah ka gen theihnate ngaihsut tak sa peuhmah keng,
Hong kam vaikhak nunung pen ke’n ngaihsun leng;
Hong pai kik in hong la ning cih hong kam vaikhak khin zo a,
Ka Topa maitang muh ding mah ka geel ciang ka ngaklah zo ta.
chorus:
Topa hong pai kik ciang bangzah tak a nuam ding hiam.
A tate hong kaihkhop ciang Bangzah tak a nuam ding hiam.
A mai tang mu nuam zen sing, a khut pawn lawng nuam zen sing,
Topa hong pai kik ciang bangzah tak a nuam ding hiam!

verse1:
Vantung sangpi pai ding ih hamciam hangin ah,
Aksite khengin gamla pek pai hang;
Topa' ading leitung in inndei neu no khat,
Vantung teng in a huang no them khat bek hi.
verse2:
Phalbi khuadamin paakte a pulh sak hangin,
Tuuk hun ciangin tua paakte hong palh bang;
Na lungziin' leh pianthakna in hong bawlpha ding,
Pasian' khut in nang hong laam to ding hi.
chorus:
Topa lian hi A gam in bangzah in zai hiam?
Kam tawh gen ding ka kipat sim loh ngal,
Amah lian hi, vangam lei mong uk dingin ah,
Ka lung tang sung Amah tu’n hong teng hi.

crossrefs: I. G. Martin, Arr. by I.G. Martin
verse1:
Ni suahna lam kongpi sungah,
Zing tung in nang kong dawn ding;
Khualzin pa aw, kiging khol in,
Nong zekai loh nang in ah.
verse2:
Nang' kei sang na masak zawk leh,
Tua kongpi ah na ngak in;
Kei zong zingtung in kong pai ding,
Sawtvei hong ngak kei ni teh.
verse3:
Na meivak tang sak tawntung in,
Mopipa’n nang hong ngak hi;
Amah zong hong pai ding tua ah,
Ni suahna lam kongpi ah.
verse4:
Tua kikhopna bangzah nuam ding!
Hong ngak mi siangthote tawh,
Thupha a dim nuamna kikhop
Ni suahna lam kongpi ah.
chorus:
Nang kong dawn ding, Nang kong dawn ding,
Ni suahna lam kongpi sung tua lai ah,
Nang kong dawn ding, Nang kong dawn ding,
Nang kong dawn ding, zingsang tungin tua lai ah.

crossrefs: A sung by Rex Nelson Singer
verse2:
Neih le lam ka hau kei hi, Puan thak zong silh zo keng;
Topa Nang kong nei zo! Sum le paai hawm mah leeng,
Mite’n hong pimuh loh hang, Awlmawh taak sa nawn keng.
Nuam lua ing, Nong piak thupha hangin.
chorus:
Ka teen nading inn nong pia a, Nuamtakin Nong khim a,
An zong Nong vak den a, Khedap Nong guan hi,
It tawp lo Nong it a, Innkuan Nong nuam sak hi.
Nuam lua ing, Nong piak thupha hangin.

verse1:
Lo no nim dildial ni liim a om na ah,
A ta itte Pasian hong kha.
Tui dam luanna ah a gim te khe hong sil sak,
A ta itte Aman' hong kha.
verse2:
Khatvei le mual sang dawn ni tang silsial sung,
A ta itte Pasian hong kha.
Khat veivei mualkuam zang le zan khuamial lak,
A ta itte Aman' hong kha.
verse3:
Satan in hong do a dahna hong tun ciang,
A ta itte Pasian hong kha.
Hong hehpihna tawh i galte hong zawh pih,
A ta itte Aman' hong kha.
chorus:
Pawlkhatte tui thuk tuihual sungah,
Pawlkhatte mei sung, sisan suang in thuak;
Zan thapai khuamial sung le sun hun in,
Amah phatna la hong sa sak zo den.

crossrefs: Zawhang 11:5, E. Taylor Cabbel (1849 - 1930), Floratt. Cassel (1852 - 1911)
verse1:
Mualtung le zanglei pan thu khat hong kiko sawn,
Khazih tungah thumaanna, thumaan cihtakna;
Tua la ngaih hong kithawn, Mual te’n zong hong thawn sawn,
Thumaanna hi, Thumaanna, Khazih tung thumanna.
verse2:
Za un, tua la kithawn, leitung teng thawn kawikawi,
Khazih tungah thumaanna, thumaan cihtakna;
Sem gam dingin tho un, Thumaan ging sak un, tu'n,
Thumaanna hi, Thumaanna, Khazih tung thumanna.
verse3:
Thumaan pawl hong pawm un, khialhna bei sak khawm un.
Khazih tungah thumaanna, thumaan cihtakna;
Satan' dial khiatna mun, Pengkul tumin do un,
Thumaanna hi, Thumaanna, Khazih tung thumanna.
verse4:
Thahat lai khangnote, Zeisu tung kipia ni,
Khazih tungah thumaanna, thumaan cihtakna;
Leitung gam khempeuh ah, Taangko ni lungdam thu,
Thumaanna hi, Thumaanna, Khazih tung thumanna.
chorus:
Gal zo ding kuan un! Gal zo ding kuan un!
I galkap Mangpa’n ci: "Kuan!"
A hong sawlna mang ni.
I ngah ding hi tua gam, Thumaanna hi,
Thumaanna, Khazih tung thumaanna.

engTitle: Home Is Where the Heart Is
verse1:
"Inn mah ki lunggulh pen hi." cih paunak ka za zel hi,
Mi tampite in inn mah lunggulh sa ing;
Kei bel Topa Zeisu tawh kikholh ding mah lunggulh veng, 
Amah tawh kiteeng khempeuh-peuh leng ka vakthap nawn kei ding.
verse2:
Inn mah khenglah ih hih leh, Zeisu' tenna inn hi veh,
Amah tawh ten ding lunggulh bel in nei ing;
Sum le paite ka nei kei hi, Gual nopna ka zong kei hi,
Ka To Zeisu in van ah innpi nei teh hong ci nuam sing.
verse3:
Inn leh lo deih masa keng, Nopsakna ding zong teel keng,
Ahih hang lawm hoih tampi ke’n ka nei hi;
Hih leitung ka nusia baih ding, Ka deihna Topa’n cin' ding,
Ka tun ngei lohna inn lianpi ah tun' ding ka ngaklah hi.
chorus:
"Inn mah ki khenglah pen hi," cih kei ading ka kha muanna hi,
Ka ciahna ding mun Paradise ai ve,
Hih lei-ah mun tampi teeng zo ing, tua khempeuh ken cimtak zo ing,
Zeisu ka kipiak teh ka khenlah van a zuan ding kai ve!

zoTitle: Nuam Lua Ing, Ka Honpa Hang
engTitle: Thanks to God for My Redeemer
crossrefs: Zawhang 16:33, August Ludwig Storm, Tr. by Corl E. Backstorm, TRACK O GUD, J. A. Hultman
verse1:
Nuam lua ing, Nong piak Honpa hang,
Nuam lua ing, Nong huhna hang,
Nuam lua ing, Zeisu ka kiang om,
Nuam lua ing, hun beisa hang;
Nuam lua ing, khuahun nuamte hang,
Nuam lua ing, zan khuamial hang,
Nuam lua ing, khitui nong nul sak,
Nuam lua ing, lung nopna hang.
verse2:
Nuam lua ing, thungetna Nong dawn,
Nuam lua ing, Nong dawn loh hang,
Nuam lua ing, buk na'ng inn Nong pia,
Nuam lua ing, Nong vaakna hang;
Nuam lua ing, haksat nuamna hang,
Nuam lua ing, Nang Nong hehnem,
Nuam lua ing, Nong hehpihna hang,
Nuam lua ing, Nong itna hang.
verse3:
Nuam lua ing, paak hoihte hangin,
Nuam lua ing, paak lingte hang,
Nuam lua ing, innlum, lolum hang,
Nuam lua ing, lametna hang,
Nuam lua ing, dah le nuamna hang,
Nuam lua ing, khamuanna hang,
Nuam lua ing, ka lametna hang,
Nuam lua ing, tawntung sung dong.

zoTitle: Topa In A Khut Tawh Hong Lawng Hi
engTitle: I Was Touched by the Hand of the Lord
chorus:
Topa in a khut tawh hong lawng hi.
Lung khamna up lohnate mang ta;
Ka kha lungdam kipak,
Hong suah taak, hong damsak,
Topa in a khut tawh hong lawng hi

verse1:
La sa thei ing khawl in ka phawk ciangin ah,
Lung gimna tam ka gual zawh nang hi zaw,
Tua lampi te’n a saan na hong tun pih a,
 Hih leitung bel teen suak nang hi kei zaw.
verse2:
Leitung nate ih thupi’t sakna kiam ding,
Hong kikawm pak a hih lam phawk thei leng,
Lunggulhna tawh hong liingsak leitung nate,
Nuih san lel ni a mu khol thei hi leng.
verse3:
Hih leitung ah nasepna, gimna dim a,
Gen theihna leh gimna ih tuak pahpah,
Mite’ kha in mu van lai leeng ding bang a,
Kikhah peuh leh a tupna "Van" tung pah.
chorus:
Tua ni ciangin ke’n pawh la sasa mai ning,
Tua ciangin ka lungdam den ta ding;
Tua ni ciang in, Ka mit ten khuapi en ding
Pasian in kei,
Tuah hong sam ding.

zoTitle: Tuukhun Nong Khap Man Nuam Si'ng
engTitle: Thank God for the Promise of Spring
verse1:
Ka tungah meii a vom hangin,
Sun khuavak ka, muh theih loh hang,
Meii vom sung pan ni vang in hong kap suk in,
A nuih mai mu dek ding hi hang.
verse2:
Ih tenna tul in kolh hangin,
Khaicite zong, A kausan hang,
Tuate khempeuh hong no kik pah ding uh hi,
Tuuk hong nai kuan mahmah thei ta’ng.
chorus:
Tuuk hun nong khap manin nuam zen sing,
Khatvei la saa kik thei ning,
Ni thak khat hong suak kik dek ta ding,
Tuuk hun Nong khap manin nuam sing.

zoTitle: Zeisu Phatna La Simloh Sak Ding Nei Keng
verse1:
Zeisu phatna la simloh sak ding nei keng,
Pasian’ Ta hi, hong hon ding hong pai Pa,
Mawh mai na’ng le tatkhiat na’ng Aman thuak zo,
Singkhuam tungah a nuntakna pia zo.
verse2:
Ling lukhu le puan san Amah pia uh a,
Singlamteh tung a si manpha baang hi,
Hong pai kik ding lametna a han hawm a,
Hih thu mi teng tung ka sa den ding hi.
verse3:
Zeisu phatna la simloh sak ding nei keng,
Gun gal khatah ka tun ciang nangawn in,
Vantung mite tawh phatna la sa khawm leng,
Kei hong Honpa tawntung ka phat ding hi.
chorus:
Zeisu phatna la simloh sak ding nei keng,
Kalvari leh Khazih bek sasa ning,
La kasak sial hih thu mah tang ko den ning,
Sa sa den ning, a lamdang hong itna.

engTitle: Little Is Much, When God Is In It
verse1:
Lo sungah ante min khin zo,
Mi’kim sep theih ding om a,
Ngai dih ve, Pasian in hong sam,
Tua ante a la ding in.
verse2:
Topa in nang hong koihna mun,
Neu in kuama’n theih loh hang,
Hong koih pa hangin thupi hi,
A man hong mangngilh ngeilo.
verse3:
Na pumpi hong zawngkhal tadia,
Sep zawh loh hun hong tun ciang,
Thungetna tawh Topa' ading,
Gal nasim thei lai veve.
verse4:
Leitung haksat nate nusia’n,
I nasep i zawh khit ciang,
Citak-a nasempa tungah,
Pha hi,"ta" hong ciah ta’n ci.
chorus:
Pasian kihelna neucih omlo,
Minthanna hauhna zong ken,
Zeisu min suanga nasep leh,
Kham lukhu na ngah ding hi.

zoTitle: Ka Mitte Khitui Tawh Hong Sil Sak Hi
engTitle: He Washed My Eyes with Tears
verse1:
Ka mitte khitui tawh hong sil sak hi,
Tel takin khua ka muh theih zawk nang hi,
Ka lungtang phelkham a, a sung en hi,
Launa, kisak theihna, ngen tang mu hi,
Ka mit hong mial sak meii sem khiain bei,
Tu’n ka mit kihong a, khua ka mu thei,
Kei hoih peen nang a hi, tu’n ka thei hi,
Ka mitte khitui tawh hong sil sak hi.
verse2:
Ka mitte khitui tawh hong sil sak hi,
Hih zah tak hong itna lamdang lua hi,
Kei khut tang ding a khut kikhen let aa,
Kei khe tang ding a khe  kikilh cip hi,
Kei mawh a sian’ nading A si bua a,
Kei thuak ding dan khempeuh Aman thuak hi,
Tu’n kei pawh nuam mah si'ng, Tatsa ka hi,
Ka mitte khitui tawh hong sil sak hi.

engTitle: Will You Make Me This Promise Too?
verse1:
Khatvei ni ciangin ah, kikhen cih om nawn lo ding,
Ih leitung khual zinna hong bei ding,
Hi zong, mangpha kikhak ma’n, Ih nuntakna a bei ma in,
Kamciam na nong pia ngam diam tuni’n.
verse2:
Ke’n bel hong kamciam ing, Gun piauah ih kimu ding,
A dum dildial gun piauah teeng ding,
Lung kiatna cih om nawn lo, Singtehte zong vul ngei nawn lo,
A pai sa lawmte mu ding hi zo!
verse3:
In nun’na ah sihna tung peelmawh ding cih thei hang,
Bang lo kal hun sungin bei thei hi,
Khatvei ni teeiteei ciangin, Ei’ tungah hong tung veve ding,
Tua ni ading na khamuang nai diam?
chorus:
Khat khat in gun gal khatah ih kan ta ding aa,
Kihal lo in a kan ih om zeel ta,
Tua man kiptak nong kamciam diam,
Gun piauah ih kimu ding hiam?,
Ken bel tung ning ci’n hong kamciam ing.

crossrefs: Isa. 25:4, Mosie Lister, Worship His Majesty 539
verse1:
Zankim khua mial laitakin,
Lau in ka bu zeel a, ka tungah huihpi nungin,
Ka belh ding lah thei keng,
Hih van ginna phual panin,
Hong ngai-in, kong thumna,
"Hong kem in huihpi a ve'n mateng."
verse2:
Hahkat hang a mawkna pi,
Dahna bei thei lo pi, lametna zong om beek kei ci'n,
Satan' hong khem hi,
Aih hang Nong ompih thei ing,
Zing ciang tho to in-ah,
"Ka pai ding huihpi om lohna ah."
verse3:
Zan saupi bei khinta a,
Huihpi a ven ciang in, Na maiah ka ding ding hi,
Tua a ta'ng gun gei-ah,
Tua gamah huihpi omlo
Hong teng ning Topa aw,
"Huihpi a ve'n khit tak ciangin maw."
chorus:
Huihpite veng mang khin a,
Vangingte a bei siang dong,
Van a meeite bei mang a, khua phat dong,
Topa aw hong len in, Na khutkuak sung hong koih in,
Hong kem in huihpi a ven mateng.

zoTitle: Nuntak Tawntungna Ciktui Ka Dawn Hi
verse1:
Mawhna, zumna dim leitung ah ka dangtak hi,
A pha sak thei bangmah ka mu kei hi,
Nuntak tawntung na ciktui tampi a luanna,
Thupha Khazih kiang ni khat ka pai hi.
verse2:
Pasian kiang pan hong luang tui-in lim mahmah a,
A tawntung in ka lung hong damsak hi,
Min thanna hehpihna le thupha ka ngah hi,
Nisim in "Hallelujah" la ka sa.
verse3:
Nang zong tu ni'n Kalani pai lo ding na hiam?,
Tua takah thuk a zai ciktui luang ci,
Na kha dangtakna a pha sak thei tua munah,
Tua tui dawn ding Honpa'n tun nang hong sam.
chorus:
Nuntak tawntung na ciktui ka dawn hi,
Tu'n ka lungdam hi,
Ka kha dangtak nawn kei,
Nuntak tawntung na ciktui ka dawn hi,
O a lamdang tui tampi a luang hi.

zoTitle: Pasian' Khut In Hong Keembit Hi
engTitle: Sheltered in the Arms of God
verse1:
A neel a dik khut in hong lawn ke'n ka phawk,
Tua khut in ka lampi ah hong makaih,
Zeisu tawh ka ton khop ciang lau om nawn lo,
Pasian' khut in kei hong kep hang hi.
verse2:
A sawt loin van pan sapna ka za ding,
"Ka ta hong ciah'n na khual zinna tung ta teh,"
Ihmu suk in vantung ah ka khang lo ding,
Pasian' khut in kei hong keem bit hi.
chorus:
Tuihual lianpi om in, khua hong mial hang,
Hong lungkham sak lo,
Pasian' khut in kei hong keep bit manin ah,
Hong tonpih man leitung in hong zo lo ding,
Pasian' khut in kei hong keem bit hi.

zoTitle: Nute' Hong Itna Bang Zah In Lian!
verse1:
Mim bang ka pian cil in, ka nu'n hong it manin,
A aang nunkhumtui tawh hong vak den a,
Ka deihna bangbang in hong gamtat sak manin,
Ka nu hong itna bang zah in lian hiam?
verse2:
Ka nu'n man phat nading, a hong pattah manin,
Nu aw nong itna lian ka phawl den a,
Topa'n hong hehpih in na nun kum sawt sak hen,
Sim leitung kum sawt gua bang hing khawm leeng.
verse3:
Nute' pumpi khempeuh ei aa dingin manpha,
A aang ah hong tawiin hong lum sak a,
A nungah hong pua in nuamtak hong ihmu sak,
Nu aw nong itna lian ka phawk den hi.
chorus:
Hong it ka nu, bang tawh ka teh thei diam?,
Nong ho kam khum bang tawh ka teh thei diam?,
Lei zawh loh suang manpha sang lian zaw hi,
Nu aw nong ho kam khum za nuam den ing.

crossrefs: Philipih 3:7, Charles Wesley, SAGINA, Thomas Campbell
verse1:
Kei hong Honpa sisan sung pan,
Hamphatna ke'n ngah thei ding maw?,
Amah gim sak keima' ading
Keima ading in hong si maw?
verse2:
Van a A pa' tokhom nu sian',
Khawnkhong itna bei ngeilo tawh,
Vantung liatna khempeuh nusian,
Cimawh Adam' tate hon maw?
verse3:
Kei guak om hang' lau nawn kei ing, Amah kei aa, kei Ama aa,
Ka lutang hi, A sung' teeng ing,
Thumaan thutak in hong tuam ta.
chorus:
Hi thei ding maw ka Pasian aw,
Nangmah takpi hong si ding maw?,
Lamdang itna ka Pasian aw,
Nang mah takpi hong si ding maw?

crossrefs: 1&2: Gin Khat Suan, 3: Thang Gin Lian
verse1:
Theihloh meel mak gam zang sing vang khua pan lungzuan za tam,
Tun nu mu bang hong ngai ing tang bang na dam lai nam,
Ang lai nun khum leh na' tong nem no lungah sial leng,
Aw, na von lungzuang sial zatam tawh tui bang kiam veng,
Tuanglam ka sik khial a zong, Tun na min thei bang kong lo,
Hei na peuh tum bang guai dong, tun ngaih gim duangah theng mawh,
Tun ngaih aw, Tun ngaih aw, kawi-ang pan ke'n hong sial lai veng, Tang bang na dam in mim bang pianna, Sen tunnu aw.
verse2:
Thei bang sen zu bang mom aa, tongdam nem tawh ma bang nong pat,
Gual lai sawl bang hei mai mit nong suat zal mang nong mat,
Sei sang tang kuan gi bang kikhenna heina khat lo,
Zan ciang zal mang meel in hong mu ing sen tunnu aw,
Ei bawl sin thu hi lo aa khang vai mang nu sin thu,
Ho nuam lai gi bang kikhen, lai lung zuan za tam Tunnu,
Tungsian mang in hong huai hen heina peuhah tang bang dam ni,
Na von lungzuang meel hong mu lai aw, Sen tunnu aw.
verse3:
Tun aw, sin lai lungah nau bang na san, Sian mang sin thu,
Na tawi vonno te'n tuu bang cingin, paai bang kuah ung,
Sian in lum bang hong sung gual tawh tan bang kim ta ung,
Lai lung muang in maw, mim bang pian na, sen tunnu aw,
Ei bawl sin thu hi lo aa khang vai mang nu sin thu,
Ho nuam lai gi bang kikhen, lai lung zuan za tam Tunnu,
Tungsian mang in hong huai hen heina peuhah tang bang dam ni,
Na von lungzuang meel hong mu lai aw, Sen tunnu aw.

zoTitle: Khanan Gam Zuau In Ka Pai Hi
engTitle: I Am Bound for the Promised Land
verse1:
Zawdan gun gei-ah ding in a gal lam,
Lunggulhna tawh ka en,
Nop tuak mahmah kei luah ding gam,
Khanan ka gal muh hi.
verse2:
Tua gam zapi zang lei nuamah kuan a,
Vaak tawntung na mun hi,
Pasian' Tapa' maanna hi a,
Zan khualmial om nawn lo.
verse3:
Tua gam ah natna sihna kikhenna,
Te om nawn lo ding a,
Dahna launate bei siang ding,
Tua lungdamna gam sungah.
verse4:
Cik ciang tua gam nuam sung,
Kei ka tung ding hiam?,
Kei tung mengmeng nuam ing,
Ka Pa mai nuam enen nuam ing,
Khawl nuam ing A aang ah.
chorus:
Tua gamnuam a sawt lo in a,
Luah dingin i pai ta ding hi,
O kua teng in hong zui nuam diam?,
Tua Khanan gam nuamah.

verse1:
Leitung kimkot in kei khualzin ngei keng,
Gam hoihte le mun nop ci ke'n tam muh ngei keng,
Ahih hangin kei ka khualzinna mun khat om a,
Calvary mual a ka Honpa en dingin.
verse2:
Zeisu paina Calvary lam ke'n zui ing,
Pasian Tapa kikhaina ke'n ka mu khin hi,
Ka khukdin a khitui luangin ka thumna hong za,
Oh! praise the Lord kei Calvary ah pai ing.
chorus:
Calvary pai khin ing, ke'n Topa ka mu khin ta,
Calvary pai khin ing,
A kammalte tung panin hong itna siangtho hang,
Tua in kei hong liingsak hi,
1: A thei ding tua Honpa kei a hi.
2: A phawk ding tua Honpa kei a hi.
3: Lung ngai ding tua Honpa kei a hi.

verse1:
Zeisu thungetna huanah a khutte hen sak uh aa,
Kong lakah zumhuai pi'n pai pih,
Mawh neilo a siangtho Honpa
Cilphih gawp uh aa,
Mawh hi, sing tung that un ci uh hi.
verse2:
A manpha a lutung ah ling lukhu khu sak uh,
Zahpih in "Kumpi en un" ci,
Haamsiat in sat gawp uh aa,
Min siangtho zah pih uh
 Na khempeuh Amah bek in thuak hi.
verse3:
Sing tung a khet uh ciangin ah, A nu a gei ding aa,
"Numei na ta en in!" a ci,
"Tui ka duh hi" ci na pi'n
Dawn ding bangmah pia lo aa,
Mawhnei mite thahna a thuak hi.
verse4:
Migilo te tung kiap in, hehpihna a ngen kei hi,
Zumna sing Amah kia'n thuak ta,
"A zozo hi" ci'n awng aa, lusu in si ta hi,
A lamdang hotkhiat nasep manta.
chorus:
Leitung susia'n Amah khah khia ding,
Vantung mi tul sawm sam thei napi'n,
Vantung mi tul sawm sam thei na pi'n,
Nang leh kei aading'n in hong si hi.

verse1:
Kumpipa' galkap dingin sapna aw kiza,
Gal kuan ding galkapte, sapna na za hiam?,
Lawpna tawh zekaai lo, dawng in hong sapna,
Nangma ut tawmna tawh na min na pia diam?
verse2:
Vaang tawh a dim galkap ding Zeisu in hong sam,
Ama na a seem ding, nisim naisim in,
Hong taisan lo ding pi, ih kiang hong om den,
Nangma ut tawmna tawh na min na pia diam?
verse3:
Migi mahmah Topa in hong it man hong sam,
Mi nam kimte aa ding, A lung himawh mi,
Tu'n zong hong sam lai veh, Aw kitel takin,
Nangma ut tawmna tawh na min na pia diam?
verse4:
Gal kisimna hun bei-in gal ih zawh ciangin,
Thuman diktat mite, hong kikhop ciangin,
Min thanna kumpi lukhu hong khu sak ding,
Nangma ut tawmna tawh na min na pia diam?
chorus:
Zeisu aading a thuman, a hoih galkap,
Midang te'n min pia zo, nang e leh?,
Zeisu Kumpipa hi, launa ding om lo,
Nangma ut tawmna tawh na min na pia diam?

verse1:
Mite'n gen uh ka khual zinna gamla pekpek munah,
Aksi le vante khengin ka zin ding,
Sik longte kitumna munah,
Van mite la sakna munah,
Van inn ka lut teh ka mu ding.
verse2:
Tawm vei sung ih kikhen hangin ih tot lam kibang hi,
Nang kia na zin hangin "Lungkia kei in",
Lawmte in hong dawn ding uh aa,
Zeisu in zong hong muak ding aa,
Van inn na lut teh na mu ding.
chorus:
Lung khamna le dahna tam, kei kia ka zin laitak,
Khat veivei nopna a om teei hang,
Gamla pekpek munah O! Topa khatvei teiiteii,
Teeng na ve'ng, Teeng na ve'ng.

verse1:
Kum leh hun tampi bei ta, ka zak masak pek pan,
Zeisu hong pai ding nai zaw sem ta,
Kiging khol in sanggam aw, Hong huh thei lo ding kai ve,
Hong pai ding hun nai mahmah ta aive!
verse2:
Kidona hong tam semsem, gitlohna khang semsem,
Upmawh loh laitak hong pai ding ci,
Pasian' kammal taang tung ta,
A teelsate hong la ding,
Muan' om nawn ke'n Zeisu hong pai ding hi!
chorus:
Mun tengah lim hong kilangh ta,
Thusia lasia tawh leitung kidim ta,
Vantung lam vilin ngak gige in,
Na lu phong in, tatna ni hong nai ta!

verse1:
Tuipi geiah ka ding a, a gal khat lam ka galet leh,
Tuipi geiah tembaw khat a khawl ding mu ing ee,
A maute a dawn dingin, A lawmte tampi om veh,
It teng tawh kikhen lohna, Vantung hong phawk sak ee.
verse2:
Ka nu in nunna huihpi thuakin hong paisan khin zo a,
Tawntung mun hong pi dingin, Honpa nei teh hong ci,
Tu'n ka telsiang thei ta hi, ke'n zong tua mun ka zuan ta,
Ka nu'n gal-ah hong ngak hi, nui kawm'n hong dawn ta ding.
chorus:
Innlam ka zuan hi, Zion tembaw tung tuangin,
Gal khat pekah meilum lak-ah a taang ka galmuh ta,
Tembaw khawlna ciang dong, hoihtak, inn ka tun mateng in,
Vantung mite aw, kei hong kha aw!

verse1:
Leitung ah inn hoihpi cih nei kei ing,
Topa hong piaksa bukno khat nei ing,
Tua sungah Ama hong piak thupha sang ing,
Mi dangte in kei hong theih pih kholh loh uh hang,
Topa hong piak thupha tawh kei ka lungkim hi,
Tawmvei hih leitung a kantan pak ka hi,
Mi hau tampite neih bang ka neih zawh loh hangin.
verse2:
Khat veivei leitung ah ka maimial a,
Ka kiim ka paam a mite ka en kha,
Amaute in ih Honpa thei het lo a,
Bang hangin dau pai in nuamsa thei cih thei khang,
Pasian kammal hoih tak ka et kik tak ciangin,
Ih suah lai-in bangmah ih ken' loh mah bang'n,
Ih leitung nun'na bei in, lei ih nusiat ciangin,
Ih neihsa bangmah kengin ciah ding hi khang.
chorus:
Na lung kham ke'n, lung hei nei ke'n,
Vantung a ka Pa um in,
Kei zong hong um peuh le cin, na om nading bawlin pai ning,
Mite lam tawm a hilo, Innpi liante kong lam sak,
A hun tun' ciang i teeng ding hi.

zoTitle: Vantung Pawh Nuam Mah Si Ih Ci Ding
engTitle: This is Just What Heaven Means To Me
verse1:
Hua gamah gimna natna om nawn lo,
A tawntung in-ah ih lung nuam den ta ding,
Tua khuapi ah huihpi cih bang kimu nawn lo,
Vantung nuam mah si ee ih ci ding!
verse2:
Khatvei ciang Zeisu' mai tang ihmu ding,
A maitang mu peuh leng lungzuan om thei lo,
Kumpi te Kumpipa ci'n i phat den ding hi,
Vantung nuam mah si ee ih ci ding.
chorus:
Hua gal khatah ih kimuh ciang nuam si'n teh!
Tatsa mi honte tawh ih kikhawl ding,
It teng tawh kimu in Khazih Kumpi suah ciang,
Vantung nuam mah si ee ih ci ding.

zoTitle: Nang Deihna Mun Peuhah Pai Ning
engTitle: I'll Go Where You Want Me to Go
verse1:
Topa hong deihna mun ke'n thei keng, mual tung sangpi maw tui tung
Gal mai, sa mai bangmah ke'n thei keng
Hong deihna khat om ding hi
A aw khumno tawh hong sam leh maw?
Gam mial maw khuapi sung maw?
Hi hen! Topa aw, ka khut hong len kip in
Pai ning Na deihna mun peuh ah
verse2:
Mawhna sungah kha mangthangte kiang, Lungdamna thu gen dingin
Lampi haksa khuamial sungah zong
Topa hong makaih in maw
Tua lungdamna thu ka gen ding a
Nong gen sak thu khumte
Hi hen! Topa aw, tua thu ka gen ding
Gen ning Na deihna bangbang in
verse3:
Leitung bup ah ante min khin zo, a gina lo mun ah zong
Leitung tom no i nuntak sungin
Zeisu ading in sem ni
Ka vai na khempeuh Nangma kong ap
Kei nong it luat thei ing!
Lungsim tak tawh Na deih bang seem ning
Nang deihna bangbang mang ding hing
chorus:
Kong it Topa aw, Nong sawlna peuh ah
A mual, a guam zang sungah
Gen ding a Nong deih bangbang gen ding
Nong deihna mun peuhah pai ning

verse1:
A gim mite khawl nang mun khat om hi
Lungnop tawldamna mun hi
Inn dei tungnung ah Zeisu tawh lungkham vangikte hong puak sak
verse2:
A tawl khualzin mi ading tuivot om
Lungsim tam khamte' ading damna
Vangik pua a gim mite' ading zong tawldamna tak Aman hong pia ding
chorus:
Inn dei tungnung a Zeisu tawh
A khe phung ah ka tu hi
Oh, Oh kikholh khopna nuam zen si!
Topa'n lung nopna hong pia

crossrefs: Zawhang 15:13, F.M. Lehman, Arranged by Claudia L. Mays
verse1:
Pa' hong itna lian zen si maw! Gen zawh hi lo, gelh zawh hi lo
Aksi sang pente sang' sang zaw, Hell niam pen sung nangawn ban zo
Mawh neite hong ngah kik dingin, A Tapa hong pia hi
Amah tawh hong kilem sak a, Mawhna hong maisak hi
verse2:
Haksatna hun hong bei ding a, Leitung gamte hong bei ding hi
Mite'n mualte tung thum ding a, Hong vukcip un, ci ding uh hi
Ahih hang Pasian' hong itna, Kisia ngeilo ding hi
Adam' tate hong hehpihna, Van mite'n sa ding hi
verse3:
Tuipi khempeuh laitui hi in, Vantung khempeuh laidal hi le
Singkung khempeuh laikung hi le, Mi khempeuh in gelh thei hi le
Pasian' hong itna gelh sak leng, Tuipi hong bei ding hi
Vantung dimin ih gelh zongin, Kicing zolo ding hi
chorus:
Pa' hong itna, lian zen mah si, Tehpih ding om lo hi
Kisia kik ngei nawn lo ding ci,
Van mite'n sa ding hi

verse1:
I nuntak khualzinna hong bei pak ding
Gamlapi a om a hoih gun piau ah
A taang van innah i kimuh mateng
Kimu kik nawn lo kha ding hi hang
verse2:
Gi bang khen leeng sin lai hong kuai thei a
Kikhen thunget in, lai lung na sak in
Aih! hang vantung ah dahna om nawn lo
Kimuh kik dong Sian nang tawh om hen
verse3:
Mei vom kai in van te a khuh loh na
Tua lai-ah i dah ngei nawn kei ding hi
Nung ciangin a nopna tua gun gei-ah
Kimu kik ding tua gam pha bel sung
chorus:
Leitung ah kimuh kik loh hang
Haksat nate i phut kawmin, khua ah i kimuh nang mun khat
Nuntakna luitui gei hi ding
Paak hoihte a tawntung paak ding, Kikhen na zong om nawn lo ding hi
Leitung ah i kimuh loh hang, Hoih gun piau ah kimu ding

verse1:
Zeisu kia in, Gethsemane huanah A hong thuak hi
A dah huai pen dahna hai kei' aading in hong dawn hi
Kalani mualah Amah kia in singlamteh pua in
Pa' deihna bangin Honpa hong pai hi
verse2:
Zeisu kia in, a gilo singkhuam tungah hong si hi
Kei' sian nading a manpha A si hong luang khia sak hi
Khuamial dai paam, lei vot sungah, Amah guak kisial hi
Pa' deihna bangin Honpa hong pai hi
verse3:
Zeisu kia in, a kisin cip han sung pan hong tho hi
Sihna zo in launa, dahna khempeuh bei mang sak hi
A pa' ngim sa bangin na khempeuh kicing sak zo hi
Pa' deihna bangin hong nungta kik hi
verse4:
Zeisu kia in, ka mawhna khempeuh hong paihkhiat sak hi
A lauhuai thu khenna pan mawhnei keimah hong hon hi
Gen zawh loh nuamna le lungdamna tawh ka kidim hi
Pa' deihna bangin ka nungta nuam hi
chorus:
Hi hi, Honpa kia bek kei ading hong si hi!
Hi hi, mawhna pan hong suakta sak khin zo hi!
Lametna bei, mawhna tawh dim, Hih khuamial leitung ah
Pa' deihna bangin Honpa hong pai hi

zoTitle: Nung Ciangin I Thei Na Ding Hi
verse1:
Lunggimna haksa i tuah ciangin ah
Bang hangin ke'n hih zahta thuak a
Ka kiim ka paam a, mi dangte in lah
Tuak ngei se lo hiam, lamdang ka sa
verse2:
I it i ngaih khat sihna'n ong laak ciang
I inn sung hawmin, ong gamdai a
Banghang a hiam kei' thuakna hihzah liang
Khantawn mi tatsiate lah nuamsa
verse3:
Ong it i Topa'n A hong vaikhakna
Tawl khat na thuak keeikaai lai le teh
Gen tham lo ding hi tu a na thuakna
Van innpi nuam sung na lut tak teh
verse4:
Van innpi nuam sung lut hun a tun ciang
I Topa in ei ong la hi a
Ama inn nuam sung A mai i muh ciang
Tel siang ding hi hang i lung manna
chorus:
Nung ciang a vekpi'n i thei na ding hi
Banghang ei dah a mi nuamsa hiam?
Na lung nuam sak in ni taang khuavak ah
I telna ding hi i nua ciangah

zoTitle: Ka Khut Hong Len In, Topa Aw
verse1:
Ka lampi lauhuai ciang, hong nai in keima kiang
Ka sih dek laitak Topa
Ka thumna hong ngai aw, ka puk ding hong len aw
Innpi ah hong tun in maw, Topa
verse2:
Sun in hong tum san in, khua hong mui semsem in
Zan khuamial in hong tuam ta
Gun gei-ah ka ding khin, hong len in, hong pi in
Innpi ah hong tun in maw, Topa
verse3:
Khualzin hun bei dek ta, hong makaih in, Topa
Kei hong hatsak in, Topa
Nang aa ka hi khin zo, kei kia pai ding hi lo
Innpi ah hong tun in maw, Topa
verse4:
Hong phongin, hong len aw, hong kai in, Topa aw
Kei ka gim kei ka zawm, kei ka bah
Huihpi nung ta se leh, khuavak ah hong pi ve
Innpi ah hong tun in maw, Topa

zoTitle: Topa' Nasepna Ah Nuamsa Semsem Ing
engTitle: The Longer I Serve Him The Sweeter He Grows
verse1:
Zeisu'n ka vekpi'n hong tang khin,
Amah ka piak nung sang
Ka lungsim ka piak khit nung sang
Topa' nasepna ah, nuamsa semsem ing
verse2:
Ka sapna khempeuh hong pia hi,
Tam zaw sem sim zo keng
Nisim ka lampi hong tang sak
Topa' nasepna ah, nuamsa semsem ing
chorus:
Topa nasepna ah nuamsa semsem ing
Nisim in tha hong guan hong thahat sak hi
Vantung gam bang hi ka lung sung hong dim sak
Topa nasepna ah nuamsa semsem ing

verse1:
Hih leitung ah ka khen’ lah na khempeuh in
Hong kikawm pak hi, kei a’ hi kei;
Zeisu in ka nuntak sung hong zat sak pak a hi,
Hong phawk sak in, phawk sak in, Topa.
verse2:
Pasian Ta suah nading hoihna khat beek nei keng,
A khut pawnte tawh kei kituak keng;
Ahih hang Kalani lampi kei ading’n teel zaw,
Hih zah hong itna ke’ n tel zo ke’ng.
chorus:
Topa aw keimah hong phawk sak zelzel in,
Nong hotkhiat man lau huaina tawh ka kipelh zo ta;
A mangngilh thei mi khat kahih man'n Topa
Hong phawk sak in, phawk sak in, Topa.

engTitle: Life at Best is very Brief
verse1:
Nuntak hun tom mahmah hi,
Singteh pulh tawh kibang hi
Husan khat tawh kibang hi, Hun lap in!
Ani a nai hong cingcing
A hun na lap kei kha ding,
Na husan hong bei kha ding, Hun lap in!
verse2:
Paak hoih pen zong vul pak thei,
Meel hoihna zong kik pak thei
Sawtpi hing ding na hi kei, Hun lap in!
Kha Siangtho’ hong zol lai in
Mawhnei aw, vak nawn kei in,
Siatna na bawl suak ma-in, Hun lap in!
verse3:
Hunte mengmeng in bei hi,
Sihna, thukhenna nai hi
Zeisu’ ang va zuan ta ni, Hun lap in!
Lawm aw, geel in na tuak ding
Gimna mun na tung kha ding,
Hell khuk sung na tung kha ding, Hun lap in!
verse4:
Mawhnei aw, A aw ngai ve,
Tu’n Topa mah hong teel ve
Hong nuam pih ding vantung in, Hun lap in!
Khuamial pan khuavak zuan aw
Zeisu kibawl hoih sak aw,
Van lam zuan ding hong pai aw, Hun lap in!
chorus:
Hun lap in! Hun lap in!
Zeisu in nang hong sap lai in, Hun lap in!
Mawhna sung sawtna thaam leh,
Kong honsa’n mu kei niteh.
Na kiko na’n lap ken the, Hun lap in!

zoTitle: Ka Pa Inn Sungah Omna Tampi A Om Hi
verse1:
Ka Pa’ inn sungah omna tampi a om hi
Om kei leh Amah in hong gen zo ding hi;
Tua khuapi nuamah teeng dii’n Amah pai zo hi
Kei ading omna hong bawl sak ka thei hi.
verse2:
Zeisu in singlamteh tung ka dahna pua a
Nuntakna thak na neih nang in hong si hi;
Ni khat ni ciangin Amah hong pai kik ding a,
Leitung ah mawhna, dahna om lo ding hi.
verse3:
Na lawmte’n hong nusia a, na lungzuan ciangin
Lungkham a na cih nang na theih loh ciangin;
Mawhna nusia in Zeisu’ kiang zuan pah le cin,
Gen zawh loh lung nopna nang hong pia ding hi.
chorus:
Sanggam aw, Hon Pa’ itna na nial kha kei in,
Nial le ci’n vantung la ngaih sa lo ding hi teh;
Ka Pa’ inn sungah omna tampi a om hi,
Zeisu na san leh nang zong pai ding hi teh.

zoTitle: Kum Tul Kum Then A Bei Zong
verse1:
Lawm aw na ngaihsun ngei maw Honpa hong paina
Sing tung zum huaina tawh a hong kithatna?
Na tel dong na kan ngei hiam hih zah hong thuakna
Kalvary ah hong sihna ei’ ding mawhlawh hong tawina.
verse2:
Zeisu’n ei hong kepna thu tel zo kei mah ni;
Ih lawm hong suakna thu, Hong hehnepna thu
Ih tel zawh loh thu tampi Pasian bek in thei
Hong itna lamdang manin tu in Amin lian phat ni.
chorus:
Kum tul kum then a bei zong hi thei ding maw?
Nang le kei' tang ding singlamteh tung/Hong sihna thu tel thei ding maw?
Ih mawhna a bei nangin mawh lo pi hong sihna thu
Kum tul kum then a bei zongin tua zah itna tel ding maw?

zoTitle: Siangtho Lawmpa Khat Ka Nei Hi
verse1:
Kei hong cing den siangtho lawmpa khat ka nei hi,
Kei tawh ton in ka lam hong pi den ta,
Hong lungdam sak, zan mial pen zong hong taang sak hi,
Ka Topa hi, ka pumpi hong uk ta.
verse2:
Kum tampi sung hong itna man thei kei kha ing,
Singlamteh tung hong sih thu ka zak ciang,
Amah ka muan teh keima Honpa hong suak ta,
Tua a kipan kei hong tonpih den hi.
chorus:
Lam haksa in a kawi hang phamawh sa keng,
Keen lak guam lak khuamial in tuam ta leh;
Ka kiang hong om den ka theih teh lungmuang ta ing,
Kham kong zing ah kei hong paipih ding hi.

verse1:
Topa aw, Na thupha khat nangawn
Ngah dingin Nang a' ding'n 
Bang sem khong ka hi ham?
Topa aw, Nong lahsa mi gitna
Itnate ngah dingin,
Bang sem khong ka hi hiam?
verse2:
Topa aw, Nang tung kong bat khempeuh
Loh zawh nangin lampi
A om leh hong hilh in
Topa aw, Nang kiang kong zuat kikna
Ka muhsa thu khempeuh
Ka lawmte kiang lak ning
chorus:
Hong huh in Zeisu,
Ka hun mawk bei sak kha ing Zeisu,
Kei bang mah man ke'ng
Tu'n Nang kong kisap lam
Thei ta ing tu'n hong huh in Zeisu
Ka hong ki-ap hi

verse1:
Lawm aw, Nang na lungkham in
Tua vangik na lel hiam?
Na vangik hong dawn dingin
Lawm aw, na zong ngei zel hiam?
verse2:
Khual zinpa kaw'h na om hiam?
Na meivak a taang hiam?
Na dah ciang hong hehnem ding,
Na sap ciang kua'n hong za hiam?
verse3:
Na lungkiatna kua'n thei hiam?
Na thumna kua'n za hiam?
Na lungkhamna kua'n tel hiam?
Na khitui kua'n hong nul hiam?
chorus:
Na thei maw, ka Zeisu?
Na thei maw, ka Lawm?
Aman nang hong it hi
A tawp dong hong ompih den ding hi

verse1:
Aw, a etlawm Betlen aksipi,
Khuamial thukpi hong taan ciaituai
Sawt veipi sung gam mang mi hong taan hi
Zeisu a kisialna mun dongah
Mi pilte lam paina lak hi,
Hong taan in etlawm Betlen aksi aw
verse2:
Aw, etlawm aksi, lamet khuavak,
Mual sang dawn pan zingsang mateng
Khualzinte zan tawntung in lam na lak
Khuavaak mahmah na ih tun ciang pawh
It huai vang tang khia sak ding hi,
Hong taan in etlawm Betlen aksi aw
verse3:
Aw, etlawm aksi, tawl damna lim,
Tat khiatsa midik ta dingin
Gal khat minthang kham lukhu ih san ciang
Zeisu'n tua siangtho aksi hi ta
Tang semsem, tang semsem ding hi,
Hong taan in etlawm Betlen aksi aw
chorus:
Aw, a etlawm Betlen aksipi
Ko tungah hong tangin zingsang mateng
Na khuavak tawh lampi hong taan in,
Khuavak mahmah gam tun mateng
Hong taan in etlawm Betlen aksi aw

zoTitle: Vanglian Khut Te'n Lam Hong Pi
verse1:
Kei hong kiphawk kha lo in ah,
A gam mang bang ka hih hang
Pasian in kei hong cing gige,
A mai ka muh theih loh hang
verse2:
A ma kiangah thu ka nget ciang,
Nuam sa'ng hong za ka theih teh
Ka lung khamna khempeuh ko ning,
Lungkham in kei ka vul teh
verse3:
Mihing khempeuh ading in ah,
Hong geel sak sa khat om aa
Ni khat ni teh ih thei ding a,
Leitung ni bei ciangin ah
verse4:
Ka kumte Amah'n sim khin aa,
Ka hun khempeuh zong keem hi
Natna, khitui a om lohna,
Gal khatah hong la ding hi
verse5:
Nung ciang bang piang ding ke'n thei keng,
Ka muan man zong lau tuan ke'ng
Upna hang ka ngah kha muanna,
Leitung tawh zong khek nuam ke'ng
chorus:
Vanglian khut ten'n lam hong pi,
Vanlian khut te'n lam hong pi
Hih leitung ka hin lai in,
Kei kia hilo ka thei hi
A vanglian khut te'n lam hong pi

verse1:
Leitung ah dahna tam, Lungsim sung launa tam
Mun tengah gal gim nam, bang cih khong ding?
Pasian kiang zuan le cin, Ama hehna pan in
Taang mi siangte bangin, na suakta ding
verse2:
Itna hong kiam ding a, inn leh lo bei ding a
Siatna hong tam ding a, Thu bu'n gen zo
Hih teng hong tun tak teh, Beina nai ding hi veh
Peengkul mut pak ven teh, mitphiat kal lo
verse3:
Gimna hong bei pah ding, tawntung lungdam den ding
Dahna om nawn lo ding, hong pai ciangin
Vantung ah leeng to ning, Leitung mangpha khak ning
Amah tawh mang khawm ding, tua hun ciangin
chorus:
Zeisu hong pai baih ding, Sun lai maw, zan maw zing
Mi tampi'n gim thuak ding, pengkul mut ciang
Misite tho kik ding, midik te'n van zuan ding
Si kik ngei nawn lo ding, Vantung tun ciang

verse1:
Pasian in ah, A tapa hong sawl,
Hong it ding le, hong damsak ding
Ka mawhnate maisak ding hong pai
Nungta ahih manin a han guak bek om hi
verse2:
Naungekte zong, Ama'n hong kep sak,
Bangzah takin, lungdam huai hiam
Tua sang in zong lungdam huai zaw lai
Nungta ai'h man lau nang om lo, cih thu mahmah!
verse3:
Ni khat ni ciang, sihna gul gal ah,
Haksa pi in, ka kah ding hi
Tua hun ciangin, sihna zo zo in
Amah Kumpi a hih lam ka mu thei ding hi
chorus:
Nungta a hih man, bangbang piang ta se leh
Phamawh sa ke'ng, zong lau beek ke'ng
Mailam hunte, A khut sung om cih thei ing
Amah nungta ahih man' ka nunna'n man nei

verse1:
Sihna mual kuam gal-ah khuapi khat a om hi
A hoihna kua man gen zo lo hi
Zan kim lai in tuuno in khuavak bang tang a
Tua a etlawm kham khuapi sungah
verse2:
Tua lai ah dahna, natna, sihna, om nawn lo
Mi siang khempeuh zong teek thei nawn lo
Tua khua-ah ut zen sing zan khuamial lah bei ta
Tua a etlawm kham khuapi sungah
chorus:
Tua lai ah, ni tum lo
Singteh zong vul ngeilo
Midikte a tawntung aksi bangin taang a
Tua a etlawm kham khuapi sungah

zoTitle: Tua Ni Ciang Bangzah In A Nop Zen Tam!
engTitle: What A Day That Will Be!
verse1:
Khatvei ciang gen theihna, om loh hun hong tung ding
Van ah meiite theng in, khitui luanna om lo ding
Tua a nuam kham khuapi ah a tawntung lungdam den ding
Tua ni ciang bangzah in a nop zen tam!
verse2:
Dahna om nawn lo ding, van puak ding om lo ding
Natna om nawn lo ding, kikhenna zong om lo ding
Kei tang ding a sipa tawh a tawntung teengkhawm den ding
Tua ni ciang bangzah in a nop zen tam!
chorus:
Zeisu ka muh ciangin bangzah in a nuam zen tam!
Hehpihna tawh hong Tanpa a maitang ka et ciangin ah
Ka khut in hong len ding aa, khapsa gamah hong paipih ding
Tua ni ciang bangzah in a nop zen tam!

zoTitle: Topa, Nang Ka Vision Hi In
verse1:
O Topa aw, Nang ka vision hi in
Nang lo kua in kei hong hon ding om kei
Sun le zan in Nang bek kong ngaihsun
Ihmut sung khanlawh ciang zong Nong ompih
verse2:
O Topa aw, Nang ka pilna hi in
Kei tawh Nang na hong om khawm tawntung ding
Nang ka Pa tatak kei Nangma ta
Kei sungah Nong teng a pumkhat i hi
verse3:
Hauh le mi phat ding ka vision hi kei
A tawntung in Nang ka neihgil na hi
Ka lungsim tawngah Nang bek na om
Vantung Kumpipa ka neihgil na hi
verse4:
Vantung Kumpipa ka gual zawhna hi
Vantung nopnate kei hong ban sak in!
Bangbang piang ta le ka lung sung ah
Na khempeuh a uk, ka vision na hi

verse1:
Vantung thusim khat za kha ngei ing
Tua in ka lunggulh luatna
Lai Siangtho in Tua mun hoihna hong gen
Ka Topa bawl kholh kei aa, ding mun
verse2:
Vantung pai nang leithei lo hi teh
Pai theih nang lampi khat om
Calvary ah, Topa'n a man pia khin
Hong pai ziau lel in, Tua sisan ah
verse3:
A lamdang tua khuapi ih tun ciang
Ih Topa maitang mu ding
A tawntung in a kha nuai-ah teng ding
Aw kei tawh hong pai khawm lo ding maw
chorus:
Vantung na geel khol thei hiam?
Lung nopna khempeuh kicin'na
Lungkhamna om nawn lo, Vangik khempeuh zang ta
Tua in a tawntung nopna hi

verse1:
Tan bang tehpih ding om lo pian-na ka zua pa aw
Na von tawite lo bang nong khualna lian lua
Sim leitung tom kal gua bang hingin ka dam lai teng
Zua pa itna lunglai ah, ngil ngei kei ning
verse2:
Thei bang ka sen lai pan in, zeh zum ding nong khual man
Gentheih haksat gimna tawlna nong thuak maw
Ka pil ding nong deih manin sin thu an bang nong muam
Tu in sian min phatin hong pahtawi ung ee
verse3:
Sim lei mi zatam lai ah, zua pa zatam lai ah
Pianna ka zua bang tawh ka teh thei ding hiam
Leitung hauhna sum leh paai kham leh ngun sangin zong
Manpha zaw lai leitung ka Pasian na hi
chorus:
Tung sianmang in liim bang hong sungin
Kum sawt tang bang dam khawm leng
Tun leh zua ang lim pan in na vontawi momno ten sian min phatin
Na min thei bang lolo nung

verse1:
Ka nu, ka tuun bang tuun nu
Koi mun koi kuam zong mah leng
Amah bang om lo hih lei ah
Ka nu hong it ka tuun nu
verse2:
Ka nu hong deihsak tuun nu
A ma nek tangin hong pia
Ka sapna khempeuh hong guan hi
Ka nu hong deihsak tuun nu
verse3:
Ka nu hong lainat tuun nu
Ka thuak tangin a man thuak
Ka haksak thuak ding hong phal lo
Ka nu hong lainat ka nu
verse4:
Ka nu pianna ka tuun nu
A khan kum khua sawt hen la
A sep gimnate thukkik leng
Ka nu pianna ka tuun nu
chorus:
Tuunnu bang tawh kong teh thei diam
Kham leh ngun sang zong na manpha zaw
Nong itna loh ding ka hin na'n cin kei
Ka leitung Pasian, hong it ka tuunnu

verse1:
Ka theih ngeiloh lungnopna ke'n ngah khin zo ta'ng
Leitung in hong piak theih loh nopna
Topa tung pum le kha ka kipiak khit nung sang
Lamdang a lamdang ka Topa
verse2:
Ka nuntakna khempeuh uk dingin kong deih hi
Tua hi leh kicing ding Na deihna
Na thu ngeihna bek in Na deihna kimsak hi
Lamdang a lamdang ka Topa
verse3:
Ka siamna khempeuh Na khe phungah kong nga hi
Nong san bangbang kei thaman hi pah
Ka neihsate khempeuh Nang tungah kong pia hi
Lamdang a lamdang ka Topa
verse4:
:Leitung-a a hoih pen sangin, Na hoih zaw hi
Nuntakna hong pia vanglian Topa
Tangtawng-a ka Pasian phat ding Na kilawm hi
Lamdang a lamdang ka Topa
chorus:
Lamdang ka Topa, lamdang ka Topa
Vantung misiang te'n phat in bia hi, van ah
Vanglian ka Honpa, kei aa Na hi ta
Lamdang a lamdang ka Topa

zoTitle: A Ni A Ni In Ngaih Semsem
engTitle: Sweeter as the Days Go By
crossrefs: 1Peter 1:8, S.S. 510, John R. Sweney (1837-1899), Mrs. Elisa Edmunds Hewitt (1851 -)
verse1:
A deihhuai tangthu Honpa itna thu
A ni a ni in ngaih semsem
Hong khap sa van inn hang lungmuanna thu
A ni a ni in ngaih semsem
verse2:
Nuntakna khuavak pan a vang tangpi
A ni a ni in tang semsem
Dahna hong hehnem kamciamna aksi
A ni a ni in tang semsem
verse3:
Huihpi nun ciang a hong len sik kippi
A ni a ni in kip semsem
Nuntak tawntungna thu i thei ta hi
A ni a ni in thei semsem
verse4:
Zeisu in eite hong piak lungnopna
A ni a ni in nuam semsem
Christian-te ading kihong lam etna
A ni a ni in lian semsem
chorus:
A ni sim in, Amah phatna la sasa ni
Hun zong nuam semsem,
Van a Pasian i phatna la
A ni a ni in ngaih semsem

engTitle: May They be United Forever, Wedding Band
crossrefs: Word: ZCLS la committee (1999), Tune: R.S. 11, William Howard Doane (1832-1915)
verse1:
Pasian geelsa hong tung ta, Lia le tang kigawmna
Itna tawh pumkhat suak ding, Khukdin uh, Na mai ah
Kamciamna kip la uh aa, Amau khutte kilen
Pasian gawmsa amaute, Mite in khenkei hen
verse2:
Nangma thupha namkim tawh, Lung nopna guan ta in
Gentheih hun le nopsak hun, Ki-it hun suak sak in
Inn sung, phung sung kilemna, kipatna suak uh hen
Christian innkuan hoih suak in, limpha lak den uh hen
verse3:
Topa aw, hiih nupate, Thupha tampi pia in
Tu le ta tawi uh hen la, Neih le lamh cing sak in
Upna, lawpna kip nei in, Nang sung lungkim uh hen
A khan kum uh sawt hen la, Tawntung kha kihual hen

zoTitle: Lia Leh Tang Mu Bang Kingai
crossrefs: Late 128:1-6, Neng Khan Cin (1957-), Tune: R.S. 790, George D. Moore 19th century
verse1:
Lia le tang mu bang kingai, Thei bang kilo
Kum sawt tang bang dam khawm uh hen
Seino gual te'n pak bang tawi, nun nop i zo
Sian' lungdeih tuang tunna hi hen
verse2:
Inn le lo suang zo dingin, Na siam in la
Khawhma, ehma daupai sak in
Zin le leng dosiam, innkuan suak sak in la
Van daingo tawh Na tuam den in
verse3:
Se sum minthang le sung nek, Mim le tang tawh
Nunnop liibang Na cing sak in
Zaitha saan uh hen, thunget lasakna tawh
Christian innkuan pha suak dingin
verse4:
Van Lau Kha Siangtho va bang hong leng in la
Nangmah'n zingvai Na hawm pih in
Simlei nun sungin, mi lun vontawi hen la
Thangvan tuang tun dong Na huai in
chorus:
Sih na'n sam gibang khen mateng, mateng in
Sian tawh maciang suan uh hen
Itna le tongciam na'n khaubang hualkhawm in
Gual lai ah ni bang tang uh hen

zoTitle: Zingni Suak Sangin A Tang Zaw
verse1:
Zingni suak sangin a tang zaw,
Ka Honpa le Kumpi hi,
Na hoihna le na thupitna,
La in ka sasa nuam hi.
verse2:
Vangliatna puan tawh kizem in,
Min thanna lukhu khu hi,
Thupha vangliatna le hatna,
A tawntung in na nei hi.
verse3:
Na migitna lian mahmah a,
Na hehpihna kicing hi,
Na ukna itna tawh dim a,
Kei a’ding hong bawlsak hi.
verse4:
Ngun meivak khaute kitat in,
Ka nuntakna bei ciangin,
Kumtul kum then Topa mai ah,
Phatna la ka sa ding hi.
chorus:
Zingni suak sangin a tangzaw,
Sun ni tang sang tang zaw Nang na hi,
Vangliatna tawh dim na mai ah,
Khuamial leh meii lum theng hi.

crossrefs: Heb. 13:8, Rev. A.B. Simpson, MP. 290, J.H.Burke
verse1:
Upna bek tawh i ngah theih thupha lamdang lua hi,
Zanni, tuni, a tawntung Zeisu kikhel lo hi,
Mawhneite  gum nuam, cinate zong damsak nuam den,
A dah mite lung nuamsak hi, A minthang ta hen!
verse2:
Mawhneite lawm bawlin gum nuam a, a hong zong Pa,
Tu’n zuanin, kisikna tawh kuun in, a khe phungah,
Thu hong khen kei ning, na mawh nawn ken a ci Pa in,
Na mawhna hong maisak nuam hi tanglai mah bangin.
verse3:
Leitung a om lai, Zeisu'n cinate damsak hi,
I natnate a thupiakna tawh dam thei lai hi,
Numei khat in a puan mong a lawn ciang dam pah hi,
Tua bang upna mah tawh nang zong hong damsak thei hi.
chorus:
Zanni tuni le a tawntung Zeisu kikhel lo,
Na dang khempeuh a kikhel hang Zeisu kikhel lo!
A minthang ta hen! A minthang ta hen!
Na dang khempeuh a kikhel hang, Zeisu kikhel lo!

zoTitle: Topa Kiang Lo Koi Pai Diam?
verse1:
Mawhna dim hih lei ah ka nuntakna,
Ka kha buk na’ng mun zong dingin,
Ze-etna lianpi ke’n ka sunsiah hi
Topa kiang lo, koi’h ka pai diam?
verse2:
I it lawmte khempeuhte ke’n it ing,
I lung sungah kingil thei lo,
Ka kha a’ding in Kha an kisam ing
Topa kiang lo, koi’h ka pai diam?
verse3:
Nun in nuam e hiah i it lawmte tawh,
Pasian hong piak hehnepna hi,
Sihna daitui ka tal ah hong kai ciang
Topa kiang lo, koi’h ka pai diam?
chorus:
Koi’h ka pai diam? Oh! koi ah ka pai diam?
Ka kha buk na’ng mun zong dingin,
Ni tawpni ciang hong gum ding kisam ing,
Topa kiang lo, koi’h ka pai diam?

verse1:
Khatvei lai in mawhnei ka hi a,
Mawhmai na’ng Topa ka zuat leh,
Hong kipia khong hilhial na hi a,
A kammal kip den hi veh
verse2:
Pasian’ hehna thuak ding launa tawh,
Singlamteh phung ka khukdin a,
Vantungte kihong in ka mit tawh
Ka min kigelh ka mu ta!
verse3:
Hehpihna hang gupna kingah ta,
Thu bu sung ka mu nuammah sing!
Telzo ing, ka mawhna mai zo ta!
Sisan hang dam siang zo ing
chorus:
Van gam sungah min thak khat kigelh hi,
Kei’ min hi, keima min hi!
Puanpak silh vantung mi ten la sa hi,
Mimawh khat hong tung ci
Vantung gam sungah min thak khat kigelh hi,
Kei min hi, keima min hi!
Ka mawhna mai zo a, vantung lam ka zuan ta!
Nuam hithiat zen si!

verse1:
Ni taang sung' lampai, nuntak khualzinna,
Mual tung leh kuam thuk, lam dung teng ah,
Hong nusia lo ding, Zeisu’n hong ciam zo,
Pasian’ kamciam hi, ciampeel ngeilo.
verse2:
Ka kiim, ka paam ah, khuamial a tam hang,
Hong liah zo ngeilo, ka Honpa vaang:
Amah khuavak hi, khuamial in zo lo,
Mun dang pai thei keng, Ama’ kiang lo.
verse3:
Nitaang khuavak sung, ka paisuak ding hi,
Lung damna tawh inn, ka tung ding hi:
Amah phatna la sa in ka pai hi,
Itna khuavak sung’ lam ka pai hi.
chorus:
Vantung khuavak aw, Pasian' khuavak aw,
Na minthan’na tawh Nong tuam ta maw!
Halleluijah! Lungdam, kipaak in,
Zeisu kei-a ci’n la sasa ning.

verse1:
Leitung nopna sung, bual kik nawn lo ding, khentat khin zo ta ing,
A sangzaw nate’n a pha zaw nate'n,
Ka mit hong la zaw hi.
Manlang', zuan ning Amah, kipak leh suakta in,
Kipak suakta takin
Zeisu, lian pen, sangpen, Nang kong zui ding hi
verse2:
Mawhnate nusia’n Honpa' kiang pai ding, khentat khin zo ta ing,
Amah thumaan pen, Amah thutang pen, Nunna kammal zong hi.
Manlang', zuan ning Amah, kipak leh suakta in,
Kipak suakta takin
Zeisu, lian pen, sangpen, Nang kong zui ding hi
verse3:
Citak in nisim, Honpa' nung zui ding, khentat khin zo ta ing,
A gen bang mang ding, A deih bang sem ding,
Nuntakna lampi hi.
Manlang', manlang’ zuan ning Amah, kipak leh suakta in,
Kipak, suakta takin,
Zeisu, Zeisu, lian pen, sangpen, Nang kong zui ding hi.
verse4:
Mawhna zawi nusia’n, Kumpi gam lut ding, khentat khin zo ta ing,
Lawmte’n langdo zong, galte’n hong neh zong,
Ka lut veve ding hi.
Manlang', Manlang’ zuan ning Amah, kipak leh suakta in,
Kipak, suakta takin,
Zeisu, Zeisu, lian pen, sangpen, Nang kong zui ding hi.

crossrefs: Eliza E. Hewitt, William J. Kirkpatric
verse1:
Hahkatin zui ding Honpa khekhapte ah,
Hahkatin zui ni hong hon Kumpipa;
Amah et-teh in i nunna siampha ni,
Lungdam, kipak in, langaihte sak ni.
verse2:
Lampial ding zeh-etna i tuak ciangin ah,
Hong makaih Pa naih zawk ding hanciam ni;
Hong dal zo ding a thahat khut i muang hi,
Lungdam, kipak in, nisim in phat ni.
verse3:
Cihtakna, hehpihna leh itna zui in,
Thuakzawhna tawh dam takin mainawt ni;
Man ngen lo hehpihna kamciam mitsuan ni,
Lungdam, kipak in, tunglam zinna ah.
verse4:
Hahkatin zui ding Honpa khekhapte ah,
A suk a to ah zui ni hongpi pa;
A hoihna tawh Kumpipa mai i mu ding,
Lungdam, kipak in, Ama' kiang om ding.
chorus:
Aw, bangzah in etlawm, Honpa kalsuanna zuihna,
Khuavak sung paina, khuavak sung tun'na;
Aw, bangzah in etlawm, Honpa' nung zui-a paina,
Khuavak sung tun'na.

Lamdang Zeisu’ hong hehpihna teh theih ding om lo hi
Tuipi lian sangin zong thuk zaw hi; zong thuk zaw hi.
A lamdang hi mawhnei kei ading hehpihna kicing,
Ka mawhhuamna sangin zong zai zaw hi
Mawhna zumna sangin lian zaw hi
O liansak ni a manpha pen Zeisu min, phat ciat ni!

verse1:
Pasian in a geelna khel ngeilo hi,
Ama aa nasem mite hong telsit a,
Topa tung lungdam ko in hong ze-et ciang,
Khuamial sung la hong sa sak ding.
verse2:
Kamai nilimte hang khua muthei keng,
Tuama ka Honpa singlamteh ka en a,
Topa deihna ah ka kiap khit ciangin,
Khitui kangin nopna ngah ingh.
verse3:
Van pan hong pai ze-etna thu thei tangh
Pasian in a tate hong thakhauh sak hi,
Ka pa theisiam in Amah ka muang ta hi,
Ka gah hong tam sak semsem hi.
chorus:
Topa sung lungdam un, Leitung bei ni ciang Aman,
Hong thei in hong telkhial lo ding hi,
Gimna ka thuak ciang hong siang sak den,
Kham bang hong siang sak hi.

verse1:
Innkuan nuam in hauhna liatna hi kei
Kitawng kawmkawm a sameh limpen nek sang,
Zawng thilthial hang ki-it diamdiam aa,
Anteh meh nek hoih zaw thamlai hi.
verse2:
Nu le pa ten tate a neulai in
Pasian' thu mah tawh pantah in thuhilh un,
Taten' zong nu leh pa zahtak in thu mang un,
Na nahlawh pekin na daupai ding.
verse3:
Mo ten' tekte pianna nu leh pa bang
Ngaihsun in itna kam tawh ho tawntung un,
Tek ten' zong na mote, na sunga piang bangin,
It un la simmawh bawlsia kei un.
chorus:
Zeisu tawh innkuan teng leng bangkim itna tawh dimin
Kitawt kisel kiphunsan nate om lo in
Lungzinna meipi thengin nopna nitang silsial dinga
Bangkua hoih pen innkuan nuam pen na suak ding hi.

verse1:
Ka nuntak tawntung tuivot cim,
Khat lunggulh in zong den ingh.
Ka lungsung a ka dangtakna 
A phasak ding lamen ingh.
verse2:
Ka thaneih teng a bei phial dong,
Ka kiim ka pam teng mai ingh;
A hoih zaw khat lunggulh den in
Nop tuamna ngahthei tuan keng.
verse3:
Ka zawn luat man hauhna zong ingh,
Hong lungkim sak thei dingin,
Ka lawhsa-te leivui bang hi
Lungkimna hong pia zo kei.
verse4:
Tawntung phul den nuntak tuinak,
Hinna anlum khawnkhong cing,
A bei ngeilo hauhna kicing,
Hong Tanpa in kei-a hi.
chorus:
Hallejah! Ken mu khin ingh,
Ka zon den ka lunggulh pen,
Zeisu’n ka lunggulhna cing sak,
A sisan hang suakta ingh.

zoTitle: Zeisu Hong Pai Kik Ding Hi
verse1:
A lamdang thu kong puak hi,
Min thanna la kong sa hi,
A lamdang kumpi thu hi,
Zeisu hong pai kik ding hi.
verse2:
Singkung lopate kiko,
Mual leh guamte zong kiko,
Vantung leh leitung zong so,
Zeisu hong pai kik ding hi.
verse3:
Ama mai-ah ih ding ding,
Haksatna teng bei siang ding,
Amai ah lukhu nga ding,
Zeisu hong pai kik ding hi.
chorus:
Hong pai kik ding, Hong pai kik ding
Zingsang hi thei, sun hi thei,
Nitak hi thei, nai mahmah ding.
Hong pai kik ding, Hong pai kik ding,
Oh, Tuani ding lawphuai zen sin cia maw!
Zeisu hong pai kik ding hi.

zoTitle: Na Khempeuh Pasian Hehpihna Hang In
engTitle: All Because of God’s Amazing Grace
verse1:
Hong hehpihna lamdang zen si,
Hehpih huai mawhnei hong hon khia!
Ka manthan hangin tun hong kimu zo,
Mittaw tu in khua ka mu thei ta!
verse2:
Lungkiatna lauhuai nate panin,
Haksat dahna pan ka suakta!
Pasian hehpihna in bittak hong kem,
Hong hehpihna’n inn hong tun ding ta!
verse3:
Tatkhiat sate tawh tokhom kiim ah,
Honpa Kumpipa i phat ding!
Hong hehpihna mah i sutsut lai ding,
Khang tawntung hih mah la’n i sa ding!
chorus:
Tua in lamdang Pasian hehpihna hang hi!
Calvary mual tungah kei tang ding si hi.
Minthan ni zingsang khat ciangin
A maitang ken ka mu ding
Lamdang Pasian hehpihna hang hi.

Ka sungah nungta kei Nang' sungah,
Tawntung om khawm dingin kong thum hi.
Kiteh lo na vanglian hong pia in,
Nang tung pan mi tungah vangliatna.

zoTitle: Zan Cih Om Ngei Lo Hi
crossrefs: Mangmuhna 21:25; 22:5, John R. Clements (1868-), S.S. 1012, H.P. Danles (1903)
verse1:
Kiu li nei khuapi om a,
Ni tum ngei lohna hi;
Cikmah ciang sia lo ding a,
Zan cih om ngeilo hi.
verse2:
Kiu li nei khuapi om a,
A kongpi kep a hi;
A kong zingte kham hi a,
Zan cih om ngeilo hi.
verse4:
Tua kui li nei khua sungah,
Nitang kisam lo hi;
Tuuno ni bang tanna ah,
Zan cih om ngeilo hi.
chorus:
Pasian in khitui nul a,
Sihna natna om lo hi;
Hun le kum cih om lo a,
Zan cih om ngeilo hi.

engTitle: The Coming King Is at the Door
verse1:
Kumpipa kong kiangah om hi,
Mawhneite’ tang sihna thuak mi;
Mi siangthote bek mah tu in,
Kaikhawm ding hong pai hi.
verse2:
Hong pai ding naina lak limte,
Kum simin kicing mengmeng hi;
Vantung zingsang khuavak tawntung,
Sawt lo i mu ding hi.
verse3:
Kidona, gimna veng lo ding,
Leitung ah nopna zong kei in;
Honpa hong paikik ni ciangin,
Mawhna, sihna bei ding.
verse4:
Van le lei thak i tun ciangin,
A tawntungin i teng ding hi;
Sihna om nawn lo nuntakna,
A tawntung hun zang ding.
chorus:
Kong biangah, kong biangah
Kong biangah, hi, kong biang hong tung zo;
Hong pai ta hi, hong pai ta hi
Kong biang nangawn hong tung zo.

zoTitle: E’n A Hun Lian Thei Lo
verse1:
Topa hong pai ding a-hun lian kua mah’n thei lo,
Tua hun hong nai hi, ci-in lim ten hong lak zo;
Hong pai kik ding hi cih kamciamna thupha kho
E’n a hun lian thei lo
verse2:
Hotkhiatna a zong mipil tading khuavak hi,
Topa thu hilhna Lai Siangtho sungah om hi;
Hong hilhna thu in hun bei nading hong lak hi
E’n a hun lian thei lo
verse3:
Meivak tang sakin thungen kawmin i ngak ding,
Topa hong pai dong, ngak khawm-in na i sem ding;
Na lamdang pian sim hong naina thu phawk sem ding,
E’n a hun lian thei lo
chorus:
Hong pai ding kiging sa in om ciat ni,
Hong pai ding Hallelujah! Hallelujah!
Pasian vangliatna tawh
Mei-tung tuang in hong pai ding,
E’n a hun lian thei lo.

crossrefs: Late: 107:2, Fanny Jane Crosby (1820-1915), Translated by Rev. Hau Go Ham (1954-), R.H. 369, William J. Kirkpatrick (1838-1921)
verse1:
Tatkhiatna thu ka tangko nuam hi,
Tuuno si tawh hong tatkhiatna;
A bei thei lo hong hehpihna hi,
Pasian ta cihna ka ngahna.
verse2:
Zeisu in keimah hong tatkhiatna,
Kam a gen zawh ding hilo hi;
Ama khuavak sungah ka om ta,
Amah tawh ka tengkhawm den ding.
verse3:
Ka lungsung om hong Tanpa itna,
Sun niloh in hong phawng den hi;
Ke’n sasa nuam ing, Amah phatna,
Tua la mah ka sasa nuam hi.
verse4:
Ka thei hi a hoihna ka mu ding,
Amah ka Kumpi hong hi ta;
Amah in kei hong kem tawntung ding,
Hong pia de’n, Amah phatna la.
verse5:
Ka thei hi kham lukhu ka ngah ding,
Hong bawlkholh sak mun ka tun ciang;
Ama mel bangin ka kicing ding,
Amah tawh ka tenkhop hun ciang.
chorus:
Tatkhiat, Tatkhiat
Tuuno sisan tawh tatkhiat sa;
Tatkhiat, Tatkhiat
Pasian' ta cihna ka ngah ta.

crossrefs: Thlk. 11:12, Word Arr: Rev. Tuan Khan Mung (1960-), Tune: G. Biak Nawl
verse1:
Tuan-a pupa lamtual saina,
Khawhlo phungpha tonkhuang saina,
Lungdeih sinthu khaubang sutna,
Phuhbang kho hen, Pianna Zogam
verse2:
Tuan pupa’ ma bang i zopna,
Siamsil minlian tuang i tutna;
Tongdam siktui zu bang khumna,
Kil bang khang hen, Pianna Zogam
verse3:
Aw Zogam nuam huihdam semna,
Milun za ta lai tual len-na;
Lungtuak momno ngabang lenna,
lawibang thang hen, Pianna Zogam
chorus:
Sianmang lumsun, Lungtuak vontawi,
Sian sinthu tawh mawngbang kikawi;
Nunnuam kisung, Lungtuak zai-awi,
Sian in siam hen, Pianna Zogam

verse1:
Beh le phung, pawlpi, ngeina, pau kilamdang zong,
Tun sung khat pan piang laizom sanggamte hi hang,
Zogam kicin-na, Zomite zawhna,
Zeisu in Topa ci’n phat un
verse2:
Thungen in nasem hanciam Zogam tate aw,
Zomite i belh i suan in Pasian bek hi,
Zogam kicin-na, Zomite zawhna,
Zeisu in Topa ci'n phat un
chorus:
Zogam, Zomi, Zogam ei hong pia,
Pa Pasian thang hen!
Zogam, Zomi, Zogam ei hong pia,
Pa Pasian thang hen!/n/nZogam aading Pasian, Zomi aading Pasian,
Lungsim khutte lamto in Pasian lian sak un
